(118, 2, 111, 'Nnan: "ur ikeççem Loennet, siwa win illan d uday, ne$ d amasiêi". D wagi ay d asirem nnsen. Ini: "awit ed atebbet nnwen, ma tessawalem tidep".'),
(119, 2, 112, 'Xaîi, win iunzen i Öebbi, u d aâôvi, ad isâu arraz is, ar Mass is. Ur ppagwaden, ur $weblen.'),
