(133, 2, 126, 'Mi inna Ibôahim: "a Mass iw! Err wagi d tamdint n laman, £it imezda$ is s ppemôat; wid, segsen, iumnen s Öebbi akked wass aneggaru". Inna: "win ijehlen, a t Ooe$ ad izhu cwiî, sinna, a t Nehôe$ ar uâaqeb n tmes. A tu$alin tucmip"!'),
