(135, 2, 128, 'A Mass nne$! Err ane$ d imvuâen iK, u, si dderya nne$, lois ar aK ianzen. Mel a$ isekkiren nne$, Ssuref a$. Keçç, s tidep, Tessurufev, Tepêunuv.'),
