(201, 2, 194, 'Aggur iôqan s waggur iôqan. Tiririt n ppaô $ef wayen ippugedlen. Win ikwen id ibbwven, awvet ep, akken ikwen id ibbwev. Ëezzbet i Öebbi. Cfut ar Öebbi ar wid ipêezziben.'),
