(721, 5, 52, 'A pwaliv imuvan n wul, ppazzalen $uôsen, qqaôen asen: "nugad ay d itezzin fella$". Ahat a d Ias Öebbi s l$elb, ne$ s lameô s$uôeS. A d gwrin di nndama, $ef wayen ffren deg iman nnsen.'),
(722, 5, 53, 'A d inin wid iumnen: "day d wigi i iggullen s Öebbi, tagallit meqqwôen, ar nitni llan yidwen"? Mêan igiten nnsen, gwran d d imexsuôen.'),
