(756, 5, 87, 'A wid iumnen! Ur pgeddilet ayen imaânen i wen Iêell Öebbi. Ur zegret tilas. Öebbi, s tidep, ur Iêemmel ara wid izegren tilas.'),
(757, 5, 88, 'Eççet seg wayen ikwen Iôéeq Öebbi, iêellen, imaânen. Ëezzbet i Öebbi. YiS, kunwi, ay tumnem.'),
(758, 5, 89, 'Ur kwen Ipqassa Öebbi $ef tgallit n tkerkas. Maca, a kwen Iqiss $ef tgallit n ûûeê. Takweffaôt is: a ppecceççem mraw ime$ban, akken tecceççam tawacult nnwen, ne$ a ten tesselsem, ne$ a pserêem i wakli. Win ur nwâa ara, ad iuéum krav wussan. D tagi ay d takweffaôt n tgallit nnwen, ma teggullem. Eîîfet di tgallit nnwen. Akka i wen d Ipbeggin Öebbi issekniyen, amar a ppesnemmrem.'),
(759, 5, 90, 'A wid iumnen! Ccôab, leqwmeô, tiâancuôin, taseqqaôt, d ayen kan icemten, seg igi n Cciîan. Ihi, veôôeft asen, amar a prebêem.'),
(760, 5, 91, 'Ib$a kan Cciîan ad isker ticenga akked dd$el garawen, s ccôab akked leqwmeô, a kwen iveôôef seg usmekti n Öebbi, akked téallit. Day ur tepfukkum ara?'),
(761, 5, 92, 'A$et awal i Öebbi, a$et awal i Umazan. £uôwat! Ma twexxôem, cfut ar Amazan, iwata yas kan anabi ipbegginen.'),
(762, 5, 93, 'Ur telli tiyta deg wid iumnen, u xeddmen ayen ilhan, $ef wayen ççan, ma êezzben, umnen, xedmen ayen ilhan, sinna êezzben, umnen, sinna, êezzben u maânen. Öebbi Iêemmel lâuûam.'),
(763, 5, 94, 'A wid iumnen! War ccekk, a kwen Iweddeb Öebbi $ef wayen tepûeggidem s ifassen nnwen, u s ixtucen nnwen, iwakken ad Iéeô Öebbi anwa i T ippagwaden, di tbavnit. Win izegren tilas, deffir waya, fellas aâaqeb aqeôêan.'),
(764, 5, 95, 'A wid iumnen! Ur pûeggidet di zzyaôa nnwen. Win iûeggden segwen, u iâammed, aqeîîi: ad iseddeq, si lmal is, ayen in$a s ûûyada s, a d êudden, f waya, sin irgazen iêesbiyen segwen. D tikci ara iawven ar Lkaâba. Ne$ takweffaôt: ad icceçç ime$ban, ne$, ayen iswan aya, ad iuéum. Ad ijeôôeb vveôô n lameô is. Öebbi Isemmeê i wayen iâaddan. Win iu$alen a d Irr Öebbi segs ppaô. Öebbi d Uzmir, Ippara d ppaô.'),
(765, 5, 96, 'Têell awen ûûyada n yill akked uççi s. D lqut i kunwi akw iminigen. Tepwagdel awen ûûyada di tmurt, skud aql akwen d zziyyaô. Ëezzbet i Öebbi, $uôeS ara tepwafesrem.'),
(766, 5, 97, 'Irra Öebbi Lkaâba d axxam iôqan ipwabnan i l$aci, aggur iôqan, asfel, isenoaq, ayagi iwakken a ppeéôem ar Öebbi Iéôa i illan deg igenwan u di tmurt, u Öebbi Issen yal cci.'),
(767, 5, 98, 'Cfut iwâaô uâaqeb n Öebbi. Öebbi, s tidep, Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu.'),
(768, 5, 99, 'Amazan, iwata yas kan unabi. Öebbi Iéôa ayen temmalem u ayen teppeffrem.'),
(769, 5, 100, 'Ini: "ur iaâdil ara wayen n dir akked wayen imaânen", xas teswehm ik lkwetôa n wayen n dir. Ëezzbet i Öebbi, a yuâqilen, amar a prebêem.'),
(770, 5, 101, 'A wid iumnen! Ur steqsayet $ef t$awsiwin ara kwen icwe$ben, ma mlan awen tent. Ma testeqsam fellasent mara d iprusu Leqwôan, ad awen ppufessrent. Öebbi Isemmeê aya. Öebbi Ipsemmiê, Iêellem.'),
(771, 5, 102, 'Ni$ isteqsa fellasent ugdud, uqbel nnwen. Sinna, segsent, gwran d d ijehliyen.'),
(772, 5, 103, 'Ur d Ifki Öebbi Baêiôa, ne$ Sayba, ne$ Waûila, ne$ Ëami. Maca, wid ijehlen gren d tikerkas $ef Öebbi. Tegwti degsen ur fhimen.'),
(773, 5, 104, 'Ma nnan asen: "yyaw ar wayen id Issers Öebbi, u ar Umazan". Qqaôen: "beôka ya$ ayen id nufa, $ef waya, $eô imezwura nne$". I ma imezwura nnsen ur ssinen acemma, ur pwanhan?'),
(774, 5, 105, 'A wid iumnen! Fellawen iman nnwen. Ur kwen iîîuôôu win innetlafen, ma tepwanham. Ar Öebbi, tu$alin nnwen akw. A kwen Ixebbeô $ef wayen txeddmem.'),
(775, 5, 106, 'A wid iumnen! Ccada garawen, ma tusa d tmeppant ar yiwen segwen. Di lawan uweûûi, sin irgazen iêesbiyen, segwen, ne$ wiyav war segwen, ma tellam d iminigen di tmurt, u tusa kwen id twa$it n tmeppant. A ten qesden deffir téallit. Ma tcukkem, sgallet pen s Öebbi: "ur d nesfayday syis, xas iaâna llzem nne$, ur nteffer ccada n Öebbi, mulac, nekwni a nili seg imednab".'),
(776, 5, 107, 'Ma ivehô ed fellasen denben, ad ppuneûfen s wiyav, si loiha n wid vuôôen imezwura. Ad ggalen s Öebbi: "ih, ccada nne$ tif ccada nnsen. Ur nzegger tilas, mulac, war ccekk, a nili seg imednas".'),
(777, 5, 108, 'Ppif akka iwakken a d awin ccada iwulmen, ad agwaden a ppili tgallit deffir tgallit nnsen. Ëezzbet i Öebbi, ssemêesset, Öebbi ur Inehhu agdud iballa$en.'),
(778, 5, 109, 'Ass ideg ara Issemlil Öebbi imazanen, ad Yini: "acu i wen d jawben"? Ad inin: "ur telli tussna $uône$. D Keçç, s tidep, i Issnen tibavniyin".'),
(779, 5, 110, 'Mi Inna Öebbi: "a Âisa, mmi s n Meryem! Mmekti d i kwen £$ate$, keçç akked imma k, mi k Âiwne$ s ôôuê iôqan. Tepmmeslayev i medden si dduê, am unqaqôi. Mi k Slemde$ Tazmamt, ûûwab, Tuôa, Linoil. Mi tûenâav, si talaxt, ûûifa n ufrux, s– tsriê iW; tûuvev degs, tu$al d afôux, s– tsriê iW. Tesseêlayev agugam, amuvin n lberû, s– tsriê iW. Mi tessenkarev lmeggtin, s– tsriê iW. Mi Sbaâde$ fellak At Isôail, mi d tusiv $uôsen, s ubeggen, u nnan wid ijehlen segsen: "ayagi iban d ssêur kan".'),
(780, 5, 111, 'Mi Weêêa$ i inmahalen: "amnet yissI, akw s umazan iW". Nnan: "numen. Echhed ar nekwni d imvuâen".'),
(781, 5, 112, 'Mi nnan inmahalen: "a Âisa, mmi s n Meryem! Ma Izmer Mass ik ad a$ d Issers lmaida seg igenni"? Inna: "êezzbet i Öebbi, ma d lmumnin ay tellam".'),
(782, 5, 113, 'Nnan: "neb$a a neçç segs, a nevmen ulawen nne$, a néeô ar tenniv a$ d tidep, a nili d inagan iS".'),
(783, 5, 114, 'Inna Âisa, mmi s n Meryem: "a Öebbi, Mass nne$, Ssers a$ d lmaida, seg igenni, ad a$ tili d lâid i umezwaru u i uneggaru nne$, u d assekni s $uôeK. £it a$ d. Keçç, Tifev akw im$iten".'),
(784, 5, 115, 'Inna Öebbi: "ad awen p id Sserse$. Win ijehlen segwen, deffir waya, a t Âaqbe$ aâaqeb ur Sâadda$ i yiwen deg imavalen".'),
(785, 5, 116, 'Mi Inna Öebbi: "a Âisa, mmi s n Meryem! D keçç i innan i l$aci: erret a$, nek akked imma, d sin iôebbiten war Öebbi"? Inna: "gedha s yiseK! Ur iyi ippunefk ara a d ini$ ayen i$ef ur sâi$ lêeqq. Lemmer i t id nni$, yili Teéôiv t. Tesnev i illan deg iman iw, ur ssine$ ayen illan deg iman iK. Keçç, s tidep, d Amusnaw n tbavniyin.'),
(786, 5, 117, 'I asen nni$, siwa ayen iyi d Tumôev: âabdet Öebbi, Mass iw, u Mass nnwen. Lli$ d anagi nnsen, skud lli$ garasen. Mi iyi n Tessuliv $uôeK, d Keçç i ten id Iquôâan. Keçç, d Anagi n yal cci.'),
(787, 5, 118, 'Ma Tâaqbev ten, ni$ d imdanen iK, ma Tsemmêev asen, Keçç, s tidep, d Uzmir, d Bab n ûûwab".'),
(788, 5, 119, 'Inna Öebbi: "wagi d ass ideg ara stenfâan imawlan n tidep, si tidep nnsen. I nitni leonanat, ddawat sen isaffen ppazzalen, ad wekkôen degsen, i lebda". Iôuva ten Öebbi, u ôuvan T, d wagi ay d rrbeê ameqwôaêan.'),
(789, 5, 120, 'N Öebbi tagelda n tmurt akked igenwan, akked wayen illan degsen. Neppa Izmer i yal cci.');
INSERT INTO `ber_mensur` (`index`, `sura`, `aya`, `text`) VALUES
(790, 6, 1, 'A neckeô Öebbi i Ixelqen tamurt akked igenwan. Irra tillas, tafat. Sinna, wid ijehlen pparan tanudda i Mass nnsen.'),
(791, 6, 2, 'Neppa, ikwen Ixelqen s talaxt, sinna, Iseyya lajel. £uôeS lajel ipwassnen. Deffir waya, kunwi la tepcukkum.'),
(792, 6, 3, 'Neppa, d Öebbi deg igenwan, di tmurt. Issen sser nnwen, d wayen d teqqaôem. Iéôa ayen tkesbem.'),
(793, 6, 4, 'Ur ten id ippas ussekni seg issekniyen n Mass nnsen, mebla ma ugin t.'),
(794, 6, 5, 'Ni$ skaddben tidep, mi ten id tusa. A ten id ias usali n wayen i$ef ttihin.'),
(795, 6, 6, 'Day ur walan ara acêal isuta, uqbel nnsen, ay Nekkes. Nesserked iten di tmurt akken ur kwen Nesserked. Nuzen asen aîas ugeffur, Nerra yasen isaffen, ppazzalen seddawat sen. Nesnegr iten ilmend ibekkaven nnsen. Nxelq ed, deffir sen, sself nniven.'),
(796, 6, 7, 'Xas ad ak ed Nessers Tazmamt, di lka$ev, ara nnalen s ifassen nnsen, war ccekk, a d inin wid ijehlen: "wagi, s tidep, siwa ssêur n ûûeê".'),
(797, 6, 8, 'Qqaôen: "a lemmer id irs $uôes lmelk". Lemmer a n Nessers lmelk, war ccekk, ad iûaô lameô, sinna, ur pganin.'),
(798, 6, 9, 'Lemmer i t Nerri d lmelk, yili Nerra t d argaz, ad as Nessels ayen plusun.'),
(799, 6, 10, 'Ni$ mmaâlken $ef imazanen, uqbel ik. Ayen i$ef ttihin, izzi i wid, segsen, immaâlken.'),
(800, 6, 11, 'Ini: "ddut di tmurt, sinna walit amek tevôa d wid iskiddiben".'),
(801, 6, 12, 'Ini: "w i t ilan wayen akw illan di tmurt akked igenwan"? Ini: "d Öebbi". Iura, deg iman iS, aêunu. A kwen Issemlil i wass n tnekra, ur ccekk fellas. Wid isxesôen iman nnsen, ur ppamnen.'),
(802, 6, 13, 'IneS i ized$en deg iv, deg wass. Neppa Issel, d Amusnaw.'),
(803, 6, 14, 'Ini: "day ara sâu$ bab, war Öebbi, Axellaq n tmurt akked igenwan? Neppa Icceççay ur t cceççayen". Ini: "nek pwamôe$ d ad ili$ d amenzu ara ianzen. Ur ppilit seg imcurak".'),
(804, 6, 15, 'Ini: "nek ugade$, ma aâûa$ Mass iw, aâaqeb n wass ameqwôaêan".'),
(805, 6, 16, 'Win imenâan segs, assen, ni$ Iêun fellas. Wagi d rrebê n ûûeê.'),
(806, 6, 17, 'Ma Isâadda Öebbi fellak cedda, ur p itekkes yiwen, siwa Neppa. Ma Isrebê ik, Neppa Izmer i yal cci.'),
(807, 6, 18, 'D Neppa ay d Aqehhaô, sennig imdanen iS; d Neppa ay d Bab n ûûwab, i Iéôan.'),
(808, 6, 19, 'Ini: "anda p ccada sennig akw tiyav"? Ini: "Öebbi d Anagi gari yidwen. Iweêêa yi d Leqwôan agi, iwakken a kwen nabi$ yis, kunwi akked wid u$uô ibbwev. Day, kunwi, war ccekk, a pcehhdem ar, ar tama n Öebbi, llan iôebbiten nniven"? Ini: "ur cehhde$"! Ini: "Neppa d Öebbi, siwa Yiwen. Nek, rri$ akin ayen tepcarakem".'),
(809, 6, 20, 'Wid iwumi Nefka Tazmamt, ssnen p, akken ssnen arraw nnsen. Wid isxesôen iman nnsen, ihi, ur ppamnen.'),
(810, 6, 21, 'Anwa idensen sennig win d igren tikerkas $ef Öebbi, ne$ iskaddben issekniyen iS? Ih, ur rebêen imednas.'),
(811, 6, 22, 'Ass ideg ara ten Nefser meôôa, sinna a Nini i wid icurken: "anda ten icriken nnwen, i la tâabdem"?'),
(812, 6, 23, 'Deg uhewwel nnsen, siwa ma nnan d: "s Öebbi, Mass nne$, ur nelli d imcurak"!'),
(813, 6, 24, 'Wali amek skaddben $ef yiman nnsen. Itelf iten wayen la d snulfuyen.'),
(814, 6, 25, 'Garasen wid i k issemêasen. Nerra aêurrim $ef ulawen nnsen, iwakken ur t fehmen. Tiâééegt deg imeééu$en nnsen. Ma walan yal assekni, ur ppamnen yis. Alamma, ma usan d $uôek, a k namren, ad ak inin wid ijehlen: ayagi siwa tiêkayin imezwura.'),
(815, 6, 26, 'Sîixxiôen segs, îîeôôifen segs. Ay squccun siwa iman nnsen, ur faqen.'),
(816, 6, 27, 'Lemmer a ten twaliv, mara bedden ar tmes, a d inin: a ssexv nne$! Awi $ irran, ur neskiddib issekniyen n Mass nne$! A nili si lmumnin.'),
(817, 6, 28, 'Xaîi! Iban asen d wayen teffren, zik. Lemmer a d kren, ad u$alen ar wayen i sen ipwagedlen. Nitni, s tidep, d ikeddaben.'),
(818, 6, 29, 'U qqaôen: "siwa tameddurt n ddunit i illan. Nekwni, ur fella$ tanekra".'),
(819, 6, 30, 'Lemmer a pwaliv mara bedden ar Mass nnsen, ad Yini: "ni$ ayagi s tidep"? A d inin: "ih, s Mass nne$"! Ad Yini: "ihi jeôôbet aâaqeb, ilmend n wayen tejhilem".'),
(820, 6, 31, 'Ni$ xesôen wid iskaddben timlilit akked öÖebbi. Alamma, ma iusa ten id yimir, deqzalla, a d inin: "a yamxix nne$, $ef wayen ideg nestehza"! Nitni ad bibben tiâakkwumin nnsen $ef izugar nnsen. I icmet wayen bubben!'),
(821, 6, 32, 'Tameddurt n ddunit d urar kan akked lhawiyya. Axxam aneggaru, war ccekk, yif ip i wid ipêezziben. Day ur tepmeyyizem ara?'),
(822, 6, 33, 'Ni$ Neéôa i$webben ik, s tidep, wayen qqaôen. Ihi, nitni ur k skiddiben. Maca imednas veggôen issekniyen n Öebbi.'),
(823, 6, 34, 'Ni$ skaddben imazanen uqbel ik. Üebôen $ef wayen i ten skaddben, akked wayen i ten meêênen, armi i ten id iusa usellek nne£. Ur illi ubeddel i wawalen n Öebbi. Ni$ usan k id, kra isallen imazanen.'),
(824, 6, 35, 'Ma ééay fellak uwexxeô nnsen, ma tzemôev a tessarmev aderbuz di tmurt, ne$ sellum s igenni, ad asen d tawiv assekni. Ma ihwa yaS i Öebbi, a ten Issemlil ar nnhaya. Ur ppili seg wid ur nessin.'),
(825, 6, 36, 'Siwa wid isellen, ara d ijawben. Lmegtin a ten id Issker Öebbi, sinna, $uôeS tu$alin nnsen.'),
(826, 6, 37, 'Qqaôen: "acimi ur as d irs ara ussekni s$uô Mass is"? Ini: "Öebbi, s tidep, Izmer a d Issers assekni", maca tegwti degsen ur éôin.'),
(827, 6, 38, 'Ur illi lweêc di tmurt, ne$ ufrux ippafgen s wafriwen is, ur nelli d leoyus am kunwi. Ur Nestehza, di Tezmamt, $ef wacemma. Sinna, ar Mass nnsen, ad pwafessren.'),
(828, 6, 39, 'Wid iskaddben issekniyen nne£, âaégen, gugmen, di tillas. Win i S ihwan i Öebbi, a t Itlef. Win i S ihwan, a t Iawi d ubrid uwqim.'),
(829, 6, 40, 'Ini: "twalam ma iusa kwen id uâaqeb n Öebbi, ne$ ma iusa kwen id yimir, day ar war Öebbi ara tnaâôem, ma tessawalem tidep?'),
(830, 6, 41, 'Xaîi! £uôeS ara tnujem. Ad Issiferr ayen i$ef tnujem $uôeS, ma ihwa yaS, a ppeppum ayen tcurkem".'),
(831, 6, 42, 'Ni$ Nuzen ed ar leoyus, uqbel ik. Nesâadda fellasen tilufa, ccqa, amar ad êiwten.'),
(832, 6, 43, 'A lemmer êawten, mi ten id tusa tiyta nne£. Maca, qehôen wulawen nnsen. Cciîan Icebbeê asen ayen xeddmen.'),
(833, 6, 44, 'Mi ppun ayen i sen d smmektin, Nelli yasen tibbura n yal cci, armi, mi feôêen s wayen i sen ippunefken, Newwet iten, deqzalla. D$a qevâen layas.'),
(834, 6, 45, 'Pwakksen wid id igwran seg ugdud idensen. Ccekôan i Öebbi, Mass imavalen.'),
(835, 6, 46, 'Ini: "twalam, ma Iddem awen Öebbi timesliwt nnwen, akked iéôi nnwen; ma Isle$ ulawen nnwen; anwa ôebbi, war Öebbi, ar awen ten id iawin"? Wali amek Nessefham issekniyen, u nitni, sinna, zzin akin.'),
(836, 6, 47, 'Ini: "acu twalam, ma iusa kwen id uâaqeb n Öebbi, deqzalla, ne$ âinani? Day ara Ine$, siwa agdud imednas"?'),
(837, 6, 48, 'Ur d Nuzen imazanen, siwa i ubecceô, d unabi. Wid iumnen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan, ur ppagwaden, ur $weblen.'),
(838, 6, 49, 'Wid iskaddben issekniyen nne£, a ten iêaz uâaqeb, ilmend n wayen be$wven.'),
(839, 6, 50, 'Ini: "ur awen qqare$ sâi$ igerrujen n Öebbi, ur ssine$ tabavnit; ur awen qqare$: nek, d lmelk. Nek, teddu$ kan akked wayen iyi d ippuweêêan". Ini: "day iaâdel uder$al d win ipwalin? Day ur d tepmeyyizem ara"?'),
(840, 6, 51, 'Nabi yis wid iugaden ad pwafessren ar Mass nnsen. Ur sâin bab, war Neppa, ne$ amcafaâ. Amar ad êezzben.'),
(841, 6, 52, 'Ur ppara wid ipnujun $uô Mass nnsen, taûebêit, tameddit, pnadin udem iS. Ur fellak a ten têasbev deg wacemma, ur fellasen a k êasben, deg wacemma. Ma terriv ten, ihi, a ppiliv seg imednas.'),
(842, 6, 53, 'Akka ay Nhewwel kra s wiyav, iwakken a d inin: "day d wigi i I$at Öebbi, garane$"? Day ur Issin ara Öebbi, sennig akw, wid isnemmiren?'),
(843, 6, 54, 'Ma usan k id wid iumnen s issekniyen nne£, ini: "tifrat fellawen"! Mass nnwen Iura, i iman iS, aêunu. Ihi, i win, segwen, ixedmen tucmip, ur iâammed, sin akin, isteôoaâ, u ixdem ayen ilhan, Neppa Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu.'),
(844, 6, 55, 'Akka ay Nfeûûel issekniyen, iwakken a d iban ubrid ibe$wviyen.'),
(845, 6, 56, 'Ini: "nek, ippugdel iyi ad âabde$ wid u$uô la tepnujum, war Öebbi". Ini: "ur teddu$ d lemcihwat nnwen, mulac ad nnetlafe$, ur ppili$ seg wid ipwanhan".'),
(846, 6, 57, 'Ini: "nek, îîfe$ deg ubeggen n Mass iw. Teskaddbem t. Ur illi $uôi wayen u$uô têarem. Ih, aêuddu $eô Öebbi kan. Issawal tidep. Neppa Yif akw wid issenqaden".'),
(847, 6, 58, 'Ini: "lemmer illi $uôi wayen u$uô têarem, yili iûaô lameô, gari yidwen". Öebbi Yif akw akken Issen imednas.'),
(848, 6, 59, '£uôeS tisura n tbavnit. Siwa Neppa itent Issnen. Iéôa i illan di lberr, di yill. Ur i$elli ifer siwa ma Iéôa t. Akken aâqqa di tillas n tmurt, tizzegzewt, ta$eôt, akw di tezmamt ipbegginen.'),
(849, 6, 60, 'D Neppa i wen ippaddamen leôwaê deg iv. Iéôa ay txeddmem, deg wass. Sinna, Ippara kwen id degs, iwakken ad ivôu lajel ipwassnen. Sinna, $uôeS tu$alin nnwen, sinna, a kwen Ixebbeô $ef wayen txeddmem.'),
(850, 6, 61, 'D Neppa ay d Aqehhaô sennig imdanen iS. Ippazen ed $uôwen imêaraben, alamma, ma tusa d tmeppant ar yiwen segwen, ad ddmen ôôuê is, imceggâen nne£. Nitni ur stehzayen.'),
(851, 6, 62, 'Sinna, ad u$alen ar Öebbi, Bab nnsen n tidep. Aêuddu, day maççi d ayla S? Neppa Yif akw akken Ip$awal ar uqeîîi.'),
(852, 6, 63, 'Ini: "anwa ara kwen Isellken si tillas n lberr d yill, u$uô tnujem s uêiwet akked tugwdi"? "Ma Isellek a$ si tagi, war ccekk, a nili seg wid isnemmiren".'),
(853, 6, 64, 'Ini: "Öebbi Isellek ikwen segs, akw si yal lhemm, sinna, kunwi la tepcarakem".'),
(854, 6, 65, 'Ini: "Neppa, Izmer ad awen d Iazen aâaqeb sennig wen, ne$ seddaw ivaôen nnwen. Ne$ a kwen Issemfaôaq, kra segwen ad jeôôben leqheô n wiyav". Wali amek id Nemmal issekniyen, amar ad meêûen.'),
(855, 6, 66, 'Iskaddeb it ugdud ik, u neppa d tidep. Ini: "ur awen lli$ d awkil.'),
(856, 6, 67, 'Yal asali s lweqt is. A ppu$alem a ppeéôem".'),
(857, 6, 68, 'Ma twalav wid ipnamaren $ef issekniyen nne£, eoo iten, alamma bedlen anamer. Ma iseppu k Cciîan, mi d temmektiv, ur p$imi d ugdud imednas.'),
(858, 6, 69, 'Ur isefk ara i wid ipêezziben, a ten êasben deg wacemma. Maca d asmekti, amar ad êezzben.'),
