(883, 6, 94, 'Ni$ tusam a£ d, d ifôiden, akken ikwen Nexleq abrid amezwaru. Teooam deffir wen, ayen i wen Nefka. Ur Nwala, $uôwen, imcafâen nnwen, wid i tâabdem, nitni, d icriken nnwen. Ni$ temfaôaqem, u ooan kwen wid la tâabdem.'),
(884, 6, 95, 'Öebbi, s tidep, Ifeôôec aâqqa, i$es. Issuffu$ ed amuddir si lmegget. Issuffu$ ed lmegget seg umuddir. Akka ay d Öebbi. Acimi tugim?'),
