(886, 6, 97, 'D Neppa i wen Irran itran, ad awen mlen abrid, di tillas n lberr akked yill. Ni$ Nemmal issekniyen i ugdud issnen.'),
(887, 6, 98, 'D Neppa ikwen id Ixelqen si yiman afôid, sinna: amkan, tarusi. Ni$ Nemmal issekniyen i ugdud ifehhmen.'),
(888, 6, 99, 'D Neppa id Isrusun aman seg igenni. Nessuffu$ ed yissen yal im$an. Nessuffu$ ed yissen tizzegzewt. Nessuffu$ ed yissen iâaqqayen mbabben, iguza n ppmeô id ipûubbun si tezdayin, leonanat n tfeôôant, uzemmur, n ôemman, ppemcabin ne$ ur ppemcabin. Walit ppemôa nnsen mi d teffe$ tebbwa. Ih, deg waya, war ccekk, issekniyen i ugdud iumnen.'),
(889, 6, 100, 'Rran i Öebbi, leonun d icriken, u Ixelq iten. Snulfan aS d arrac, tullas, ur éôin. Gedha s yiS! Ay Aâlay sennig wayen d qqaôen!'),
(890, 6, 101, 'Axellaq n tmurt akked igenwan, amek ara Isâu mmi S, ur Isâi tameddakwelt? U Ixleq yal cci, u Neppa, yal cci, Issen it.'),
