(922, 6, 133, 'Mass ik d Asâay, d Bab uêunu. Ma ihwa yaS a kwen Ikkes, a d Inûef, deffir wen, ayen i S ihwan, akken ikwen id Ixleq si tarwa n ugdud nniven.'),
