(936, 6, 147, 'Ma skaddben k, ini: "Mass nnwen d Bab uêunu iwsâan, ur ipwexxiô ssexv iS, af ugdud ibe$wviyen".'),
(937, 6, 148, 'Ad inin imcurak: "lemmer i S ihwi i Öebbi, nekwni akked imezwura nne$, ur ncurek, ur negdel acemma". Akka ay skaddben imezwura nnsen, armi jeôôben ssexv nne£. Ini: "day tesâam tussna ar a$ d tesseknem? Teppeddum kan d nnwaya, kunwi tesnulfuyem d kan".'),
(938, 6, 149, 'Ini: "n Öebbi timenna tunûiêin. Lemmer i S ihwi, yili Inha kwen akw".'),
(939, 6, 150, 'Ini: "awit ed inagan nnwen, ara icehhden ar Öebbi Igdel ayagi". Ma cehhden, ur cehhed yidsen. Ur teddu d lhawiyya n wid iskaddben issekniyen nne£, akked wid ur numin s laxeôt, u pparan tanudda i Mass nnsen.'),
(940, 6, 151, 'Ini: "yyaw, ad ini$. I wen Igdel Mass nnwen: ur aS tepcarakem acemma; elhut ar imawlan nnwen; ur neqqet tarwa nnwen, di tigullelt - d Nekwni ara kwen Iôeéqen yidsen -, ur ppaéet ar lâaô, d uvhiô ne$ d uffir; ur neqqet amdan, d ayen Igdel Öebbi, siwa ma s lêeqq". Ar waya i kwen Iweûûa, amar a pfehmem.'),
(941, 6, 152, 'Ur pqeôôibet s ayla ugujil, siwa s wayen ilhan, alamma immeêtel. Weznet, ktilet s lewqama. Ur Nepkellif amdan siwa ar wayen iwumi izmer. Ma thedôem d, weznet, xas ma $eô llzem nnwen. Qadôet lemâahda n Öebbi. Iweûûa kwen $ef waya, amar a d temmektim.'),
(942, 6, 153, 'D wagi ay d abrid iW uwqim, ddut degs. Ur teddut d iberdan ara kwen isîixôen seg ubrid iS. Iweûûa kwen $ef waya, amar a pêezzbem.'),
(943, 6, 154, 'Sinna, Nefka Tazmamt i Musa. Tewqem i wid imaânen, tfeûûel yal cci, d nnhaya u d aêunu. Amar ad amnen s timlilit n Mass nnsen.'),
(944, 6, 155, 'Tagi d Tazmamt, Nessers ip id, teôqa. Ihi, ddut yides, êezzbet, amar fellawen aêunu.'),
