(947, 6, 158, 'D acu pôaoun, siwa ma ten id asent lmalayek, ne$ a d Ias Mass ik, ne$ a d asen kra issekniyen n Mass ik? Ass ideg ara d asen kra issekniyen n Mass ik, ur infaâ umdan liman is, ma, iu$ lêal, ur iumin ara, ne$ ur iksib lxiô, di liman is. Ini: "gganit, nekwni, ih, la nepgani".'),
(948, 6, 159, 'Ih, wid ibvan ddin nnsen, u gan ikabaren, ur tepkkiv yidsen deg wacemma. Lameô nnsen ar Öebbi kan, sinna, a ten Ixebbeô $ef wayen xeddmen.'),
(949, 6, 160, 'Win id iusan s yise$, ines mraw i t icban; win id iusan s tucmip, ad ippuqeîîi s tin kan i p icban; nitni ur pwadensen.'),
