(952, 6, 163, 'Ur aS illi ucarek. Pwamôe$ d s waya: nek d amduâ amenzu".'),
(953, 6, 164, 'Ini: "day b$i$ mass, war Öebbi? U Neppa d Mass n yal cci". Ur ikesseb yal yiman, siwa mgal is. Ur ipbibbi win ibubben taâkkwemt n wayev. Sinna, ar Mass nnwen, tu$alin nnwen. Sinna, a kwen Ixebbeô $ef wayen tellam temgaradem.'),
(954, 6, 165, 'D Neppa i kwen Irran d igensas di tmurt. Irra, kra segwen, tiseddaôin sennig wiyav, iwakken a kwen Ijeôôeb $ef wayen i wen Ifka. Ih, Mass ik Ip$awal deg uâaqeb. Neppa, s tidep, Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu.');
INSERT INTO `ber_mensur` (`index`, `sura`, `aya`, `text`) VALUES
(955, 7, 1, 'Almû.'),
(956, 7, 2, 'Tazmamt ters ed $uôek, ur teppili segs lhejna deg idmaren ik, iwakken a pnabiv yis; u d asmekti i lmumnin.'),
(957, 7, 3, 'Ddut d wayen id irsen $uôwen, s$uô Mass nnwen. Ur teddut d imawlan, war Neppa. Drus id tesmektayem.'),
(958, 7, 4, 'Acêal n temdinin ay Nessenger. Tusa ten id tiyta nne£, deg ives nnsen, ne$ deg uqeggel nnsen.'),
(959, 7, 5, 'Ti$ôi nnsen, mi ten id tusa tiyta nne£, siwa mi d nnan: "ih, nella d imednas".'),
(960, 7, 6, 'War ccekk, a Nesteqsi wid u$uô id Nuzen, a Nesteqsi imazanen.'),
(961, 7, 7, 'War ccekk, ad asen Neêku, s tmusni, ur Nelli N$ab.'),
(962, 7, 8, 'Awzan, assen, d tidep. Wid iwumi ééayet lweznat nnsen, widak d wid irebêen.'),
(963, 7, 9, 'Wid iwumi fessuset lweznat nnsen, widak d wid ixesôen iman nnsen, seg akken sednasen issekniyen nne£.'),
(964, 7, 10, 'Ni$, s tidep, Nesrekd ikwen di tmurt, Nerra yawen, degs, tamâict nnwen. Drus ay tesnemmirem.'),
(965, 7, 11, 'Ni$, s tidep, Nxelq ikwen, sinna, Nmesl ikwen, sinna, Nenna i lmalayek: "knumt i Adem"! Knant, siwa Iblis. Ur illi seg wid iknan.'),
(966, 7, 12, 'Inna: "acu k iîîfen ur tekniv ara, mi k d Umôe$"? Inna d: "Nek, ife$ t. Txelqev iyi si tmes, Txelqev t si talaxt".'),
(967, 7, 13, 'Inna: "ihi, ûûub segs! Ur ak ippunefk ara a ppesme$wôev iman ik, degs. Effe$, keçç seg wid ixuûen"!'),
(968, 7, 14, 'Inna: "Eoo iyi, ar ass ideg ara d kkren".'),
(969, 7, 15, 'Inna: "keçç, ih, seg wid ara iqqimen".'),
(970, 7, 16, 'Inna d: "imi iyi Tâammdev a$ewwu, ad asen qqime$, war ccekk, deg ubrid iK uwqim.'),
(971, 7, 17, 'Sinna, ad asen d tekke$ zdat, deffir, yeffus, zelmev. Ur Teppafev, $eô tugwti segsen, asnemmer".'),
(972, 7, 18, 'Inna: "effe$ segs, d ameêquô ippuvegôen! War ccekk, ad Acaôe$ Loahennama s wid, segsen, i k ivefôen, akked yiswen akw.'),
(973, 7, 19, 'A Adem, ezde$ Loennet, keçç akked tmeîîut ik, eççet seg wayen i wen ihwan. Ur pqeôôibet ttejôa agi, mulac a ppilim seg imednas".'),
(974, 7, 20, 'I$ewwa ten Cciîan, iwakken ad asen d iban âaryan nnsen i illan iffer. Inna: "Ikkes awen, kan, Mass nnwen, ttejôa agi, iwakken ur teppilim d lmalayek, ne$ ur tepwekkiôem".'),
(975, 7, 21, 'Iggul asen: "nek, i kunwi, d unûiê".'),
(976, 7, 22, 'Isdull iten s u$uôôu. Mi âaôven si ttejôa nni, walan iman nnsen aâran. Lhan d la pcuddun, $ef iman nnsen, afriwen n Loennet. Issawel asen d Mass nnsen: "day ur awen Gdile$ ara ttejôa nni? Ad awen Ini$: war ccekk, Cciîan, i kunwi, d acengu n ûûeê".'),
(977, 7, 23, 'Nnan: "a Mass nne$! Nvuôô iman nne$. Ma ur a$ Tsemmêev, ur Têunev fella$, a nili seg imexsuôen".'),
(978, 7, 24, 'Inna: "erset! Kra d icenga n kra. A pzed$em di tmurt, a ppezhum, tallit kan".'),
(979, 7, 25, 'Irna: "degs a ppidirem, degs a ppemmtem, segs a d teff$em".'),
(980, 7, 26, 'A tarwa n Adem! Ni$ Nessers awen ed aceîîiv ara kwen issôen, ôôêuê, akked uceîîiv uêezzeb. Wagi yif iten". Ayagi seg issekniyen n Öebbi, amar a d mmektin.'),
(981, 7, 27, 'A tarwa n Adem! £uôwat a kwen ihewwel Cciîan, akken id issuffe$ imezwura nnwen si Loennet! Ikkes asen iceîîiven nnsen, iwakken ad asen issken âaryan nnsen. Neppa, war ccekk, ipwali kwen - neppa akked ccetla s - seg wanda ur ten tepwalim. Ni$ Nerra ccwaîen d imawlan n wid ur numin.'),
(982, 7, 28, 'Mi xedmen ayen n dir, ad inin: "nufa d akka ar imezwura nne$, u Öebbi Iumeô a$ d $uôes. Ini: "Öebbi, s tidep, ur Ippameô ar wayen n dir. Day a d tinim $ef Öebbi, ayen ur tessinem"?'),
(983, 7, 29, 'Ini: "Iumeô ed Öebbi lmizan. Zzit $uôeS udmawen nnwen di yal lekni, nujet $uôeS. £uôeS, s ddin iûfan. Akken ikwen id Ixleq, a ppu$alem".'),
(984, 7, 30, 'Arbaâ Inha it, arbaâ iura ttelfan fellas. Nitni, s tidep, rran ccwaîen d iêbiben, war Öebbi. U $ilen nitni, war ccekk, pwanhan.'),
(985, 7, 31, 'A tarwa n Adem! Ccebêet i yal lekni, eççet, esswet, ur sîuqqutet. Neppa, s tidep, ur Iêemmel ara wid isîuqquten.'),
(986, 7, 32, 'Ini: "anwa i igedlen ccbaêa n Öebbi, id Issuffe$ i imdanen iS, akked ôôeéq ilhan"? Ini: "ayagi, di tmeddurt n ddunit, i wid iumnen. I nitni kan ass n tnekra". Akka ay Nfeûûel issekniyen i ugdud issnen.'),
(987, 7, 33, 'Ini: "Mass iw Igdel kan ayen n dir, d uvhiô ne$ d uffir, abekkav, tem$weô war ssebba, a pcarkem i Öebbi ayen iwumi ur d irs udabu, a ppinim $ef Öebbi ayen ur tessinem".'),
(988, 7, 34, 'Yal lois isâa lajel. Ma iusa d lajel nnsen, ur t swexxiôen s ssaâa, ur t id ééaéan.'),
(989, 7, 35, 'A tarwa n Adem! Ma usan kwen id imazanen segwen, mmalen awen issekniyen iW, wid ipêezziben, ixeddmen ayen ilhan, ur ppagwaden, ur $weblen.'),
(990, 7, 36, 'Wid iskaddben issekniyen nne£, u sme$wôen iman nnsen fellasen, widak d at tmes, nitni degs ad wekkôen.'),
(991, 7, 37, 'Anwa idensen sennig win id igren tikerkas $ef Öebbi, ne$ iskaddben issekniyen iS? Widak, a ten iêaz umur i sen iuran di Tezmamt. Alamma, mi ten id usan imceggâen nne£, ad ddmen leôwaê nnsen, ad inin: "anida ten wid u$uô tepnujum, war Öebbi"? A d inin: "ur ten nufi". Ad cehhden, $ef yiman nnsen, ar nitni llan d ijehliyen.'),
(992, 7, 38, 'Inna: "kecmet di tmes ar leoyus n leonun akked yimdanen, i kwen id izwaren"! Yal tikelt ara ikcem lois, ad ixzu gma s. Alamma, mi mlalen degs akw, ad yini uneggaru nnsen $ef umezwaru nnsen: "a Mass nne$! Wigi telfen a$, Aâqeb iten s tmes, berdayen". Inna: "i yal yiwen berdayen, maca ur teéôim ara".'),
(993, 7, 39, 'Inna umezwaru nnsen i uneggaru nnsen: "ur kwen smenyafen i nekwni, ihi jeôôbet aâaqeb, ilmend n wayen tkeppbem".'),
(994, 7, 40, 'Ih, wid iskaddben issekniyen nne£, u sme$wôen iman nnsen fellasen, ur asen tellin tibbura igenni, ur keçmen Loennet, skud ur iâadda ara ul$em di tiî n tsegnit. Akka ay Nepqeîîi ibe$wviyen.'),
(995, 7, 41, 'I nitni ameîôeê di Loahennama, ad $ummen s tmes. Akka ay Nepqeîîi imednas.'),
(996, 7, 42, 'Wid iumnen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan - ur Nepkellif i umdan siwa ayen iwumi izmer - widak, d at Loennet, nitni, degs, ad wekkôen.'),
(997, 7, 43, 'A Nekkes i d igwran n dd$el, deg idmaren nnsen. Isaffen ad ppazzalen ddawat sen. Ad inin: "ccekôan i Öebbi i $ Inhan $eô waya. Ur nepwanhu, lemmer ur a$ Inha ara Öebbi. Ni$ usan d imazanen n Mass nne$, s tidep". Ad pwanecden: "appan Loennet, tweôtem p, ilmend n wayen txeddmem".'),
(998, 7, 44, 'At Loennet ad siwlen i at tmes: "ni$ nufa i $ Iâahed Mass nne$, s tidep. Ma tufam ayen i wen Iâahed Mass nnwen, s tidep"? A inin: "Ih". Iberreê uberraê garasen: "xezzu n Öebbi i imednas,'),
(999, 7, 45, 'wid iîîeôôifen seg ubrid n Öebbi, ssaramen t d uâwij, u nekôen laxeôt".'),
(1000, 7, 46, 'Garasen ssteô. £ef iqacucen, irgazen, ssnen ten akw, ar ûûiffat nnsen. Ad siwlen i at Loennet: "tifrat fellawen"! Ur p keççmen, xas ssarmen.'),
(1001, 7, 47, 'Mi zzint wallen nnsen ar at tmes, ad inin: "a Mass nne$! Ur a$ Ppara s agdud imednas"!'),
(1002, 7, 48, 'Ad siwlen at iqacucen i irgazen, ssnen ten ar ûûiffat nnsen. Ad inin: "acu i wen d issuli wayen tjemâam akked wayen tzuxxem"?'),
(1003, 7, 49, 'Day wigi d wid i$ef teggulem, ar ur sen ippak Öebbi aêunu? "Kecmet Loennet, ur teppagwadem, ur t$weblem".'),
(1004, 7, 50, 'At tmes ad siwlen i at Loennet: "smiret ed fellane$ aman, ne$ seg wayen is ikwen I$at Öebbi". Ad inin: "Öebbi, s tidep, Igdel iten i ijehliyen,'),
(1005, 7, 51, 'wid irran ddin nnsen d zzhu, d urar, u t$uôô iten tmeddurt n ddunit". Ihi, assa, a ten Neppu, akken ppun timlilit n wass nnsen agi, u nekôen issekniyen nne£.'),
(1006, 7, 52, 'Ni$ Nusa ten id s Tezmamt, Nfeûûel ip s tussna. D nnhaya, d aêunu i ugdud iumnen.'),
(1007, 7, 53, 'Day la pôaoun kan veôôu s? Ass n tisin n veôôu s, ad inin wid illan, iu$ lêal, ppun p: "ni$ usan d imazanen n Mass nne$, s tidep. Day nesâa imcafâen ara $ icafâen, ne$ ad a$ rren, a nexdem ayen mgirrden wayen nxeddem"? Ni$ sxeûôen iman nnsen. Itelf iten wayen d snulfuyen.'),
(1008, 7, 54, 'S tidep, Mass nnwen d Öebbi. Ixelq ed tamurt akked igenwan di sdis wussan, sinna, Iâannec $ef usgeld. Ip$ummu iv s wass, ip$awalen $uôes. Iîij, aggur, akked yitran unzen i lameô iS. Day maççi ineS lxelq akked lameô? D Asaâdi Öebbi, Mass imavalen!'),
(1009, 7, 55, 'Naâret Mass nnwen, s wannuz, di tbavnit. Neppa, s tidep, ur Iêemmel ara wid izegren tilas.'),
(1010, 7, 56, 'Ur ssefsadet di tmurt deffir useêôet is. Naâôet eP, s tugwdi d usirem. Aêunu n Öebbi, s tidep, ar tama n lâuûam.'),
(1011, 7, 57, 'D Neppa id Ippaznen avu, d abecceô s uêunu S. Alamma, ma ibbub ed asigna aéayan, Nenheô it ar tmurt immuten. Nesse$li d syis aman. Nessuffe$ ed yissen yal ppemôa. Akka ay d Nessuffu$ lmeggtin, amendeô ma d tesmektim.'),
(1012, 7, 58, 'Di tmurt lâali, teff$en d im$an is, ma Irad Öebbi. Di tin icemten, teff$en d kan d iweqweqen. Akka ay Nepbeggin issekniyen i ugdud isnemmiren.'),
(1013, 7, 59, 'Ni$ Nuzen ed Nuê i ugdud is. Inna: "a yagdud iw! Âabdet Öebbi! Ur tesâim ôebbi war Neppa. Nek ugade$ fellawen aâaqeb, ass ameqwôaêan".'),
(1014, 7, 60, 'Nnan imvebbôen n ugdud is: "$uône$, s tidep, aql ak di ttelfan n ûûeê".'),
(1015, 7, 61, 'Inna: "a yagdud iw! Ur illi dgi ttelfan. Maca nek d amazan s$uô Mass imavalen.'),
(1016, 7, 62, 'Bbwi$ awen d tibratin n Mass iw, a kwen neûêe$. Ssne$, s$uô Öebbi, ayen ur tessinem.'),
(1017, 7, 63, 'Day twehmem mi kwen id iusa usmekti s$uô Mass nnwen, ibbwi t id urgaz segwen, iwakken a kwen inabi, iwakken a pêezzbem, amar fellawen aêunu"?'),
(1018, 7, 64, 'Skaddben t. Nsellek it, akked wid illan yides, di lbabuô. Ne$meq wid iskaddben issekniyen nne£. Nitni, s tidep, d agdud ader$al.'),
(1019, 7, 65, 'Ar Âad, gmat sen Hud. Inna: "a yagdud iw! Âabdet Öebbi! Ur tesâim ôebbi, war Neppa. Day ur tepêezziben ara"?'),
(1020, 7, 66, 'Nnan imvebbôen, wid ijehlen seg ugdud is: "s tidep, $uône$, deg k tisselbi; $uône$, ih, keçç seg wid iskiddiben".'),
(1021, 7, 67, 'Inna: "a yagdud iw! Ur dgi tisselbi. Maca nek d amazan s$uô Mass imavalen.'),
(1022, 7, 68, 'Bbwi$ awen d tibratin n Mass iw. Nek, i kunwi, d aneûûaê muman.'),
(1023, 7, 69, 'Day twehmem mi kwen id iusa usmekti s$uô Mass nnwen, ibbwi t id urgaz segwen, iwakken a kwen inabi. Mmektit ed mi kwen Irra d igensas, deffir ugdud n Nuê. Isem$weô aîas lqedd nnwen. Mmektit ed lxiô n Öebbi, amar a prebêem".'),
(1024, 7, 70, 'Nnan: "day a$ d tusiv, iwakken a naâbed Öebbi Yiwen, a neoo ayen llan âabden imezwura nne$? Awi ya$ d ayen is la $ tessagwadev, ma d tidep ay tessawalev".'),
(1025, 7, 71, 'Inna: "ni$ iwwet ikwen id ddell akked zzâaf s$uô Mass nnwen. Day ad iyi namren $ef ismawen i tefkam, kunwi akked imezwura nnwen, i wid iwumi ur d Issers Öebbi kra udabu. Ihi, gganit, nek yidwen seg wid ara igganin".'),
(1026, 7, 72, 'Nsellek it, akked wid illan yides, s uêunu s$uône£. Nessenger wid iskaddben issekniyen nne£, ur nelli d lmumnin.'),
(1027, 7, 73, '£uô Tamud, gmat sen Üaliê. Inna: "a yagdud iw! Âabdet Öebbi! Ur tesâim ôebbi war Neppa. Ni$ iusa kwen id ubeggen s$uô Mass nnwen. Tal$wemt agi n Öebbi, d assekni i kunwi. Ooet ep a ppeçç di tmurt n Öebbi. Ur p îîuôôut, mulac a kwen iêaz uâaqeb aqeôêan.'),
(1028, 7, 74, 'Mmektit ed mi kwen Irra d igensas, deffir Âad. Isseqâad ikwen di tmurt, tepparram lebôuj di swaêel, teqqazem ixxamen deg durar. Ihi, mmektit ed lxiô n Öebbi, ur ssexsaôet tamurt, s usefsed".'),
(1029, 7, 75, 'Imvebbôen seg ugdud is, wid isme$awôen iman nnsen, nnan i wuôhifen, wid segsen iumnen: "day teéôam ar ÛüÜaliê d amazan s$uô Mass is"? Nnan: "ih, numen s wayen is id ippuceggaâ".'),
(1030, 7, 76, 'Nnan imzuxiyen: "nekwni, s tidep, nenkeô ayen is tumnem".'),
(1031, 7, 77, 'Ëerrfen avaô n tel$wemt, gelzen lameô n Mass nnsen. Nnan: "a Üaliê, awi ya$ d ayen is la $ tessagwadev, ma d amazan ay telliv".'),
(1032, 7, 78, 'Tewwet iten zzenzla, gwran d, deg ixxamen nnsen, d loeppat.'),
(1033, 7, 79, 'Iwexxeô asen, u inna: "a yagdud iw! Ni$ ssawve$ awen d tabôap n Mass iw, neûêe$ kwen, maca ur têemmlem ara win ineûêen".'),
(1034, 7, 80, 'I Luî, mi inna i ugdud is: "day a txeddmem lâaô ur ixdim yiwen, uqbel nnwen, deg imavalen?'),
(1035, 7, 81, 'Ih, kunwi tpeddum ar irgazen, tcehwam ten, war tilawin. Kunwi, ih, d agdud izegren tilas".'),
(1036, 7, 82, 'Tiririt n ugdud is siwa nnan: "ssuff$et pen si temdint nnwen, nitni d imdanen issaramen tezdeg".'),
(1037, 7, 83, 'Nsellek it, neppa akked twacult is, siwa tameîîut is, teqqim akked wid igwran.'),
(1038, 7, 84, 'Nesse$li d fellasen ageffur…Wali amek tevôa d ibe$wviyen.'),
(1039, 7, 85, '£uô Madian, gmat sen Cuâayeb. Inna: "a yagdud iw! Âabdet Öebbi! Ur tesâim ôebbi war Neppa. Ni$ iusa kwen id ubeggen s$uô Mass nnwen. Ktilet, weznet, s lewqama. Ur îîuôôut medden di cci nnsen, ur ssefsadet di tmurt, deffir useêôet is. I kunwi yif it wayagi, ma d lmumnin ay tellam.'),
(1040, 7, 86, 'Ur p$imit di yal abrid, tessagwadem u tessefôa$em seg ubrid n Öebbi, wid iumnen yiS. Teb$am t d uâwij. Mmektit ed mi tellam d takwemmict, Iketteô ikwen. Walit amek tevôa taggara ifessaden.'),
(1041, 7, 87, 'Ma illa iumen urbaâ segwen s wayen is id ppuceggâa$, arbaâ nniven ur iumin ara. Üebôet ard Iêudd Öebbi garane$. Neppa Yif akw imêaddan".'),
(1042, 7, 88, 'Nnan d imvebbôen imzuxiyen, n ugdud is,: "a k nessuffe$ a Cuâayeb, keçç, akked wid iumnen yidek, si temdint nne$, ne$ a d tu$alev ar ddin nne$". Inna: "xas nugi?'),
(1043, 7, 89, 'Ihi, nger ed tikerkas $ef Öebbi, ma nu$al ar ddin nnwen, mbaâd ma Isellek a$ Öebbi, segs. Ur a$ ilaq ara a nu$al $uôes, siwa ma Irad Öebbi, Mass nne$. Mass nne$ Issemêalleq i yal cci s tmusni. Nepkel $ef Öebbi". A Mass nne$! Fru p garane$ akked ugdud nne$, s tidep. Keçç Tifev akw wid iferrun.'),
(1044, 7, 90, 'Nnan imvebbôen, wid ijehlen, n ugdud is: "ma teddam d Cuâayeb, war ccekk a pxesôem."'),
(1045, 7, 91, 'Tewwet iten zzenzla, gwran d, deg ixxamen nnsen, d loeppat.'),
(1046, 7, 92, 'Wid iskaddben Cuâayeb, u$alen amzun ur zdi$en. Wid iskaddben Cuâayeb, d nitni ay d imexûuôen.'),
(1047, 7, 93, 'Iwexxeô asen, u inna: "a yagdud iw! Ni$ ssawve$ awen d tibôatin n Mass iw, neûêe$ kwen. Amek ara $weble$ $ef ugdud ijehliyen"?'),
(1048, 7, 94, 'Ur Nuzen ara nnbi ar temdint, mebla ma Newwet imezda$ is s cedda, akked lemveôôa, amar ad êiwten.'),
(1049, 7, 95, 'Sinna, Nerra ise$ deg umkan n tucmip, armi wexxôen, nnan: "ni$ jeôôben imezwura nne$ lemveôôa akked ttrika". Newwet iten deqzalla, nitni ur bnin.'),
(1050, 7, 96, 'Lemmer kan uminen u êezzben imezda$ n temdinin, war ccekk, ad asen Nelli lbaôakat seg igenni akked tmurt. Maca, skaddben. Nessemêalleq asen, ilmend n wayen keppben.'),
(1051, 7, 97, 'Day $ilen imezda$ n temdinin, ur ten id teppawev tiyta nne£, deg yiv, nitni îîsen?'),
(1052, 7, 98, 'Ne$ day $ilen imezda$ n temdinin, ur ten id teppawev tiyta nne£, deg wazal, nitni ppuraren?'),
(1053, 7, 99, 'Day $ilen sellken i tandit n Öebbi? Siwa agdud i ixesôen, i i$ilen sellken i tandit n Öebbi.'),
(1054, 7, 100, 'Ne$ day ur d Iban ara, i wid ara iweôten tamurt, deffir imezda$ is, ar, ma ihwa ya£, a ten Newwet $ef ibekkaven nnsen, a Nesle$ ulawen nnsen, d$a nitni ur sellen?'),
(1055, 7, 101, 'D timdinin agi, i$ef ak Nêekku, si teqûivin nnsent. Ni$ usan $uôsent imazanen nnsent, s ubeggen. Ur llint d tid ara iamnen deg wayen skaddbent uqbel. Akka i Iselle$ Öebbi ulawen ijehliyen.'),
(1056, 7, 102, 'Ur Nufi nnesba ar tegwti nnsen. Nufa, tegwti nnsen, d iballa$en.'),
(1057, 7, 103, 'Sinna, deffir sen, Nuzen ed Musa, s issekniyen nne£, ar Ferâun akked imvebbôen is. Densen ten. Wali amek tevôa d ifessaden.'),
(1058, 7, 104, 'Inna Musa: "a Ferâun! Nek d amazan s$uô Mass imavalen.'),
(1059, 7, 105, 'D ûûeê, ur qqaôe$, $ef Öebbi, siwa tidep. Ih, usi$ kwen id, s ubeggen n Mass nnwen. Ihi, azen yidi At Isôail".'),
(1060, 7, 106, 'Inna: "ma tusiv d s ussekni, zzi t id, ma tessawalav tidep".'),
(1061, 7, 107, 'Iveggeô taâkwazt is, appan d azrem n ûûeê.'),
(1062, 7, 108, 'Issuffe$ ed afus is, iban ed d amellal i imnezhen.'),
(1063, 7, 109, 'Nnan d imvebbôen n ugdud n Ferâun: "wagi, s tidep, d aseêêar amusnaw".'),
(1064, 7, 110, '"Ib$a a kwen issuffe$ si tmurt nnwen, d acu t lameô nnwen"?'),
(1065, 7, 111, 'Nnan: "anef as, neppa akked gma s. Azen iberraêen ar temdinin,'),
(1066, 7, 112, 'ad ak d awin yal aseêêar amusnaw".'),
(1067, 7, 113, 'Usan d iseêêaren n Ferâun, nnan: "s tidep, ad a$ tkafiv, ma d nekwni ara i$elben"?'),
(1068, 7, 114, 'Inna: "ih, u, s tidep, a ppilim d iqôiben".'),
(1069, 7, 115, 'Nnan: "a Musa! A pveggôev keçç, ne$ a nveggeô nekwni"?'),
(1070, 7, 116, 'Inna: "veggôet"! Mi veggôen, sdehcen allen n l$aci, ssagwden ten. Bbwin d ssêur anect ilat.'),
(1071, 7, 117, 'Nweêêa i Musa: "veggeô taâkwazt ik"! Apan tesseblaâ ayen d ûenâan.'),
(1072, 7, 118, 'Tûaô tidep, inqev wayen xeddmen.'),
(1073, 7, 119, 'Akka ay pwa$elben. U$alen ar deffir, d unqisen.'),
(1074, 7, 120, '£lin iseêêaren, knan.'),
(1075, 7, 121, 'Nnan: "numen s Mass imavalen,'),
(1076, 7, 122, 'Mass n Musa akked Haôun".'),
(1077, 7, 123, 'Inna Ferâun: "day tumnem yis, uqbel ma âammde$ awen? Ayagi, war ccekk, d tifxep. Tundim p di temdint, iwakken a ppessuff$em, segs, imezda$ is. Ihi, deqqal a ppeéôem.'),
(1078, 7, 124, 'War ccekk, ad awen gezme$ afus ssya, avaô ssya. Sinna, ih, a kwen semmôe$ akw $ef imudag".'),
(1079, 7, 125, 'Nnan: "nekwni a nu$al ar Mass nne$.'),
(1080, 7, 126, 'Terriv d ppaô segne$, imi kan numen s issekniyen n Mass nne$, mi $ d usan. A Mass nne$! Azen a$ d ûûbeô, Ddem leôwaê nne$ d imvuâen".'),
(1081, 7, 127, 'Imvebbôen n ugdud n Ferâun, nnan: "day a ppeooev Musa akked ugdud is, ad ssefsaden di tmurt, a kwen ooen, keçç akked iôebbiten ik"? Inna: "a nene$ arrac nnsen, a nessider tilawin nnsen. Nekwni, sennig sen, d iqehhaôen".'),
(1082, 7, 128, 'Inna Musa i ugdud is: "ppret afus n Öebbi, u ûebôet. Tamurt, war ccekk, n Öebbi. A p iwôet win i S ihwan, deg imdanen iS. Taggara i wid ipêezziben".'),
(1083, 7, 129, 'Nnan: "njaf uqbel a $ d tasev, u deffir tisin ik". Inna: "amar Mass nnwen ad Ine$ acengu nnwen, a kwen Irr d igensas di tmurt, ad Iwali amek ara txedmem".'),
(1084, 7, 130, 'Newwet, d$a, lois n Ferâun s iseggwasen n llaé, akked nneqs n ppemôa, amar a d mmektin.'),
(1085, 7, 131, 'Ma iusa ten id ise$, ad inin: "nne$ wagi". Ma tusa ten id tucmip, a p sbibben i Musa akked wid illan yides. Ayen iveôôun yidsen, day maççi ar Öebbi kan? Maca, tegwti segsen ur ssinen.'),
(1086, 7, 132, 'Nnan: " wicqa assekni ara d tawiv, ur a$ tepseêêirev yis. Nekwni, ur neppamen yisek".'),
(1087, 7, 133, 'Nuzen asen aêemmal, ajôad, tilkin, imqweôqwôen, idammen, d issekniyen ifeûlen. Sme$wôen iman nnsen. Llan d agdud ibe$wviyen.'),
(1088, 7, 134, 'Mi tevôa yidsen twa$it, qqaôen: "a Musa! Nâaô Mass ik i nekwni, s wayen i k Iâahed. Ma tekksev a$ tawa$it, a namen yisek, a nazen yidek At Isôail".'),
(1089, 7, 135, 'Mi sen Nekkes tawa$it, ar lajel iten iggunin, atnan nitni xedâan.'),
(1090, 7, 136, 'Nerra d segsen ppaô, N$emq iten deg ill, imi skaddben issekniyen nne£, ur d celâen degsen.'),
(1091, 7, 137, 'Nessewôet i ugdud i illan qehôen t, igmav akked ituram n tmurt, i Neôqa. Itam wawal ûûam n Mass ik, $ef At Isôail, ilmend n wayen ûebôen. Nhudd ayen iûennaâ Ferâun akked ugdud is, u wayen bennun.'),
(1092, 7, 138, 'Nesâadda ill i At Isôail. Mmugren d agdud i iâabden tiâancuôin is. Nnan: "a Musa! Err ane$ ôebbi am iôebbiten nnsen". Inna: "kunwi, s tidep, d agdud ur nessin.'),
(1093, 7, 139, 'Wigi, s tidep, ad inger wayen ideg llan, ad inqev wayen xeddmen".'),
(1094, 7, 140, 'Inna: "day awen budde$ ôebbi, war Öebbi, u Neppa Ismenyaf ikwen $ef imavalen"?'),
(1095, 7, 141, 'Mi kwen Nsellek si lois n Ferâun, sukken fellawen aâaqeb uqsiê mavi; neqqen arrac nnwen, ssidiren tilawin nnwen. Deg waya, ajeôôeb s$uô Mass nnwen ameqwôaêan.'),
(1096, 7, 142, 'Nemlal akked Musa kravet wavan, Nerna yasen mraw. Tebbwev tallit n Mass is, kuzet wavan. Inna Musa i gma s Haôun: "enûef iyi ar ugdud iw, exdem ayen ilhan, ur teddu d ubrid ifessaden".'),
(1097, 7, 143, 'Mi d iusa Musa ar temlilit nne£, u Immeslay as Mass is, inna: "a Mass iw! Ssenâat iyi d, a K wali$". Inna d: "ur iyI tepwaliv, d awez$i, maca muqel s adrar. Ma iqqim deg umekkan is, ad iyI twaliv". Mi d Iusa Mass is s adrar, Irra t d saêel. I$li Musa, ixsef. Mi d iuki, inna: "gedha s yiseK! Utube$ K, nek d amezwaru n lmumnin".'),
(1098, 7, 144, 'Inna: "a Musa! Aql I Smenyafe$ k $ef imdanen, i tebôatin iW, i wawal iW. Ddem ayen i k d Fki$, ili seg wid isnemmiren".'),
(1099, 7, 145, 'Nura yas, di tlewêin, si yal cci, anabi akked ufeûûel n yal cci. Ddem itent s tezmert, ameô i ugdud ik a tent iîîef s lmaâna nnsent. Ad awen Ssekne$ tanezdu$t iballa$en.'),
(1100, 7, 146, 'Ad Veôôfe$, seg issekniyen iW, wid isme$wôen iman nnsen di tmurt, war ssebba. Mi walan yal assekni, ur ppamnen yis. Ma walan abrid uûwib, ur teddun degs. Ma walan abrid n le$wlav, a t awin. Ayagi, acku, s tidep, skaddben issekniyen nne£, ur d celâen degsen.'),
(1101, 7, 147, 'Wid iskaddben issekniyen nne£, akked temlilit n laxeôt, ur swin igiten nnsen. Day a ten kafin $ef wayen ur nelli d ayen xeddmen?'),
(1102, 7, 148, 'Agdud n Musa, deffir es, isbedd, s ôôêuê is, aâjmi bu loeppa isrugmuten. Day ur walan ara ar, s tidep, ur asen d ipmeslay, ur la ten inehhu s abrid? Âabden t, llan d imednas.'),
(1103, 7, 149, 'Mi ppuêeccmen, u walan ar, zi$ nnetlafen, nnan: "ma ur Iêun ara fella$ Mass nne$, ma ur a$ Isemmeê ara, war ccekk, a nu$al seg imexsuôen".'),
(1104, 7, 150, 'Mi d iu$al Musa ar ugdud is, s wurrif akked lêemûa, inna: "ay d ucmit wayen is iyi tneûfem, deffir iw! Teb$am a d i$iwwel lameô n Mass nnwen"? Iveggeô tilewêin, iîîef gma s seg uqeôôu, ijebt it id $uôes. Inna d: "a mmi s n yimma, s tidep, iêqeô iyi ugdud, qôib iyi n$an. Ur ssefôaê icenga yissi. Ur iyi pparra seg ugdud imednas".'),
(1105, 7, 151, 'Inna: "a Mass iw! Semmeê ane$, nek akked gma, Ssekcem a$ ar uêunu K. Keçç, Tifev akw wid ipêunun".'),
(1106, 7, 152, 'Ih, wid iâabden aâajmi, a d i$li fellasen wurrif n Mass nnsen, ad ndellen di tmeddurt n ddunit. Akka ay Nepqeîîi wid id isnulfuyen.'),
(1107, 7, 153, 'Wid ixedmen tucmitin, sinna, steôoâen deffir sent, u umnen, Mass ik, s tidep, deffir sent, ar Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu.'),
(1108, 7, 154, 'Mi irs wurrif is, iddem ed Musa tilewêin. Di tira nnsent, nnhaya akked uêunu i wid ippagwaden Mass nnsen.'),
(1109, 7, 155, 'Ifren ed Musa ûatet irgazen seg ugdud is, ad mlilen yidne£. Mi ten tewwet zzenzla, inna: "a Mass iw! Lemmer i K ihwi, yili, iu$ lêal, Ten$iv ten, u Tegliv yissi. Day ad a$ Temêuv, ilmend n wayen xedmen ije$lufen segne$? Wagi d ahewwel iK kan, Tettellifev syis win i K ihwan, Tnehhuv win i K ihwan. Keçç d Bab nne$, Semmeê a$, Ëun fella$, Keçç Tifev akw wid ipsemmiêen.'),
(1110, 7, 156, 'Aru ya$ ise$ di ddunit, di laxeôt; aql a$ nu$al ed $uôeK". Inna d: "aâaqeb iW, a t Sâaddi$ $ef win iyI ihwan. Aêunu W ijemmel yal cci. A t Aru$ i wid ipêezziben, ipzekkin, akked wid iumnen s issekniyen nne£,'),
(1111, 7, 157, 'wid iteddun d Umazan, Nnbi ur ne$ôi, i ufan iura $uôsen di Tuôa akked Linoil". Iumeô asen d lqanun, Itekkes asen ayen n dir. Iêell asen lâali, igdel asen dduni. Ikkes asen aruz akked lqid nnsen. Ihi, wid iumnen yis, i t iâawnen, i t isellken, iddan d tafat id irsen yides, widak d imerbaê.'),
(1112, 7, 158, 'Ini: "a yimdanen! Nek d Amazan n Öebbi $uôwen meôôa. Neppa, ineS tagelda n tmurt akked igenwan. Ur illi ôebbi siwa Neppa. Issidir, Ineqq". Ihi, amnet s Öebbi akked Umazan iS, Nnbi ur ne$ôi, i iumnen s Öebbi akked wawal iS. Ddut yides, amar a ppepwanhum.'),
(1113, 7, 159, 'Deg ugdud n Musa, arbaâ iteddu s tidep. U syis ay pêuddun.'),
(1114, 7, 160, 'Nessemfaôaq iten $ef mrawsin laâôac, n leoyus. Mi s issuter ugdud is tissit, Nweêêa i Musa: ewwet aéôu s tâakwaz ik. F$ent ed segs mrawsnat tliwa; akka, yal amdan iéôa anda ara issew. Nesbur iten s usigna, Nessers asen d lmenna akked ifeôôuoen: "eççet seg wayen ilhan, is ikwen N$at". Ur a£ dnisen, maca la ddennisen iman nnsen.'),
(1115, 7, 161, 'Mi pwanecden: "zed$et di temdint agi, eççet segs, ayen i wen ihwan, init: "laâfu"! Âaddit di tebburt, s lekni. Ad awen Nsemmeê tuccva nnwen. A Nernu i lâuûam".'),
(1116, 7, 162, 'Wid idensen segsen, neûfen awalen s wid ur nelli d wid i sen nnan. Nuzen asen tiyta seg igenni, ilmend n wayen ddennisen.'),
(1117, 7, 163, 'Steqsi ten $ef temdint i illan $ef rrif n yill, mi ur d rzin di ssebt, mi ten id usan iselman nnsen, walan ten, ass n ssebt. Ass, war ssebt, ur ten id ppasen. Akka ay ten Njeôôeb, deg wayen ssexsaôen.'),
(1118, 7, 164, 'Mi d inna lois, segsen: "iwumi la tepnabim agdud ara Isqucc Öebbi, ne$ ara Iâaqeb s leqseê"? Nnan: "d aste$feô ar Mass nnwen, amar ad êezzben".'),
(1119, 7, 165, 'Mi ppun ayen i$ef pwafekkôen, Nsellek wid itekksen ayen n dir, Nesâadda aâaqeb adiran $ef imednas, ilmend n wayen ssexsaôen.'),
(1120, 7, 166, 'Mi sme$wôen iman nnsen $ef wayen i sen ipwakksen, Nenna yasen: "ilit d uddawen ucmiten"!'),
(1121, 7, 167, 'Mi Ixebbeô Mass ik, ard asen d Iazen ara ten iâaqben, s ééuô, alamma d ass n tnekra. Mass ik, s tidep, Ip$awal ar uâaqeb. Neppa, s tidep, Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu.'),
(1122, 7, 168, 'Nessemfaôaq iten di tmurt, d leoyus, garasen wid imaânen, garasen wid ur nemâin. Njeôôeb iten s ise$iyen akked tucmitin, amar a d u$alen s abrid.'),
(1123, 7, 169, 'Neûfen ten, deffir sen, ineûûafen i iweôten Tazmamt. Ppaddamen lerbaê n ddunit, qqaôen: "ad a$ semmêen". Ma rnan usan ten id lerbaê, am widen, a ten ddmen. Day ur âahden ara s Tezmamt, ard tidep kan, ara inin $ef Öebbi? U lemden i illan degs. Ppif axxam aneggaru, i wid ipêezziben. Day ur tfehmem ara?'),
(1124, 7, 170, 'Wid iîîfen di Tezmamt, ipéallan, s tidep, ur Nveggiâ arraz n lâuûam.'),
(1125, 7, 171, 'Mi Nessuli adrar sennig sen, amzun d tili, $ilen, s tidep, ara d i$li fellasen. Ïîfet nezzeh ayen i wen Nefka, smektit ed ayen illan degs, amar a pêezzbem.'),
(1126, 7, 172, 'Mi d Iddem Mass ik, si tgeééal n tarwa n Adem, dderya nnsen, Inna yasen a d cehhden $ef yiman nnsen: "day ur Lli$ ara d Mass nnwen"? Nnan: "ih, ncehhed". Akka ur d teqqaôem ara, ass n tnekra: "s tidep, ayagi d ayen ur neéôi".'),
(1127, 7, 173, 'Ne$ a d tinim: "d imezwura nne$ kan i icurken, zik. Nekwni d tarwa deffir sen. Day a$ Ten$ev, ilmend n wayen xedmen wid iôejjnen"?'),
(1128, 7, 174, 'Akka ay Nfeûûel issekniyen, amar a d u$alen s abrid.'),
(1129, 7, 175, 'Eêku yasen d tadyant n win iwumi Nefka issekniyen nne£. Irra ten akin. Idda yides Cciîan, iu$al seg wid i$eôqen.'),
(1130, 7, 176, 'Lemmer i £ ihwi, Nessuli t yissen. Maca, ib$a tamurt, idda d lhawiyya s. Ihi, amedya s am win n waydi, ma teddiv p fellas, ad ilehhet, ma teooiv t, ad ilehhet. D wagi ay d amedya n ugdud i iskaddben issekniyen nne£. Eêku d tadyant, amar a d mmektin.'),
(1131, 7, 177, 'Agdud iskaddben issekniyen nne£, d yir amedya. Pddennisen iman nnsen.'),
(1132, 7, 178, 'Win Inha Öebbi, ihi, idda d ubrid. Wid Itlef Öebbi, nitni d imexsuôen.'),
(1133, 7, 179, 'Ni$ Neswejd ed, i Loahennama, aîas n leonun akked yimdanen. Sâan ulawen, ur fehhmen yissen; sâan allen, ur pwalin yissent; sâan imeééu$en, ur sellen yissen. Nitni am lmal, ne$ nnetlafen kteô. Wigi d i$wefliyen.'),
(1134, 7, 180, 'I Öebbi, ismawen ûûam. Naâôet eP, yissen. Veôôfet seg wid issexsaôen ismawen iS. Ad ppuqeîîin $ef wayen xeddmen.'),
(1135, 7, 181, 'Deg wayen Nexleq, yiwen n lois ivfeô tidep. Ipêuddu syis.'),
(1136, 7, 182, 'Wid iskaddben issekniyen nne£, a ten Nawi, cwiî, cwiî, ar wanda ur éôin.'),
(1137, 7, 183, 'Ad asen Fke$ lmudda. Ih, ticeôkep iW d tunûiêt.'),
(1138, 7, 184, 'Day ur d tepmeyyizem ara? Ur illi umeddakwel nnwen d aôehbani. Neppa, d aneddaô kan ipbegginen.'),
(1139, 7, 185, 'Day ur walan ara tagelda n tmurt, igenwan, akked wayen Ixleq Öebbi n cci? Ni$, ahat, iqeôb ed lajel nnsen. Anwa awal, deffir wagi, ar amnen?'),
(1140, 7, 186, 'Win Itlef Öebbi, ur Isâi nnahi. A ten Ioo ad hemlen di tjehli nnsen.'),
(1141, 7, 187, 'A k steqsayen $ef yimir, melmi ara d yili. Ini: "i t Iéôan siwa Mass iw. D Neppa kan a t id Isseknen, di lweqt is. Ad iaéay di tmurt akked igenwan. Ur kwen id ippawev siwa deqzalla". A k steqsayen amzun tesâiv asali fellas. Ini: "i t Issnen siwa ÔÖebbi", maca tegwti n yimdanen ur ssinen.'),
(1142, 7, 188, 'Ini: "ur ksibe$ i iman iw, aba$uô ne$ vveôô, kkes ed ayen Irad Öebbi. Lemmer ssine$ tabavnit, ad ôwu$ lxiô, ur iyi ipnal ixmiô. Nek d aneddaô kan, u d abcir, i ugdud iumnen".'),
(1143, 7, 189, 'D Neppa ikwen id Ixelqen si yiwen n yiman. Iddem ed segs tameîîut is, ad izde$ yides. Mi insa yides, tebbwi tadist tafessast; telêa yis. Mi d teûbeê ééayet, naâôen Öebbi: "a Mass nne$! Ma Tefkiv a$ d aâeôvi, war ccekk, a nili seg wid isnemmiren".'),
(1144, 7, 190, 'Mi sen d Ifka aâeôdi, rran aS icriken s wayen i sen d Ifka. I aâlay Öebbi, sennig wayen pcaraken!'),
(1145, 7, 191, 'Day ad carken ayen ur nexliq acemma, u d nitni i ipwaxelqen?'),
(1146, 7, 192, 'Ur zmiren a ten âiwnen, ne$ ad âiwnen iman nnsen.'),
(1147, 7, 193, 'Ma tnecdem ten ar nnhaya, ur teddun yidwen. Iâuva fellawen ma tnecdem ten, ne$ ma tessusmem.'),
(1148, 7, 194, 'S tidep, wigi tnaâôem, war Öebbi, d imdanen am kunwi. Naâret pen, ma ad awen d rren, maday tessawalem tidep.'),
(1149, 7, 195, 'Day sâan ivaôen, ad lêun fellasen, ne$ sâan ifassen, ad ddmen yissen, ne$ sâan allen, ad walin yisent, ne$ sâan imeééu$en, ad slen yissen. Ini: "naâret icriken nnwen, sinna, andit iyi. Ur iyi sganayet".'),
(1150, 7, 196, 'Ih, Bab iw d Öebbi id Issersen Tazmamt, i Iêemmlen lâuûam.'),
(1151, 7, 197, 'Wid tnaâôem, war Neppa, ur zmiren a kwen âawnen, ne$ ad âawnen iman nnsen.'),
(1152, 7, 198, 'Ma tnecdem ten ar nnhaya, ur sellen. A ten twaliv a k id pmuqulen, nitni ur pwalin.'),
(1153, 7, 199, 'Ddem ayen ilhan, ameô ar lewqama, veôôef i wid ur nessin.'),
(1154, 7, 200, 'Ma ilaâj ik Cciîan ar dduni, ppkel $ef Öebbi. Neppa, s tidep, Issel, d Amusnaw.'),
(1155, 7, 201, 'Ih, wid ipêezziben, ma innul iten urbaâ n ccwaîen, a d mmektin, d$a ad asen llint wallen.'),
(1156, 7, 202, 'Zgan $elîen atmaten nnsen, d$a nitni ur xevvun.'),
(1157, 7, 203, 'Ma ur asen d tebbwiv ara assekni, ad ak inin: "acimi ur t id isnulfa ara"? Ini: "teddu$ kan d wayen iyi d ippuweêêan, s$uô Mass iw". Wagi, s$uô Mass nnwen, d tafat, d nnhaya, d aêunu, i ugdud iumnen.'),
(1158, 7, 204, 'Ma qqaôen Leqwôan ssemêesset as, ssusmet, amar fellawen aêunu.'),
(1159, 7, 205, 'Mmekti d Mass ik, deg iman ik, s wannuz akked lxuf, s wawal irsen, taûebêit, tameddit. Ur ppili seg i$wefliyen.'),
(1160, 7, 206, 'Ih, wid illan ar Mass ik, ur sme$wôen ara iman nnsen, $ef uâbad iS. Sbuccuâen T, i Neppa kennun.');
INSERT INTO `ber_mensur` (`index`, `sura`, `aya`, `text`) VALUES
(1161, 8, 1, 'Steqsan k $ef rrbeê. Ini: "rrbeê i Öebbi akked Umazan. Ihi, êezzbet i Öebbi, elhut garawen, a$et awal i Öebbi akked Umazan iS, ma d lmumnin ay tellam".'),
(1162, 8, 2, 'Lmumnin d wid kan iwumi ippergigi wul nnsen, ma Ipwabder ed Öebbi. Ma $ôan asen issekniyen iS, ad innerni liman nnsen. £ef Mass nnsen, ay ppeklen.'),
(1163, 8, 3, 'Wid ibedden i téallit, ipûeôôifen seg wayen is iten N$at.'),
(1164, 8, 4, 'Wigi d ûûeê, d lmumnin. I nitni, ar Mass nnsen, tiseddaôin, ssmaê, akked l$it uùkyis.'),
(1165, 8, 5, 'Akken ik id Issuffe$ Mass ik, seg uxxam ik, s tidep, wanag ur ib$i urbaâ si lmumnin.'),
(1166, 8, 6, 'La k pnamaren $ef tidep, deffir ubeggen is, amzun kan pwanehôen ar tmeppant, nitni pêekkiôen.'),
(1167, 8, 7, 'Mi wen Iâahed Öebbi, ara ppili nnwen, yiwet si snat n trebbuyaâ, tessarmem a ppili nnwen tin ur nepwaselleê. Öebbi Ib$a a d itebbet tidep s wawalen iS, ad ôéen wakali ijehliyen.'),
(1168, 8, 8, 'A ppili tidep, ad inqev lbaîel, xas ugin ibe$wviyen.'),
(1169, 8, 9, 'Mi tepprem afus s$uô Mass nnwen, Ijaweb awen d: "Nek ad awen Fke$ agim lmalayek, mestebâant".'),
(1170, 8, 10, 'Irra t kan Öebbi d abecceô iwakken ad nnevmanen yis wulawen nnwen. Ur illi l$elb, siwa s$uô Öebbi. Öebbi, s tidep, d Uzmir, d Bab n ûûwab.'),
(1171, 8, 11, 'Mi kwen I$umm s yives, d îîmana s$uôeS; Isse$li d fellawen aman seg igenni; a kwen Izzizdeg yissen, ad Issebâad, fellawen, a$way n Cciîan, ad Isseohed ulawen nnwen, ad Itebbet, yissen, isurifen.'),
(1172, 8, 12, 'Mi Iweêêa Mass ik i lmalayek: "Nek yidkwent; tebbtemt wid iumnen. Ad Skecme$ tugdi deg ulawen n wid ijehlen. Ewwtemt sennig tmegrav, ewwtemt ar ixfawen ivudan".'),
(1173, 8, 13, 'Ayagi, acku nitni, s tidep, xuûmen Öebbi akked Umazan iS. I win ixuûmen Öebbi akked Umazan iS, ihi, Öebbi Iwâaô deg uâaqeb.'),
(1174, 8, 14, 'Wagi i kunwi, jeôôbet ep! U i ijehliyen, aâaqeb n tmes.'),
(1175, 8, 15, 'A wid iumnen! Ma temmugrem d wid ijehlen la d éeddmen, ur sen reggwlet.'),
(1176, 8, 16, 'Win i sen irewlen, assen, siwa ma la issewjad i umennu$, ne$ ma ikcem s arbaâ, winna, a t immager wurrif n Öebbi; axxam is d Loahennama, a yir tu$alin!'),
(1177, 8, 17, 'Ur ten tennu$em, maca d Öebbi iten Innu$en. Ur teôoimev mi tôeomev, maca Öebbi Iôoem, iwakken ad Ijeôôeb lmumnin s ujeôôeb umâin s$uôeS. Öebbi, s tidep, Issel, d Amusnaw.'),
(1178, 8, 18, 'Akka, Ih, Öebbi Issadar ticeôkep ijehliyen.'),
(1179, 8, 19, 'Tessutrem l$elb, atan iusa kwen id. Ma tfukkem, ppif i kunwi. Ma tu$alem, a Nu$al. Ula iwumi tent, bippa, trebbuyaâ nnwen, xas îîuqtent. Ih, Öebbi Idda d lmumnin.'),
(1180, 8, 20, 'A wid iumnen! A$et awal i Öebbi akked Umazan iS. Ur T ppaooat, u kunwi tsellem.'),
(1181, 8, 21, 'Ur ppilit am wid innan: "nesla", nitni ur sellen.'),
(1182, 8, 22, '£eô Öebbi, s tidep, ineggura imexlaq d iâeééugen, d igugam, ur nfehhem.'),
(1183, 8, 23, 'Lemmer Iéôi Öebbi degsen lxiô, yili Irra ten sellen. Ma Irra ten sellen, war ccekk, ad akwren avaô, u nitni aâûan.'),
(1184, 8, 24, 'A wid iumnen! Jawbet i Öebbi akked Umazan, ma Inced ikwen ar wayen ikwen issidiren. Cfut ar Öebbi Ippili ger umdan akked wul is. £uôeS, Neppa, s tidep, ara tepwafessrem.'),
(1185, 8, 25, 'Ëezzbet i uhewwel. Ur ipêaz ara kan imednas segwen, weêêedsen. Cfut ar Öebbi Iqseê deg uâaqeb.'),
(1186, 8, 26, 'Mmektit ed mi, kunwi, drus ay tellam, d uôhifen di tmurt, teppagwadem a kwen xevfen medden. Iûûeô ikwen, Isellek ikwen s l$elb iS, I$at ikwen s wayen ilhan, amender ma a ppesnemmrem.'),
(1187, 8, 27, 'A wid iumnen! Ur pxeyyinet Öebbi akked Umazan, ur pxeyyinet lamanat nnwen, kunwi teéôam.'),
(1188, 8, 28, 'Cfut ar, ayla nnwen akked tarwa nnwen, d ahewwel kan, u ar £uô Öebbi, ôôaîeb ameqwôaêan.'),
(1189, 8, 29, 'A wid iumnen! Ma têezzbem i Öebbi, ad awen Ifk afraz, ad awen Imêu tucmitin nnwen, ad awen Isemmeê. Öebbi d Bab n lfevl ameqwôaêan.'),
(1190, 8, 30, 'Ma ppandin ak, wid ijehlen, iwakken a k êebsen, ne$ a k n$en, ne$ a k ssuff$en; ppandin u Öebbi Ippandi. Öebbi Yif akw imendayen.'),
(1191, 8, 31, 'Ma $ôan asen issekniyen nne£, ad inin: "ih, nesla. Ma ihwa ya$ a d nini am ayagi. Ayagi, s tidep, siwa d timucuha imezwura".'),
(1192, 8, 32, 'Mi nnan: "a Öebbi, ma illa wagi d tidep s$uôeK, Sse$li d, fella$, id$a$en seg igenni, ne$ Awi a$ d aâaqeb aqeôêan".'),
(1193, 8, 33, 'Ur illi Öebbi d win ara ten Iâaqben, skud telliv garasen. Ur Illi Öebbi d win ara Ipâaqben ma nitni la suturen ssmaê.'),
(1194, 8, 34, 'Acimi ur ten Ipâaqab ara Öebbi, u nitni swexxiôen si Loamaâ n Lêaôam, ur llin d imawlan is. Imawlan is, d wid kan ipêezziben. Maca, tegwti segsen ur éôin.'),
(1195, 8, 35, 'Taéallit nnsen deg Uxxam, siwa aseffeô akked llir. Jeôôbet aâaqeb, $ef wayen tjehhlem.'),
(1196, 8, 36, 'Ih, wid ijehlen pûeôôifen ayla nnsen, iwakken ad veôôfen seg ubrid n Öebbi. A t ûeôôfen, ad asen iu$al d lexsaôa. Sinna, ad ppu$elben. Wid ijehlen ad pwafessren di Loahennama.'),
(1197, 8, 37, 'Iwakken ad Ifrez Öebbi dduni d lâali, ad Irr ixabiten, wa $ef wa, a ten Izdi akw, a ten Irr ar Loahennama. Widak d imexsuôen.'),
(1198, 8, 38, 'Ini i wid ijehlen: "ma fukken, ad awen Isemmeê ayen iâaddan; ma u$alen, ihi, akken tevôa d imezwura".'),
(1199, 8, 39, 'Nna$et pen alamma tfukk lfetna, u iu$al ddin s lekmal is, i Öebbi. Ma êebsen, Öebbi, s tidep, Ipwali ay xeddmen.'),
(1200, 8, 40, 'Ma wexxôen, cfut ar Öebbi d Bab nnwen, Bab amxalef, Asellak amxalef.'),
(1201, 8, 41, 'Akken ib$u yili wayen id t$eltem n cci, cfut amur wis smus n Öebbi akked Umazan iS, akked llzem, igujilen, ime$ban, win d ibbwi ubrid; ma illa tumnem s Öebbi akked wayen id Nessers i umdan nne£, ass n ufraz, ass ideg mlalent snat n trebbuyaâ. Öebbi Izmer i yal cci.'),
(1202, 8, 42, 'Mi tellam di loiha taqôibt, u nitni agwemmav, imnayen seddawat wen, xas temyefkem ppaâud, tzeglem timlilit. Maca, iwakken ad Isâaddi Öebbi lameô ara iâaddin, ad immet win immuten, s ubeggen, ad yidir win idren, s ubeggen. Öebbi, s tidep, Issel, d Amusnaw.'),
(1203, 8, 43, 'Mi k ten id Issenâat Öebbi, d takwemmict, di targit ik ... Lemmer ik ten id Issenâat qwan, war ccekk, a pfeclem, a ppemnamarem $ef lameô. Maca, Öebbi Ijbeô ikwen. Ih, Neppa Issen i illan deg idmaren.'),
(1204, 8, 44, 'Mi wen ten Issenâat, mi ten temmugrem, twalam ten d takwemmict. Iééeméi kwen ar tmu$li nnsen, iwakken ad Isâaddi Öebbi lameô ara iâaddin. Ar Öebbi ppu$alen lumuô.'),
(1205, 8, 45, 'A wid iumnen! Ma temmugrem d arbaâ, tebbtet, mmektit ed aîas Öebbi, amar a prebêem.'),
(1206, 8, 46, 'A$et awal i Öebbi akked Umazan iS, ur ppemnamaret. Mulac a pfeclem, a pnegfem. Üebôet! S tidep, Öebbi ar iûebôiyen.'),
(1207, 8, 47, 'Ur ppilit am wid id iff$en s tem$weô, seg ixxamen nnsen, iwakken a ten id walin medden. Swexxiôen seg ubrid n Öebbi. Öebbi Izzi i wayen xeddmen.'),
(1208, 8, 48, 'Mi sen icebbeê Cciîan igiten nnsen, u inna: "ur kwen i$elleb yiwen seg imdanen, ass agi. Nek d amalal nnwen". Mi mwalant snat trebbuyaâ, iuker avaô, inna: "nek xvi$ kwen, nek wala$ ayen ur twalam, nek ugade$ Öebbi. Öebbi Iqseê deg uâaqeb".'),
(1209, 8, 49, 'Mi nnan ixabiten akked imehzulen n wul: "wigi, i$uôô iten ddin nnsen". Win ippeklen $ef Öebbi, ihi, Öebbi d Uzmir, d Bab n ûûwab.'),
(1210, 8, 50, 'Lemmer a pwaliv mara ddment lmalayek leôwaê n wid ijehlen, ad kkatent udmawen nnsen, izugar nnsen. "Jeôôbet aâaqeb n tmeô$iwt!'),
(1211, 8, 51, 'Ayagi ilmend n wayen d bbwin ifassen nnwen", u Öebbi ur pdennis imdanen.'),
(1212, 8, 52, 'Am tikli n ugdud n Ferâun akked wid i ten id izwaren. Nekôen issekniyen n Öebbi. Issemêaleq asen Öebbi s ibekkaven nnsen. Ih, Öebbi d Uzmir, Iqseê deg uâaqeb.'),
(1213, 8, 53, 'Akka, acku Öebbi ur Ipbeddil l$it is I$at agdud, alamma bedlen i illan deg iman nnsen. Öebbi Issel, d Amusnaw.'),
(1214, 8, 54, 'Am tikli n ugdud n Ferâun akked wid i ten id izwaren. Skaddben issekniyen n Mass nnsen. Nen$a ten s ibekkaven nnsen, Ne$meq agdud n Ferâun; llan akw d imednas.'),
(1215, 8, 55, '£uô Öebbi, imexlaq ucmiten mavi, d wid ijehlen, d$a ur uminen,'),
(1216, 8, 56, 'wid ukud tgiv lemâahda, sinna, di yal tikelt, neqven lemâahda nnsen, u nitni ur pêezziben.'),
(1217, 8, 57, 'Ma tugarev ten di îôad, sserwel yissen wid i ten id ivefôen, amar a d mmektin.'),
(1218, 8, 58, 'Ma tugadev lexdaâ seg ugdud, err iten akin, s tezdeg. Öebbi, s tidep, ur Iêemmel ara ixeddaâen.'),
(1219, 8, 59, 'Ur p$ilin menâan, wid ijehlen. Nitni, s tidep, ur zmiren.'),
(1220, 8, 60, 'Heggit asen d ayen iwumi tzemrem n lemêella akked yimnayen, a ppessagwdem yissen acengu n Öebbi, acengu nnwen, akked wiyav, war segsen, ur tessinem; Öebbi Issen iten. Ayen tseddqem n cci, deg ubrid n Öebbi, ad awen d iu$al. Kunwi ur tepwadensem.'),
(1221, 8, 61, 'Ma nudan talwit, nadi ep. Ppkel $ef Öebbi. Neppa, s tidep, Issel, d Amusnaw.'),
(1222, 8, 62, 'Ma b$an a k xedâan, ihi, âammed $ef Öebbi, Neppa i k Ifkan afus s tallalt iS, akked lmumnin.'),
(1223, 8, 63, 'Issemlal ulawen nnsen. Lemmer a pûeôfev i illan akw di tmurt, ur tessemliliv ulawen nnsen. Maca, Öebbi Issemlal iten. Neppa, s tidep, d Uzmir, d Bab n ûûwab.'),
(1224, 8, 64, 'A Nnbi! Âammed $ef Öebbi, keçç, akked wid iddan yidek si lmumnin.'),
(1225, 8, 65, 'A Nnbi! Eg lêir i lmumnin, ad nna$en. Ma llan segwen warem iûebôiyen, ad rnun snat twinas. Ma llan segwen twinas, ad rnun agim n wid ijehlen, acku, nitni d agdud ur nfehhem.'),
(1226, 8, 66, 'Tura, Issafes Öebbi fellawen. Iéôa tella garawen rrehma. Ihi, ma llan segwen twinas iûebôiyen, ad rnun snat twinas, ma llan segwen agim, ad rnun sin igima, ma Irad Öebbi. Öebbi ar iûebôiyen.'),
(1227, 8, 67, 'Ur issefk ara i Nnbi ad isâu imeêbas, alamma pwa$elben di tmurt. Teb$am tukci n ddunit. Öebbi Ib$a laxeôt. Öebbi d Uzmir, d Bab n ûûwab.'),
(1228, 8, 68, 'Lemmer maççi d ayen iuran s$uô Öebbi, izwar ed, yili a kwen iwwet uâaqeb abarar, ilmend n wayen tebbwim.'),
(1229, 8, 69, 'Eççet ayen ilhan, iêellen, seg wayen i t$elltem, êezzbet i Öebbi. Öebbi, s tidep, Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu.'),
(1230, 8, 70, 'A Nnbi! Ini i wid teîîfem seg imeêbas: "ma Iufa Öebbi lxiô deg ulawen nnwen, ad awen Ifk ayen yifen ayen i wen ipwakksen, ad awen Isemmeê. Öebbi Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu".'),
(1231, 8, 71, 'Ma b$an a k xedâan, ni$ iu$ lêal xedâen Öebbi. D$a, Ikkes asen ôôay. Öebbi Iéôa, d Bab n ûûwab.'),
(1232, 8, 72, 'Ih, wid iumnen, iunagen, ijuhden s wayla nnsen, akked yiman nnsen, deg ubrid n Öebbi, wid isnubgten u fkan afus, widak d imeddukwal bwaygarasen. Wid iumnen ur unagen, ur awen llin d imeddukwal, s wacemma, alamma unagen. Ma ppren afus nnwen di ddin, iwata yawen ad asen tefkem afus, siwa mgal agdud ukud tâaqdem. Öebbi Ipwali ayen txeddmem.'),
(1233, 8, 73, 'Wid ijehlen d imeddukwal bwaygarasen. Ma ur tgim ara akka, a ppili lfetna di tmurt, akked usefsed ameqwôan.'),
(1234, 8, 74, 'Wid iumnen, iunagen, ijuhden deg ubrid n Öebbi, wid isnubgten u fkan afus, widak, s tidep, d lmumnin. I nitni ssmaê akked l$it ukyis.'),
(1235, 8, 75, 'Wid iumnen syin $er da, u unagen, u juhden yidwen, widak segwen. Llzem ppemyilin kteô di Tezmamt n Öebbi. Öebbi, s tidep, Izôa yal cci.');
INSERT INTO `ber_mensur` (`index`, `sura`, `aya`, `text`) VALUES
(1236, 9, 1, 'Öebbi akked Umazan iS kksen aêeppem i imcurak ukud tâaqqdem.'),
(1237, 9, 2, 'Ddut di tmurt kué wagguren. Cfut ar kunwi ur tesfunnugem i Öebbi, u Öebbi ad Isdull ijehliyen.'),
(1238, 9, 3, 'Aberreê i medden, s$uô Öebbi akked Umazan iS, ass n êioo ameqwôaêan, ar Öebbi akked Umazan iS, kksen aêeppem i imcurak. "Ma testeôoâam, ppif i kunwi, ma twexxôem, cfut ar kunwi ur tesfunnugem i Öebbi". Becceô wid ijehlen s uâaqeb aqeôêan.'),
(1239, 9, 4, 'Kkes ed wid ukud tâaqqdem seg imcurak, sinna ur kwen bbwiven s wacemma, ur ullen yiwen mgal nnwen. Ïîfet di lemâahda nnsen ar lmudda s. Öebbi, s tidep, Iêemmel wid ipêezziben.'),
(1240, 9, 5, 'Mi âaddan wagguren iôqan, nna$et imcurak anda ten tufam. Ïîfet pen, êeôset pen, andit asen yal taxettalt. Ma steôoâan, ééulen, zekkan, ooet asen abrid. Öebbi, s tidep, Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu.'),
(1241, 9, 6, 'Ma issuter ak laânaya, yiwen seg imcurak, êareb fellas, ard issel i wawal n Öebbi, sinna, ssiwev it s amkan is n laman. Akka, acku nitni, s tidep, d agdud ur nessin.'),
(1242, 9, 7, 'Amek ara tili i imcurak, lemâahda s$uô Öebbi u s$uô Umazan iS, siwa wid tâahdem ar Loamaâ n Lêaôam. Skud sweqmen yidwen, sweqmet yidsen. Öebbi, s tidep, Iêemmel wid ipêezziben.'),
(1243, 9, 8, 'Amek, mi kwen $elben, ur kwen qudôen ilmend n yi$es, ne$ n lemâahda. Öuvan kwen s imawen nnsen; ulawen nnsen ugin. Tegwti segsen d iballa$en.'),
(1244, 9, 9, 'U$en s issekniyen n Öebbi ayen ôxisen. Ssefôa$en $ef ubrid iS. S tidep, ay dir wayen xeddmen nitni!'),
(1245, 9, 10, 'Ur qudôen lmumen ilmend n yi$es, ne$ n lemâahda. Wigi, ih, d wid izegren tilas.'),
(1246, 9, 11, 'Ma steôoâan, ééulen, zekkan, d atmaten nnwen di ddin. Nepfeûûil issekniyen i ugdud issnen.'),
(1247, 9, 12, 'Ma sêenten tagalit nnsen, deffir lemâahda nnsen, u wwten di ddin nnwen, nna$et iqweôôa n tijehli. Nitni, s tidep, ur ppaîafen di tgallit. Amar ad fukken.'),
(1248, 9, 13, 'Day ur tepna$em ara agdud i isêenten tagalit nnsen, u ib$an ad ssuff$en Amazan, u nitni heomen kwen d imezwura? Day ten tugadem? D Öebbi i iklalen a T tagwadem, ma d lmumnin ay tellam.'),
(1249, 9, 14, 'Nna$et pen, a ten Iâaqeb Öebbi s ufus nnwen, a ten Ixzu, a kwen Iserbeê fellasen, ad Icfu idmaren n ugdud n lmumnin.'),
(1250, 9, 15, 'Ad Ikkes urrif n wulawen nnsen. Öebbi Issuruf i win i S ihwan. Öebbi d Amusnaw, d Bab n ûûwab.'),
(1251, 9, 16, 'Day t$ilem a ppepwaterkem, wanag ur Iéôi Öebbi wid, degwen, ijuhden, ur neddi d imawlan, war Öebbi akked Umazan iS, akked lmumnin? Öebbi Iéôa ay txeddmem.'),
(1252, 9, 17, 'Ur issefk ara i imcurak ad kecmen leowamaâ n Öebbi, ad cehhden $ef tijehli nnsen. Widak neqven igiten nnsen, di tmes ad wekkôen.'),
(1253, 9, 18, 'Ara ikecmen kan leowamaâ n Öebbi, d wid iumnen s Öebbi akked wass aneggaru, iééulen, izekkan, ippagwaden siwa Öebbi. Ahat wigi ad ilin seg wid ipwanhan.'),
(1254, 9, 19, 'Day terram win i isswan iéaâlak, i ibedden i Loamaâ n Lêaôam, am win iumnen s Öebbi akked wass aneggaru u innu$ deg ubrid n Öebbi? Ur aâdilen ar Öebbi. Öebbi ur Inehhu agdud imednas.'),
(1255, 9, 20, 'Wid iumnen, iunagen, u nnu$en deg ubrid n Öebbi s wayla nnsen akked iman nnsen, aâlay umekkan nnsen, ar Öebbi. Wigi d wid ara irebêen.'),
(1256, 9, 21, 'Ibecceô iten Mass nnsen s uêunu s$uôeS, akked llza, akked leonanat, degsen ssaâd imezgi;'),
(1257, 9, 22, 'ad wekkôen degsen i lebda. Ih, ar Öebbi, arraz ameqwôaêan.'),
(1258, 9, 23, 'A wid iumnen! Ur pparat d imawlan, ibabaten nnwen akked watmaten nnwen, ma smenyafen tijehli i liman. Wid segwen i ten iran d imawlan, ad ilin, nitni, d imednas.'),
(1259, 9, 24, 'Ini: "maday, sennig Öebbi akked Umazan iS, akked umennu$ deg ubrid iS, ay têemmlem ibabaten nnwen, tarwa nnwen, atmaten nnwen, tilawin nnwen, alag nnwen, ayla i tkesbem, ttjaôa i tugadem a ppe$li, tinezdu$in i kwen iâaoben, ihi, gganit ar d Ias Öebbi, s lameô iS. Öebbi ur Inehhu agdud iballa$en.'),
(1260, 9, 25, 'Ni$ Isrebê ikwen Öebbi deg waîas imukan, akked wass n Ëunain, mi kwen taâoeb îîaqa nnwen. Ur awen d tebbwi acemma. Tamurt iwsâan, tu$al awen tediyeq. D$a tezzim d, trewlem.'),
(1261, 9, 26, 'Sinna, Issers ed Öebbi talwit iS $ef Umazan iS, akked lmumnin, Issers ed iâsekôiwen ur tepwalim. Iâaqeb wid ijehlen. D wagi ay d aqeîîi ijehliyen.'),
(1262, 9, 27, 'Sinna, deffir waya, Öebbi Issuruf i win i S ihwan. Öebbi Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu.'),
(1263, 9, 28, 'A wid iumnen! Imcurak maâfunit kan. Ur d pqeôôiben ar Loamaâ n Lêaôam, mara ifukk useggwas agi nnsen. Ma tugadem lqella, a kwen I$it Öebbi, s lfevl iS, ma ihwa yaS. Ih, Öebbi d Amusnaw, d Bab n ûûwab.'),
(1264, 9, 29, 'Nna$et wid ur numin ara s Öebbi, u s wass aneggaru, ur pgeddilen ayen Igdel Öebbi akked Umazan iS, ur xeddmen ddin n tidep, seg wid iwumi teppunefk Tezmamt, alamma xelûen tabzert s war amunnu, d imejjîuêen.'),
(1265, 9, 30, 'Nnan wudayen: "Âuzayeô d mmi S n Öebbi". Nnan imasiêiyen: "lmasiê d mmi S n Öebbi". Ayagi, nnan t id s imawen nnsen. Ppaâwaden d awal n wid ijehlen, n zik. A ten Ine$ Öebbi! Acêal îeôôifen!'),
(1266, 9, 31, 'Rran lquôôaê nnsen, ixelwiyen nnsen, lmasiê mmi s n Meryem, d imawlan war Öebbi. Pwamôen kan ad âabden Öebbi Yiwen; ur illi ôebbi siwa Neppa. Gedha syiS, seg wayen pcaraken!'),
(1267, 9, 32, 'B$an s yimawen nnsen ad ssexsin tafat n Öebbi. I Ib$a Öebbi, ad Itim kan tafat iS, di nneqwma ijehliyen.'),
(1268, 9, 33, 'D Neppa id Iuznen Amazan iS, s nnhaya akked ddin n tidep, iwakken a t Issifer $ef ddin meôôa, xas ugin ijehliyen.'),
(1269, 9, 34, 'A wid iumnen! Aîas n lqweôôaê d ixelwiyen, s tidep, teppen d aêerfi ayla n medden. U îeôôifen seg ubrid n Öebbi. Wid ixeznen ddheb d lfeîîa, ur ten pseddiqen deg ubrid n Öebbi, becceô iten s uâaqeb aqeôêan.'),
(1270, 9, 35, 'Ass ideg ara ô$en di tmes n Loahennama, ad kwin, yissen, inyiren nnsen, ibeôdiyen nnsen, iârar nnsen. "D ayagi ay txezznem i iman nnwen. Jeôôbet ayen txezznem!"'),
(1271, 9, 36, 'Ih, ar Öebbi, amvan n wagguren: mrawsin; di Tezmamt n Öebbi, ass ideg Ixleq tamurt akked igenwan. Garasen, kué ôqan. D wagi ay d ddin n ddwam. Ur ddenniset iman nnwen degsen. Nna$et ijehliyen $ef ccfa, akken i kwen nnu$en $ef ccfa. Cfut, Öebbi Iteddu d wid ipêezziben.'),
(1272, 9, 37, 'Aswexxeô n waggur d timerniwt kan n tijehli. Nnetlafen yis wid ijehlen. Aseggwas a t êellen, aseggwas a t gedlen, iwakken ad wafqen amvan n wayen Igdel Öebbi. Ad êellen ayen Igdel Öebbi. Âaoben ten yir igiten nnsen. Öebbi ur Inehhu agdud ijehliyen.'),
(1273, 9, 38, 'A wid iumnen! Acu kwen iu$en? Ma nnan awen: "hejjmet ar ubrid n Öebbi", a ppebrum i iman nnwen. Day kwen taâoeb tmeddurt n ddunit, sennig tin n laxeôt? Zzhu n tmeddurt n ddunit d amejîiîuê kan, zdat win n laxeôt.'),
(1274, 9, 39, 'Ma ur tehjjimem ara, a kwen Iâaqeb s lqeôê, a d Iawi agdud nniven, deg umekkan nnwen. Ur T teîîuôum s wacemma. Öebbi Izmer i yal cci.'),
(1275, 9, 40, 'Ma ur t tsellkem, ihi, Isellek it Öebbi, mi t ssuff$en wid ijehlen. Wissin n sin, mi llan deg ifri, mi inna i umeddakwel is: "kkes a$wbel, Öebbi, s tidep, yidne$". Issers ed Öebbi talwit iS fellas, Iâawen it s iâsekriwen, ur ten twalam. Isse$li mavi awal n wid ijehlen. Awal n Öebbi, neppa, aâlay sennig akw. Öebbi d Uzmir, d Bab n ûûwab.'),
(1276, 9, 41, 'Hejjmet fessusit u ééayit, juhdet s wayla nnwen akked yiman nnwen, deg ubrid n Öebbi. Ppif wakka i kunwi, lemmer teéôim.'),
(1277, 9, 42, 'Lemmer d aba$uô isehlen, d inig wezzilen, yili vefôen k in. Maca, $wezzif fellasen umecwaô. Ad ggalen s Öebbi: "lemmer nezmir, yili neffe$ yidwen". Nn$an iman nnsen, Öebbi Iéôa ar nitni, war ccekk, d ikeddaben.'),
(1278, 9, 43, 'Ad ak Isemmeê Öebbi! Acimi i sen tserêev? Ard ak d iban anwi innan tidep, a ppissinev ikeddaben.'),
(1279, 9, 44, 'Ur ak d ssutren ara tsriê, wid iumnen s Öebbi akked wass aneggaru, mi juhden s wayla nnsen akked yiman nnsen. Öebbi Issen wid ipêezziben.'),
(1280, 9, 45, 'I k issutren tsriê, d wid ur numin s Öebbi akked wass aneggaru. Cukken wulawen nnsen, d$a, s ucukku nnsen, kukran.'),
(1281, 9, 46, 'Lemmer b$in tuff$a, yili heggan as d ayen ilaqen. Maca, Iugi Öebbi ad ppucegâan, Iurez iten. Nnan asen: "qqimet d wid iqqimen".'),
(1282, 9, 47, 'Lemmer ffi$en yidwen, ar awen rnun siwa ccwal. War ccekk, ad kecmen garawen, b$an ahewwel nnwen. Kra segwen ssemêasen asen. Öebbi Issen imednas.'),
(1283, 9, 48, 'Ni$ b$an, si zik, ahewwel. Sxeôben ak lumuô, armi d tusa tidep. Ivehô ed lameô n Öebbi, nitni ur b$in.'),
(1284, 9, 49, 'Garasen win id innan: "serreê iyi, ur iyi gar di lfetna"! Day ur $lin ara di lfetna? Loahennama, s tidep, a ppezzi i ijehliyen.'),
(1285, 9, 50, 'Ma iusa k id yise$ ad $weblen. Ma tusa k id twa$it, ad inin: "ni$, iu$ lêal, neqva lameô nne$". Ad wexxôen, zzhan.'),
(1286, 9, 51, 'Ini: "ur a$ ipêaz wacemma, siwa ayen i $ Iura Öebbi". Neppa d Bab nne$. £ef Öebbi ara ppeklen lmumnin.'),
(1287, 9, 52, 'Ini: "acu teggunim ad ivôu yidne$, siwa yiwen si sin ise$iyen? Nekwni negguni a kwen Iwwet Öebbi, s uâaqeb ara d iasen s$uôeS, ne$ seg ifassen nne$. Ihi gganit, nekwni a neggani yidwen".'),
(1288, 9, 53, 'Ini: "seddqet, teb$am ne$ tugim, d ayen ur neppwaqbal segwen, d awez$i. Kunwi, s tidep, d agdud iballa$en".'),
(1289, 9, 54, 'Ay sen ikksen a tepwaqbal ssadaqa nnsen, imi kan jehlen, s tidep, ar Öebbi akked Umazan iS, u s laâgez kan ay d ppasen ar tpéallit, s usmiglez kan ay pseddiqen.'),
(1290, 9, 55, 'Ur k ippaâoab wayla nnsen, ne$ tarwa nnsen. Ib$a kan Öebbi a ten Iâaqeb yissen di tmeddurt n ddunit, ad iffe$ ôôuê nnsen, nitni d ijehliyen.'),
(1291, 9, 56, 'Ad ggalen s Öebbi, ar nitni, war ccekk, segwen. Ur nitni segwen, maca d agdud iugaden.'),
(1292, 9, 57, 'Lemmer ad afen ssôan, ne$ ifran, ne$ anda ara kecmen, ad ôuêen $uôes s tazla.'),
(1293, 9, 58, 'Garasen, wid ikkaten deg k, $ef ssadaqat. Ma ippunefk asen segsent, ad ôavin, ma ur asen ippunefk, ad neêwen.'),
(1294, 9, 59, 'Lemmer nitni, s tidep, ôuvan ayen i sen Ifka Öebbi akked Umazan iS, u nnan d: "nesteqnaâ s Öebbi. Ad a$ d Ifk, si lfevl iS, Öebbi akked Umazan iS. Ih, d Öebbi i$ef neô$eb".'),
(1295, 9, 60, 'Ssadaqat siwa i ime$ban, iéawaliyen, i wid ice$wlen degsent, i usemlili n wulawen, i userreê imeêbas, i imeîîulba, i ubrid n Öebbi, i win d ifka ubrid. D aêeppem s$uô Öebbi. Öebbi d Amusnaw, d Bab n ûûwab.'),
(1296, 9, 61, 'Garasen, wid icettmen deg Umazan, qqaôen: "neppa d aêessas". Ini: "d aêessas n lxiô i kunwi. Iumen s Öebbi, iumen lmumnin. D aêunu i wid iumnen segwen". I wid icettmen deg Umazan n Öebbi, aâaqeb aqeôêan.'),
(1297, 9, 62, 'Ad awen ggalen s Öebbi, iwakken a kwen ôavin. Öebbi akked Umazan iS, Iklal kteô a T ôavin, lemmer llin d lmumnin.'),
(1298, 9, 63, 'Day ur éôin ara ar, win ixuûmen Öebbi akked Umazan iS, i neppa times n Loahennama, ad iwekkeô degs? D wagi ay d ddell abarar.'),
(1299, 9, 64, 'Ixabiten ugaden ad asen d ters tsuôep, ad asen tessken i illan deg ulawen nnsen. Ini: "mmaâlket. Öebbi, s tidep, a d Issuffe$ ayen tugadem".'),
(1300, 9, 65, 'Ma testeqsav ten, a d inin, war ccekk: "la nheddeô kan, nepqessiô". Ini: "day la tettihim di Öebbi akked issekniyen iS, akked Umazan iS?'),
(1301, 9, 66, 'Ur steôoiâat. Ni$ tu$alem ar tijehli, deffir liman nnwen". Ma Nsemmeê i urbaâ segwen, a Naâqeb arbaâ, imi nitni llan d ibe$wviyen.'),
(1302, 9, 67, 'Ixabiten akked txabitin, wa ippameô i wa, ayen n dir, ppemyegdalen lewqama, pcuddun ifassen nnsen. Ppun Öebbi, Ippu ten. Ih, ixabiten d iballa$en.'),
(1303, 9, 68, 'Iwaââed Öebbi, i ixabiten, txabitin, akked ijehliyen, times n Loahennama, degs ad wekkôen. Beôka ten. Ixza ten Öebbi. Fellasen aâaqeb imezgi,'),
(1304, 9, 69, 'am imezwura nnwen. Llan ifen kwen tazmert, $elben kwen ayla, tarwa. Zhan deg umur nnsen, tezham deg umur nnwen, akken zhan imezwura nnwen deg umur nnsen. Teccvem akken ccven nitni. Widak, mêan igiten nnsen di ddunit, di laxeôt. Widak d imexsuôen.'),
(1305, 9, 70, 'Day ur ten id iusa ara usali imezwura nnsen? Agdud n Nuê, Âad, Tamud, agdud n Ibôahim, At Median, tid ippin. Usan ten id imazanen nnsen, s ubeggen. Ur ten Idennis Öebbi, maca llan dennisen iman nnsen.'),
(1306, 9, 71, 'Lmumnin, argaz tameîîut, d imeddukal wa n wa. Ppamôen lewqama, pgeddilen ayen n dir. Péallan, pzekkin, ppa$en awal i Öebbi akked Umazan iS. Wigi, ad Iêun Öebbi fellasen. Ih, Öebbi d Uzmir, d Bab n ûûwab.'),
(1307, 9, 72, 'Iwaââed Öebbi i lmumnin, argaz tameîîut, leonanat, ddawat sen isaffen ppazzalen, ad wekkôen degsen; ixxamen igerzen di leonanat n Âaden, akked llza s$uô Öebbi - iten i$elben akw -. D wagi ay d rrbeê ameqwôaêan.'),
(1308, 9, 73, 'A Nnbi! Jahed ijehliyen akked ixabiten. Iqsiê $uôsen. Axxam nnsen d Loahennama, d taggara tucmip!'),
(1309, 9, 74, 'Ggulen s Öebbi ur d nnin, wanag nnan awal n tijehli. Jehlen deffir wannuz nnsen. Vemâen ayen iwumi ur wâan. Ur êzinen imi iten I$at, si lfevl iS, Öebbi akked Umazan iS. Ma steôoâen, yif it i nitni. Ma wexxôen, a ten Iâaqeb Öebbi s leqôeê, di ddunit, di laxeôt. Ur sâun, di tmurt, bab ne$ amâiwen.'),
(1310, 9, 75, 'Garasen, wid iâahden Öebbi: "ma Ifka ya$ d, si lfevl iS, a nseddeq, a nili si lâuûam".'),
(1311, 9, 76, 'Mi sen Ifka si lfevl iS, a t bexwlen, ad wexxôen, ad namren.'),
(1312, 9, 77, 'Issegwra yasen d tanaâuôt deg ulawen nnsen, ar ass ideg ara mlilen yideS, imi xed$an Öebbi deg wayen i S âahden, imi llan skiddiben.'),
(1313, 9, 78, 'Day ur éôin ara Öebbi Issen sser nnsen akked wayen qqaôen u, ar Öebbi Issen tibavniyin?'),
(1314, 9, 79, 'Wid ipqeôôiven di lmumnin i ib$an ad seddqen, u deg wid i iufan siwa tazmert nnsen, d$a ttihin fellasen; ad Ittihi Öebbi fellasen. Fellasen aâaqeb aqeôêan.'),
(1315, 9, 80, 'Ssuter ad ppusemmêen, ne$ qqim. Ma tessutrev ûavet iberdan, ur sen Ipsemmiê Öebbi, d awez$i. Akka, imi nitni jehlen ar Öebbi akked Umazan iS. Öebbi ur Inehhu agdud iballa$en.'),
(1316, 9, 81, 'Wid igwran, feôêen mi llan deffir Umazan n Öebbi. Ugin ad nna$en s wayla nnsen akked teôwiêt nnsen, deg ubrid n Öebbi. Nnan: "Ur pôuêut deg una$uô". Ini: "times n Loahennama teêma kteô, lemmer day fehhmen".'),
(1317, 9, 82, 'Anef ad vsen cwiî, ad run aîas, d aqeîîi n wayen keppben.'),
(1318, 9, 83, 'Ma Irra k id Öebbi ar urbaâ segsen, u ssutren ak d tsriê ad ff$en, ini: "d awez$i, ur teppeff$em yidi, ur tepna$em acengu yidi. Akken, kunwi, iâoeb ikwen i$imi, abrid amenzu, ihi, qqimet akked ineggura.'),
(1319, 9, 84, 'Ur péalla $ef yiwen degsen, ma immut, d awez$i. Ur pbedda ar tenîelt is. Nitni, s tidep, jehlen ar Öebbi akked Umazan iS, mmuten nitni d iballa$en.'),
(1320, 9, 85, 'Ur k ippaâoab wayla nnsen, ne$ dderya nnsen. Öebbi Ib$a kan a ten Iâaqeb yissen di ddunit, ad asen teffe$ taôwiêt nitni d ijehliyen.'),
(1321, 9, 86, 'Ma ters ed tsuôep: "amnet s Öebbi, jahdet akked Umazan iS", imeôkantiyen nnsen a k ssutren tsriê, ad inin: "anef ane$ ar wid iqqimen".'),
(1322, 9, 87, 'Öuvan ad ilin akked wid igwran. Ppusel$en wulawen nnsen, ur fehhmen.'),
(1323, 9, 88, 'Maca, amazan akked wid iumnen yides, jehden s wayla nnsen akked yiman nnsen. Widak, nnsen lxiô. Widak, d nitni ara irebêen.'),
(1324, 9, 89, 'Ihegga yasen d Öebbi leonanat, ddawat sen isaffen ppazzalen, degsen ad wekkôen. D wagi ay d rrbeê ameqwôaêan.'),
(1325, 9, 90, 'Wid id iufan ssebba, seg waâôaben n ucluê, usan d, ad asen ifk tsriê. Wid iskaddben Öebbi akked Umazan iS, qqimen. Wid ijehlen, segsen, ad sâaddin aâaqeb aqeôêan.'),
(1326, 9, 91, 'Ur telli tuzzma $ef uôhifen, imuvan, wid ur nufi ara fken, ma neûêen ar Öebbi akked Umazan iS. Ur telli tuzzma $ef iâaôviyen. Öebbi Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu.'),
(1327, 9, 92, 'Am akken, i wid ik id iusan a ten tneqqlev, tenniv: "ur awen ufi$ ara kwen ineqqlen". U$alen, allen feggvent seg imeîîawen, $weblen imi ur ufin ara sedqen.'),
(1328, 9, 93, 'Tuzzma kan $ef wid ik issuturen tsriê, nitni d imeôkantiyen. Öuvan ad ilin akked ineggura. Isle$ Öebbi ulawen nnsen, d$a ur ssinen.'),
(1329, 9, 94, 'Ad awen ssutren ssmaê, ma tu$alem d $uôsen. Ini: "ur ssuturet ssmaê, ur kwen numin d awez$i. Ni$ Imla ya$ Öebbi asali nnwen. Ad Iéeô Öebbi akked Umazan iS, igiten nnwen. Sinna, a ppu$alem ar Umusnaw n wayen iffren akked wayen ur neffir, ad awen Imel ayen txeddmem".'),
(1330, 9, 95, 'Ad awen gren Öebbi, mi d tu$alem $uôsen, iwakken ad asen tanfem. Wexxeôt asen; nitni, s tidep, d laâôuô; axxam nnsen d Loahennama, d aqeîîi n wayen keppben.'),
(1331, 9, 96, 'Ad awen ggalen iwakken a ten tôavim. Ma tôuvam ten, ihi, Öebbi ur Ipôavi agdud iballa$en.'),
(1332, 9, 97, 'Aâôaben n ucluê zaden di tijehli akked nnxayel, zeggwiren ar uzgar n tilas id Issers Öebbi i Umazan iS. Öebbi d Amusnaw, d Bab n ûûwab.'),
(1333, 9, 98, 'Ger waâôaben n ucluê, wid iêesben ayen seddqen d tabzert. Ggunin a ppekêes fellawen teswiât. Fellasen abeddel adiran n teswiât! Öebbi Issel, Issen.'),
(1334, 9, 99, 'Ger waâôaben n ucluê, wid iumnen s Öebbi d wass aneggaru, êesben ayen seddqen a ten iééié ar Öebbi akked téilla Umazan. Day maççi, s tidep, d ayen ara ten iééiéen? A ten Issekcem Öebbi deg uêunu S. Öebbi, s tidep, Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu.'),
(1335, 9, 100, 'Imenza i izwaren, seg iminigen, imâiwnen, akked wid i ten iâanden ar lewqama, Iôuva ten Öebbi, ôuvan T. Ihegga yasen d leonanat, ddawat sen isaffen ppazzalen, ad wekkôen degsen, i lebda. D wagi ay d rrbeê ameqwôaêan.'),
(1336, 9, 101, 'Ger waâôaben n ucluê, i wen d izzin, llan at sin wudmawen, akw ger imezda$ n Lmadina. Zgan di nnxayel. Ur ten tessinev. Nekwni, Nessen iten. A ten Nâaqeb berdayen, sinna, ad ppunefken i uâaqeb abarar.'),
(1337, 9, 102, 'Wiyad qaôôen s ibekkaven nnsen, ssemlalen igi ilhan d win nniven icemten. Izmer Öebbi ad asen Issuref. S tidep, Öebbi Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu.'),
(1338, 9, 103, 'Eddem ed ssadaqa seg wayla nnsen, a ten tezzizdeg, a ten tûeffi. èÈéal ilmend nnsen. Ih, tiéilla k d talwit nnsen. Öebbi Issel, d Amusnaw.'),
(1339, 9, 104, 'Day ur éôin ara Öebbi, Neppa, Iqebbel asteôoaâ s$uô ixdimen iS? Ippaîaf ssadaqat. Ih, Öebbi Issuruf, Ipêunu.'),
(1340, 9, 105, 'Ini: "xedmet! Ad Iwali igiten nnwen, Öebbi, Umazan iS, akked lmumnin. Tu$alin nnwen ar Umusnaw n wayen iffren akked wayen ur neffir, ad awen Imel ayen txeddmem".'),
(1341, 9, 106, 'Wiyav pganin lameô n Öebbi, a ten Iâaqeb, ne$ ad asen Issuref. Öebbi d Amusnaw, d Bab n ûûwab.'),
(1342, 9, 107, 'Wid irran loamaâ i lemveôôa akked tijehli, i lefôaq ger lmumnin; d taxettalt i wid, iu$ lêal, llan pna$en Öebbi akked Umazan iS, ad ggalen, war ccekk: "ay neb$a siwa lewqama". Ad Icehhed Öebbi ar nitni, s tidep, d ikeddaben.'),
(1343, 9, 108, 'Ur ppili, degs, d awez$i. Iklal kteô, tilin ik, loamaâ ibnan $ef uêezzeb, seg wass amenzu. Degs irgazen i iêemmlen ad izdigen. Öebbi Iêemmel izedganen.'),
(1344, 9, 109, 'Day win issersen lebni s $ef uêezzeb i Öebbi akked llza, ur yif ara win issersen lebni s $ef rrif n ucôuf ara iseggxen? Iseggex yis ar tmes n Loahennama. Öebbi ur Inehhu agdud imednas.'),
(1345, 9, 110, 'Izga lebni, bnan, ippara ccekk deg ulawen nnsen, alamma gezmen wulawen nnsen. Öebbi d Amusnaw, d Bab n ûûwab.'),
(1346, 9, 111, 'Ih, Öebbi Iu$ ar lmumnin, iman nnsen akked wayla nnsen, imi Loennet i nitni. Pna$en deg ubrid n Öebbi. Nn$an, pwan$an. D lemâahda fellas, s tidep, di Tuôa, di Linoil akked Leqwôan. Anwa yifen Öebbi di tuîîfa n lemâahda s? Feôêet, ihi, di ssuq tsewwqem. Wagi d rrbeê ameqwôaêan.'),
(1347, 9, 112, 'Wid isteôoâen, wid iâabden, wid ipcekkiôen, ixelwiyen, wid iîîinizen, wid ikennun, wid ippamôen lewqama, wid ipgeddilen ayen n dir, wid ipêaraben $ef tlisa n Öebbi ... Becceô lmumnin.'),
(1348, 9, 113, 'Ur issefk ara i Nnbi akked wid iumnen, ad ssutren ad pwasemmêen imcurak, xas ppilin asen, ma iban asen d ar, nitni, war ccekk, d at tmes.'),
(1349, 9, 114, 'Ibôahim ur issuter ara ad ipwasemmeê baba s, siwa ilmend n lemâahda i s ifka. Mi s d iban ar neppa d acengu n Öebbi, ifra p yides. Ibôahim, war ccekk, ippanez, iêellem.'),
(1350, 9, 115, 'Ur p Ixeddem Öebbi, ad Itlef agdud mbaâd ma Inha ten, alamma i sen Ibeggen acu ara êezzben. Öebbi, s tidep, Issen yal cci.'),
(1351, 9, 116, 'Ih, Öebbi, IneS tagelda n tmurt akked igenwan, Issidir, Ineqq. Ur awen illi, war Öebbi, bab ne$ amâiwen.'),
(1352, 9, 117, 'Ni$ Issuref Öebbi i Nnbi akked iminigen, akked imâiwnen i iddan yides, di lweqt uwâiô, mbaâd ma qôib nneqlaben wulawen n urbaâ segsen. Sinna, Issuref asen. Ih, Neppa, i nitni, dUmâin, d\'Aênin.'),
(1353, 9, 118, 'U i krav id igwran, armi, tamurt iwsâan, tediyyeq fellasen. Vaqen deg iman nnsen. Ufan ur illi ssôan si Öebbi, siwa Neppa. Sinna, Issuref asen, akken ad steôoâen. Öebbi, s tidep, Issuruf, Ipêunu.'),
(1354, 9, 119, 'A wid iumnen! Ëezzbet i Öebbi, ilit seg imawlan n tidep.'),
(1355, 9, 120, 'Ur issefk ara i imezda$ n Lmadina, d wayen i sen d izzin n waâôaben n ucluê, ad gwrin deffir Umazan n Öebbi, ne$ ad smenyafen iman nnsen i iman is. Ayagi, acku ur ten ipêaz fad, ne$ âaggu, ne$ llaé, deg ubrid n Öebbi. Ur keçmen akal ara isserfun ijehliyen, ur ppaîîafen acemma s$uô ucengu, siwa ma dayen i sen iuran d igi n wayen ilhan. Öebbi, s tidep, ur Isôuêu arraz iâaôviyen.'),
(1356, 9, 121, 'Ur pûeôôifen cwiî ne$ aîas, ur zeggren asif, siwa ma iura yasen, iwakken a ten Ikafi Öebbi $ef wayen ilhan deg wayen xeddmen.'),
(1357, 9, 122, 'Ur Issefk ara i lmumnin ad ff$en akw. Awufan ad iffe$ ugraw si yal arbaâ, ad $bun di ddin, ad nabin agdud nnsen, mara u$alen $uôsen. Amar ad steêdren.'),
(1358, 9, 123, 'A wid iumnen! Nna$et ijehliyen i kwen iqeôben. Ad afen, $uôwen, teqseê. Cfut, Öebbi Ippili d wid ipêezziben.'),
(1359, 9, 124, 'Mi d ters tsuôep, llan garasen wid iqqaôen: "anwa degwen, iwumi terna tagi, di liman"? Ma d wid iumnen, terna yasen liman, u nitni feôêen.'),
(1360, 9, 125, 'Ma d wid iwumi blan wulawen, terna ammus i wammus nnsen. Mmuten u nitni d ijehliyen.'),
(1361, 9, 126, 'Day ur walan ara, ar nitni la d sskaren lfetna, yal aseggwas, yiwen ubrid ne$ berdayen? Sinna, ur steôoiâen, ur d smektayen.'),
(1362, 9, 127, 'Mi d ters tsuôep, ad mesmuqalen: "day illa yiwen ikwen id Ipwalin"? Sinna, ad wexxôen. Isswexxeô Öebbi ulawen nnsen, imi nitni d agdud ur nfehhem.'),
(1363, 9, 128, 'Ni$ iusa kwen id Umazan seg iman nnwen. èéay fellas laâtab nnwen. Ipêarab fellawen, d umâin, d aênin i lmumnin.'),
(1364, 9, 129, 'Ma wexxôen, ini: "Iqadd iyi Öebbi. Ur illi ôebbi siwa Neppa. FellaS ppekle$. Neppa d Mass n usgeld ameqwôaêan.');
INSERT INTO `ber_mensur` (`index`, `sura`, `aya`, `text`) VALUES
(1365, 10, 1, 'Alô, wigi d issekniyen n Tezmamt tuûwibt.'),
(1366, 10, 2, 'Day d lwehma, i medden, ma Nweêêa n i urgaz nnsen: "nabi imdanen, becceô wid iumnen ar ad afen arraz umâin ar Mass nnsen"? Nnan ijehliyen: "wagi, s tidep, d aseêêar n ûûeê".'),
(1367, 10, 3, 'Ih, Mass nnwen d Öebbi, i Ixelqen tamurt akked igenwan di sdis wussan. Sinna, Iâannec $ef usgeld, Iseyyi lameô. Ur illi umcafaâ siwa ma Iâammed as. D wagi ay d Öebbi, Mass nnwen. Ihi, âabdet eP. Day ur d tesmektayem ara?'),
(1368, 10, 4, '£uôeS akw tu$alin nnwen. Lemâahda n Öebbi d tidep. Ih, Inezzu axlaq, Ippales, iwakken ad Ikafi wid iumnen u xeddmen ayen ilhan, s lmizan. I wid ijehlen, tissit iô$an, aâaqeb aqeôêan, imi llan jehlen.'),
(1369, 10, 5, 'D Neppa i Irran iîij d lefnaô, aggur d tafat. Iwezn as tiswaâin, iwakken a ppissinem amvan iseggwasen, akked leêsab. Ur Ixliq Öebbi ayagi, siwa s tidep. Ipfeûûil issekniyen i ugdud issnen.'),
(1370, 10, 6, 'S tidep, di lemgarda ger yiv akked wass, akked wayen Ixleq Öebbi di tmurt akked igenwan, ard issekniyen i ugdud i ipêezziben.'),
(1371, 10, 7, 'Ih, wid ur negguni ara timlilit yidne£, i tqennaâ tmeddurt di ddunit, u rekden degs, d wid i istehzan $ef issekniyen nne£.'),
(1372, 10, 8, 'Wigi, axxam nnsen di tmes, ilmend n wayen keppben.'),
(1373, 10, 9, 'Ih, wid iumnen u xeddmen ayen ilhan, a ten Inhu Mass nnsen, s liman nnsen. Ad ppazzalen isaffen seddawat sen, di leonanat isaâdiyen.'),
(1374, 10, 10, 'Anuju nnsen degs: "gedha s yissek a Öebbi"! Azul nnsen d: "tifrat". Anuju nnsen aneggaru: "ccekôan i Öebbi, Mass imavalen".'),
(1375, 10, 11, 'Lemmer ad Iaâoel Öebbi cceôô ar imdanen, akken nitni êaren $ef lxiô, yili ibbwev asen lajel nnsen. A Nanef i wid ur negguni ara timlilit yidne£, ad ddebdben di lbe$wv nnsen.'),
(1376, 10, 12, 'Amdan, ma iêuza t ccqa, ad a£ £ d isiwel, iééel, iqqim ne$ ibedd. Mi s Nekkes ccqa s, ad iteddu amzun ur d inuj $uône£ilmend n ccqa i t iêuzan. Akka ay ppucebêen igiten nnsen i imaâfan.'),
(1377, 10, 13, 'Ni$ Nesqucc isuta, uqbel nnwen, imi densen. Ussan d $uôsen imazanen nnsen, s ubeggen, ur llin d wid ara iamnen. Akka ay Nepqeîîi agdud ibe$wviyen.'),
(1378, 10, 14, 'Sinna, Nerra kwen d igensas di tmurt, deffir sen, a Nwali amek ara txedmem.'),
(1379, 10, 15, 'Ma $ôan asen issekniyen nne£ iberrzen, wid ur negguni ara timlilit yidne£, ad inin: "awi d Leqwôan nniven, ne$ beddel it". Ini: "ur felli a t beddle$, s leb$i n yiman iw. Teddu$ kan akked wayen iyi d ippuweêêan. Nek ugade$, ma xedâa$ Mass iw, aâaqeb n wass ameqwôaêan".'),
(1380, 10, 16, 'Ini: "lemmer i S ihwi i Öebbi, ur awen t id mli$, ur awen t id mmekti$. Ni$ zed$e$ yidwen tameddurt, uqbel is. Day ur tfehmem ara"?'),
(1381, 10, 17, 'Anwa i idensen kteô, ger win id igren tikerkas $ef Öebbi, ne$ win inekôen issekniyen iS? Ih, ur rebêen ibe$wviyen.'),
(1382, 10, 18, 'La âabden, war Öebbi, ayen ur ten neîîuôu, ur ten nenfaâ. La qqaôen: "wigi d imcafâen nne$ ar Öebbi". Ini: "day a pxebbôem Öebbi $ef wayen ur Issin, di tmurt akked igenwan"? Gedha s yiS! I Aâlay sennig wayen pcaraken!'),
(1383, 10, 19, 'Llan imdanen d yiwen n lois kan. Sinna, mgaraden. Lemmer ur d izwar ara wawal, s$uô Mass ik, ad yili uêuddu, garasen, $ef wayen i$ef mgaraden.'),
(1384, 10, 20, 'La qqaôen: "a lemmer id irs $uôes ussekni n Mass is"! Ini: "tabavnit ar Öebbi kan. Ihi, gganit. Nek, yidwen, seg wid iggunin".'),
(1385, 10, 21, 'Ma Nesêess i imdanen aêunu, deffir twa$it i ten iêuzan, atnan la ppandin i issekniyen nne£. Ini: "Öebbi Yif akw akken Ip$awal di tiêeôci". Imersulen nne£, s tidep, pparun ayen teppandim.'),
(1386, 10, 22, 'Neppa i kwen Ippawin di lberr, di yill. Alamma, mi tellam di lembwabeô, teppedum degsen s wavu uûwib, feôêen yis, tusa d tbucivant $uôsen, ppasent ed lemwao $uôsen, si yal tama, êulfan a d tezzi fellasen. Naâôen Öebbi, s lqaâida i Neppa: "ma Tsellkev a$ si tagi, ar a nili seg wid isnemmiren".'),
(1387, 10, 23, 'Mi ten Isellek, imiren u$alen be$wven di tmurt, war ssebba. A yimdanen! Lbe$wv nnwen, siwa $ef yiman nnwen. Zzhu di tmeddurt n ddunit, sinna, $uône£ tu$alin nnwen, ad awen Nmel ayen txeddmem.'),
(1388, 10, 24, 'Amedya n tmeddurt di ddunit, am aman kan. Nesse$li ten id seg igenni, xelven akked im$an n tmurt, iseg teppen imdanen akked lmal. Mi tcebbeê tmurt, tu$al d tuzyint, $ilen, imezda$ is, ar deg ufus nnsen ay tella. Iusa p id lameô nne£, deg iv, ne$ deg wass, Nerra p d ahicuô, amzun ur teoouoeg ass izeryen. Akka ay Nfeûûel issekniyen i ugdud ipxemmimen.'),
(1389, 10, 25, 'Inecced Öebbi s axxam n tifrat. Inehhu win i S ihwan, ar ubrid uwqim.'),
(1390, 10, 26, 'I wid iweqmen, lewqama, ternuv as. Udmawen nnsen, ur ten ipnal bufsus, ne$ ddell. Widak, d at Loennet, nitni, degs ad wekkôen.'),
(1391, 10, 27, 'Aqeîîi n wid id ibbwin tucmitin, d tucmip itent icban. Ad ndellen. Ur sâun amenêul ar Öebbi. Amzun $ummen wudmawen nnsen, s ccevyat n yiv iberkanen. Widak d at tmes, nitni, degs, ad wekkôen.'),
(1392, 10, 28, 'Ass ideg ara ten Nfesser akw, a Nini, imiren, i wid icurken: "imukan nnwen, kunwi akked icriken nnwen"! Sinna Nessemfaôaq iten. A d inin, icriken nnsen: "maççi d nekwni ay tâabdem.'),
(1393, 10, 29, 'Ad Iqadd Öebbi, d Anagi garane$ yidwen, ar ur d necliâ deg uâbbed nnwen".'),
(1394, 10, 30, 'Din, yal amdan ad iwali ayen iwasa. Ad u$alen ar Öebbi, Bab nnsen n tidep. Itelf iten wayen d snulfuyen.'),
(1395, 10, 31, 'Ini: "anwa ikwen Ip$itin seg igenni akked tmurt? Anwa ay d Bab n tmejjin akked yiéôi? Anwa id Issuffu$en amuddir si lmegget, id Issuffu$en lmegget seg umuddir? Anwa i Iseyyin lameô"? A d inin: "d Öebbi". Ini: "ihi, day ur tepêezzibem ara"?'),
(1396, 10, 32, 'D wagi ay d Öebbi, Mass nnwen n tidep. Deffir tidep, acu i illan, siwa ttelfan? Ihi, acimi texdâam?'),
(1397, 10, 33, 'Akka i iûaô wawal n Mass ik, $ef wid ixedmen tucmitin. Ih, nitni ur ppamnen.'),
(1398, 10, 34, 'Ini: "day illa ger icriken nnwen, win id inzan lxelq, sinna, iules as d"? Ini: "Öebbi inezzu lxelq, sinna, Ippales as d. Ihi, amek ara twexxôem"?'),
(1399, 10, 35, 'Ini: "day illa, ger icriken nnwen, win i inehhun ar tidep"? Ini: "Öebbi Inehhu ar tidep. Win Inehhun ar tidep, day ur Yif ara, akken Iklal tikli yideS, win ur nennehhu, siwa ma ipwanha? Acu ikwen iu$en? Amek tepseyyim"?'),
(1400, 10, 36, 'Tegwti, segsen, teddun kan d nnwaya. Nnwaya, war ccekk, ur tebbwi acemma si tidep. Ih, Öebbi Issen acu xeddmen.'),
(1401, 10, 37, 'Leqwôan agi ur d innulfa ara, war Öebbi. Maca, d atebbet n wayen it id izwaren, d afeûûel n Tezmamt, ur degs ccekk, s$uô Mass imavalen.'),
(1402, 10, 38, 'Ne$ la qqaôen: "isnulfa t id". Ini: "awit ed tasuôep i t icban, neccdet seg wanda tzemrem, war Öebbi, ma tessawalem tidep".'),
(1403, 10, 39, 'Xaîi, skaddben ayen ur nekcim di tmusni nnsen, ur ten id iusi usefhem is. Akka ay skaddben, wid i ten id izwaren. Wali, ihi, amek tevôa d imednas.'),
(1404, 10, 40, 'Garasen, wid iumnen yis; garasen, wid ur numin yis. Mass ik Yif akw akken Issen ifessaden.'),
(1405, 10, 41, 'Ma skaddben k, ini: "i nek igiten iw, i kunwi igiten nnwen. Ur teppkam deg wayen xedme$, ur ppka$ deg wayen txedmem".'),
(1406, 10, 42, 'Garasen, llan wid i k issemêasen. Day tzemrev a pperrev ad slen iâeééugen, ma llan ur fehhmen?'),
(1407, 10, 43, 'Garasen, llan wid i k ipmuqulen. Day tzemrev a ppenhuv ider$alen, ma llan ur pwalin?'),
(1408, 10, 44, 'Öebbi, s tidep, ur Iddennis imdanen, s wacemma, maca imdanen densen iman nnsen.'),
(1409, 10, 45, 'Ass ideg ara ten Ifser, amzun sâaddan kan saâa n wass, ad msaâqalen. Ni$ xesôen wid iskaddben timlilit d Öebbi. Ur pwanhan.'),
(1410, 10, 46, 'Ad ak Nessken kra seg wayen i sen Nâahed, ne$ a k id Nawi $uône£. Ihi, $uône£ tu$alin nnsen. Sinna, Öebbi d Anagi n wayen xeddmen.'),
(1411, 10, 47, 'I yal lois, amazan. Ma iusa d umazan nnsen, a ppefru garasen s lmizan, ur pwadensen.'),
(1412, 10, 48, 'Qqaôen: "melmi lemâahda agi, ma tessawalem tidep?'),
(1413, 10, 49, 'Ini: "ur mlike$ i iman iw vveôô, ne$ aba$uô, siwa ayen Ib$a Öebbi. Yal lois s lajel is". Ma iusa d lajel nnsen, ur t swexxiôen s saâa, ur t id sseqôaben.'),
(1414, 10, 50, 'Ini: "acu twalam, ma iusa kwen id uâaqeb iS, deg iv, ne$ deg wass? Acimi êaren $uôeS ibe$wviyen?'),
(1415, 10, 51, 'D$a, ma iusa d, a ppamnem yis? Tura, aql akwen t$eûbem fellas".'),
(1416, 10, 52, 'Sinna, ad asen inin i wid idensen: "jeôôbet aâaqeb n lebda. Ma teppuqeîîan siwa kan $ef wayen tkeppbem"?'),
(1417, 10, 53, 'Steqsayen k: "d tidep ayagi"? Ini: "ih, s Mass iw, ar ayagi d tidep! Kunwi ur tezmirem i usfunneg".'),
(1418, 10, 54, 'Xas ad isâu, yal amdan idensen, i illan di tmurt, ur d ifeddu yis. Ffren nndama mi walan aâaqeb. Aêuddu garasen, s lmizan, ur pwadensen.'),
(1419, 10, 55, 'Day, s tidep, maççi n Öebbi i illan di tmurt akked igenwan? Ih, day lemâahda n Öebbi maççi d tidep? Maca, tegwti segsen ur ssinen.'),
(1420, 10, 56, 'Neppa Issidir, Ineqq. £uôeS ara tu$alem.'),
(1421, 10, 57, 'A yimdanen! Ni$ iusa kwen id unabi s$uô Mass nnwen, akked ccfa n wayen iblan ulawen, akked nnhaya, akked uêunu i lmumnin.'),
(1422, 10, 58, 'Ini: "s lfevl n Öebbi akked uêunu S, s waya, xas ad feôêen". Yif ayen pkemmimen.'),
(1423, 10, 59, 'Ini: "twalam ayen i wen d Issers Öebbi n ôôeéq? Terram segs leêlal d leêôam". Ini: "Iâammed awen Öebbi, ne$ tesnulfam d $ef Öebbi"?'),
(1424, 10, 60, 'Acu ara meyyzen, ass n tnekra, wid id igren tikerkas $ef Öebbi? Ih, Öebbi d Bab n lfevl af imdanen, maca tegwti segsen ur snemmiren.'),
(1425, 10, 61, 'Ur teppiliv di liêala, ur temmalev si Leqwôan, ur tepce$wilem di kra, mebla ma Nella d Inagan nnwen, mara tweqmem. Lmizan ubelkim di tmurt u deg igenni, ur idrig i Mass ik. Akken seddaw waya, ne$ sennig es. Akw, di Tezmamt ipbegginen.'),
(1426, 10, 62, 'Ih, s tidep, iêbiben n Öebbi ur ppagwaden, ur $weblen.'),
(1427, 10, 63, 'Wid iumnen u llan êezzben,'),
(1428, 10, 64, 'a ten beccôen s lxiô di tmeddurt n ddunit, di laxeôt. Ur illi ubeddel deg wawalen n Öebbi. D wagi ay d rrbeê ameqwôaêan.'),
(1429, 10, 65, 'Ur k i$webbel wawal nnsen. Ih, tazmert akw n Öebbi. Neppa Isell, d Amusnaw.'),
(1430, 10, 66, 'S tidep, day maççi n Öebbi i illan deg igenwan, i illan di tmurt? D acu îîafaôen wid ipnujun, war Öebbi, ar icriken? Ïîafaôen kan nnwaya. Oaââlen kan.'),
(1431, 10, 67, 'Neppa, i wen Irran iv i ureyyeê nnwen, ass iwakken a pwalim. Deg waya, s tidep, d issekniyen i ugdud isellen.'),
(1432, 10, 68, 'Nnan: "Öebbi Isâa aqcic. Gedha s yiS! Neppa d Ameôkanti. IneS i illan deg igenwan, i illan di tmurt. Ur tesâim adabu $ef waya. Day a d tinim $ef Öebbi, ayen ur tessinem"?'),
(1433, 10, 69, 'Ini: "s tidep, wid id igren tikerkas $ef Öebbi, ur rebêen".'),
(1434, 10, 70, 'Zzhu di ddunit, sinna, $uône£ tu$alin nnsen. D$a, ad asen Nsâaddi aâaqeb uqsiê, imi llan jehlen.'),
(1435, 10, 71, 'Eêku yasen d tadyant n Nuê, mi inna i ugdud is: "a yagdud iw! Ma ééayit fellawen tilin iw, akked usmekti w n issekniyen n Öebbi, $ef Öebbi ppekle$, ihi, zduklet lameô nnwen akked icriken nnwen. Sinna, ur awen teppili lhejna $ef lameô nnwen, d$a, frut ep felli, ur iyi sganit.'),
(1436, 10, 72, 'Ma twexxôem, ur awen ssuture$ taqdiât. Ih, taqdiât iw ar Öebbi kan. Felli lameô ad ili$ seg imvuâen.'),
(1437, 10, 73, 'Skaddben t. Nsellek it, akked wid illan yides, di lbabuô. Nerra ten d igensas. Ne$meq wid iskaddben issekniyen nne£. Wali amek tevôa d wid ippunedôen.'),
(1438, 10, 74, 'Sinna, deffir es, Nuzen ed imazanen ar igduden nnsen. Usan ten id s ubeggen. Ur ssawven ad amnen $ef wayen nekôen zik. Akka ay Nselle$ ulawen ixabiten.'),
(1439, 10, 75, 'Sinna, deffir sen, Nuzen ed Musa akked Haôun, ar Ferâun akked imvebbôen is, s issekniyen nne£. Sme$wôen iman nnsen. Llan d agdud ibe$wviyen.'),
(1440, 10, 76, 'Mi ten id tusa tidep, s$uône£, nnan: "wagi, ih, d ssêur n ûûeê".'),
(1441, 10, 77, 'Inna Musa: "day a tinim d ssêur wagi, i tidep mi kwen id tusa"? Ur rebêen iseêêaren.'),
(1442, 10, 78, 'Nnan: "day d tusiv $uône$, ad a$ tesîixxôev seg wayen id nufa ar imezwura nne$, a ppu$alem, di sin, d imeqwôanen di tmurt? Ur numin, nekwni, yiswen".'),
(1443, 10, 79, 'Inna Ferâun: "awit iyi d yal aseêêar amusnaw".'),
(1444, 10, 80, 'Mi d usan iseêêaren, inna yasen Musa: "veggôet ara tveggôem"!'),
(1445, 10, 81, 'Mi veggôen, inna Musa: "ayen d tebbwim d ssêur. S tidep, a t Inqev Öebbi". Ih, Öebbi ur Issewqam ara igiten ifessaden.'),
(1446, 10, 82, 'Öebbi Itebbit tidep, s wawal iS, xas ugin ibe$wviyen.'),
(1447, 10, 83, 'I iumnen s Musa, siwa tarwa seg ugdud is, ilmend n tugdi uhewwel n Ferâun akked imvebbôen is. Ih, Ferâun d abe$wvi di tmurt. Neppa, s tidep, seg imaâfan.'),
(1448, 10, 84, 'Inna Musa: "a yagdud iw! Ma teppamnem s Öebbi, ppeklet fellaS ma d imvuâen ay tellam".'),
(1449, 10, 85, 'Nnan: "neppkel $ef Öebbi. A Mass nne$, ur a$ ppara d ahewwel i ugdud imednas;'),
(1450, 10, 86, 'Sellek a$, s uêunu K, seg ugdud ijehliyen".'),
(1451, 10, 87, 'Nweêêa i Musa akked gma s: "ebnut ixxamen i ugdud nnwen di Maûeô, erret ixxamen nnwen ar lqibla, beddet i téallit. Becceô lmumnin".'),
(1452, 10, 88, 'Inna Musa: "a Mass nne$! S tidep, Tefkiv i Ferâun akked imvebbôen is, ôôêuê akked wayla di tmeddurt n ddunit, a Mass nne$, iwakken ad nnetlafen seg ubrid iK. A Mass nne$, Squcc ayla nnsen, S$eô ulawen nnsen, ur ppamnen alamma walan aâaqeb aqeôêan".'),
(1453, 10, 89, 'Inna: "ih, tepwaqbel tnaâôit nnwen. Ddut di lewqam, ur teddut d ubrid n wid ur nessin".'),
(1454, 10, 90, 'Nezzger At Isôail di yill. Vefôen ten Ferâun akked iâsekôiwen is, s leb$wev d lewâaôa. Armi ibbwev ad i$meq, inna: "umne$! Ih, ur illi ôebbi siwa Win is umnen At Isôail. Nek seg imvuâen".'),
(1455, 10, 91, 'Tura! Ni$ zik taâûav, telliv seg ifessaden.'),
(1456, 10, 92, 'Assa, a Nsellek loeppa k, a d tegwri d assekni i wid ara k id ineûfen. Aîas n medden, s tidep, stehzan deg issekniyen nne£.'),
(1457, 10, 93, 'Ni$ Nessers At Isôail deg umkan umâin, u N$at iten s wayen ilhan. Ur mgaraden armi ten id tusa tussna. Ih, Mass ik ad Iêudd garasen, ass n tnekra, ilmend n wayen i$ef llan mgaraden.'),
(1458, 10, 94, 'Ma tcukkev $ef wayen i k ed Nessers, steqsi wid i iqqaôen Tazmamt, uqbel ik. Ni$ tusa k id tidep, s$uô Mass ik, ur ppili seg wid ipcukkun.'),
(1459, 10, 95, 'Ur ppili seg wid i iskaddben issekniyen n Öebbi, a ppiliv seg imexsuôen.'),
(1460, 10, 96, 'Ih, wid i$ef iûaô Wawal n Mass ik, ur ppamnen,'),
(1461, 10, 97, 'xas usan ten id akw issekniyen, alamma walan aâaqeb aqeôêan.'),
(1462, 10, 98, 'A lemmer telli temdint iumnen, u infaâ p liman is, siwa agdud n Yunes! Mi umnen, Nveôôef segsen aâaqeb imdelli di tmeddurt n ddunit. Neooa ten zzhan tallit kan.'),
(1463, 10, 99, 'Ma ihwa yaS i Mass ik, ad amnen wid illan di ddunit, akken ma llan. Day a pêeppmev, keçç, i imdanen ad amnen?'),
(1464, 10, 100, 'Ur ippamen umdan siwa ma Irad Öebbi. Isdullu wid ur nfehhem ara.'),
(1465, 10, 101, 'Ini: "walit i illan di tmurt akked igenwan. Ula iwumi issekniyen akked ineddiôen, i ugdud ur neppamen".'),
(1466, 10, 102, 'Day a pganin kan amedya n wussan n wid i ten id izwaren? Ini: "gganit, nek yidwen, seg wid ipganin".'),
(1467, 10, 103, 'Sinna, a Nsellek imazanen nne£, akked wid iumnen. Akka ay d lwajeb fella£, a Nsellek lmumnin.'),
(1468, 10, 104, 'Ini: "a yimdanen! Ma tcukkem di ddin iw, nek ur âabde$ wid tâabdem, war Öebbi. Maca, âabde$ Öebbi ara Idmen leôwaê nnwen. Pwamôe$ ad ili$ si lmumnin".'),
(1469, 10, 105, 'Sbedd udem ik i ddin, s umili ar tidep, ur ppili seg imcurak.'),
(1470, 10, 106, 'Ur pnuju, war Öebbi, ar wayen ur k inefâan, ur k iîîuôôun. Ma txedmev akken, keçç, imiren, a ppiliv seg imednas.'),
(1471, 10, 107, 'Ma Isâadda fellak Öebbi ccqa, ur ak illi ujebbaô siwa Neppa. Ma Irad ak lxiô, ur illi usebîîel i lfevl iS. Ippak it i win i S ihwan, deg ixdimen iS. Neppa Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu.'),
(1472, 10, 108, 'Ini: "a yimdanen! Ni$ tusa kwen id tidep s$uô Mass nnwen! Win ipwanhan, ipwanha kan i iman is; win innetlafen, innetlef kan i iman is. Ur lli$, nek, d awkil nnwen".'),
(1473, 10, 109, 'Ddu d wayen ik ed ippuweêêan, eûbeô ard Iêudd Öebbi. Neppa, Yif akw imêaddan.');
INSERT INTO `ber_mensur` (`index`, `sura`, `aya`, `text`) VALUES
(1474, 11, 1, 'Alô. Tazmamt, issekniyen iS ppuûewwben, sinna, ppufeûûlen s$uô Uûwib i Ipwaxebbôen.'),
(1475, 11, 2, 'Ur âabdet siwa Öebbi. Nek, s$uôeS $uôwen, d aneddaô u d abcir.'),
(1476, 11, 3, 'Ssutret ssmaê i Mass nnwen, steôoâet aS, ad Ifeôôeo fellawen afeôôeo ilhan, ar lajel ipwassnen. Ippak lfevl iS i yal bab n lfevl. Ma twexxôem, nekk ugade$ a ppeppuâqbem, ass ameqwran.'),
(1477, 11, 4, 'Tu$alin nnwen, ar Öebbi. Neppa Izmer i yal cci.'),
(1478, 11, 5, 'Day nitni, s tidep, ur snefvasen ara idmaren nnsen, iwakken ad ffren fellaS? Xas $ummen s iceîîiven nnsen, day ur Iéôa ara ayen teffren akked wayen d qqaôen? Neppa, s tidep, Issen i illan deg idmaren.'),
(1479, 11, 6, 'Ur illi lweêc di tmurt, mebla ma illa ôôeéq is ar Öebbi. Issen tanezdu$t is, tanîelt is. Meôôa, di Tezmamt ipbegginen.'),
(1480, 11, 7, 'D Neppa i Ixelqen tamurt akked igenwan di sdis wussan. Asgeld iS illa $ef waman. A kwen Ijeôôeb anwi segwen ara ixedmen ayen ilhan, sennig wiyav. Ma tenniv: "ih, kunwi a d tekkrem deffir tmeppant nnwen", wid ijehlen, war ccekk, a d inin: "ayagi, kan, d ssêur n ûûeê".'),
(1481, 11, 8, 'Ma Neswexxeô asen aâaqeb ar imir ipwassnen, war ccekk, a d inin: "d acu iT iîîfen"? Ass ideg ara ten id iawev, day illa wa ara ten iveôôfen segs? Ad asen izzi wayen i$ef pmmaâliken.'),
(1482, 11, 9, 'Ma Nesêess i umdan aêunu nne¨£, sinna, Nekkes as t, atan ad iayes, ad ijhel.'),
(1483, 11, 10, 'Ma Nesêess as l$it, deffir twa$it i t innulen, atan ad yini: "fukkent felli lemêayen", d$a, neppa, ad ifôeê, ad izux.'),
(1484, 11, 11, 'Kkes ed wid iûebbôen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan. I widak ssmaê akked tikci meqqwôen.'),
(1485, 11, 12, 'Ahat teppaoav kra n wayen ik ed ippuweêêan. Pzemmiven yis idmaren ik mara qqaôen: "a lemmer i s d irs ugerruj, ne$ idda d, yides, lmelk"! Keçç d aneddaô kan. Öebbi d Awkil n yal cci.'),
(1486, 11, 13, 'Ne$ ad inin: "isnulfa t id". Ini: "awit ed, s usnulfu, mraw n tsuôtin am neppa. Naâôet ayen iwumi tzemrem, war Öebbi, ma tessawalem tidep".'),
(1487, 11, 14, 'Ma ur awen d rran ara, cfut ar irs ed kan s tussna n Öebbi, ar ur illi ôebbi siwa Neppa. Ihi, ma kunwi d imvuâen?'),
(1488, 11, 15, 'I wid ib$an tameddurt n ddunit akked ôôêuê is, a Nkafi, degs, igiten nnsen, ur asen Ntekkes.'),
(1489, 11, 16, 'Widak, ur ppafen, di laxeôt, siwa times. Ad i$li wayen ûenâen degs; inqev wayen xeddmen.'),
(1490, 11, 17, 'Day win iddan d ubeggen, s$uô Mass is, u immal as t unagi s$uôeS…? U, uqbel is, Tazmamt n Musa, d nnhaya u d aêunu. Wigi umnen yis. Win i p inekôen, seg ikubar, ppaâud is d times. Ur ppili di ccekk fellas. Neppa, ih, d tidep s$uô Mass ik. Maca, tegwti n medden ur ppamnen.'),
(1491, 11, 18, 'Anwa idensen sennig win id isnulfan tikerkas $ef Öebbi? Wigi a d rsen i Mass nnsen. A d inin inagan: "d wigi i iskaddben $ef Mass nnsen". Day Öebbi ur Ixezzu yara imednas?'),
(1492, 11, 19, 'I isîixxiôen seg ubrid n Öebbi, i t issarmen d uâwij, nitni ur uminen s laxeôt?'),
(1493, 11, 20, 'Wigi, ur sfunnugen di tmurt, ur asen illi bab, war Öebbi. Fellasen aâaqeb ar wayev. Ur zmiren ad slen, ur pwalin.'),
(1494, 11, 21, 'D wigi i isxesôen iman nnsen. Itelf iten wayen d snulfuyen.'),
(1495, 11, 22, 'Ur illi ccekk, ih, nitni ad xesôen, di laxeôt, sennig wiyav.'),
(1496, 11, 23, 'Ih, wid iumnen, u xeddmen ayen ilhan, u unzen aS i Mass nnsen, widak d at Loennet, degs ad wekkôen.'),
(1497, 11, 24, 'Amedya n snat n trebbuyaâ am uder$al, uâééug, akked win ipwalin, win isellen. Day âadlen sin imedyaten agi? Day ur d tesmektayem ara?'),
(1498, 11, 25, 'Ni$ Nuzen ed Nuê i ugdud is: "nek d aneddaô nnwen ipbegginen,'),
(1499, 11, 26, 'iwakken ur tâabdem siwa Öebbi. Nek ugaded aâaqeb fellawen, ass aqeôhan".'),
(1500, 11, 27, 'Nnan imvebbôen, wid ijehlen, seg ugdud is: "keçç, $uône$, d amdan am nekwni. Nwala, d ôôdiyen nne$, kan, war ameyyez, i k ivefôen. Ur nwala s wacu i $ tifem. Xaîi, nêesb ikwen d ikeddaben".'),
(1501, 11, 28, 'Inna: "a yagdud iw! Acu twalam ma ddi$ d ubeggen n Mass iw? Ifka yi d aêunu s$uôeS. Idreg fellawen. Day a t nêeppem fellawen, ma kunwi tugim t?'),
(1502, 11, 29, 'A yagdud iw! Ur awen ssuture$ ayla, ilmend is; taqdiât iw ar Öebbi kan. Ur ppara$, nek, wid iumnen. S tidep, ad mlilen d Mass nnsen. Maca, nek wala$ kwen d agdud ur nessin.'),
(1503, 11, 30, 'A yagdud iw! Acu ara yi isellken seg ufus n Öebbi, lemmer i ten rri$ akin, day ur d tesmektayem ara?'),
(1504, 11, 31, 'Ur awen qqaôe$: $uôi lexzayen n Öebbi. Ur ssine$ tabavnit. Ur qqaôe$: nek d lmelk. Ur qqaôe$ i wid êeqôent wallen nnwen: ur asen Ippak ara Öebbi lxiô, d awez$i. Yif akw Öebbi akken Iéôa, i illan deg iman nnsen. Mulac ad ili$ seg imednas".'),
(1505, 11, 32, 'Nnan: "a Nuê! Ni$ tnamrev a$, tessugtev a$ anamer. Ihi, awi ya$ d ayen i $ tâahdev, ma tessawalev tidep".'),
(1506, 11, 33, 'Inna: "d Öebbi kan ar awen t id Iawin, ma ihwa yaS. Kunwi ur tesfunnugem.'),
(1507, 11, 34, 'Xas b$i$ a kwen neûêe$, ur tesfaydayam seg wanûaê iw, ma Ib$a Öebbi a kwen Itlef. Neppa d Mass nnwen; tu$alin nnwen $uôeS".'),
(1508, 11, 35, 'Ne$ qqaôen: "isnulfa t id". Ini: "ma snulfa$ t id, lbe$wv iw i yiri w. Nek, ur ppka$ di lbe$wv nnwen".'),
(1509, 11, 36, 'Ippuweêêa d i Nuê: "ur ippamen yiwen, d awez$i, seg ugdud ik, siwa wid illan umnen. Ihi, ur k icqi wayen xeddmen.'),
(1510, 11, 37, 'Eûnaâ lbabuô, ger wallen nne£, s uweêêi nne£. Ur iyI d pmeslay $ef wid idensen, war ccekk, ad $emqen".'),
(1511, 11, 38, 'La iûennaâ lbabuô. Yal tikelt ara âaddin $uôes imvebbôen n ugdud is, tkaâriren fellas. Inna: "ma temmaâlkem degne$, ihi, a nemmaâlek degwen akken temmaâlkem.'),
(1512, 11, 39, 'Deqqal a ppeéôem, u$uô ara d ias uâaqeb ara t isdullen, ara iêaz uâaqeb imezgi".'),
(1513, 11, 40, 'Alamma, mi d iusa lameô nne£, la pfeggiven igwefran d ihedman, Nenna: "awi degs tayuga n yal ûûenf, tawacult ik - siwa wid i$ef id izwar wawal -, akked wid iumnen". Drus kan i iumnen yides.'),
(1514, 11, 41, 'Inna: "rekbet degs, s yisem n Öebbi, acali s akked trusi s. Mass iw, s tidep, Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu".'),
(1515, 11, 42, 'Icula yissen, di lemwao anect idurar. Issawel Nuê i mmi s, i illan weêdes: "a mmi ali d yidne$, ur teppiliv ar ijehliyen"!'),
(1516, 11, 43, 'Inna: "ûûôan iw d adrar, ad iyi isellek seg waman". Inna: "assa, ulac leslak si lameô n Öebbi, siwa i win i$ef Iêun". Âaddant lemwao garasen. Iûebê ed seg wid ipwa$emqen.'),
(1517, 11, 44, 'Nnan: "a tamurt, seblaâ aman im, a yigenni eûûfu". Aman zzren. Iûaô lameô: irs $ef Loudi. Iffe$ uberraê: akin agdud imednas!'),
(1518, 11, 45, 'Inuj Nuê ar Mass is, inna: "a Mass iw! Ni$ mmi n twacult iw. Ih, lemâahda K d tidep, Keçç Tifev akw imêaddan".'),
(1519, 11, 46, 'Inna: "a Nuê! Neppa, s tidep, ur illi n wacult ik. Ih, neppa ur ixdim ayen ilhan. Ihi, ur iyI d steqsay $ef wayen ur tessinev. Nek a k Ssakwaye$, ur teppiliv seg wid ur nessin".'),
(1520, 11, 47, 'Inna: "a Mass iw! Ili di lâawen iw, iwakken ur K id steqsaye$ $ef wayen ur ssine$. Ma ur iyi Tsemmêev, ur Têunev felli, ad ili$ seg imexsuôen".'),
(1521, 11, 48, 'Nnan d: "a Nuê! Ers ed s tifrat s$uône£, akked lbaôaka, fellak akw $ef leoyus i illan yidek. Kra n legyus, a ten N$it. Sinna, fellasen s$uône£, aâaqeb aqeôêan".'),
(1522, 11, 49, 'Tagi si teqûivin n tbavnit, Nweêêa yak tent. Ur tent tessinev, keçç, ne$ agdud ik, uqbel wagi. Ihi, eûbeô, taggara, war ccekk, i wid ipêezziben.'),
(1523, 11, 50, 'I Âad, gmat sen Hud, inna: "a yagdud iw! Âabdet Öebbi! Ur tesâim ôebbi, war Neppa. Kunwi tesnulfuyem d kan.'),
(1524, 11, 51, 'A yagdud iw! Ur awen ssuture$ taqdiât $ef waya. Taqdiât iw ar Win kan, iyi d Ixelqen. Day ur tefhimem ara?'),
(1525, 11, 52, 'A yagdud iw! Ssutret ssmaê i Mass nnwen, sinna, steôoâet aS. Ad awen d Isse$li ageffur d ihedman, ad awen irnu tazmert i tezmert nnwen. Ur ppu$alet d ibe$wviyen".'),
(1526, 11, 53, 'Nnan as: "a Hud! Ur a$ d tusid s ubeggen, ur neppaoa, nekwni, iôebbiten nne$, ilmend n wawal ik, ur numin yisek.'),
(1527, 11, 54, 'Neqqaô kan, d kra iôebbiten nne$, i k i$eôqen". Inna: "nek, Anagi w d Öebbi, u cehhdet ar ur ppka$ ara deg wayen tepcarakem,'),
(1528, 11, 55, 'war Neppa. Ihi, andit iyi akken ma tellam, sinna ur iyi sganayet.'),
(1529, 11, 56, 'Nek, ppekle$ af Öebbi, Mass iw u Mass nnwen. Ur illi umexluq ur Iîîif seg ixef is. Ih, Mass iw deg ubrid uwqim.'),
(1530, 11, 57, 'Ma wexxôen, ni$ ssawve$ awen d ayen i$ef id ppuceggâa$ $uôwen. A d Inûef, Mass iw, agdud war kunwi. Ur T teîîuôum s wacemma. Mass iw, s tidep, d Amêareb n yal cci".'),
(1531, 11, 58, 'Mi d iusa lameô nne£, Nsellek Hud akked wid iumnen yides, s uêunu s$uône£. Nsellek iten seg uâaqeb uwâiô.'),
(1532, 11, 59, 'Akka Âad. Nekôen issekniyen n Mass nnsen, âuûan imazanen iS. Ddan d lameô n yal aqehhaô iggernennen.'),
(1533, 11, 60, 'A ten ivfeô xezzu di ddunit agi, u deg wass n tnekra. Day, war ccekk, ur jhilen ara Âad, ar Mass nnsen? Day maççi: "akin Âad, agdud n Hud"?'),
(1534, 11, 61, 'I Tamud, gmat sen ÛüÜaliê, inna: "a yagdud iw! Âabdet Öebbi! Ur tesâim ôebbi, war Neppa. Neppa Ixelq ikwen seg wakal, Izzde$ ikwen fellas. Ssutret aS ssmaê, sinna, steôoâet aS. Mass iw, s tidep, Iqeôb ed, Ippara d awal.'),
(1535, 11, 62, 'Nnan as: "a Üaliê, ni$ telliv garane$, uqbel aya, d asirem nne$. Day ad a$ tekksev aâbad n wayen âabden imezwura nne$? Nekwni, s tidep, aql a$ di ccekk imcebbwel, $ef wayen u$uô la $ tneccdev".'),
(1536, 11, 63, 'Inna: "a yagdud iw! Acu twalam ma ddi$ d ubeggen n Mass iw? Ifka yi d aêunu s$uôeS. Acu ara yi isellken seg ufus n Öebbi, ma aâûa$ $uôeS? Iyi ternam, siwa taxessaôt.'),
(1537, 11, 64, 'A yagdud iw! Tagi d tal$wemt n Öebbi, d assekni i kunwi. Eooet ep a ppeks di tmurt n Öebbi. Ur p pjeyyifet, mulac a kwen id isami uâaqeb iqeôben".'),
(1538, 11, 65, 'Gezmen as ivaôen. Inna: "zhut deg ixxamen nnwen, krav wussan. Apan lemâahda ur nepwankaô".'),
(1539, 11, 66, 'Mi d iusa lameô nne£, Nsellek Üaliê akked wid iumnen yides, s uêunu s$uône£, si ddell n wass nni. Ih, Mass ik d Uohid, d Uzmir.'),
(1540, 11, 67, 'Asu$u iwwet wid idensen, gwran d d imeslax deg ixxamen nnsen,'),
(1541, 11, 68, 'amzun ur rbiêen degsen. Day, s tidep, ur jhilen ara Tamud, ar Mass nnsen? Day maççi: "akin Tamud"?'),
(1542, 11, 69, 'Ni$ usan d imceggâen nne£ ar Ibôahim, s ubecceô. Nnan: "tifrat"! Inna: "tifrat"! Ur iâaîîel ara ibbwi d aâjmi icwin.'),
(1543, 11, 70, 'Mi iwala ifassen nnsen ur d ééilen ara $uôes, isêassef iten, iugad iten. Nnan: "ur ppagwad, nekwni neppuceggaâ ed ar ugdud n Luî".'),
(1544, 11, 71, 'Tameîîut is tbedd, tevûa. Nbecceô ip s Isêaq, akked Yaâqub, deffir Isêaq.'),
(1545, 11, 72, 'Tenna: "a lêif iw, day a d arwe$, nek d tam$aôt, u argaz agi inu, wesser? Ayagi, s tidep, d lwehma"!'),
(1546, 11, 73, 'Nnan: "day twehmev di lameô n Öebbi? Aêunu n Öebbi, akked lbaôaka S, fellawen ay at uxxam. Ih, Neppa d Amaâzuz, Mucaâ".'),
(1547, 11, 74, 'Mi s tekkes tugwdi i Ibôahim, u iusa t id ubecceô, inumer a£ $ef ugdud n Luî.'),
(1548, 11, 75, 'Ibôahim, s tidep, iêellem, ippanez, isteôoiâ.'),
(1549, 11, 76, '"A Ibôahim, ur keççem deg waya. Ni$ iusa d lameô n Mass ik. Nitni, a ten id ias uâaqeb, war tifrat".'),
(1550, 11, 77, 'Mi usan imceggâen nne£ ar Luî, innu$ben, ur isâi i$il a ten ifukk. Inna: "wagi d ass uwâiô".'),
(1551, 11, 78, 'Iusa d ugdud is, zeêfen d $uôes. Llan, zik, xeddmen tucmitin. Inna: "a yagdud iw! Atent an issi, nitenti zeddigit, i kunwi. Ëezbet i Öebbi, ur iyi pêeccimet ar inebgawen iw. Day ur illi ara, garawen, urgaz aêesbi"?'),
(1552, 11, 79, 'Nnan: "ni$ teéôiv ur nesâi lêeqq deg issi k. Keçç, s tidep, teéôiv d acu neb$a".'),
(1553, 11, 80, 'Inna: "a lemmer i wen zmire$, ne$ sâi$ tayep ioehden"!'),
(1554, 11, 81, 'Nnan: "a Luî, nekwni d imceggâen n Mass ik. Ur k id ppawven. Öuê akked twacult ik, deg iv. Yiwen degwen ur d itezzi! Kkes ed tameîîut ik. Neppat, s tidep, a ppepwwet s wayen ara ten iwwten. Ih, ppaâud nnsen, taûebêit. Ni$ tqeôb ed tûebêit"?'),
(1555, 11, 82, 'Mi d iusa lameô nne£, Nesredm ip. Nesse$li d fellas abruri n yiéôa ibelbaven n talaxt.'),
(1556, 11, 83, 'Pwanesxen ar Mass ik. Nitni, ur bâiden i imednas.'),
(1557, 11, 84, 'I Madian, gmat sen Cuâayeb, inna: "a yagdud iw! Âabdet Öebbi! Ur tesâim ôebbi, war Neppa. Ur ssenqaset di lkil akked lmizan. Nek, wala$ kwen teôwam, u ugade$ fellawen aâaqeb, ass itezzin.'),
(1558, 11, 85, 'A yagdud iw! Ktilet, weznet, s lewqama. Ur îîuôôut imdanen deg wayla nnsen, ur pdenniset, tessefsadem di tmurt.'),
(1559, 11, 86, 'Yif it i kunwi wayen d iqqimen i Öebbi, ma d lmumnin ay tellam. Ur lli$, nek, d amêareb nnwen".'),
(1560, 11, 87, 'Nnan: "a Cuâayeb, day a$ umôen wawalen ik, a neoo ayen âabden imezwura nne$? Ne$ a nexdem, deg wayla nne$, ayen ur a$ nehwi? Keçç, s tidep, d uêlim, d uûwib".'),
(1561, 11, 88, 'Inna: "a yagdud iw! Acu twalam, ma ddi$ d ubeggen n Mass iw? I$at iyi yis, l$it imaânen. Ur b$i$ a kwen mgirrde$, siwa $ef wayen i wen gedle$. B$i$ kan, s wayen zemre$, ad awen ûegme$ tikli. Lâawen iw s$uô Öebbi kan. Ppekle$ fellaS, utube$ T.'),
(1562, 11, 89, 'A yagdud iw! Awer kwen teppara nnmara w d ibe$wviyen, a ppevôu yidwen akken tevôa d ugdud n Nuê, ne$ win n Hud, ne$ win n Üaliê! Agdud n Luî, ur ibâad ara segwen.'),
(1563, 11, 90, 'Ssutret ssmaê i Mass nnwen, sinna, steroâet aS. Mass iw, s tidep, Ipêunu, Ipêemmil".'),
(1564, 11, 91, 'Nnan: "a Cuâayeb, ur nefhim ara aîas n wayen id tenniv. Aql a$ nwala k d uôhif garane$. Lemmer maççi d alag ik, war ccekk, a k neôoem. Ur a$ tezmirev".'),
(1565, 11, 92, 'Inna: "a yagdud iw! Day Öebbi, $uôwen, yif iT walag iw, di tezmert? Terram T ar deffir n waârur nnwen. Mass iw, s tidep, Izzi i wayen txeddmem.'),
(1566, 11, 93, 'A yagdud iw! Xedmet deg umekkan nnwen, nek ad xedme$. Deqqal a ppeéôem, u$uô ara d ias uâaqeb ara t isdullen, anwa ay d akeddab. Âasset, nek, yidwen, ad âasse$".'),
(1567, 11, 94, 'Mi d iusa lameô nne£, Nsellek Cuâayeb akked wid iumnen yides, s uêunu s$uône£. Asu$u iwwet wid idensen, gwran d d imeslax deg ixxamen nnsen,'),
(1568, 11, 95, 'amzun ur rbiêen degsen. Day maççi: "akin Madian"! Am: "akin Tamud"?'),
(1569, 11, 96, 'Ni$ Nuzen ed Musa, s issekniyen nne£, akked udabu n ûûeê,'),
(1570, 11, 97, '$uô Ferâun akked imvebbôen is. Ddan d lameô n Ferâun. Lameô n Ferâun ur illi d uûwib.'),
(1571, 11, 98, 'Ad izwir i ugdud is, ass n tnekra, a ten inheô ar usario n tmes. A yasario ucmit u$uô pwanehôen!'),
(1572, 11, 99, 'A ten ivfeô xezzu di tagi, u deg wass n tnekra. A tikci tucmip ippunefken!'),
(1573, 11, 100, 'Ayagi, si teqûivin n temdinin, i k d Nessawal. Garasent tid ibedden, tid ipwamegren.'),
(1574, 11, 101, 'Ur ten Nednis. Maca, densen iman nnsen. Ur ten nefâan s wacemma, iôebbiten nnsen i la naâôen, war Öebbi, mi d iusa lameô n Mass ik. I sen rnan, siwa ssxev.'),
(1575, 11, 102, 'Akka tiyta n Mass ik. Mi Iwwet timdinin i idensen, s tidep, tiyta S teqôeê, teqseê.'),
(1576, 11, 103, 'Ih, deg waya, assekni i wid iugaden aâaqeb n laxeôt. Ass nni, d ass unejmaâ n yimdanen. Ass nni, d ass n ccada.'),
(1577, 11, 104, 'A t Neswexxeô kan ar lajel iuran.'),
(1578, 11, 105, 'Ass ideg ara d ias, ur d ipmeslay yiwen, siwa ma s tesriê iS. Ad ilin igeswaêen, isaâdiyen.'),
(1579, 11, 106, 'Wanag igeswaêen ad ilin di tmes, s unazaâ d imeîîi,'),
(1580, 11, 107, 'ad wekkôen dinna, ayen ara dumen tmurt akked igenwan, siwa ma ur Irad ara Mass ik. Ih, Mass ik Ixeddem ayen i S ihwan.'),
(1581, 11, 108, 'Wanag isaâdiyen, di Loennet, ad wekkôen, dinna, ayen ara dumen tmurt akked igenwan, siwa ma ur Irad ara Mass ik. D tikci n war tilas.'),
(1582, 11, 109, 'Ur k ikeççem ccekk $ef wayen âabden widak. Ayen âabden am wayen âabden imezwura nnsen, zik. War ccekk, ad asen Nefk amur nnsen, ur inqis.'),
(1583, 11, 110, 'Ni$, s tidep, Nefka Tazmamt i Musa. Mgarraden fellas. Lemmer ur d izwar ara wawal s$uô Mass ik, yili useyyi garasen. Haaten, ih, di ccekk imcebbwel fellas.'),
(1584, 11, 111, 'War ccekk, akken ma llan, ad Ikafi Mass ik igiten nnsen, s lmizan. Neppa, s tidep, Issen ayen xeddmen.'),
(1585, 11, 112, 'Ihi, ili d uwqim, akken i k ippunefk lameô, keçç akked wid isteôoâen yidek. Ur be$wvet. Neppa, s tidep, Ipwali ay txeddmem.'),
(1586, 11, 113, 'Ur pqeôôibet ar wid idensen, a kwen tnal tmes! Ur tesâim bab, war Öebbi, ihi, ur tepwasellkem.'),
(1587, 11, 114, 'èéal ûbeê, tameddit, kra n lewqat n yiv. S tidep, ise$iyen neqqven tucmitin. Ayagi d asmekti i wid ismektayen.'),
(1588, 11, 115, 'Eûbeô! Öebbi, s tidep, ur Iveggiâ taqdiât n lâuûam.'),
(1589, 11, 116, 'A lemmer llan, di tsuta i kwen id izwaren, imezgiyen ineqqven asefsed di tmurt! Qlilit kan seg wid Nsellek segsen. Wid idensen ddan akked wayen i ten izhan, u$alen d ibe$wviyen.'),
(1590, 11, 117, 'Ur Isquccu ara Mass ik timdinin, d aêerfi, ma llan imezda$ nnsent d lâuûam.'),
(1591, 11, 118, 'Lemmer i S ihwi i Mass ik, ad Irr imdanen d yiwen n lois. Zgan mgarraden.'),
(1592, 11, 119, 'Kkes ed wid i$ef Iêun Mass ik. Ixelq iten i wayagi. Itam wawal n Mass ik: "ad Acaôe$ Loahennama, war ccekk, s leonun akked yimdanen mejmulen".'),
(1593, 11, 120, 'Ayen akw i k ed Neêka n tmucuha imazanen, iwakken a Ntebbet ul ik, yissent. Id iusan dagi d tidep, d anabi u d asmekti i lmumnin.'),
(1594, 11, 121, 'Ini i wid ur numin ara: "xedmet ay tzemrem, nekwni s tidep, la nxeddem.'),
(1595, 11, 122, 'Gganit, nekwni la nepgani".'),
(1596, 11, 123, 'N Öebbi tabavnit n tmurt akked igenwan. £uôeS ara u$alen akw lumuô. Ihi, âabed iT, ppkel fellaS. Ur I$effel ara Mass ik, $ef wayen txeddmem.');
INSERT INTO `ber_mensur` (`index`, `sura`, `aya`, `text`) VALUES
(1597, 12, 1, 'Alô. Wigi d issekniyen n Tazmamt ipbegginen.'),
(1598, 12, 2, 'Ih, Nessader it id d Leqwôan, s taâôabt, amar a pfehmem.'),
(1599, 12, 3, 'Nekwni Nêekku yak tiêkayin igerzen mavi, deg wayen i k Nweêêa di Leqwôan agi, xas telliv, uqbel is, seg wid istehzan.'),
(1600, 12, 4, 'Mi inna Yusef i baba s: "a baba! Nek wala$ mrawyan itran, iîij, akked waggur, wala$ ten knan iyi".'),
(1601, 12, 5, 'Inna: "a mmi! Ur êekku ayen twalav i watmaten ik, ad ak andin ticeôkep. Cciîan, s tidep, d acengu n ûûeê n umdan.'),
(1602, 12, 6, 'Akka, a k Ifren Mass ik, u ak Isselmed asefru n temsal, u ad Itim l$it iS, i keçç akked twacult n Yaâqub, akken it Itam, zik, af lejdud ik: Ibôahim akked Isêaq. Mass ik, s tidep, d Amusnaw, d Uûwib".'),
(1603, 12, 7, 'Ni$, di Yusef akked watma s, illa ussekni i wid isteqsayen.'),
(1604, 12, 8, 'Mi nnan: "war ccekk, ifen a$, Yusef akked gma s, akken iten iêemmel babat nne$, u nekwni d îîeôma. Babat nne$, s tidep, haat di ttelfan n ûûeê.'),
(1605, 12, 9, 'En$et Yusef, ne$ nfut ep si tmurt, a d ilhu degwen babat wen, sinna, a ppu$alem d imdanen ixeddmen ayen ilhan".'),
(1606, 12, 10, 'Inna win d immeslayen, degsen: "ur neqqet Yusef, veggôet ep ar lqaâa n wannu. Ma tgam akka, a t iddem yiwen umsebrid".'),
(1607, 12, 11, 'Nnan: "a babat nne$, acu k iu$en, ur a$ tuminev ara, $ef Yusef. Nekwni, fellas, s tidep, d unûiêen.'),
(1608, 12, 12, 'Sseddu t yidne$ azekka, ad izhu, ad iurar. Nekwni, war ccekk, a nêareb fellas".'),
(1609, 12, 13, 'Inna: "nek, s tidep, $weble$ ma tebbwim t yidwen, ugade$ a t içç lweêc, kunwi testehzam degs".'),
(1610, 12, 14, 'Nnan: "ma içça t lweêc, u nekwni d îîeôma, s tidep a nili d imexsuôen".'),
(1611, 12, 15, 'Mi t bbwin, mwafaqen a t rôen ar lqaâa n wannu, Nweêêa yas: "ad asen temlev, s tidep, lameô agi nnsen, nitni ur éôin".'),
(1612, 12, 16, 'U$alen d tameddit, ar babat sen, pprun.'),
(1613, 12, 17, 'Nnan: "a babat nne$, s tidep, nôuê a nemzizzel, neooa Yusef ar lqecc nne$, içça t lweêc. Ur a$ teppamnev, xas nenna d tidep".'),
(1614, 12, 18, 'Bbwin d tasedrit is, degs idamen n rrya. Inna: "xaîi! D iman nnwen i wen d iccacven lameô. Ilha ûûbeô. Anuju $eô Öebbi, mgal ayen d teêkam".'),
(1615, 12, 19, 'Usan d iminigen, uznen win id ippagwmen, issader ssvel is. Inna: "a lxiô, wagi d aqcic"! Ffren t, amzun d sselâa. Öebbi Iéôa acu xeddmen.'),
(1616, 12, 20, 'Zzenzen t, s ôôxa, s kra iûuôdiyen. Ur as fkin ara azal.'),
(1617, 12, 21, 'Inna, i tmeîîut is, Umaûôi i t iu$en: "eôêeb yis, amar ad a$ infaâ, at nerr d mmit nne$". Akka ay Nesseqâad Yusef di tmurt, iwakken ad as Nesseêfev asefru n temsal. Öebbi d Amezwaru s lameô iS, maca tegwti n medden ur éôin ara.'),
(1618, 12, 22, 'Mi d immeêtel, Nefka yas ûûwab, tussna. Akka ay Nepkafi iâaôviyen.'),
(1619, 12, 23, 'Teb$a t tin u$ur izde$. Terra tibbura, u tenna: "eyya keçç"! Inna: "ad iyi Ineooi Öebbi! Ni$ bab iw iôêeb yissi. S tidep, ur rebêen imednas".'),
(1620, 12, 24, 'S tidep, teb$a t, u neppa ib$a p, lemmer ur iwala ara atebbet n Mass is. Akka, iwakken a Nessebâad fellas tuccva, lâaô. Neppa, s tidep, seg imdanen nne£ izedganen.'),
(1621, 12, 25, 'Uzzlen ar tebburt, tcerreg as tasedrit is, si zdeffir. Mmugren, argaz is, ar tebburt. Tenna: "acu ay d aqeîîi n win iâabwlen ad iccmet tawacult ik, siwa lêebs ne$ aâaqeb aqeôêan"?'),
(1622, 12, 26, 'Inna: "d neppat iyi ib$an". Icuhhed ed yiwen unagi si twacult is: "ma teqqeôs tsedrit si zdat, tenna d tidep, u neppa d akeddab.'),
(1623, 12, 27, 'Ma teqqeôs tsedrit si zdeffir, teskaddeb, u neppa seg at tidep".'),
(1624, 12, 28, 'Mi iwala teqqeôs tsedrit si zdeffir, inna: "ayagi, war ccekk, si nncub nnkwent. Ih, nncub nnkwent d timeqwôaêanin.'),
(1625, 12, 29, 'A Yusef, ppu ayagi, u kem ssuter ssmaê ubekkav im. Kem, s tidep, teccvev".'),
(1626, 12, 30, 'La qqaôent tlawin, di temdint: "tameîîut umdebbeô têemmel acrik is. Teshebl ip tayri. F akken nwala, appan, s tidep, di ttelfan n ûûeê".'),
(1627, 12, 31, 'Mi tesla s nncub nnsent, tuzen $uôsent, thegga yasent tanalt. I yal yiwet segsent, tefka tafrut. Tenna: "effe$ ed garasent". Mi t walant, isdehc itent, jerêent ifassen nnsent, nnant: "êaca Öebbi, wagi maççi d amdan, wagi siwa d lmelk ukyis".'),
(1628, 12, 32, 'Tenna: "d wagi i$ef iyi tlummemt. Ih, b$i$ t, neppa iqqim zeddig. Ma ur ixdim ara ay s umôe$, war ccekk, ad ipwaêbes, ad ipwaêqeô".'),
(1629, 12, 33, 'Inna: "a Mass iw! Smenyafe$ lêebs i wayen u$ur iyi d ssawalent. Ma ur Tesbaâdev ara felli nncub nnsent, ad male$ $uôsent, ad ili$ seg wid ur nessin".'),
(1630, 12, 34, 'Ijaweb as d Mass is. Issebâad fellas nncub nnsent. Neppa, s tidep, Issel, d Amusnaw.'),
(1631, 12, 35, 'Sinna, mi ten usan issekniyen, ufan, war ccekk, ilaq a t irr ar lêebs, kra n tallit.'),
(1632, 12, 36, 'Kecmen yides, ar lêebs, sin ilmeéiyen. Inna yiwen degsen: "nek wala$ iman iw, la teééme$ ccôab". Inna d wayev: "nek wala$ iman iw, la ppawi$ a$ôum $ef uqeôôu w, la teppen segs ifrax. Ssefru ya$ p id. Ih, nwala k seg iâaôviyen".'),
(1633, 12, 37, 'Inna: "seg wayen iyi ss$eô Mass iw, ad awen p id ssefru$, uqbel a kwen id iawev lqut i wen ppakken. Nek ooi$ ddin n ugdud ur numin s Öebbi, u nitni nekôen laxeôt.'),
(1634, 12, 38, 'Ddi$ d ddin n lejdud iw: Ibôahim, Isêaq akked Yaâqub. Ur a$ ippunefk a nezdukkel acemma i Öebbi. Ayagi si lfevl n Öebbi fellane$, akw $ef imdanen. Maca, tegwti n yimdanen ur snemmiren.'),
(1635, 12, 39, 'A yimeddukwal iw n lêebs, menyif imawlan imfaôaqen, ne$ Öebbi Yiwen, Aqehhaô?'),
(1636, 12, 40, 'Ay tâabdem, war Neppa, d ismawen kan i sen tefkam, kunwi akked imezwura nnwen. Ur asen d Issers ara Öebbi kra udabu. Lêukm ar Öebbi kan. Iumeô ed ur tâabdem, siwa Neppa. D wagi ay d ddin uûwib, maca tegwti n yimdanen ur ssinen.'),
(1637, 12, 41, 'A yimeddukwal iw n lêebs, wanag yiwen degwen ad ismiri ccôab, i bab is, wayev ad ippusemmeô $ef umidag, ifrax ad nneqben aqeôôu s. Ippuseyya lameô $ef wayen iyi d testeqsam".'),
(1638, 12, 42, 'Inna i win iêûa ad islek, segsen: "ar bab ik, smekti iyi d". Cciîan iseppu t, ur t id ismekti ar bab is. Irna, di lêebs, kra iseggwasen.'),
(1639, 12, 43, 'Inna ugellid: "nek wala$ ûa testan tiqebwaniyin, la tent teppent ûa tuvâifin, akked ûa tyedrin tizegzawin, tiyav d tiqquôanin. A yimvebbôen, ssefrut iyi d targit, ma tellam seg wid issefruyen tirga".'),
(1640, 12, 44, 'Nnan: "d tirga iwlellsen. Ur nelli d imusnawen i usefru n tirga".'),
(1641, 12, 45, 'Win i isellken si sin nni, armi tallit id immekti, inna: "nek, ad awen d awi$ asefru ines, aznet iyi.'),
(1642, 12, 46, 'A Yusef, bab n tidep, ssefru ya$ d: ûa testan tiqebwaniyin, la tent teppent ûa tuvâifin, akked ûa tyedrin tizegzawin, tiyav d tiqquôanin. Amar, ma u$ale$ ar imdanen, amar ad éôen".'),
(1643, 12, 47, 'Inna: "zerâat ûa iseggwasen imyevfaôen. Ayen tzerâam, eooet ep di tyedrin is, siwa cwiî ara teççem.'),
(1644, 12, 48, 'Sinna, deffir sen, a d asen ûa iwaâôen. Ad ççen ayen i sen theggam siwa cwiî, seg wayen txeznem.'),
(1645, 12, 49, 'Sinna a d ias, deffir waya, useggwas n tallalt i medden, ideg ara éden".'),
(1646, 12, 50, 'Inna ugellid: "awit ep id $uôi". Mi t id iusa umersul, inna: "u$al ar bab ik, u steqsi t acu ay d l$eôv n tlawin i ijerêen ifassen nnsent. Mass iw, s tidep, Issen nncub nnsent".'),
(1647, 12, 51, 'Inna: "acu ara d tinimt mi teb$amt Yusef"? Nnant: "êaca Öebbi, ur nufi $uôes tuccva". Tenna d tmeîîut umvebbeô: "tura, a d tban tidep. D nek i t ib$an, ma d neppa, s tidep, d bab n tidep".'),
(1648, 12, 52, '"Akka, iwakken ad iéeô ur t xdiâa$ ara s tuffra. Öebbi ur Inehhu nncub n lxeyyan.'),
(1649, 12, 53, 'Ur pzekki$ iman iw. Tanefsit, s tidep, tezzu$uô ar tuccva, siwa ma Iêun Mass iw. Mass iw, s tidep, Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu".'),
(1650, 12, 54, 'Inna ugellid: "awit ep id $uôi, d laâtiq iw". Mi s immeslay, inna: "keçç, assa, nefka yak adabu, laman".'),
(1651, 12, 55, 'Inna: "wekkel iyi $ef lemxazen n tmurt, nek d amêareb amusnaw".'),
(1652, 12, 56, 'Akka ay Nesseqâad Yusef di tmurt, ad izde$ anda i s ihwa. Nepêunu $ef win i £ ihwan, ur Nesôuêu arraz iâaôviyen.'),
(1653, 12, 57, 'S tidep, arraz n laxeôt yif it, i wid iumnen u llan pêezziben.'),
(1654, 12, 58, 'Usan watmaten n Yusef, kecmen $uôes, iâqel iten, nitni ur t âqilen.'),
(1655, 12, 59, 'Mi sen ifka ppâabgat nnsen, inna: "awit iyi d gmat wen s babat wen. Day ur twalam ara zade$ awen lkil, u, nek, ife$ akw wid isnebgaten?'),
(1656, 12, 60, 'Ma ur iyi t id tebbwim ara, ur awen nepktili $uôi, ur iyi d tepsamim ".'),
(1657, 12, 61, 'Nnan: "a nêawet baba s fellas; akka ara nexdem".'),
(1658, 12, 62, 'Inna i iqeddacen is: "rret selâa nnsen deg icekkaôen nnsen, amar a p âaqlen mara awven ar twacult nnsen, amar a d u$alen".'),
(1659, 12, 63, 'Mi bbwven ar babat sen, nnan: "a babat nne$, igdel fella$ lkil, azen gmat nne$ yidne$, iwakken a d nektil. Nekwni, war ccekk, a nêareb fellas".'),
(1660, 12, 64, 'Inna: "day a kwen amne$ fellas, akken i kwen umne$, zik, $ef gma s? Öebbi Yif akw imêaraben. Neppa Iphunu sennig akw iêninen".'),
(1661, 12, 65, 'Mi ldin lqecc nnsen, ufan tu$al iten id selâa nnsen. Nnan: "a babat nne$, ur neb$i tagi, selâa nne$ tu$al a$ d. A d nessikrer i twacult nne$, a nêareb $ef gmat nne$, a d nernu ppâabga n ul$wem. Tagi d ppâabga tushilt".'),
(1662, 12, 66, 'Inna: "ur t sedduye$ yidwen, d awez$i, siwa ma tcubkem iyi s Öebbi, ard a yi t id terrem, siwa ma zzin awen". Mi s âahden, inna: "Öebbi d Awkil $ef wayen id nenna".'),
(1663, 12, 67, 'Inna: "a tarwa, ur keççmet si yiwet n tebburt, kecmet si tebbura imgarraden. Ula i wen xedme$, bippa, ar loiha n Öebbi. Aêuddu siwa win n Öebbi. FellaS ppekle$, fellaS ay ppeklen wid ippkalen".'),
(1664, 12, 68, 'Mi kecmen akken i sen iumeô babat sen, ula i sen ixdem, bippa, ar loiha n Öebbi. D ayen ilezmen kan i iseyya Yaqub, deg iman is. Neppa, s tidep, isâa tamusni i s Nesselmed, maca tegwti n yimdanen ur ssinen.'),
(1665, 12, 69, 'Mi kecmen ar Yusef, ibbwi gma s $uôes, inna: "nekkini d gma k, ur $webbel $ef wayen xeddmen".'),
(1666, 12, 70, 'Mi sen ifka ppâabgat nnsen, irra taqbuct deg ucekkaô n gma s. Sinna, iberreê uberraê: "a yat terkaf, kunwi, war ccekk, d imakwaren"!'),
(1667, 12, 71, 'Nnan, u zzin $uôsen: "d acu tesôuêem"?'),
(1668, 12, 72, 'Nnan: "nesôuê taqbuct ugellid. Win ip id ibbwin, ad as nefk ppâabga n ul$wem. Nek, vemne$ t".'),
(1669, 12, 73, 'Nnan: "s Öebbi, nni$ teéôam ur d nusa ara a nessefsed tamurt, ur nelli d imakwaren".'),
(1670, 12, 74, 'Nnan: "d acu ay d aqeîîi s, ma teskadbem"?'),
(1671, 12, 75, 'Nnan: " aqeîîi n win i p ibbwin di tcekkaôt is, d yiman is. Akka ay nepkafi imednas".'),
(1672, 12, 76, 'Ibda la ipqellib icekkaôen, uqbel win n gma s, sinna, issuffe$ ip id seg ucekkaô n gma s. Akka ay Nefka ticeôkep i Yusef. Ur izmir ad iîîef gma s, s lqanun ugellid, siwa ma Irad Öebbi. Nessalay, tiseddaôin, win i £ihwan. Sennig bu tussna, illa Umusnaw.'),
(1673, 12, 77, 'Nnan: "ma iuker, ni$ iuker, zik, yiwen n watma s". Iffer ip Yusef $uôes, ur asen p id inna ara. Inna: "aql akwen deg yir êala. Öebbi Yif akw akken Iéôa ayen d teqqaôem".'),
(1674, 12, 78, 'Nnan: "a yameqwôan, baba s, s tidep, wesser. Eîîef yiwen segne$ deg umekkan is. Nwala k, ih, telliv si lâuûam".'),
(1675, 12, 79, 'Inna: "ur a$ Iâammed Öebbi a neîîef, siwa win u$uô nufa ta$awsa nne$. Mulac, war ccekk, a nili d imednas".'),
(1676, 12, 80, 'Mi uysen segs, mcawaôen, inna umeqwôan segsen: "day ur teéôim ara, ar babat wen tcubkem t s Öebbi, u, zik, tveggâam Yusef? Ihi, ur pôuêu$ si tmurt a, d awez$i, alamma iserreê iyi baba, ne$ Ifra Öebbi felli. Neppa, Yif akw imêaddan.'),
(1677, 12, 81, 'U$alet ar babat wen, tinem as: a babat nne$, mmi k, s tidep, iuker. Ncehhed kan $ef wayen neéôa, ur nessawev i tbavnit.'),
(1678, 12, 82, 'Steqsi tamdint ideg i nella, akked terkift ukud nedda. Ih, d tidep, ay d nenna".'),
(1679, 12, 83, 'Inna: "xaîi! Lameô seg iman nnwen. Ilha ûûbeô. Amar Öebbi a yi ten id Iawi akw. Neppa, s tidep, d Bab n ûûwab, d Amusnaw".'),
(1680, 12, 84, 'Ijuneb iten, u inna: "a lêif iw $ef Yusef"! Allen is ijegger itent u$ilif, innu$ben.'),
(1681, 12, 85, 'Nnan: "s Öebbi, tezgiv tesmektayev d Yusef, alamma tu$alev d amuvin, ne$ seg wid immuten".'),
(1682, 12, 86, 'Inna: "la pcetki$ kan i Öebbi, s uneémi w akked u$wbel iw. Ssne$, s$uô Öebbi, ayen ur tessinem.'),
(1683, 12, 87, 'A yarraw iw, ôuêet, steqsit $ef Yusef akked gma s. Ur ppayset di tecvaî n Öebbi. Ih, i ippaysen di tecvaî n Öebbi, siwa agdud ijehliyen".'),
(1684, 12, 88, 'Mi bbwven $uôes, nnan as: "a yameqwôan, nekwni akked twacult nne$, nepwa$. Nusa d s selâa ôxisen, semd as lkil, seddeq a$. Öebbi, s tidep, Ipkafi wid ipseddiqen".'),
(1685, 12, 89, 'Inna: "teéôam i tgam i Yusef akked gma s, mi kunwi, d wid ur nessin"?'),
(1686, 12, 90, 'Nnan: "keçç, s tidep, maççi d Yusef "? Inna: "nek d Yusef, atan gma. Ni$ I$at a$ Öebbi. Ih, wid ipêezziben, wid iûebbôen ... Öebbi, s tidep, ur Isôuêu arraz iâaôviyen".'),
(1687, 12, 91, 'Nnan: "s Öebbi ar k Ismenyaf Öebbi garane$. Nekwni, s tidep, neccev".'),
(1688, 12, 92, 'Inna: "ur telli tiyta degwen, assa. Ad awen Isemmeê Öebbi! Neppa Yif akw wid ipêunun.'),
(1689, 12, 93, 'Awit tasedrit iw agi, erret ep $ef udem n baba, ad iêlu yiéôi s. Aset ed $uôi, s twacult nnwen, meôôa".'),
(1690, 12, 94, 'Mi teqlaâ terkift, babat sen ibda la iqqaô: "nek, s tidep, sraêe$ rriêa n Yusef, awi d kan ur teqqaôem ara: la isxeôwiv".'),
(1691, 12, 95, 'Nnan: "s Öebbi, ar k mazal di ttelfan ik n zik".'),
(1692, 12, 96, 'Mi d iusa ubcir, issers as p $ef udem is, llint ed wallen is, inna: "day ur awen nni$ ara: nek ssne$, s$uô Öebbi, ayen ur tessinem"?'),
(1693, 12, 97, 'Nnan as: "a babat nne$, ssuter ad a$ pwasemmêen ibekkaven nne$. S tidep, nella d imednab".'),
(1694, 12, 98, 'Inna: "deqqal ad ssutre$, i Mass iw, ad awen Isemmeê. Neppa, s tidep, Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu".'),
(1695, 12, 99, 'Mi bbwven ar Yusef, isteôêeb s imawlan is. Inna: "kecmet ar Maseô, di laman, ma Irad Öebbi".'),
(1696, 12, 100, 'Issuli imawlan is ar usgeld. £lin, knan as. Inna: "a baba! D wagi ay d asefru n targit iw, n zik. Ni$ Issuffe$ ip Mass iw! Ni$ Iga yi leqôaô mi yi d Issuffe$ si lêebs. Ikkes ikwen id si sseêôa, deffir tismin i isker Cciîan, gari d watma. Mass iw, s tidep, d Laîif i win i S ihwan. Ih, Neppa d Amusnaw, d Bab n ûûwab.'),
(1697, 12, 101, 'A Mass iw, ni$ Tefkiv iyi si tgelda, Tesêefvev iyi asefru n temsal. Axellaq n tmurt akked igenwan, Keçç, d Bab iw di ddunit, di laxeôt, Eddem ôôuê iw d amvua, Ssiwev iyi ar wid imaânen".'),
(1698, 12, 102, 'Tagi, si teêkayin n tbavnit, Nweêêa yak p in. Ur telliv $uôsen, mi mwafaqen a p andin.'),
(1699, 12, 103, 'Tegwti n yimdanen, xas tâapbev, ur ppamnen.'),
(1700, 12, 104, 'Ur asen ssutur kra n teqdiât. Neppa, d asmekti kan i imavalen.'),
(1701, 12, 105, 'I illan deg issekniyen di tmurt akked igenwan! La teddun fellasen, maca wexxôen asen.'),
(1702, 12, 106, 'Tegwti, segsen, ur ppamnen s Öebbi, siwa ma curken.'),
(1703, 12, 107, 'Day ppeklen ur asen isburru yara uâaqeb n Öebbi, ne$ ur ten id ippas ara yimir, deqzalla, ur pfaqan?'),
(1704, 12, 108, 'Ini: "wagi d abrid iw, la pnuju$ ar Öebbi ad Ildi allen, i nek akked wid iddan yidi. Gedha s Öebbi! Ur lli$ seg wid ipcaraken".'),
(1705, 12, 109, 'Nuzen ed kan, uqbel ik, irgazen seg imezda$ n temdinin, iwumi Nweêêa. Day ur unagen ara di tmurt, ad walin amek tevôa d wid i ten id izwaren? Ih, pifxiô axxam aneggaru i wid ipêezziben. Day ur tefhimem ara?'),
(1706, 12, 110, 'Alamma, mi uysen imazanen, u meyyzen ar skaddben ten, tusa ten id tallalt s$uône£. Nepsellik win i £ ihwan. Ur ipwakkas ara ssxev nne£, i ugdud ibe$wviyen.'),
(1707, 12, 111, 'Ni$, di teêkayin nnsen, illa uselmed i yuâqilen. Ur telli d awal id innulfan. Neppat tetebbet ed ay d izwaren, tfeûûel ed yal cci. D nnhaya u d aêunu i ugdud iumnen.');
INSERT INTO `ber_mensur` (`index`, `sura`, `aya`, `text`) VALUES
(1708, 13, 1, 'Almô. Wigi d issekniyen n Tezmamt. Ayen i k d irsen, s$uô Mass ik, d tidep, maca tegwti n medden ur ppamnen.'),
(1709, 13, 2, 'Öebbi i Issulin igenwan war tigwejda ara twalim, sinna, Iâannec $ef usgeld. Iêeppem i yiîij d waggur ad ddun, akw, ar lajel ipwassnen. Iseyyi lameô, Ipfeûûil issekniyen, amar a pepputebbtem $ef temlilit d Mass nnwen.'),
(1710, 13, 3, 'Neppa i Isswesâen tamurt. Irra degs idurar, isaffen. Irra tayuga di yal ppemôa. Ip$ummu ass s yiv. Deg waya, s tidep, d issekniyen i ugdud ipxemmimen.'),
(1711, 13, 4, 'Di tmurt, tibêirin tioiratin, leonanat n téuôin, nnaâma, tizdayin, v$an ne$ ur v$in, cerken aman nnsen. Nesmenyaf kra i kra, i wuççi. Deg waya, s tidep, d issekniyen i ugdud ifehmen.'),
(1712, 13, 5, 'Ma twehmev, issewham ay d qqaôen: "ma nu$al d akal, day fella$, s tidep, lxelq amaynut"? D wigi i inekôen Mass nnsen. Wigi, azaglu $ef tmegôav. Wigi d at tmes, nitni, degs, ad wekkôen.'),
(1713, 13, 6, 'Sêaren k ar tucmip, uqbel ise$. Ni$ vôant am tigi, uqbel nnsen. Mass ik, s tidep, $uôeS ssmaê i imdanen deg wayen ccven. Mass ik, s tidep, Iwâaô deg uâaqeb.'),
(1714, 13, 7, 'La qqaôen wid ijehlen: "a lemmer id irs $uôes ussekni, s$uô Mass is". Keçç, d aneddaô kan. I yal agdud, win inehhun.'),
(1715, 13, 8, 'Öebbi Iéôa i illan di yal tadist, amek teddun inzikmiren. Yal cci, $uôeS, s lmizan.'),
(1716, 13, 9, 'Amusnaw n wayen iffren akked wayen ur neffir. Ameqwôan, Aâlayan.'),
(1717, 13, 10, 'Iâuva segwen win i$emven awal, d win it iberêen, win iffren deg iv, d win d ivehôen deg wass.'),
(1718, 13, 11, 'Isâa iâssasen zdat es, deffir es, pêaraben fellas, s lameô n Öebbi. Öebbi, s tidep, ur Ipbeddil i illan deg ugdud, alamma bedlen i illan deg iman nnsen. Ma Irad Öebbi ayen n dir, i ugdud, ur t itekkes yiwen. Ur sâin amâiwen, war Neppa.'),
(1719, 13, 12, 'D Neppa i wen d Ippawin lebôaq, degs tugdi, asirem. Isskar ed asigna aéayan.'),
(1720, 13, 13, 'Tesbuccuâ aS termegt, s ccekôan, akken lmalayek, seg wakken ugadent eP. Ippazen ed ssiâqat, Ipêaz yisent win i S ihwan. Nitni pnamaren $ef Öebbi. Neppa teqseê tezmert iS.'),
(1721, 13, 14, '£uô Neppa, anuju n tidep. Wid u$uô la pnujun, war Neppa, ur asen d pparan s wacemma. Am win issendin ifassen i waman, ib$a ad awven s imi s, ur ibbwiv ar leb$i s. Anuju ijehliyen ar ttelfan kan.'),
(1722, 13, 15, 'I Öebbi la kennun wid illan di tmurt akked igenwan, b$an ne$ ugin, akked tili nnsen, taûebêit, tameddit.'),
(1723, 13, 16, 'Ini: "anwa ay d Mass n tmurt akked igenwan"? Ini: "d Öebbi. Ihi day a pperrem d iêbiben, war Neppa, wid ur nemlik, i yiman nnsen, aba$uô ne$ vveôô"? Ini: "day iaâdel uder$al akked win ipwalin? Ne$, day âadlent tillas akked tafat? Ne$, rran imcurak i Öebbi, i ixelqen am lxelq iS, ufan t ippemcabi"? Ini: "d Öebbi i Ixelqen yal cci. D Neppa ay d Yiwen, d Aqehhaô".'),
(1724, 13, 17, 'Isse$lay ed aman, seg igenni. Serrun deg $ezôan, s leqdeô nnsen. Acercuô ippawi ikuftan ippifliwen. Ppemcabin ikuftan ar wayen fessin di tmes, iwakken ad ûenâen ôôêuê ne$ dduzan. Akka ay d Isskan Öebbi tidep akked tkerkas. Ihi ikuftan ad ppuveggôen, ma d wayen inefâen medden, a d igwri di tmurt. Akka ay d Ippak Öebbi imedyaten.'),
(1725, 13, 18, 'Lfayeq i wid ijawben i Mass nnsen. Wid ur aS njaweb ara, xas ad sâun i illan akw di tmurt, berdayen, ur ten id ifeddu. I widak, leêsab adiran. Axxam nnsen d Loahennama. A tanezdu$t tucmip!'),
(1726, 13, 19, 'Day win iéôan ar ayen i k d irsen, s$uô Mass ik, d tidep, am win idre$len? Siwa uâqilen id ismektayen.'),
(1727, 13, 20, 'Wid iîîfen di laâqed n Öebbi, ur pôuéun nnesba.'),
(1728, 13, 21, 'Wid issemlilen ayen id Iumeô Öebbi ad imlil, u ppagwaden Mass nnsen, u ppagwaden aqeîîi adiran.'),
(1729, 13, 22, 'Wid iûebôen, ssaramen udem n Mass nnsen, bedden i téallit, pseddiqen seg wayen is iten N$at, s tuffra u âinâni, swexxiôen tucmip s yise$. I nitni, agwav s Axxam.'),
(1730, 13, 23, 'Leonanat n Âaden ara kecmen, akked wid ixeddmen ayen ilhan, seg ibabaten nnsen, si tlawin nnsen, si tarwa nnsen. Lmalayek a d ppasent $uôsen si yal tabburt.'),
(1731, 13, 24, 'Tifrat fellawen, ilmend n wayen tûebôem! D asaâdi, wagwav s Axxam!'),
(1732, 13, 25, 'Wid ipôuéun laâqed n Öebbi, deffir lemwafaqa s, wid igezmen ayen d Iumeô Öebbi ad imlil, u ssefsaden di tmurt, wigi, i nitni xezzu, i nitni yir axxam.'),
(1733, 13, 26, 'Öebbi Issugut ôôeéq i win i S ihwan, u Iwezzen. Taâoeb iten tmeddurt n ddunit. Tameddurt n ddunit, d urar kan, zdat laxeôt.'),
(1734, 13, 27, 'La qqaôen wid ijehlen: "a lemmer id iris, $uôes, ussekni s$uô Mass is"! Ini: "Öebbi, s tidep, Itellif win i S ihwan. Inehhu $uôeS, wid isteôoiâen,'),
(1735, 13, 28, 'wid iumnen, iwumi itheddin wul, mara d mmektin Öebbi". Ni$, s usmekti n Öebbi, pheddinen wulawen.'),
(1736, 13, 29, 'Ssaâd, akked taggara igerzen, i wid iumnen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan.'),
(1737, 13, 30, 'Akka ay k id Nuzen, i lois id zwaren leoyus, ad asen temlev, ayen ik d Nweêêa. Nitni jehlen $uô Uênin. Ini: "Neppa d Mass iw, ur illi ôebbi siwa Neppa; ppekle$ fellaS, asteôoaâ iw $uôeS".'),
(1738, 13, 31, 'A lemmer kan Leqwôan isselêa idurar, iceqqeq tamurt, ne$ issenîeq ed lmeggtin! Xaîi! Lumuô akw i Öebbi. Day ur éôin ara wid iumnen, ar, ma ihwa yaS, Öebbi ad Inhu medden meôôa? Zgan wid ijehlen a ten tewwet ssixîa, ilmend n wayen xeddmen. Ne$ a ppevôu ar tama n yixxamen nnsen, alamma tusa d lemâahda n Öebbi. Öebbi, s tidep, ur Ipzeggil ppaâud.'),
(1739, 13, 32, 'Ni$ mmaâlken, uqbel ik, deg imazanen. Ooi$ lmudda i wid ijehlen, sinna, Ïîfe$ ten. A yaâaqeb iW imiren!'),
(1740, 13, 33, 'Day Win Ibedden, ar yal amdan, $ef wayen ikseb…? Curken aS i Öebbi. Ini: "semmit asen! Ne$, ad aS temlem ayen ur Iéôi di tmurt? Ne$ d ismawen n tkerkas"? Xaîi! Wid ijehlen, âaobent pen nncub nnsen. Ppuveôôfen seg ubrid. Win Itlef Öebbi, ur isâi w ara t inhun.'),
(1741, 13, 34, 'Fellasen aâaqeb, di tmeddurt n ddunit. Aâaqeb n laxert, s tidep, aâer. Ur sâin ara ten ifukken, seg ufus n Öebbi.'),
(1742, 13, 35, 'Amek tga Loennet i ippuweââden i wid iêezzben: ddaw as isaffen ppazzalen, lqut is akked tili s, d imezgiyen. D tagi ay d taggara n wid iêezzben. Taggara ijehliyen, d times.'),
(1743, 13, 36, 'Wid iwumi Nefka Tazmamt, ad feôêen s wayen i k d irsen. Illa wayen ugin kra ikabaren. Ini: "pwamôe$ kan ad âabde$ Öebbi, ur aS pcarake$. Pnuju$ $uôeS, tu$alin iw $uôeS".'),
(1744, 13, 37, 'Akka ay t id Nessers, d ûûwab, s taâôabt. Ma teddiv d lhawiyya nnsen, deffir tisin n tussna $uôek, ur k ipfukku bab ne$ asettaô, seg ufus n Öebbi.'),
(1745, 13, 38, 'Ni$ Nuzen ed imazanen, uqbel ik, Nefka yasen tilawin, tarwa. Ur ippunefk ara i umazan a d iawi assekni siwa ma Iâammed Öebbi. Yal lajel s Tezmamt is.'),
(1746, 13, 39, 'Iseffev u Itebbit Öebbi ay S ihwan. £uôeS tayimmap n Tezmamt.'),
(1747, 13, 40, 'Ama Nessken ak kra n wayen i sen Nâahed, ama Neddem ôôuê ik, ay fellak kan d isallen, ay fella£ d aqeîîi.'),
(1748, 13, 41, 'Day ur walan ara Neppas ed ar tmurt, Nessenqas di leryaf is? Öebbi Ipseyyi; yiwen ur ipnamar aseyyi iS. Neppa, Ip$awal di leêsab.'),
(1749, 13, 42, 'Ni$ ppandin wid i ten id izwaren. Tiêeôci, akw, ar Öebbi. Iéôa i ikseb yal iman. Ad éôen ijehliyen anwa ara iawven s Axxam.'),
(1750, 13, 43, 'Qqaôen wid ijehlen: "ur telliv d amazan". Ini: "ad Iqadd Öebbi d Anagi gari yidwen, akked kra isâan tussna n Tazmamt".');
INSERT INTO `ber_mensur` (`index`, `sura`, `aya`, `text`) VALUES
(1751, 14, 1, 'Alô. Tazmamt, Nessers ak p id, iwakken a ppessuff$ev imdanen si tillas ar tafat, s wannuf n Mass nnsen, s abrid n Wuzmir, Amaâzuz,'),
(1752, 14, 2, 'Öebbi ilan i illan deg igenwan, i illan di tmurt. A ssxev ijehliyen, ilmend uâaqeb uqsiê,'),
(1753, 14, 3, 'i ismenyafen tameddurt n ddunit wala laxeôt, i iswexxiôen seg ubrid n Öebbi, u ssaramen t d uâwij! Widak, atnan di ttelfan u$miq.'),
(1754, 14, 4, 'Ur d Nuzen amazan, siwa s tmeslayt n ugdud is, iwakken ad asen ibeggen. Öebbi Itellif win i S ihwan, Inehhu win i S ihwan. Neppa d Uzmir, d Bab n ûûwab.'),
(1755, 14, 5, 'Ih, ni$ Nuzen ed Musa, s issekniyen nne£: "ssuffe$ agdud ik, si tillas ar tafat. Mmekti yas d ussan n Öebbi". Deg waya, war ccekk, d issekniyen i yal aûebôi isnemmiren.'),
(1756, 14, 6, 'Mi inna Musa i ugdud is: "mmektit ed l$it ikwen I$at Öebbi, mi kwen Isellek si lois n Ferâun, i issuken fellawen lhemm uqsiê. Zellun arrac nnwen, ssidiren tilawin nnwen. Deg waya, s$uô Mass nnwen, d cedda tameqwôaêant".'),
(1757, 14, 7, 'Mi d Inna Mass nnwen: "ma tesnemmrem, ih, ad awen Rnu$. Ma tjehlem, aâaqeb iW, war ccekk, ad iwâaô".'),
(1758, 14, 8, 'Inna Musa: "ma tjehlem, kunwi akked wid n tmurt meôôa, ihi, Öebbi d Asâay, d Amaâzuz".'),
(1759, 14, 9, 'Day ur kwen id ibbwiv ara usali imezwura nnwen: agdud n Nuê, Âad, Tamud, akked wid iten ivefôen? Ur ten issin yiwen, siwa Öebbi. Usan ten id imazanen nnsen, s ubeggen. Rran ifassen nnsen s imawen nnsen, nnan: "S tidep, nejhel ayen i$ef d teppuceggâam. Ih, nekwni di ccekk imcebbwel, $ef wayen u$uô la $ tneccdem".'),
(1760, 14, 10, 'Nnan imazanen nnsen: "day illa ccekk di Öebbi, Axellaq n tmurt akked igenwan? Inecced ikwen id, iwakken ad awen Isemmeê kra ibekkaven nnwen, a kwen Ioo ar lajel ipwassnen". Nnan: "kunwi, s tidep, d imdanen kan, am nekwni. Teb$am ad a$ tesîixxôem, seg wayen llan âabden imezwura nne$. Awit a$ d adabu n ûûeê".'),
(1761, 14, 11, 'Nnan asen imazanen nnsen: "nekwni d imdanen kan, am kunwi, maca Öebbi Iteg ccan i win i S ihwan, deg imdanen iS. Ur a$ ippunefk ara ad awen d nawi adabu, siwa s wannuf n Öebbi. £ef Öebbi ara ppeklen lmumnin.'),
(1762, 14, 12, 'Acu i $ iu$en, ur nepkal ara $ef Öebbi? Ni$ Imla ya$ iberdan nne$; neûbeô, war ccekk, i lmerta i tesâaddam fella$. £ef Öebbi ara ppeklen, at letkal".'),
(1763, 14, 13, 'Nnan wid ijehlen i imazanen nnsen: "war ccekk, a kwen nessuffe$ si tmurt nne$, ne$ a d tu$alem ar ddin nne$". Iweêêa yasen d Mass nnsen: "s tidep, a Nesqucc imednas,'),
(1764, 14, 14, 'd$a, war ccekk, a kwen Nerr d imezda$ n tmurt, deffir sen". Ayagi, i win ippagwaden tilin iW, ippagwaden aberri W.'),
(1765, 14, 15, 'Ssarmen l$elb. Ixseô yal aqehhaô amnafeq.'),
(1766, 14, 16, 'Loahennama deffir es, ad ites aman iwexmiyen.'),
(1767, 14, 17, 'Tissit d tije$wimin, ur izmir ad isseblaâ. Tameppant a d teppas si yal tamnaî, neppa ur ipmeppat. Deffir es aâaqeb uqsiê.'),
(1768, 14, 18, 'Amedya n wid ijehlen, ar Mass nnsen: igiten nnsen am i$i$den i$ef iédem wavu, ass n tbucivant. Ur d ppawin acemma, seg wayen kesben. D wagi ay d ttelfan u$miq.'),
(1769, 14, 19, 'Day ur twalav ara, Öebbi Ixleq tamurt akked igenwan, s tidep? Ma ihwa yaS, a kwen Ikkes, a d Iawi lxelq amaynut.'),
(1770, 14, 20, 'Ayagi, i Öebbi, ur illi d ayen izzenzafen.'),
(1771, 14, 21, 'A d rsen akw zdat Öebbi. Ad inin uôhifen i imzuxiyen: "s tidep, nella nedda yidwen, ma tzemrem ad a$ tsellkem kra, seg uâaqeb n Öebbi"? A d inin: "lemmer i $ Inha Öebbi, yili nwelleh ikwen. Iâuva fella$, neêmeq ne$ neûbeô, ur a$ illi ssôan".'),
(1772, 14, 22, 'Mi isuyya lameô, a d yini Cciîan: "Öebbi, d ûûeê, Iweââd awen lemâahda n tidep. Weââde$ awen, $uôe$ kwen. Ur sâi$ adabu fellawen, siwa anecced nnwen. Tu$em awal iw. Ur iyi plummut, lummet iman nnwen. Ur zmire$ a kwen âawne$, ur tezmirem ad iyi tâawnem. Nekôe$ wid iyi tepcarakem, zik. I imednas, s tidep, aâaqeb aqeôêan".'),
(1773, 14, 23, 'Ad skecmen wid iumnen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan, ar leonanat, ddawat sen isaffen ppazzalen, ad wekkôen dinna, s wannuf n Mass nnsen. Azul nnsen dinna d: "tifrat"!'),
(1774, 14, 24, 'Day ur twalav ara, amek id Ifka Öebbi amedya? Awal lâali am ttejôa lâali, iéuôan is ôûan, iferkawen is di tegnewt.'),
(1775, 14, 25, 'Teppak ed lfakia s, di yal imir, s wannuf n Mass is. Ippawi d Öebbi imedyaten i imdanen, amar a d mmektin.'),
(1776, 14, 26, 'Amedya n wawal ucmit, am ttejôa tucmip, teqlaâ sennig wakal, war leqôaô.'),
(1777, 14, 27, 'Öebbi Itebbit wid iumnen s wawal utebbet, di tmeddurt n ddunit akked laxeôt. Öebbi Itellif imednas. Öebbi Ixeddem ayen i S ihwan.'),
(1778, 14, 28, 'Day ur twalav ara wid ineûfen l$it n Öebbi, s tijehli? Ssersen agdud nnsen deg uxxam n twa$it.'),
(1779, 14, 29, 'Loahennama ad ô$en degs: a yir leqôaô!'),
(1780, 14, 30, 'Gan aS i Öebbi tanudda, iwakken ad telfen seg ubrid iS. Ini: "zzhut! S tidep, leqôaô nnwen d times".'),
(1781, 14, 31, 'Ini i imdanen iW iumnen, ad bedden i téallit, ad seddqen seg wayen iten N$at, s tuffra u âinani, uqbel a d ias wass ideg ur illi ssuq, ur telli tdukli.'),
(1782, 14, 32, 'Öebbi i Ixelqen tamurt akked igenwan, id Isse$layen aman seg igenni, Issufu$ ed yissen ppemôa, d ôôeéq i kunwi. Inub fellawen s isaffen, u s lbabuô i iteddun di yill, s lameô iS.'),
(1783, 14, 33, 'Inub fellawen s yiîij d waggur, d imezgiyen. Inub fellawen s yiv akked wass.'),
(1784, 14, 34, 'Ifka yawen seg wayen akw i S tessutrem. Ma pêesbem l$it n Mass nnwen, ur tessawavem. Ih, amdan, s tidep, d amednus, d ajehli.'),
(1785, 14, 35, 'Mi inna Ibôahim: "a Mass iw! Err tamdint agi d tin n laman, Âatq a$, nek d warraw iw, seg wannuz n tâancuôin.'),
(1786, 14, 36, 'A Mass iw, nitenti, s tidep, telfent aîas n medden. Win iddan yidi, neppa, s tidep, sgi. Win iyi âuûan, Keçç, s tidep, Tepsemmiêev, Tepêunuv.'),
(1787, 14, 37, 'A Mass nne$! Nek rri$ tanezdu$t, i kra n warraw iw, di te$zut ibuôen, ar Uxxam iK iôqan. A Mass nne$! Iwakken ad bedden i téallit. Err ulawen n kra n medden, ad iêninen $uôsen, £it iten s ppemôat, amar ad snemmren.'),
(1788, 14, 38, 'A Mass nne$! Keçç, s tidep, Teéôiv ayen neffer akked wayen nenna. Ur iffir wacemma i Öebbi, di tmurt ne$ deg igenni.'),
(1789, 14, 39, 'Ccekôan i Öebbi iyi d Ifkan, di tewser iw, Ismaâil akked Isêaq. Mass iw, s tidep, Issemêas i tnaâôit.'),
(1790, 14, 40, 'A Mass iw, Err iyi ad bedde$ i téallit. Akked kra, si tarwa w. A Mass iw, Steôêeb s unuju w.'),
(1791, 14, 41, 'A Mass nne$! Semmeê ane$, nek d lwaldin iw, akked lmumnin, ass ideg ara d ias uqeîîi".'),
(1792, 14, 42, 'Ur p$ili ar I$fel Öebbi, $ef wayen xeddmen imednas. Iooa ten kan, ar ass ideg ara beêêren allen.'),
(1793, 14, 43, 'Ad p$awalen, iqweôôa ff$en d, allen ur ferzent, ulawen d ilmawen.'),
(1794, 14, 44, 'Nabi imdanen af wass ideg ara ten id yas uâaqeb. Ad inin wid idensen: "a Mass nne$! Efk ane$ lmudda wezzilen, a d njaweb i unabi K, a neddu d imazanen". "Day ur teggulem ara kunwi, zik, ar ur tep$abem?'),
(1795, 14, 45, 'Tzed$em ixxamen n wid ivuôôen iman nnsen. U Nbeggen awen d amek i sen Nga, u Nefka yawen d imedyaten".'),
(1796, 14, 46, 'Ni$ undin ccbukat nnsen. Ccbukat nnsen haatent ar Öebbi, xas ma ccbukat nnsen d tid ara isse$lin idurar.'),
(1797, 14, 47, '£uôek a p$ilev Öebbi ad Izgel lemâahda S, i imazanen. S tidep, Öebbi d Uzmir, Ippara d ppaô.'),
(1798, 14, 48, 'Ass ideg tamurt a ppu$al maççi d tamurt; akken igenwan; a d asen ar Öebbi Yiwen, Aqehhaô.'),
(1799, 14, 49, 'A pwaliv, assen, ibe$wviyen pwaqqnen wa $er wa.'),
(1800, 14, 50, 'Lebsa nnsen d qevôan, times t$umm udmawen nnsen.'),
(1801, 14, 51, 'Iwakken ad Ikafi Öebbi yal amdan, $ef wayen ikseb. Öebbi, s tidep, Ip$awal di leêsab.'),
(1802, 14, 52, 'Wagi d anecced i imdanen, ad pwanedôen yis, ad éôen ar siwa Neppa ay d Öebbi Yiwen, a d mmektin uâqilen.');
INSERT INTO `ber_mensur` (`index`, `sura`, `aya`, `text`) VALUES
(1803, 15, 1, 'Alô. Wigi d issekniyen n Tezmamt, u d Leqwôan ipbegginen.'),
(1804, 15, 2, 'Ahat wid ijehlen ssaramen ad ilin d imvuâen.'),
(1805, 15, 3, 'Eoo iten ad ççen, ad zhun, a ten issedhu usirem. Deqqal ad éôen.'),
(1806, 15, 4, 'Ur Nesquccu tamdint, siwa ma d ayen i s iuran, ipwassnen.'),
(1807, 15, 5, 'Ur illi lois ara d isqeôben, ne$ ara iswexxôen lajel is.'),
(1808, 15, 6, 'Nnan: "a win u$uô d irs usmekti! Keçç, war ccekk, d aôehbani.'),
(1809, 15, 7, 'Acimi ur a$ d tusiv ara, s lmalayek, ma d tidep ay tessawalev"?'),
(1810, 15, 8, 'Ur Nesrusu lmalayek, siwa s tidep. Imiren, ur pganin.'),
(1811, 15, 9, 'Ih, Nekwni Nessers ed asmekti. Ih, Nekwni a Nêareb fellas.'),
(1812, 15, 10, 'Ni$ Nuzen ed, uqbel ik, i ikabaren imezwura.'),
(1813, 15, 11, 'Ur ten id ippas umazan, mebla ma ttahan fellas.'),
(1814, 15, 12, 'Akka ay t Nessekcam deg ulawen ibe$wviyen.'),
(1815, 15, 13, 'Ur uminen yis, ulamma ooan d imezwura tannumi.'),
(1816, 15, 14, 'Xas ad asen Nelli tabburt igenni, ad ppalin $uôes,'),
(1817, 15, 15, 'a d inin, war ccekk: "ittules iéôi nne$, ne$ nekwni d agdud iwumi sseêren".'),
(1818, 15, 16, 'Ni$ Nerra itran deg igenni. Ncebbeê iten i wid ipmuqulen.'),
(1819, 15, 17, 'Nesdari ten, si yal cciîan imenfi.'),
(1820, 15, 18, 'Kkes ed win d issemêessen s tufra, A p iddu, fellas, ujajiê n ûûeê.'),
(1821, 15, 19, 'Tamurt Nessewsaâ p; Nerra fellas idurar; Nessem$i d, degs, yal cci, s lmizan.'),
(1822, 15, 20, 'Nerra, degs, lqut i kunwi, akw i wid ur tecceççayem ara.'),
(1823, 15, 21, 'Lexzayen n yal cci, $uône£ kan. Siwa s lkil ipwassnen i ten id Nesrusu.'),
(1824, 15, 22, 'Nuzen ed avu isswayen. Nesse$li d aman seg igenni, yissen Nessew ikwen. Ur llin ara lexzayen is $uôwen.'),
(1825, 15, 23, 'Ih, d Nekwni i Issidiren, i Ineqqen. D Nekwni ay d Iweôôaten.'),
(1826, 15, 24, 'Ni$ Nessen imezwura nnwen, Nessen ineggura.'),
(1827, 15, 25, 'Ih, Mass ik, Neppa, a ten id Ifser. Ih, Neppa, d Bab n ûûwab, d Amusnaw.'),
(1828, 15, 26, 'Ni$ Nexleq amdan si talaxt taberkant i meslen.'),
(1829, 15, 27, 'Nexleq loenn, iu$ lêal, si tmes n ccili.'),
(1830, 15, 28, 'Mi Inna Mass ik, i lmalayek: "Nek Xelqe$ amdan, si talaxt taberkant i meslen.'),
(1831, 15, 29, 'Mi t Mesle$, u Üûuve$ as si ôôuê iW, ersemt $uôes, knumt".'),
(1832, 15, 30, 'Knant akw lmalayek, akken ma llant,'),
(1833, 15, 31, 'siwa Iblis, iugi ad yili ar wid iknan.'),
(1834, 15, 32, 'Inna: "a yIblis, acu ik iu$en, ur telliv ar wid iknan"?'),
(1835, 15, 33, 'Inna: "ur kennu$ i umdan, i Txelqev si talaxt taberkant i meslen".'),
(1836, 15, 34, 'Inna: "effe$ segs! Aql ak, ihi, d imenfi.'),
(1837, 15, 35, 'Ih, fellak ddell alamma d ass uqeîîi".'),
(1838, 15, 36, 'Inna: "a Mass iw! Eoo iyi alamma d ass n tnekra nnsen".'),
(1839, 15, 37, 'Inna: "ih, keçç seg wid ipganin,'),
(1840, 15, 38, 'ar ass n yiùmir ipwassnen".'),
(1841, 15, 39, 'Inna: "a Mass iw! Imi yi Terriv d a$ewway, war ccekk, ad asen cebbêe$ ddunit, a ten $ewwu$, akken ma llan.'),
(1842, 15, 40, 'Kkes ed imdanen iK izedganen garasen".'),
(1843, 15, 41, 'Inna: "$uôI, wagi d abrid uwqim.'),
(1844, 15, 42, 'War ccekk, ur tesâiv adabu $ef imdanen iW, siwa wid i k ivefôen seg imjaêen".'),
(1845, 15, 43, 'Loahennama, s tidep, d ppaâud nnsen akw.'),
(1846, 15, 44, 'D m ûa tebbura; ar yal tabburt, s urbaâ ines.'),
(1847, 15, 45, 'Ih, wid ipêezziben, di leonanat akked tliwa:'),
(1848, 15, 46, 'kecmet pen di tifrat, akked laman"!'),
(1849, 15, 47, 'Nekkes i illan d dd$el, deg idmaren nnsen. D atmaten, deg imîeôêen, mqabalen.'),
(1850, 15, 48, 'Ur âaggun degsen, ur ten id ssuffu$en segsen.'),
(1851, 15, 49, 'Xebbeô ixdimen iW; Nek, s tidep, Psemmiêe$, Pêunu$.'),
(1852, 15, 50, 'U aâaqeb iW d aâaqeb aqeôêan.'),
(1853, 15, 51, 'Xebbeô iten $ef inebgawen n Ibôahim.'),
(1854, 15, 52, 'Mi kecmen $uôes, nnan: "tifrat"! Inna: "s tidep, nugad ikwen".'),
(1855, 15, 53, 'Nnan: "ur ppagwad, a k nbecceô kan, s uqcic amusnaw".'),
(1856, 15, 54, 'Inna: "tbecceôm iyi d, mi wessre$. Acu iyi d tbeccôem"?'),
(1857, 15, 55, 'Nnan: "Nbecceô ik id, s tidep, ur ppili seg wid iuysen".'),
(1858, 15, 56, 'Inna: "anwa iuysen aêunu n Mass is, siwa im$eôôqen"?'),
(1859, 15, 57, 'Inna: "d acu ay d lmeqsud nnwen, a yimceggâen"?'),
(1860, 15, 58, 'Nnan: "Nekwni, s tidep, neppuceggaâ d s agdud ibe$wviyen.'),
(1861, 15, 59, 'Kkes ed tawacult n Luî, ara nsellek akw,'),
(1862, 15, 60, 'siwa tameîîut is. Ih, Nseyya a ppili, neppat, seg ineggura".'),
(1863, 15, 61, 'Mi ôuêen imceggâen ar twacult n Luî,'),
(1864, 15, 62, 'inna: "kunwi, s tidep, d imdanen ur nessin".'),
(1865, 15, 63, 'Nnan: "xaîi, Nusa d, $uôek, s wayen rran di ccekk.'),
(1866, 15, 64, 'Nusa d, $uôek, s tidep. Nekwni, war ccekk, nessawal tidep.'),
(1867, 15, 65, 'Öuê akked twacult ik, mi mazal yiv. Ddu deffir sen. Ur d itezzi yiwen degwen! Âaddit anda i wen ippunefk lameô".'),
(1868, 15, 66, 'Nseyya yas lameô agi: a d gwrin ad pwagezmen wakali.'),
(1869, 15, 67, 'Usan d, imezda$ n temdint, feôêen.'),
(1870, 15, 68, 'Inna: "wigi, s tidep, d inebgawen iw, ur iyi cmmatet.'),
(1871, 15, 69, 'Ëezbet i Öebbi, ur iyi sdullut"!'),
(1872, 15, 70, 'Nnan: "day ur ak negdil ara imdanen"?'),
(1873, 15, 71, 'Inna: "atent an issi, ma taânam".'),
(1874, 15, 72, 'S tudert ik, ar ddebdeben si ssekôan nnsen!'),
(1875, 15, 73, 'Iwwet iten usu$u, tafrara.'),
(1876, 15, 74, 'Nesrewt ip. Nesse$li d fellasen ageffur n yiéôa n talaxt.'),
(1877, 15, 75, 'Deg waya, s tidep, d issekniyen i wid issnen ad ssikden.'),
(1878, 15, 76, 'Apan, ih, deg ubrid n yal ass.'),
(1879, 15, 77, 'Deg waya, s tidep, d assekni i lmumnin.'),
(1880, 15, 78, 'Ih, llan At Teégi, war ccekk, d imednas.'),
(1881, 15, 79, 'Nerra d ppaô segsen. Ihi, atent an, snat nni, deg ubrid ibanen.'),
(1882, 15, 80, 'Ni$ At Lêioô skaddben imazanen.'),
(1883, 15, 81, 'Nebbwi yasen d issekniyen nne£. Wexxôen asen.'),
(1884, 15, 82, 'Llan qqazen ixxamen n laman, deg idurar.'),
(1885, 15, 83, 'Iwwet iten usu$u, taûebêit.'),
(1886, 15, 84, 'Ulay sen ixdem wayen la keppben.'),
(1887, 15, 85, 'Ur Nexliq tamurt, igenwan, akked wayen illan garasen, siwa s tidep. Imir a d ias, war ccekk. Ihi, ssuref s lekyasa.'),
(1888, 15, 86, 'Ih, Mass ik d Axellaq, d Amusnaw.'),
(1889, 15, 87, 'Ni$ Nefka yak d ûa i usniles, akked Leqwôan ameqwôaêan.'),
(1890, 15, 88, 'Ur pmuqul ar wayen is N$at kra n twaculin nnsen. Ur $webbel ilmend nnsen. Zger tacvaî ik $ef lmumnin.'),
(1891, 15, 89, 'Ini: "nekkini, s tidep, d aneddaô ipbegginen.'),
(1892, 15, 90, 'Akken id Nessers i wid ibvan,'),
(1893, 15, 91, 'i irran Leqwôan d iêricen.'),
(1894, 15, 92, 'S Mass ik, ard a ten Nesteqsi akw'),
(1895, 15, 93, '$ef wayen xeddmen!'),
(1896, 15, 94, 'Ihi, emdeê ayen i$ef i k ippunefk lameô, îixxeô i imcurak.'),
(1897, 15, 95, 'Ih, a k Nqennaâ mgal wid ittihin,'),
(1898, 15, 96, 'i irran ôebbi nniven, ar tama n Öebbi. Deqqal ad éôen.'),
(1899, 15, 97, 'Ni$ Neéôa ar ul ik, keçç, iaâûeô seg wayen qqaôen.'),
(1900, 15, 98, 'Sbuccaâ Mass ik s ccekôan. Ili seg wid ikennun.'),
(1901, 15, 99, 'Aâbed Mass ik, ar k id ias utebbet!');
INSERT INTO `ber_mensur` (`index`, `sura`, `aya`, `text`) VALUES
(1902, 16, 1, 'Ad ias lameô n Öebbi, ur pêirit $uôes. Gedha s yiS! Ay Aâlay, sennig wayen pcaraken.'),
(1903, 16, 2, 'Issrusu d lmalayek s ôôuê si lameô iS, $ef win i S ihwan, deg imdanen iS: "Nedôet ar ur illi ôebbi siwa Nek. Ihi, êezzbet iyI".'),
(1904, 16, 3, 'Ixleq tamurt akked igenwan, s tidep. Ay Aâlay sennig wayen pcaraken!'),
(1905, 16, 4, 'Ixelq ed amdan si tiqqit; atan iu$al aS, d axûim n ûûeê.'),
(1906, 16, 5, 'Ixelq awen d lmal, segsen iceîîiven iêman, aba$uô, u, segsen, teppeppem.'),
(1907, 16, 6, 'D ccbaêa nnwen mara ten id terrem, u mara ten teksem.'),
(1908, 16, 7, 'Ppawin tiâkkwmin nnwen ar tmurt ur teppawvem, siwa ma tâapbem. Ih, Mass nnwen, war ccekk, d Umâin, d Aênin.'),
(1909, 16, 8, 'Iâewdiwen, iserdyan, i$wyal, i rrekba nnwen akked ccbaêa. Ixelleq ayen ur tessinem.'),
(1910, 16, 9, 'D Öebbi i Ippawin d ubrid. Ff$en segs. Ma ihwa yaS, a kwen Inhu meôôa.'),
(1911, 16, 10, 'D Neppa i wen d Isse$layen aman seg igenni. Segsen tissit nnwen, segsen ttjuô i itepp lmal.'),
(1912, 16, 11, 'Isskar awen d yissen nnaâma, azemmur, tizdayin, tiéuôin, akked yal ppemôa. Deg waya, s tidep, assekni i ugdud ipxemmimen.'),
(1913, 16, 12, 'Inub awen d s yiv akked wass, iîij akked waggur. Itran ppemnuben s lameô iS. Deg waya, s tidep, issekniyen i ugdud ifehmen.'),
(1914, 16, 13, 'I wen d Ixleq di tmurt, degs initen imgarraden. Deg waya, s tidep, assekni i ugdud ismektayen.'),
(1915, 16, 14, 'D Neppa i Inuben s yill, iwakken a pteppem, segs, aksum aleqqaq, a d teksem, segs, rrêuê i teppeqqnem. A pwaliv lbabuô ipcerrig it, iwakken a pnadim si lfevl iS, amar a ppesnemmrem.'),
(1916, 16, 15, 'Issers idurar $ef tmurt, ur teppembwiwil yiswen; isaffen, iberdan, amar a ppepwanham;'),
(1917, 16, 16, 'timuliwin: s yitran, nitni pwanhan.'),
(1918, 16, 17, 'Day Win Ixelqen am win ur nxelleq? Day ur d tesmektayem ara?'),
(1919, 16, 18, 'Lemmer a pêesbem l$it n Öebbi, ur tezmirem. Ih, Öebbi, war ccekk, Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu.'),
(1920, 16, 19, 'Öebbi Iéôa ayen teffrem akked wayen teqqaôem.'),
(1921, 16, 20, 'Wid u$uô pnujun, war Öebbi, ur illi wayen xelqen. D nitni i ipwaxelqen.'),
(1922, 16, 21, 'D lmeggtin ur d imuddiren, ur éôin melmi ara ten id ssekren.'),
(1923, 16, 22, 'Öebbi nnwen d Öebbi Yiwen. Wid ur numin ara s laxeôt, d ulawen nnsen i iugin. U nitni pzzuxun.'),
(1924, 16, 23, 'War ccekk, Öebbi Iéôa ayen teffren, akked wayen qqaôen. Neppa, s tidep, ur Iêemmel ara imzuxiyen.'),
(1925, 16, 24, 'Ma nnan asen: "d acu id Issers Mass nnwen"? Qqaôen: "d timucuha imezwura".'),
(1926, 16, 25, 'Ad bibben, ass n tnekra, tiâakkwmin nnsen, s pmam nnsent, akked wumur si tâakkwmin n wid telfen, mebla ma faqen. Day maççi dir it wayen bubben?'),
(1927, 16, 26, 'Ih, undin p, wid i ten id izwaren. Öebbi Iaâtad lebni nnsen, si llsas. I$li d ssqef fellasen. Iusa ten id uâaqeb seg wanda ur bnin.'),
(1928, 16, 27, 'Sinna, ass n tnekra, a ten Idull, ad Yini: "anda ten icriken iW, i$ef temnamarem"? Nnan imawlan n tussna: "war ccekk, ddell akked ddens, assa, $ef ijehliyen'),
(1929, 16, 28, 'iwumi ddment lmalayek leôwaê, nitni densen iman nnsen". A d ssutren tifrat: "ur nexdim kra n tucmip". Xaîi, Öebbi, s tidep, Iéôa ayen txeddmem.'),
(1930, 16, 29, 'Kecmet si tebbura, ar Loahennama; degs a pwekkôem. A yicmet uxxam imzuxiyen!'),
(1931, 16, 30, 'Ad inin i wid ipêezziben: "d acu id Issers Mass nnwen"? A d inin: "d lxiô". I wid imaânen, ise$ di ddunit agi. Pifxiô, war ccekk, axxam aneggaru. Ay d umâin uxxam n wid ipêezziben!'),
(1932, 16, 31, 'Ad kecmen leonanat n Âaden, ddawat sen isaffen ppazzalen; degsen, i nitni, ayen i sen ihwan. Akka i Ipkafi Öebbi wid ipêezziben,'),
(1933, 16, 32, 'wid iwumi ddment lmalayek leôwaê, nitni maânen, ad asen inint: "tifrat fellawen! Kecmet Loennet, ilmend n wayen txeddmem".'),
(1934, 16, 33, 'Day a pôaoun kan tisin n lmalayek $uôsen, ne$ a d iawev lameô n Mass ik? Akka ay xedmen imezwura nnsen. Ur ten Idnis Öebbi, maca densen iman nnsen.'),
(1935, 16, 34, 'D tucmitin xeddmen, i ten iwwten. Izzi yasen wayen i$ef pmmaâliken.'),
(1936, 16, 35, 'Nnan wid ipcaraken: "Lemmer i S ihwi i Öebbi, ur naâbed acemma, war Neppa, nekwni akked imezwura nne$. Ur negdel acemma, war ayen Igdel". Akka ay xedmen imezwura nnsen. Day illa wayen iwatan i Umazan, siwa awal ipbegginen?'),
(1937, 16, 36, 'Ni$ Nuzen ed amazan i yal lois: "âabdet Öebbi, janbet iôebbiten n tkerkas". Garasen, llan wid Inha Öebbi; garasen, wid i$ef iura ttelfan. Iniget di tmurt, walit amek tevôa d inekkaôen.'),
(1938, 16, 37, 'Xas tôe$wbev $ef nnhaya nnsen, Öebbi, s tidep, ur Inehhu wid Itlef. Ur asen illi usettaô.'),
(1939, 16, 38, 'Ggulen s Öebbi, liman iûeêêan nnsen, ar ur d Ippara ara Öebbi wid immuten. Xaîi, lemâahda fellas d tidep, maca tegwti n medden ur ssinen.'),
(1940, 16, 39, 'Iwakken ad asen d ibeggen ayen i$ef mgarraden, iwakken ad éôen wid ijehlen, ar nitni, war ccekk, llan d ikeddaben.'),
(1941, 16, 40, 'Awal nne£ kan, i t$awsa, ma Neb$a p, ad as Nini: "ili"! A ppili.'),
(1942, 16, 41, 'Wid iunagen i Öebbi, mbaâd ma pwadensen, a ten Nesserked di ddunit s yise$. Arraz n laxeôt a t i$leb, war ccekk, lemmer éôin'),
(1943, 16, 42, 'wid iûebôen u ppeklen $ef Mass nnsen.'),
(1944, 16, 43, 'Id Nuzen, uqbel ik, siwa irgazen iwumi Nweêêa. Steqsit imawlan usmekti, ma ur teéôim ara.'),
(1945, 16, 44, 'S ubeggen akked Ihellilen, Nuzen ak d asmekti, iwakken a pbeggnev i medden, ayen i sen d irsen, amar a d mmektin.'),
(1946, 16, 45, 'Wid iundin tucmitin, aâni $ilen ur Iôemmu ara Öebbi di tmurt, ne$ ur ten id ippawev ara uâaqeb, seg wanda ur bnin?'),
(1947, 16, 46, 'Ne$ ur ten id ikkat ara di cce$l nnsen, ur sfunnugen?'),
(1948, 16, 47, 'Ne$ ur ten ikkat ara cwiî, cwiî. Ih, Mass nnwen, war ccekk, Issuruf, Ipêunu.'),
(1949, 16, 48, 'Day ur walan ara ayen akw Ixleq Öebbi, ippara tili s yeffus, zelmev; tkennu i Öebbi, s wannuz.'),
(1950, 16, 49, 'I Öebbi ikennu meôôa wayen illan deg igenwan, akked wayen illan di tmurt, imexlaq akked lmalayek. Nitni ur sme$wôen iman nnsen.'),
(1951, 16, 50, 'Ppagwaden Mass nnsen, sennig sen, xeddmen ayen i sen ippumôen.'),
(1952, 16, 51, 'Inna Öebbi: "ur sâut sin iôebbiten. Neppa, d Öebbi Yiwen kan. Ihi, Nek, agwadet iyI".'),
(1953, 16, 52, 'IneS i illan di tmurt akked igenwan. Ddin, ineS i lebda. Day a têezzbem i war Öebbi?'),
(1954, 16, 53, 'S$uô Öebbi, ayen akw ikwen i$aten. D$a mi kwen têuza lemveôôa, $uôeS ay tnedhem.'),
(1955, 16, 54, 'Sinna, mi wen Ikkes lemveôôa, arbaâ segwen, atnan pcaraken i Mass nnsen.'),
(1956, 16, 55, 'Nekôen, akka, i sen Nefka. Zhut, deqqal a ppeéôem.'),
(1957, 16, 56, 'La qesden, i wur ssinen, amur seg wayen is iten Neôzeq. S Öebbi, ar fellawen asteqsi, $ef wayen id tesnulfuyem!'),
(1958, 16, 57, 'Gern aS d, i Öebbi, tullas. Gedha s yiS! I nitni, ayen ssarmen.'),
(1959, 16, 58, 'Ma becceôn yiwen s teqcict, ad yibrik wudem is, ad iqbeô.'),
(1960, 16, 59, 'Ad iveôôef iman is, si medden, ilmend n yir usali it id ibbwven. A p ijmaâ, tamara, ne$ a p irr seddaw wakal? Ay dir wamek debbiôen!'),
(1961, 16, 60, 'I wid ur numin ara s laxert: amedya ucmit. I Öebbi: amedya aâlayen mavi. Neppa d Uzmir, d Bab n ûûwab.'),
(1962, 16, 61, 'Öebbi, lemmer Ipqissi medden, $ef ddens nnsen, ur d Ippaoa, degs, amexluq. Maca, Iswexxiô iten ar lajel ipwassnen. Ma iusa d lajel nnsen, ur t swexxiôen, ur t id seqôaben, s ssaâa.'),
(1963, 16, 62, 'Garen aS d, i Öebbi, ayen keôhen. Skaddben yilsawen nnsen, mi qqaôen ar ayen ilhan, nnsen. Ay nnsen, war ccekk, d times. Ih, nitni ad zwiren.'),
(1964, 16, 63, 'S Öebbi, ni$ Nuzen ed, i leoyus, uqbel ik. Cciîan icebbeê asen igiten nnsen. Assa, d bab nnsen. I nitni, aâaqeb aqeôêan.'),
(1965, 16, 64, 'Nessader ak edTazmamt, iwakken kan ad asen tbeggnev ayen i$ef mgarraden, akw i nnhaya akked uêunu i ugdud iumnen.'),
(1966, 16, 65, 'Öebbi Isse$li d aman, seg igenni. Issader yissen akal, deffir tmeppant is. Deg waya, s tidep, assekni i ugdud isellen.'),
(1967, 16, 66, 'Ih, ameyyez, i kunwi, di lmal. Nesswa kwen s wayen illan deg ufwad nnsen, ger lfert d idamen, i$i iûfan, aéidan i wid itessen.'),
(1968, 16, 67, 'Si ppemôa n tezdayin akked tfeôôant, teppawim d ayen iûûekôen, akked ôôezq igerzen. Deg waya, s tidep, assekni i ugdud ifehmen.'),
(1969, 16, 68, 'Iweêêa Mass ik i tzizwa: "gemt ixxamen deg durar, di ttjuô, di te$wôasin.'),
(1970, 16, 69, 'Sinna, eççemt si yal ppemôa. Ddumt s wannuz, iberdan n Mass nnkwent. Iteffe$ ed seg iâabbav nnsent ayen tessen, n yal ini, degs êellu i imdanen". Deg waya, s tidep, assekni i ugdud ipxemmimen.'),
(1971, 16, 70, 'Ixelq ikwen Öebbi, sinna, ad awen Iddem ôôuê. Kra, segwen, ad ccerfeffen mavi, alamma ur ppissinen acemma mbaâd ma ssnen. Ih, Öebbi d Amusnaw, d Aêernuk.'),
(1972, 16, 71, 'Öebbi Ismenyaf ad I$it kra i wiyav. Wid Ismenyaf, ur ilaq ara ad rren, ôôeéq nnsen, i waklan nnsen, d$a ad âadlen yidsen. Day ara nekôen l$it n Öebbi?'),
(1973, 16, 72, 'Iga yawen Öebbi, seg iman nnwen, tilawin nnwen. Ifka yawen, si tlawin nnwen, arraw d warraw n warraw. Iôeéq ikwen s wayen ilhan. Day ad amnen di tkerkas, ad nekôen l$it n Öebbi?'),
(1974, 16, 73, 'Âabden, war Öebbi, wid ur nesâi acemma, swayes ara ten ôeéqen, si tmurt akked igenwan, u ur zmiren.'),
(1975, 16, 74, 'Ur d ppawit imedyaten i Öebbi. Ih, Öebbi Issen, kunwi ur tessinem.'),
(1976, 16, 75, 'Ifka d Öebbi amedya n wakli, d ayla, ur izmir i wacemma, akked yiwen iwumi Nefka, s $uône£, ôôeéq ilhan. Ipseddiq, segs, s tuffra ne$ âinani. Day âadlen? Ccekôan i Öebbi. Maca, tegwti, segsen, ur ssinen.'),
(1977, 16, 76, 'Ifka d Öebbi amedya n sin irgazen. Yiwen d agugam, ur izmir i wacemma. D taâkkwemt i bab is. Anda it iuzen, ur d ippawi lxiô. Day iaâdel akked win ippamôen lêeqq, u neppa deg ubrid uwqim?'),
(1978, 16, 77, 'N Öebbi tabavnit n tmurt akked igenwan. Lameô n yimir, am unqaj n tiî kan, ne$ ur ibbwiv. Ih, Öebbi Izmer i yal cci.'),
(1979, 16, 78, 'Öebbi Issuffe$ ikwen id si tâabbav n tyimmatin nnwen, ur tessinem acemma. Ifka yawen timejjin, iéôi, ul, amar a ppesnemmrem.'),
(1980, 16, 79, 'Day ur walan ara ifôax, têeppem fellasen lhawa igenni, ur ten iîîif yiwen siwa Öebbi? Deg waya, s tidep, issekniyen i ugdud iumnen.'),
(1981, 16, 80, 'Öebbi Irra yawen ixxamen nnwen d tanezdu$t. Irra yawen ixxamen, s igwelman n lmal nnwen. Fessusit, ass n yinig, d wass uqeggel. Taduî nnsen, ccâaô nnsen, inéaden nnsen, i leêwal akked dduzan, tallit kan.'),
(1982, 16, 81, 'Deg wayen Ixleq, Öebbi Ifka yawen d tili. Irra yawen, deg idurar, ûûôanat. Ifka yawen iceîîiven i kwen isdarayen seg u$amac, iceîîiven i kwen ipfukkun si lbe$wv nnwen. Akka, ad awen Itim l$it iS. Amar a ppanzem.'),
(1983, 16, 82, 'Ma wexxôen, i illan fellak, siwa awal ipbegginen.'),
(1984, 16, 83, 'Âaqlen l$it n Öebbi, sinna, nekôen t. Tegwti, degsen, d ijehliyen.'),
(1985, 16, 84, 'Ass ideg ara d Nessker, si yal lois, anagi, imiren ur ippili tesriê i wid ijehlen, u nitni ur ste$fiôen'),
(1986, 16, 85, 'Mi walan, imednas, aâaqeb, ur ippifsus fellasen, ur ppestaâfun.'),
(1987, 16, 86, 'Mi walan, wid ipcaraken, wid curken, ad inin: "a Mass nne$! D wigi i d icriken nne$ u$uô nepnuju, war Keçç". Ad asen d rren: "kunwi, war ccekk, d ikeddaben".'),
(1988, 16, 87, 'Assen, ad fken mayna i Öebbi. Itelf iten wayen d snulfuyen.'),
(1989, 16, 88, 'Wid ijehlen, u sîixxiôen seg ubrid n Öebbi, Nerna yasen aâaqeb sennig wayev, ilmend n wayen ssefsaden.'),
(1990, 16, 89, 'Ass ideg ara d Nessker, i yal lois, anagi segsen, fellasen, a k id Nawi d anagi mgal wigi. Nessers ak d Tazmamt, d abeggen n yal cci, d nnhaya, d aêunu, u d abecceô i imvuâen.'),
(1991, 16, 90, 'Ih, Öebbi Iumeô ed lêeqq, akked lewqama, talalt i llzem. Igdel tucmitin, ayen n dir, ddeôk. A kwen Ipnabi, amar a d temmektim.'),
(1992, 16, 91, 'Eîîfet di lemâahda n Öebbi ma tâahdem. Ur êentet di tgallit ma tetebbtem, u tcubkem Öebbi. Ih, Öebbi Iéôa acu txeddmem.'),
(1993, 16, 92, 'Ur cebbut tin ifsin lxiv is, mbaâd ma tcudd it, s loehd. Tepparam tagallit nnwen i umkellex garawen: ad ikk lois sennig wayev. Öebbi Ipjeôôib ikwen kan, yis. War ccekk, ad awen Ibeggen, ass n tnekra, ayen i$ef temgarradem.'),
(1994, 16, 93, 'Lemmer i S ihwi, i Öebbi, a kwen Irr d yiwen n lois. Maca, Itellif win i S ihwan, Inehhu win i S ihwan. S tidep, a ppepusteqsim $ef wayen txeddmem.'),
(1995, 16, 94, 'Ur pparat tagallit nnwen i umkellex garawen. Ad iccev uvaô mbaâd ma iîîef. A pjeôbem tawa$it, ilmend n wayen tveôôfem seg ubrid n Öebbi. I kunwi, aâaqeb abarar.'),
(1996, 16, 95, 'Ur ppa$et s lemâahda n Öebbi ayen ôxisen. Ih, yif it i kunwi wayen illan $eô Öebbi, lemmer teéôim.'),
(1997, 16, 96, 'Ayen illan $uôwen, ad ifukk; ayen illan $eô Öebbi, ad idum. War ccekk, a Nkafi wid iûebôen, s wazal n wayen xeddmen ifuqen.'),
(1998, 16, 97, 'Wid ixeddmen ayen ilhan, d ddkeô ne$ d nnta, u umnen, a ten Nessider di tmeddurt tumâint, a ten Nkafi s wazal n wayen xeddmen ifuqen.'),
(1999, 16, 98, 'Mara te$ôev Leqwôan, ssuter a k Iaâteq Öebbi, si Cciîan imenfi.'),
(2000, 16, 99, 'Neppa, s tidep, ur isâi adabu $ef wid iumnen, i ippeklen $ef Mass nnsen.'),
(2001, 16, 100, 'Adabu ines, $ef wid kan i t irran d bab, d wid i S ipcaraken.'),
(2002, 16, 101, 'Ma Nbeddel assekni s ussekni, u Öebbi Yif akw akken Issen ayen id Issers, a d inin: "keçç, d win kan id isnulfuyen". Xaîi! Tegwti, degsen, ur ssinen.'),
(2003, 16, 102, 'Ini: "Issers it id ôôuê iôqan, s$uô Mass ik, s tidep, iwakken ad itebbet wid iumnen; d nnhaya u d abecceô i imvuâen".'),
(2004, 16, 103, 'Ih, Neéôa, qqaôen: "d amdan kan it isselmaden". Tameslayt n win d gren, d tabeôôanit, wagi d awal aâôab n ûûeê.'),
(2005, 16, 104, 'Ih, wid ur numin ara s issekniyen n Öebbi, ur ten Inehhu Öebbi. I nitni, aâaqeb aqeôêan.'),
(2006, 16, 105, 'Ih, gren d kan tikerkas, wid ur numin ara s issekniyen n Öebbi. Widak, d nitni ay d ikeddaben.'),
(2007, 16, 106, 'Win inekôen Öebbi, deffir liman is, siwa ma êeppmen fellas, u ul is izga iumen…. Ma d wid illin idmaren nnsen, ar tijehli, ad Izâaf Öebbi fellasen. Fellasen aâaqeb abarar.'),
(2008, 16, 107, 'Ayagi, acku smenyafen tameddurt n ddunit i laxeôt. Ih, Öebbi ur Inehhu agdud ijehliyen.'),
(2009, 16, 108, 'D wigi iwumi Isle$ Öebbi ulawen nnsen, timejjin nnsen, iéôi nnsen. Wigi d i$efliyen.'),
(2010, 16, 109, 'War ccekk, nitni, di laxeôt, ad ilin d imexsuôen.'),
(2011, 16, 110, 'Sinna, Mass ik, s tidep, i wid iunagen mbaâd ma thewwlen, sinna juhden, ûebôen; ih, Mass ik, deffir waya, Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu.'),
(2012, 16, 111, 'Ass ideg ara d ias, yal yiwen, ad inamer $ef yiman is, u yal yiwen ad iîîukafi $ef wayen ixdem, nitni ur pwadensen.'),
(2013, 16, 112, 'Ifka d Öebbi amedya n temdint, i illan di laman u îîmana. Ippas ip id ôôeéq is, s lufa, si yal tama. Tenkeô l$it n Öebbi. Isukk Öebbi fellas tawa$it n llaé akked lweêc, ilmend n wayen la ûûenâan.'),
(2014, 16, 113, 'Ni$ iusa ten id umazan, segsen. Skaddben t, iwwet iten uâaqeb, nitni densen.'),
(2015, 16, 114, 'Eççet seg wayen is ikwen I$at Öebbi, i iêellen, i imaânen. Snemmret l$it n Öebbi, ma d Neppa ay tâabdem.'),
(2016, 16, 115, 'I yawen Igdel siwa loifa, idim, aksum n yilef, akked wayen id irsen s yisem ur nelli d win n Öebbi. Ma d win terra tmara, ur ijuô, ur inufeq, Öebbi, s tidep, Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu.'),
(2017, 16, 116, 'Ur qqaôet tikerkas id ppawin ilsawen nnwen: "aya d leêlal, aya d leêôam". A d tegrem tikerkas $ef Öebbi. Wid id iggaren tikerkas $ef Öebbi, ur rebêen.'),
(2018, 16, 117, 'Drus ara zhun, fellasen aâaqeb aqeôêan.'),
(2019, 16, 118, 'I wudayen, Negdel ayen i$ef i k Neêka, iu$ lêal. Ur ten Nednis, maca nitni ddennisen iman nnsen.'),
(2020, 16, 119, 'Sinna, Mass ik, i wid ixedmen cceôô, ur ssinen, d$a steôoâen deffir waya, u sweqmen, Mass ik, war ccekk, deffir waya, Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu.'),
(2021, 16, 120, 'Ibôahim, ih, d amdan i imalen ar tidep, i iunzen i Öebbi. Ur illi seg imcurak.'),
(2022, 16, 121, 'Isnemmar l$it iS. Ifren it u Inha t s abrid uwqim.'),
(2023, 16, 122, 'Nefka yas di ddunit ise$, u, di laxeôt, neppa, s tidep, ad yili seg izedganen.'),
(2024, 16, 123, 'Sinna, Nweêêa yak d a ppedduv d ddin n Ibôahim, i imalen ar tidep. Ur illi seg imcurak.'),
(2025, 16, 124, 'Ssebt, iu$al kan i wid imgarraden fellas. Ih, Mass ik ad Iêudd garasen, ass n tnekra, $ef wayen llan mgarraden.'),
(2026, 16, 125, 'Enced s abrid n Mass ik, s ûûwab akked nnhaya tumâint. Mmeslay iten, s yiles aéidan mavi. Ih, Mass ik Yif akw akken Issen, anwi i iff$en seg ubrid iS. Neppa Yif akw akken Issen, anwi i ipwanhan.'),
(2027, 16, 126, 'Ma tâaqbem, âaqbet akken teppuâaqbem. Ma tûebôem, yif it i iûebôiyen.'),
(2028, 16, 127, 'Eûbeô. Üûebô ik s Öebbi kan. Ur $webben ilmend nnsen, ur pveyyiq si tcengal nnsen.'),
(2029, 16, 128, 'Ih, Öebbi Atan ar wid ipêezziben, akked wid issewqamen.');
INSERT INTO `ber_mensur` (`index`, `sura`, `aya`, `text`) VALUES
(2030, 17, 1, 'Gedha s Win Ibbwin amdan iS, d iminig n yiv, si Loamaâ n Lêaôam, ar Loamaâ ibaâden mavi, ideg Neôqa i as d izzin, iwakken ad as Nessken, seg issekniyen nne£. Ih, Neppa, d Win Isellen, Ipwalin.'),
(2031, 17, 2, 'Nefka Tazmamt i Musa, u Nerra p d nnhaya i At Isôail. "Ur sâut awkil, war Nek".'),
(2032, 17, 3, 'D tarwa n wid i Nebbwi akked Nuê. Neppa, s tidep, d amdan isnemmiren.'),
(2033, 17, 4, 'Nsseyya di Tezmamt, i At Isôail: "war ccekk, a ppesfesdem, di tmurt, berdayen, u aîas ara tesme$wôem iman nnwen".'),
(2034, 17, 5, 'Mi d iusa usefsed amenzu segsen, Nuzen awen d imdanen nne£, s loehd uqsiê, kecmen ixxamen; lemâahda tevôa.'),
(2035, 17, 6, 'Sinna, Nerra d ppaô nnwen, segsen. Nebbwi yawen d ayla, tarwa. Nesîuqqet iâsekôiwen nnwen.'),
(2036, 17, 7, 'Ma tmaânem, i iman nnwen, ma tdensem, i iman nnwen. Mi d tusa lemâahda taneggarut, ssexven udmawen nnwen, kecmen Loamaâ, akken i t kecmen abrid amenzu; hudden, wakali, ayen is ipzuxxun.'),
(2037, 17, 8, 'Ahat Mass nnwen ad Iêun fellawen. Ma tulsem, a Nales. Nerra Loahennama d lêebs i ijehliyen.'),
(2038, 17, 9, 'Ih, Leqwôan agi inehhu ar wayen iweqmen mavi, ibecceô lmumnin i ixeddmen ayen ilhan, ar i nitni akafi meqqwôen.'),
(2039, 17, 10, 'Wanag wid ur numin ara s laxeôt, Nhegga yasen d aâaqeb aqeôêan.'),
(2040, 17, 11, 'Amdan issawal i cceôô, akken issawal i lxiô. Amdan izga d aêemmaq.'),
(2041, 17, 12, 'Nerra, iv akked wass, d sin issekniyen. Assekni n yiv Nerra d tellis, Nerra win n wass d win ipwalin, iwakken a pnadim lfevl n Mass nnwen, a ppissinem amvan iseggwasen, akked leêsab. Yal ta$awsa, Nfeûûel ip akken iwata.'),
(2042, 17, 13, 'I yal amdan, Ncudd as lbext is s amgarv is. Ass n tnekra, ad as d Nessuffe$ tazmamt ara iaf teldi.'),
(2043, 17, 14, '"£eô tazmamt ik! Tqaddev, assa, s yiman ik, i uqeîîi k".'),
(2044, 17, 15, 'Win ipwanhan, i iman is kan, win innetlafen, innetlaf mgal iman is kan. Ur ipbibbi yiwen taâkkwemt n wayev. Ur Nekkat, alamma Nuzen amazan.'),
(2045, 17, 16, 'Ma Neb$a a Nesqucc tamdint, Neppak lameô i isâiyen is, ad xedmen, degs, cceôô. Ad iâaddi fellas Wawal, a p Nhudd wakali.'),
(2046, 17, 17, 'Acêal n tsuta ay Nesqucc, deffir Nuê! Ad Iqadd Mass ik, i tussna akked tmeéôiwt ibekkaven n imdanen iS.'),
(2047, 17, 18, 'Win ib$an taêemmaqt, Nezzazzal as degs, i £ ihwan, i win i £ Neb$a. Sinna, Nerra yas Loahennama ad din iô$, indell, ippuveggeô.'),
(2048, 17, 19, 'Win ib$an laxeôt, iaâzem fellas yal laâzem, u neppa iumen; widak, tajmilt i laâzem nnsen.'),
(2049, 17, 20, 'I akw, i wigi d wiyav, Nwessaâ tikci s$uô Mass ik. Tikci n Mass ik, ur meêdudet.'),
(2050, 17, 21, 'Wali amek Nesmenyaf kra i wiyav. War ccekk, di laxeôt, lfeôq d usmenyef, ad ilin sennig waya.'),
(2051, 17, 22, 'Ur sâu, ar tama n Öebbi, ôebbi nniven, mulac a ppu$alev d imdelli, d imveggaâ.'),
(2052, 17, 23, 'Iseyya d Mass ik: ur tâabdem siwa Neppa, elhut ar imawlan. Ma, $uôek wesser yiwen, ne$ ma wessren i sin, ur asen qqaô: "ttfuh"! Ur ten ppara. Mmeslay asen s lkyasa.'),
(2053, 17, 24, 'Zger fellasen tacvat n lmaênana. Ini: "a Mass iw! Ëun fellasen, akken iyi d ssekren d amejtuê".'),
(2054, 17, 25, 'Mass nnwen Yif akw akken Issen, i illan deg iman nnwen. Ma telham, Neppa, s tidep, Ipsemmiê wid isteôoiâen.'),
(2055, 17, 26, 'Efk i llezm ik amur is, akw i ume$bun akked win d ibbwi ubrid. Ur pjeggiê d ajeggeê.'),
(2056, 17, 27, 'Ijeggaêen, s tidep, d atmaten n Cciîan. Cciîan ijhel ar Mass is.'),
(2057, 17, 28, 'Ma tfuôqev ten, tôe$bev u tegguniv aêunu s$uô Mass ik, ini yasen awal aéidan.'),
(2058, 17, 29, 'Ur pcuddu afus ik ar yiri k, ur as berru aîas, mulac a ppu$alev d ambaûi, d ame$bun.'),
(2059, 17, 30, 'S tidep, Mass ik I$ennu win i S ihwan, u Iwezzen. Neppa, s tidep, Ipwali, Issen imdanen iS.'),
(2060, 17, 31, 'Ur Neqqet arraw nnwen, ma tugadem tiggulelt. D Nekwni ara ten Iôezqen, kunwi yidsen. Ih, timen$iwt nnsen d tucmip meqqwôen.'),
(2061, 17, 32, 'Ur zennut, d ayen n dir, d abrid ucmit.'),
(2062, 17, 33, 'Ur neqqet amdan i wen Igdel Öebbi, siwa ma di tidep. Win ipwan$an s le$deô, ihi, a Nefk adabu i walag is. Ur ipjuôôu di tmen$iwt, ihi, neppa, ad ippusellek.'),
(2063, 17, 34, 'Ur pnalet ayla ugujil, siwa ar wayen imaânen, ar d immeêtel. Qadôet lemâahda; ih, lemâahda s usteqsi.'),
(2064, 17, 35, 'Qadôet lkil ma tektalem, weznet s lmizan imaânen. Yif it wakka, a ppelhu taggara.'),
(2065, 17, 36, 'Ur îîafaô ayen ur tessinev. Timejjin, iéôi, ul, s tidep, ad ppuseqsin akw.'),
(2066, 17, 37, 'Ur teddu di tmurt, d amzuxxi. Ih, keçç ur tezmirev, d awez$i, a pneqôev tamurt, ne$ a ppessiwvev laâli idurar.'),
(2067, 17, 38, 'Adiran, deg waya akw, Ikerh it Mass ik.'),
(2068, 17, 39, 'Ayagi, seg wayen i k Iweêêa Mass ik, n ûûwab. Ur ppara, ar tama n Öebbi, ôebbi nniven, mulac a ppepwaveggôev ar Loahennama d ambaûi, d amnafeq.'),
(2069, 17, 40, 'Day wen d Ifren Mass nnwen arrac, u Iddem, i iman iS, tullas, si lmalayek? S tidep, kunwi tegrem d awal anecilat.'),
(2070, 17, 41, 'Ih, ay d Nebbwi di Leqwôan agi, iwakken a d mmektin. I yasen d irna, siwa a$unfu.'),
(2071, 17, 42, 'Ini: "lemmer llin yides iôebbiten, akken la d qqaôen, yili ad nadin abrid ara ten iawin ar n Bab n usgeld".'),
(2072, 17, 43, 'Gedha s yiS, aîas i Aâlay sennig wayen d qqaôen!'),
(2073, 17, 44, 'Ppanzen aS igenwan di ûa, tamurt, u wayen illan degsen. Ur illi wayen ur aS neppanez, ur T Nesbuccuâ s ccekôan. Maca, ur tfehmem ara annuz nnsen. Ih, Neppa Iêellem, Ipsemmiê.'),
(2074, 17, 45, 'Mara teqqaôev Leqwôan, Neppara, garak d wid ur numin ara s laxeôt, aêurrim abavni.'),
(2075, 17, 46, 'Nerra $ef ulawen nnsen ssteô, iwakken ur t fehmen; di tmejjin nnsen, tiâéegt. Ma tesmektiv d, di Leqwôan, Mass ik d Yiwen, ad zzin akin, s u$unfu.'),
(2076, 17, 47, 'Nekwni, Nif akw akken Neéôa, acu iwumi sellen, mara k ssemêasen, mara hedôen, mi qqaôen imednas: "la teppeddum kan d urgaz iwumi sseêren".'),
(2077, 17, 48, 'Wali amek i k d bbwin imedyaten. Nnetlafen. Ur zmiren ad afen abrid.'),
(2078, 17, 49, 'Nnan: "day mi nu$al d i$san, d a$webbaô, d ûûeê a d nu$al di lxelq amaynut"?'),
(2079, 17, 50, 'Ini: "ilit d azôu ne$ d uzzal,'),
(2080, 17, 51, 'ne$ d lxelq id iusan deg idmaren nnwen". A d inin: "anwa ara a $ d irren"? Ini: "d Win ikwen id Ixelqen, abrid amenzu". Ad huzen iqweôôa nnsen $uôek, ad inin: "melmi ayagi"? Ini: "izmer ad yili iqeôb ed".'),
(2081, 17, 52, 'Ass ideg ara awen d Isiwel, a d tjawbem s ccekôan iS, a p$ilem cwiî kan ay teqqimem.'),
(2082, 17, 53, 'Ini i imdanen iw ad inin awal ifuqen. Cciîan, s tidep, isskar ameôéi garasen. Ih, Cciîan d acengu n ûûeê i umdan.'),
(2083, 17, 54, 'Mass nnwen Yif akw akken ikwen Issen. Ad Iêun fellawen, ma Ib$a; a kwen Iâaqeb ma Ib$a. Ur k id Nuzen ara d awkil nnsen.'),
(2084, 17, 55, 'Mass ik Yif akw akken Iéôa i illan di tmurt akked igenwan. Ni$ Nesmenyaf kra n lambiyya i wiyav. I Dawed Nefka Ihellilen.'),
(2085, 17, 56, 'Ini: "nujet $eô wid tepkabarem, war Neppa. Ur zmiren ad awen kksen ccqa, ne$ a t bedlen.'),
(2086, 17, 57, 'Wigi u$uô la pnujun, la pqelliben ppawil ara ten isqeôben nezzeh ar Mass nnsen. Ssaramen aêunu S, ppagwaden aâaqeb iS". Ih, aâaqeb n Mass ik, issagwad.'),
(2087, 17, 58, 'Ur telli temdint ur Nesquccu, uqbel ass n tnekra, ne$ ur Nâaqeb s leqseê. Ayagi iura di Tezmamt.'),
(2088, 17, 59, 'I £ iîîfen $ef uceggaâ issekniyen, d nnkeô nnsen, kan, s$uô imezwura. Nuzen ed tal$wemt i Tamud, d ayen pwalin. Densen p. Ur d Neppazen issekniyen siwa i ussigwed.'),
(2089, 17, 60, 'Mi k Nenna: "Mass ik, s tidep, Izzi i imdanen". Ma dayen i k Nerra teéôiv t, d ahewwel kan i medden. Akken ttejôa tamenâult di Leqwôan. Nessagwad iten. Ay sen d irennu siwa nnfaq ameqwôan.'),
(2090, 17, 61, 'Mi Nenna i lmalayek: "knumt i Adem", knant, siwa Iblis. Inna: "day ad knu$ i win Txelqev s talaxt"?'),
(2091, 17, 62, 'Inna: "Twalav wagi i Tâuzzev sennig iw, lemmer a yi Teooev, ar ass n tnekra, war ccekk, ad $wu$ tarwa s, siwa ixeîîayen".'),
(2092, 17, 63, 'Inna: "Öuê! Wid, segsen, i iddan yidek, ihi, aqeîîi nnwen d Loahennama, d aqeîîi meqqwôen.'),
(2093, 17, 64, 'Laâaj win iwumi tzemôev, degsen, s ta$wect ik. £ewwes fellasen s imnayen ik, d iterrasen ik. Ecrek yidsen ayla, tarwa. Âahed asen". I yasen iâahed Cciîan, siwa a$uôôu.'),
(2094, 17, 65, '" Ma d imdanen iW, ur tesâiv adabu fellasen". Mass ik Iqadd d Awkil.'),
(2095, 17, 66, 'Mass nnwen, i wen Isselêayen lbabuô di yill, a pnadim lfevl iS. Ih, Neppa Ipêunu fellawen.'),
(2096, 17, 67, 'Ma tevôa yidwen lmuûiba di yill, ayen u$uô tepnujum, war Neppa, ittellif. Mi kwen Isellek ar lberr, twexxôem. Amdan izga d lkaraâ.'),
(2097, 17, 68, 'Day t$ilem ur Ipseggix ara tamurt yiswen, ne$ ur awen d Ippazen ara tabucivant, d$a ur teppafem awkil?'),
(2098, 17, 69, 'Ne$ day t$ilem ur kwen id Ippara ara tikelt nniven, ad awen d Iazen aûeôûaô, a kwen I$mes ilmend n tijehli nnwen, sinna ur teppafem, mgal a£, amalal?'),
(2099, 17, 70, 'Ni$ Nkeyyes tarwa n Adem. Nebbwi ten di lberr, di yill, N$at iten s wayen ilhan, Nesmenyaf iten, nezzeh, i waîas seg wid i Nexleq.'),
(2100, 17, 71, 'Ass ideg ara Nenced akw imdanen, s imvebôen nnsen; win id tusa tezmamt is yeffus is, widak ad $ôen tazmamt nnsen, ur pwadensen s tissegnit;'),
(2101, 17, 72, 'win illan d ader$al di tagi, ad yili d ader$al di laxeôt, ad izid di tuff$a n ubrid.'),
(2102, 17, 73, 'S tidep, qôib i k hewwlen $ef wayen i k d Nweêêa, a d tesnulfuv ayen nniven, mgal a£. D$a, a k rren d aêbib.'),
(2103, 17, 74, 'Lemmer ur k Ntebbet ara, qôib tmalev cwiî $uôsen.'),
(2104, 17, 75, 'Yili ad ak Nesâaddi tudert akked tmeppant, berdayen, sinna, ur teppafev, mgal a£, w ara k isellken.'),
(2105, 17, 76, 'Ih, qôib i k id srewlen si tmurt, a k id ssuff$en segs. Yili cwiî kan ara d gwrin, deffir ek.'),
(2106, 17, 77, 'D tannumi imazanen nne£, id Nuzen, uqbel ik. Ur teppafev ara abeddel, di lâadda nne£.'),
(2107, 17, 78, 'Bedd i téallit mi istu$la yiîij, alamma d tellis n yiv. Leqwôan, tafrara. Ih, Leqwôan, tafrara, isâa inagan.'),
(2108, 17, 79, 'Aâwez yis kra n yiv, d nnafila k, amar a k id Irr Mass ik, deg umkan i pcekkiôen.'),
(2109, 17, 80, 'Ini: "a Mass iw! Ssekcem iyi, anekcum n tidep. Ssuffe$ iyi, tuff$a n tidep. Efk iyi, s$uôeK, adabu ipselliken".'),
(2110, 17, 81, 'Ini: "tusa d tidep, $abent tkerkas. Ih, tikerkas ilaq ad $abent".'),
(2111, 17, 82, 'Nesrusu d, si Leqwôan, ayen illan d êellu akked uêunu i lmumnin. I irennu, i imednas, siwa lexsaôa.'),
(2112, 17, 83, 'Ma N$at amdan ad iwexxeô, ad iveôôef iman is. Ma iêuza t wugur ad iayes.'),
(2113, 17, 84, 'Ini: "yal yiwen ixeddem akken ipwali. Mass nnwen Yif akw akken i Issen anwa i ipwanhan kteô".'),
(2114, 17, 85, 'Steqsan k id $ef ôôuê. Ini: "ôôuê si lameô n Mass iw. Drus kan n tmusni i wen ippunefken".'),
(2115, 17, 86, 'Ma ihwa ya£, a Nekkes ayen i k Nweêêa. D$a ur teppafev, mgal a£, awkil,'),
(2116, 17, 87, 'siwa aêunu s$uô Mass ik. Ih, lfevl iS, i keçç, izga meqqweô.'),
(2117, 17, 88, 'Ini: "lemmer ad mlilen imdanen akked leonun, iwakken a d awin am Leqwôan agi, ur d ppawin i t icban, xas mâawanen".'),
(2118, 17, 89, 'Ni$ Nefka d i imdanen, di Leqwôan agi, si yal imedyaten. Tegwti n yimdanen ur b$in, siwa tijehli.'),
(2119, 17, 90, 'Nnan: "ur k neppamen alamma tesfeggvev a$ d a$balu, si tmurt;'),
(2120, 17, 91, 'ne$, tesâiv leonan n tezdayin akked tfeôôant, ideg feggven isaffen;'),
(2121, 17, 92, 'ne$, a d tesse$liv igenni d ifeûlan, akken i $ tzuxxev; ne$, a d tasev s Öebbi akked lmalayek, zdat nne$;'),
(2122, 17, 93, 'Ne$ a ppesâuv axxam imzewweq, ne$ a ppaliv s igenni. Ur neppamen, s walluy ik, alamma tessersev ane$ d tazmamt ara n$eô". Ini: "gedha s Mass iw! Day lli$ d ayen nniven, siwa d amdan amazan"?'),
(2123, 17, 94, 'I iîîfen imdanen ur uminen, mi ten id tusa nnhaya, mara d inin kan: "Iuzen ed Öebbi amdan d amazan".'),
(2124, 17, 95, 'Ini: "lemmer llint, di tmurt, lmalayek, teddunt di laman, yili Nessers asent ed, seg igenni, lmelk amazan".'),
(2125, 17, 96, 'Ini: "Iqadd Mass iw d Anagi, gari yidwen. Neppa, s tidep, Ipwali imdanen iS, Issen iten".'),
(2126, 17, 97, 'Win Inha Öebbi, atan idda d ubrid. Wid Itlef, ur asen teppafev imawlan, war Neppa, d awez$i. A ten id Nefser ass n tnekra $ef udmawen nnsen, dre$len, gugmen, âaégen. Axxam nnsen d Loahennama. Mi tenqes tmes, ad asen Nernu ajajiê.'),
(2127, 17, 98, 'D wagi ay d aqeîîi nnsen, imi nekôen issekniyen nne£, u nnan: "day mi nu$al d i$san, d a$webbaô, a d nu$al di lxelq amaynut"?'),
(2128, 17, 99, 'Ne$, day ur walan ara ar Öebbi i Ixelqen tamurt akked igenwan, Izmer a d Ixleq i ten icban? Irra yasen lajel, ur degs ccekk. Ur b$in imednas, siwa tijehli.'),
(2129, 17, 100, 'Ini: "lemmer tesâim igerrujen uêunu n Mass iw, ur ten tepnalem, a ppagwadem a ten tûeôôfem. Amdan izga d imceêêi".'),
(2130, 17, 101, 'Ni$ Nefka, i Musa, tza issekniyen iberrzen. Steqsi At Isôail. Mi d iusa $uôsen, inna yas Ferâun: "a Musa! Nek, wala$, war ccekk, seêêern ak".'),
(2131, 17, 102, 'Inna: "ni$ teéôiv ur d issers yiwen wigi, d tiftilin, siwa Mass n tmurt akked igenwan. Nek, wala$, a Ferâun, war ccekk, tîeêênev".'),
(2132, 17, 103, 'Ib$a a ten iééaâ si tmurt, N$emmeq it, akked wid iddan yides, meôôa.'),
(2133, 17, 104, 'Deffir es, Nenna i At Isôail: "zed$et tamurt. Mi d tusa lemâahda n laxeôt, a kwen id Nawi, d îayfat".'),
(2134, 17, 105, 'Nessers it id s tidep. S tidep, ay d irs. Nuzen ik id, kan, i ubecceô d uneddeô.'),
(2135, 17, 106, 'Leqwôan Nfeôq it, iwakken a t temlev i medden, s laâqel. Nessader it id, s l$eôv.'),
(2136, 17, 107, 'Ini: "amnet yis, ne$ qqimet". Ih, ma mlan t i wid tebbwev tussna, uqbel is, ad $lin $ef udmawen, knan.'),
(2137, 17, 108, 'Ad inin: "gedha s Mass nne$! Tûaô lemâahda n Mass nne$".'),
(2138, 17, 109, 'Ad $lin $ef udmawen s imeîîawen. Ad innerni wannuz nnsen.'),
(2139, 17, 110, 'Ini: "nujet $er Öebbi, ne$ nujet $er Uênin. Akken tnujem, ineS ismawen imaânen yifen akw wiyav". Di téallit ik, ur saâlay ûûut ik, ur t ssrusu. Ad isker kan.'),
(2140, 17, 111, 'Ini: "ccekôan i Öebbi, ur Nesâi aqcic, ur Nesâi acrik di tgelda, ur Nesâi bab mgal asdullu". Ssem$weô iT yal tem$weô.');
INSERT INTO `ber_mensur` (`index`, `sura`, `aya`, `text`) VALUES
(2141, 18, 1, 'Ccekôan i Öebbi, id Issersen Tazmamt, i uxdim iS. Aâwaj, degs, ur Irri.'),
(2142, 18, 2, 'Tewqem, iwakken a ppâaggen $ef ssxev uwâiô, s$uôeS; u a pbecceô lmumnin ixeddmen ayen ilhan, ar nnsen warraz igerzen.'),
(2143, 18, 3, 'Ad ilin degs, i lebda.'),
(2144, 18, 4, 'A ppâaggen i wid innan: "Öebbi Isâa mmi S".'),
(2145, 18, 5, 'Ur illi wayen ssnen fellas; akken, imezwura nnsen. D awal uqbiê id iff$en seg imawen nnsen. D tikerkas kan ay ssawalen.'),
(2146, 18, 6, 'Ahat a phelkev iman ik, ar loiha nnsen, a p$weblev, imi ur uminen ara s usali agi?'),
(2147, 18, 7, 'Ni$ Nerra i illan di tmurt, d ccbaêa ines, iwakken a Néeô menyif iten, ar igiten ilhan.'),
(2148, 18, 8, 'A Nu$al a Nerr, i illan degs, d akal ibuôen.'),
(2149, 18, 9, 'Ne$ t$ilev d At yifri kan, akked Öaqim, ay d lwehma, ger issekniyen nne£?'),
(2150, 18, 10, 'Mi ssôen iman nnsen ilmeéiyen deg ifri, nnan: "a Mass nne$! Efk ane$ d aêunu s$uôeK; Err a$ lameô nne$ d uûwib".'),
(2151, 18, 11, 'Deg ifri, Nesle$ imeééu$en nnsen, acêal iseggwasen.'),
(2152, 18, 12, 'Sinna, Nessker iten id, a Néeô anta, ger snat n trebbuyaâ, i iêesben acêal qqimen.'),
(2153, 18, 13, 'Nekwni, ad ak Neêku, s tidep, taqsiî nnsen. Nitni, ih, d ilmeéiyen, umnen s Mass nnsen. Nerna yasen nnhaya.'),
(2154, 18, 14, 'Nesseohed ulawen nnsen, mi kren nnan: "Mass nne$ d Mass n tmurt akked igenwan. Ur nepnuju, d awez$i, ar ôebbi, war Neppa, mulac a d nini awal dduni.'),
(2155, 18, 15, 'Widak d agdud nne$. Âabden iôebbiten, war Neppa. Ay$eô ur a$ d bbwin, fellasen, adabu n ûûeê? Anwa i idensen sennig win id igren tikerkas $ef Öebbi?'),
(2156, 18, 16, 'Mi ten tfuôqem, nitni akked wayen âabden war Öebbi, essôet iman nwen deg ifri. Ad awen Izraâ, Mass nnwen, seg uêunu S. Ad awen Iheggi amwanes i lameô nnwen".'),
(2157, 18, 17, 'A pwaliv iîij, mi d inqeô, iwexxeô i ifri nnsen, ar yeffus. Mi i$li, ad asen iâaddi $eô zelmev. Nitni, din, di littsaâ. Ayagi seg issekniyen n Öebbi. Win Inha Öebbi, neppa ipwanha; win Itlef, ur isâi, d awez$i, bab ara t inhun.'),
(2158, 18, 18, 'Ad as tiniv ukin, nitni îîsen. Ntezzi ten yeffus, zelmev. Aydi nnsen, $ef umnaô, iééel ivaôen is. Lemmer a ten twaliv, ad asen trewlev, si tugdi; a k terkeb, segsen, lefqaâ.'),
(2159, 18, 19, 'Akka ay ten id Nessenker, iwakken ad mesteqsin. Inna yiwen segsen: "acêal n lweqt ay tesâaddam"? Nnan d: "nesâadda ass ne$ ur ibbwiv wass". Nnan: "Mass nnwen Yif akw akken Izôa ay tesâaddam. Aznet ar temdint, yiwen segwen, s idrimen agi nnwen. Ad iwali anwa lqut iûfan mavi, ad awen d iawi ôôeéq, segs. Ad iêader iman is, iwakken ur awen ipfaq yiwen.'),
(2160, 18, 20, 'Nitni, war ccekk, ma éôan kwen, a kwen ôeomen, ne$ a kwen rren ar ddin nnsen, d$a ur trebêen, d awez$i".'),
(2161, 18, 21, 'Akka ay sen ten Nessken, iwakken ad éôen ar lemâahda n Öebbi d tidep; u, $ef yimir, ur illi ccekk. Mi mqellaân $ef lameô nnsen, nnan: "bnut axxam sennig sen. Mass nnsen Yif akw akken iten Issen". Nnan wid iwumi iâadda wawal, $ef lameô nnsen: "a nerr, ihi, lemqam sennig sen".'),
(2162, 18, 22, 'Ad inin: "di krav yidsen, aydi nnsen d wis kué"; u ad inin: "di semus yidsen, aydi nnsen d wis sdis", pqelliben tabavnit. U ad inin: "di ûa yidsen, aydi nnsen d wis îam". Ini: "Mass iw Yif akw akken Iéôa amvan nnsen. Drus kan i t iéôan". Ur pnamar fellasen, siwa $ef wayen id ivehôen. Ur ppesteqsay yiwen fellasen.'),
(2163, 18, 23, 'Ur qqaô ta$awsa a p xedme$, s tidep, azekka,'),
(2164, 18, 24, 'siwa ma Irad Öebbi. Mmekti d Mass ik, ma teppuv. Ini: "amar ad iyi Inhu Mass iw, ar wayen yifen ayagi di ûûwab".'),
(2165, 18, 25, 'Sâaddan, deg ifri nnsen, krav twinas iseggwasen, rnan tza nniven.'),
(2166, 18, 26, 'Ini: "Öebbi Yif akw akken Iéôa, acêal sâaddan. IneS tabavnit n tmurt akked igenwan. Amek Neppa Ipwali, Isell! Ur sâin bab, war Neppa. Ur Izdukkul yiwen i useyyi S".'),
(2167, 18, 27, 'Mel ayen ik ed ippuweêêan, si Tezmamt n Mass ik. Ur illi ubeddel deg wawal iS. Ur teppafev ssôan, war Neppa, d awez$i.'),
(2168, 18, 28, 'Üebbeô iman ik, akked wid ipnujun ar Mass nnsen, taûebêit, tameddit, pnadin udem iS. Ur ten tekkes si ger wallen ik, a pvemâav lefnun n tmeddurt n ddunit. Ur ssemêas i win iwumi Nesse$fel ul is, ar usmekti nne£, i iddan d lhawiyya s, iwumi iffuhri lameô.'),
(2169, 18, 29, 'Ini: "tidep s$uô Mass nnwen. Ad iamen win ib$an, ad ijhel win ib$an". Ih, Nhegga d times, i imednas; ad asen zzin iêeoouoa s. Ma ppren d, ad asen ppunefken waman am uzzal ifsin. Ad cwin wudmawen nnsen. A tissit tamcumt, a tanezdu$t tucmip!'),
(2170, 18, 30, 'Ih, wid iumnen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan, s tidep, ur Nveggiâ akafi n win ixedmen ayen ilhan.'),
(2171, 18, 31, 'I wigi, leonanat n Âaden, ddaw sen isaffen ppazzalen. Ad qqnen, dinna, imeqyasen n ddheb, ad lsen iceîîiven izegzawen n leêrir, êewcen s ddheb. Ad élen, degs, $ef imîeôêen izewwqen. A lebsa lâali, a tanezdu$t tumâint!'),
(2172, 18, 32, 'Awi yasen d amedya n sin irgazen. I yiwen, Nefka snat tebêirin n téuôin, Nezzi yasent tizdayin, Nerra iger garasent.'),
(2173, 18, 33, 'Yal tibêirt teppak ed l$ella s, ur ipxuûûu, segs, wacemma. Nesfeggev asif garasent.'),
(2174, 18, 34, 'I$ellet ed ppemôa. Inna i umdakwel is, mi s immeslay: "$elbe$ k taôkunt, iffe$ k alag".'),
(2175, 18, 35, 'Idens iman is mi ikcem leonan is, inna: "ur cukke$ ara, d awez$i, ad iqucc wayagi.'),
(2176, 18, 36, 'Ur cukke$ ara ad yili yimir, u ma bbwve$ ar Mass iw, ard affe$, war ccekk, ayen yifen aya, deg umekkan is".'),
(2177, 18, 37, 'Inna yas umdakwel is, mi s immeslay: "day tnekôev Win ik Ixelqen seg wakal, sinna, si tiqqit, sinna, Imessel ik d argaz?'),
(2178, 18, 38, 'Maca, Neppa d Öebbi, Mass iw. Ur pcarake$ yiwen, i Mass iw.'),
(2179, 18, 39, 'Lemmer id tenniv, mi tkecmev ar tebêirt ik: akken Irad Öebbi. Ur telli tezmert siwa s$uô Öebbi. Ma twalav iyi d, nek, tifev iyi ayla, tarwa,'),
(2180, 18, 40, 'Izmer Mass iw ad iyi d Ifk ayen i ifen tibêirt ik. A d Iazen $uôes ssxev, seg igenni, a ppu$al d aêecraruf issiccigen;'),
(2181, 18, 41, 'ne$, ad zzren waman is, ur ten teppafev, d awez$i".'),
(2182, 18, 42, 'Tqucc l$ella s. D$a la izeyyeô ifassen is, $ef wayen iseôôef fellas. Tqucc tfeôôant is. Inna: "a yamxix iw, a lemmer ur curke$ yiwen, i Mass iw"!'),
(2183, 18, 43, 'Ur as illi urbaâ ara t isellken, war Öebbi. Ur isellek iman is.'),
(2184, 18, 44, 'Akka, laânaya s$uô Öebbi, Tidep. Yif akw i ukafi, Yif akw i taggara.'),
(2185, 18, 45, 'Awi yasen d amedya n tmeddurt n ddunit. Am aman id Nesse$li seg igenni. Eâluâlen yissen im$an n tmurt. D$a u$alen d asa$uô, issebruzzaâ iten wavu. Ni$ Öebbi Izmer i yal cci.'),
(2186, 18, 46, 'Ayla akked dderya d ccbaêa n tmeddurt n ddunit. Ar Mass ik, leûlaê idumen ifen ten i ukafi, ifen ten i tmeôoiwt.'),
(2187, 18, 47, 'Ass ideg ara Nesselêu idurar, a pwaliv tamurt d aza$aô. A ten Nefser, ur Neppaoa yiwen segsen.'),
(2188, 18, 48, 'A d rsen zdat Mass ik, d leûfuf: "ni$ tusam a£ d, akken ikwen Nexleq tikelt tamenzut. Irna tetebbtem ar ur awen Neppara ppaâud, d awez$i".'),
(2189, 18, 49, 'Ters ed Tezmamt. A pwaliv ibe$wviyen s uêebbiô, $ef wayen illan degs. Qqaôen: "a yamxix nne$! Acimi tazmamt agi ur teooi ayen meééiyen, u wayen meqqwôen, armi ten teêseb"? Ufan illa wayen xedmen. Mass ik ur Idennis yiwen.'),
(2190, 18, 50, 'Mi Nenna i lmalayek: "knumt i Adem", knant, siwa Iblis. Neppa, si leonun, iaâûa lameô n Mass is. Day a ten terrem, neppa akked tarwa s, d imawlan, war Nek? U nitni d icenga nnwen! D abdil ucmit n imednas.'),
(2191, 18, 51, 'Ur ten Rri$ d inagan n lxelq n tmurt akked igenwan, ne$ n lxelq nnsen. Ur Ïîife$ im$eôôqen d imâiwnen.'),
(2192, 18, 52, 'Ass ideg ara d Yini: "neccdet wid iyI terram d icriken iW". Ad asen siwlen, ur asen d pparan. Nerra, garasen, asif n twa$it.'),
(2193, 18, 53, 'Ibe$wviyen ad walin times. ÊëËûan ar nitni, degs, ara $lin. Ur ppafen, segs, tisensert.'),
(2194, 18, 54, 'Ni$ Nefka d, di Leqwôan agi, yal amedya, i imdanen. Maca, ipnamar umdan sennig akw.'),
(2195, 18, 55, 'D acu i iîîfen imdanen ad amnen, mi ten id tusa nnhaya, u ad ste$fôen Mass nnsen? Ar ten id tas kan, tin ivôan d imezwura, ne$ ar d irs, zdat sen, uâaqeb?'),
(2196, 18, 56, 'Ur Neppazen imazanen, siwa i ubecceô d uneddeô. Wid ijehlen pnamaren, s tkerkas, îîeggiôen yissent tidep. Pmaâliken $ef issekniyen iW, akked wayen i$ef ppunedôen.'),
(2197, 18, 57, 'Anwa idensen sennig win iwumi d pwafekkôen issekniyen n Mass is, iwexxeô asen, u ippu i ixdem ufus is. Ih, Nerra aêurrim $ef wulawen nnsen, ur t fehhmen; akked tiâéegt deg imeééu$en nnsen. Ma tneccdev ten ar nnhaya, ur pwanhan, d awez$i.'),
(2198, 18, 58, 'Mass ik Ipsemmiêen, d Bab uêunu. Lemmer ad Iêud fellasen ilmend n wayen kesben, ad I$iwel ar uâaqeb nnsen. Maca, sâan ppaâud, ur ppafen segs tisensert.'),
(2199, 18, 59, 'Timdinin nni i Nesqucc mi densent, Nga ppaâud i usquccu nnsent.'),
(2200, 18, 60, 'Mi inna Musa i uqeddac is: "ur êebbse$ alamma bbwve$ ar umlili n sin ilellen, xas ad sâaddi$ tallit".'),
(2201, 18, 61, 'Mi bbwven ar umlili nnsen, ppun aslem nnsen. Iu$al ar yill d ilelli.'),
(2202, 18, 62, 'Mi zegren, inna i uqeddac is: "awi a$ d imekli nne$, ni$ naâteb deg inig nne$ agi".'),
(2203, 18, 63, 'Inna: "ur twalav ara, mi nreyyeê ar teéôut, nek ppu$ en aslem? D Cciîan kan iyi isseppun ur ak nni$. Ibbwi abrid is ar yill, d lwehma"!'),
(2204, 18, 64, 'Inna: "d ayagi ay neb$a". D$a u$alen d $ef isurifen nnsen.'),
(2205, 18, 65, 'Ufan d amdan seg imdanen nne£, iwumi Nefka aêunu s$uône£. Neslemd as tussna i illan $uône£.'),
(2206, 18, 66, 'Inna yas Musa: "Ma ad ddu$ yidek, ad iyi tesêefvev ay tesnev n ûûwab"?'),
(2207, 18, 67, 'Inna d: "keçç, s tidep, ur tezmiôev, yidi, a pûebôev.'),
(2208, 18, 68, 'Amek ara tûebôev i wayen i$ef ur tesâiv asali"?'),
(2209, 18, 69, 'Inna: "ad iyi tafev, ma Irad Öebbi, d aûebôi. Ur pnaqwame$ lameô ik".'),
(2210, 18, 70, 'Inna: "ma teddiv yidi, ur iyi d steqsay $ef wacemma, alamma smekti$ k id fellas".'),
(2211, 18, 71, 'Lêan, armi rekben di lbabuô. Ixeôq it. Inna: "txeôqev t, iwakken ad $evûen l$aci s! Ni$ ayen txedmev d dduni".'),
(2212, 18, 72, 'Inna: "day ur ak nni$ ara, keçç, s tidep, ur tezmiôev, yidi, a pûebôev, d awez$i"?'),
(2213, 18, 73, 'Inna: "ur iyi pqasa imi ppu$, ur ssukku lwaâôan $ef lameô iw".'),
(2214, 18, 74, 'Lêan, armi d mmugren ileméi. In$a t. Inna: "ten$iv amdan ur nen$i yiwen! Ni$ d ayen idensen ay txedmev".'),
(2215, 18, 75, 'Inna: "day ur ak nni$ ara, keçç, s tidep, ur tezmiôev, yidi, a pûebôev, d awez$i"?'),
(2216, 18, 76, 'Inna: "ma steqsa$ k $ef t$awsa, deffir ta, ur teddu yidi. Ni$ ssutre$ ak d ssmaê".'),
(2217, 18, 77, 'Lêan, armi bbwven ar imezda$ n yiwet n temdint, ssutren asen lqut. Ugin a ten snubgten. Ufan en lêiv, qôib ad i$li. Iûeggem it. Inna: "ma teb$iv, tzemrev a ppepwaxellûev $ef waya".'),
(2218, 18, 78, 'Inna: "Tura a nemfaôaq. Ad ak d fke$ lmaâna n wayen i$ef ur tezmirev a pûebôev, d awez$i".'),
(2219, 18, 79, 'Lbabuô nni, n igellilen i ixedmen di yill. B$i$ a t ôée$, acku yiwen ugellid, deffir sen, itekkes yal lbabuô, s yi$il.'),
(2220, 18, 80, 'Wanag ileméi nni, llan imawlan is d lmumnin. Nugad ad iêeppem fellasen tinufqa, tijehli.'),
(2221, 18, 81, 'Neb$a ad asen d Irr, Mass nnsen, it yifen: win iûfan, iqeôben nezzeh aêunu.'),
(2222, 18, 82, 'Wanag lêiv, n sin warrac igujilen n temdint. Illa ugerruj seddaw as, i nitni. Babat sen d argaz ilhan. Mass ik Ib$a, ard im$uôen, ara d ssuff$en agerruj nnsen. D aêunu s$uô Mass ik. Ur t xdime$ s lameô iw. D tagi ay d lmaâna n wayen i$ef ur tezmiôev a pûebôev".'),
(2223, 18, 83, 'Steqsan k $ef Bu sin wacciwen. Ini: "ad awen d awi$, fellas, asmekti".'),
(2224, 18, 84, 'S tidep, Nefka yas di tmurt, u Nsehhel as iberdan di yal cci.'),
(2225, 18, 85, 'Iîîef yiwen n ubrid,'),
(2226, 18, 86, 'armi sanda i$elli yiîij. Iufa i$elli $ef tala ilu$en. Iufa n $uôes agdud. Nenna: "a Bu sin wacciwen, âaqeb iten, ne$ lhu $uôsen".'),
(2227, 18, 87, 'Inna: "win idensen a t nâaqeb, sinna, ad iu$al ar Mass is at Iâaqeb aâaqeb unekkaô.'),
(2228, 18, 88, 'Wanag i win iumnen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan, akafi igerzen. Ad as Nini i isehlen si lameô nne£".'),
(2229, 18, 89, 'Sinna, ilêa d yiwen n ubrid,'),
(2230, 18, 90, 'armi sanda d ineqqeô yiîij. Iufa n ineqqeô ed $ef ugdud, iwumi ur Nefki ar at isdarin segs.'),
(2231, 18, 91, 'Am akka. Ni$ ibbwev a£ d akw usali s.'),
(2232, 18, 92, 'Sinna, idda d yiwen n ubrid,'),
(2233, 18, 93, 'armi ibbwev ger sin iêdiden. Iufa, deffir sen, agdud qôib ur fehhmen awal.'),
(2234, 18, 94, 'Nnan: "a Bu sin wacciwen, s tidep, Iaouo akked Maouo la ssefsaden di tmurt. A k nxelleû ma terriv ûûuô garane$ yidsen".'),
(2235, 18, 95, 'Inna: "yif it iyi Ifka Mass iw. Efket iyi afus, ad rre$ ûûuô garawen yidsen.'),
(2236, 18, 96, 'Awit iyi d tiqaùmtin n wuzzal alamma irgel wayen illan ger idurar". Inna: "ûuvet alamma tekker degs tmes. Awit iyi d ad smire$ fellas nnêas ifsin".'),
(2237, 18, 97, 'D$a ur zmiren a t id zegren, ur zmiren a t id flun.'),
(2238, 18, 98, 'Inna: "ayagi d aêunu s$uô Mass iw. Mi d tusa lemâahda n Mass iw, a t Isawi. Lemâahda n Mass iw d tidep".'),
(2239, 18, 99, 'Assen, a ten Neoo ad ddehmen wa $ef wa. Aûuvu di lbuq, d$a a ten Nessemlil akw.'),
(2240, 18, 100, 'A d Nessken nezzeh Loahennama, assen, i ijehliyen,'),
(2241, 18, 101, 'wid iwumi sêurrment wallen nnsen, mgal asmekti W. Llan ur zmiren i usemêes.'),
(2242, 18, 102, 'Day $ilen, wid ijehlen, ad rren imdanen iW, d imawlan war Nek? Ih, Nhegga Loahennama, d axxam i ijehliyen.'),
(2243, 18, 103, 'Ini: "ad awen mle$ at igiten imexsuôen sennig wiyav?'),
(2244, 18, 104, 'Wid iwumi iweddeô laâtab nnsen di tmeddurt n ddunit, wanag nitni nwan gerzen igi"?'),
(2245, 18, 105, 'Widak d wid i inekôen issekniyen n Mass nnsen, akked temlilit yideS. Mêan igiten nnsen. Ur ten Nwezzen, ass n tnekra.'),
(2246, 18, 106, 'Atan uqeîîi nnsen: Loahennama, imi jehlen, u mmaâlken deg issekniyen iW, akked imazanen iW.'),
(2247, 18, 107, 'Ma d wid iumnen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan, axxam nnsen d leonanat n Loennet.'),
