(2254, 19, 4, 'Inna: "a Mass iw! S tidep, ôéent laâvam iw, aqeôôu iôeq si ccib. A Mass iw! Anuju $uôeK uroin iyi isnu$ben.'),
(2255, 19, 5, 'Nek ugade$ llzem iw, deffir i. Tameîîut iw d tiâiqeôt. Efk iyi d lfeôx s$uôeK;'),
(2256, 19, 6, 'ad iyi iwôet, ad iwôet si twacult n Yaâqub. Err it, a Mass iw, d win iôuvan".'),
(2257, 19, 7, '"A Zakarya, s tidep, Nbecceô ik s uqcic, ism is Yeêya. Ur Nefki, i yiwen, ism agi, uqbel is".'),
(2258, 19, 8, 'Inna: "a Mass iw! Amek ara sâu$ aqcic, tameîîut iw d tiâiqeôt, u nek $emqe$ di tewser"?'),
(2259, 19, 9, 'Inna: "Akka. Inna d Mass ik: ayagi ishel fellI. Ni$ Xelqe$ k, zik, ur telliv d acemma".'),
(2260, 19, 10, 'Inna: "a Mass iw! Efk iyi d assekni". Inna: "assekni ik, ur tepmeslayev i medden, krav wavan, ur tuvnev".'),
(2261, 19, 11, 'Iffe$ ed ar ugdud is, si lemqam. Iweêêa yasen ad anzen ûûbeê, tameddit".'),
(2262, 19, 12, '"A Yeêya, eîîef Tazmamt, s loehd". D ûûebyan, Nefka yas ûûwab,'),
(2263, 19, 13, 'lmaênana akked ûûfawa, s$uône£. Ipêezzib;'),
