(2271, 19, 21, 'Inna: "Akka. Inna d Mass im: ayagi, ishel fellI. A t Nerr d assekni i medden, d aêunu s$uône£. D lameô ippuêeppmen".'),
(2272, 19, 22, 'Tebbwi tadist; syis taâzel iman is, di tama ibaâden.'),
(2273, 19, 23, 'Bdan p id inzikmiren ar loedra n tezdayt. Tenna: "anna$ lemmer mmute$, uqbel ayagi, ad pwappu$ akw"!'),
(2274, 19, 24, 'Issawel as d, seddaw as: "kkes a$wbel, ih, Mass im Irra i$éeô, seddaw am.'),
(2275, 19, 25, 'Hucc, ar $uôem, loedra n tezdayt, ad am d i$li ppmeô amaynut ibwan.'),
(2276, 19, 26, 'Eçç, ssew, ssefôeê iéôi m. Ma twalav yiwen n umdan, ini as: nek, s tidep, uéame$ i Uênin, ur pmeslaye$, assa, i umdan".'),
(2277, 19, 27, 'Tôuê yis ar ugdud is, tebbwi t. Nnan: "a Meryem! Ni$ tusiv d, s temsalt ihejjnen.'),
(2278, 19, 28, 'A ultmas n Haôun, ur illi baba m d argaz ucmit, ur telli imma m d tazennant".'),
