(2280, 19, 30, 'Inna: "nek d amdan n Öebbi. Ifka yi d Tazmamt. Irra yi d nnbi.'),
(2281, 19, 31, 'Iôqa yi anda lli$. Iweûûa yi taéallit, u zzakat, skud mazal iyi d amuddir.'),
