(2283, 19, 33, 'Tifrat felli asmi d lule$, asmi ara mmte$, asmi ara d u$ale$ d amuddir"!'),
(2284, 19, 34, 'D wagi ay d Âisa, mmi s n Meryem. D awal n tidep, i$ef cukken.'),
(2285, 19, 35, 'Ur iûwib ara, i Öebbi, ad Isâu kra n mmi S. Gedha syiS! Ma Iseyya lameô, ad as Yini kan: "ili"! Ad yili.'),
(2286, 19, 36, 'Öebbi, s tidep, d Mass iw, d Mass nnwen. Ihi, âabdet eP. D wagi ay d abrid uwqim.'),
(2287, 19, 37, 'Mgarraden ikabaren garasen. A tawa$it n wid ijehlen, mara walin ass abarar!'),
(2288, 19, 38, 'Ara slen, ara walin, ass ideg ara d asen $uône£! Maca, imednas, assa, di ttelfan s ûûeê.'),
(2289, 19, 39, 'Nabi ten, $ef ass n ssixîa, mara iûaô lameô. Nitni, di l$eflan, nitni ur uminen.'),
(2290, 19, 40, 'Ih, d Nekwni, ara Iweôten tamurt akked wayen illan fellas. £uône£ tu$alin nnsen.'),
(2291, 19, 41, 'Smekti d, di Tezmamt, Ibôahim. Ih, Neppa, illa d bab n tidep, d nnbi.'),
(2292, 19, 42, 'Mi inna i baba s: "a baba! Acimi tâabdev win ur nsell, ur nepwali, ur k ip$itin s wacemma?'),
(2293, 19, 43, 'Ih, a baba, Nek ippunefk iyi d, si tmusni, ayen ur ak neppunefk. Ihi ddu yidi, a k nhu$ ar ubrid ilhan.'),
(2294, 19, 44, 'A baba! Ur âabbed Cciîan. Ni$ Cciîan illa d amâaûu i Uênin.'),
(2295, 19, 45, 'A baba! Nek, ugade$ a k iwwet uâaqeb n Uênin, a ppiliv d ameddakwel n Cciîan".'),
(2296, 19, 46, 'Inna d: "day tugiv keçç, a Ibôahim, iôebbiten iw? Ma ur tfukkev ara, war ccekk, a k ôeome$! Ïixxeô iyi tallit $wezzifen".'),
(2297, 19, 47, 'Inna: "ili di tifrat. Ad ssutre$ i Mass iw, ad ak Isemmeê. Neppa, s tidep, Iâuzz iyi.'),
(2298, 19, 48, 'Ad âazle$ iman iw segwen, akked wayen tepnujum, war Öebbi. Ad naâôe$ Mass iw, ahat, s unuju w, ar Mass iw, ur $webne$ ara".'),
(2299, 19, 49, 'Mi iaâzel iman is segsen akked wayen âabden, war Öebbi, Nefka yas Isêaq akked Yaâqub. Yal yiwen, Nerra t d nnbi.'),
(2300, 19, 50, 'Nefka yasen seg uêunu nne£. Nerna yasen ccekôan umâin, lfayeq.'),
