(2303, 19, 53, 'Nefka yas, seg uêunu nne£, gma s, Haôun, d nnbi.'),
(2304, 19, 54, 'Smekti d, di Tezmamt, Ismaâil. Ih, neppa, illa d win ippaîafen di lemâahda s, d amazan, d nnbi.'),
(2305, 19, 55, 'Iumeô i twacult is, taéallit, zzakat. Iôuva t Mass is.'),
(2306, 19, 56, 'Smekti d, di Tezmamt, Idris. Ih, neppa, illa d bab n tidep, d nnbi.'),
(2307, 19, 57, 'Nessuli t s amkan aâlayen.'),
(2308, 19, 58, 'D wigi i I$at Öebbi, ger lambiyya, ger tarwa n Adem, ger wid i Nebbwi akked Nuê, ger tarwa n Ibôahim, akked Isôail, ger wid Nenha u Nefren. Ma $ôan asen issekniyen n Uênin, ad $lin knan, s imeîîawen.'),
(2309, 19, 59, 'Lxwelf nnsen d asatu i iooan taéallit, ddan d ccehwiyyat. Ad magren ttelfan.'),
(2310, 19, 60, 'Kkes ed wid isteôoâen, iumnen, xeddmen ayen ilhan. Wigi, ad kecmen Loennet, ur pwadensen s wacemma.'),
(2311, 19, 61, 'Leonanat n Âaden i Iwaââed Uênin, i imdanen iS, di tbavnit. Lemâahda S, s tidep, a ppevôu.'),
(2312, 19, 62, 'Ur sellen, degs, i yir awal, siwa: "tifrat"! Dinna, lqut nnsen, ûûbeê, tameddit.'),
(2313, 19, 63, 'D tagi ay d Loennet, ara Nerr d lweôt, i wid ipêezziben, seg imdanen nne£.'),
(2314, 19, 64, 'Ur d nepûubbu, siwa ma s lameô n Mass ik. IneS i illan zdat nne$, i illan deffir nne$, akked wayen illan garasen. Mass ik ur Iteppu.'),
(2315, 19, 65, 'Mass n tmurt, igenwan, akked wayen illan garasen. Ihi, âabed iT, ili d imezgi deg uâbad iS. Day tesnev win isâan ism iS?'),
