(2323, 19, 73, 'Mara asen $ôen issekniyen iberrzen nne£, qqaôen wid ijehlen i wid iumnen: "menyif sin irebbuyaâ di temâict akw i lemwansa"?'),
(2324, 19, 74, 'Acêal isuta i Nesqucc, uqbel nnsen, ifen ten tarkunt, ûûifa!'),
(2325, 19, 75, 'Ini: "ad Irnu Uênin di laâmeô, i im$eôôqen, alamma walan acu i sen ippuwaââden: d aâaqeb ne$ d imir. Ad éôen anwa illan deg umkan adiran mavi, ay d bu lâaskeô uôhifen mavi".'),
(2326, 19, 76, 'Ad Irnu Öebbi nnhaya i wid ipwanhan. Ar Mass ik, leûlaê idumen ifen akafi, asisi.'),
(2327, 19, 77, 'Ma twalav win iugin issekniyen nne£, u inna: "tarkunt, tarwa ad iyi ppunefkent, war ccekk"?'),
(2328, 19, 78, 'Aâni issen tabavnit, ne$ iu$ lemâahda s$uô Uênin?'),
(2329, 19, 79, 'Xaîi, a Naru ayen inna. Ad as Nessi$wzef nezzeh aâaqeb.'),
(2330, 19, 80, 'A Newôet ay d inna, a d ias $uône£, d awêid.'),
