(2561, 21, 78, 'I Dawed akked Sliman, mi êudden $ef yiger, ideg ksant wulli n medden. Nella d Inagan uêuddu nnsen.'),
(2562, 21, 79, 'Nessfehm as p i Sliman. I sin, Nefka ûûwab, tamusni. Nêeppem i idurar akked igvav ad sbuccâen Dawed. D ayen Newqem.'),
(2563, 21, 80, 'Nessêefv as, ad awen iûnaâ iceîîiven, ara iêarben fellawen si tiytiwin. Day a ppesnemmrem?'),
(2564, 21, 81, 'I Sliman, avu n tarikt, ipûuvu s lameô is, $er tmurt i Neôqa. Nezga Néeô yal cci.'),
(2565, 21, 82, 'Ger ccwaîen, wa i$evves as, wa iqubel cce$l nniven. Nella d imêaraben nnsen.'),
(2566, 21, 83, 'I Yub, mi inuj $eô Mass is: "nek pwa$e$. Keçç, Tifev akw wid ipêunun".'),
(2567, 21, 84, 'Njaweb as ed. Nekkes as it ivuôôen; Nerra yas d tawacult is, akw, yides, tin i p icban. D aêunu s$uône£, d asmekti i iâabaden.'),
(2568, 21, 85, 'Ismaâil, Idris, Dulkifl, akken ma llan, d iûebôiyen.'),
(2569, 21, 86, 'Nesskecm iten deg uêunu nne£. Nitni, s tidep, seg wid imaânen.'),
(2570, 21, 87, 'I Dannun, mi iôuê s wurrif. I$il ur Nesâi ara adabu fellas. Inâaô, di tellis: "ur illi ôebbi siwa Keçç. Gedha s yiseK! Nek lli$ si imednas".'),
(2571, 21, 88, 'Njaweb as ed. Nâateq it si éémik. Akka ay Nâateq lmumnin.'),
(2572, 21, 89, 'I Zakaria, mi inuj $uô Mass is: "a Mass iw! Ur iyi Ippaooa ara d amengur. Keçç, Tifev akw iweôôaten".'),
(2573, 21, 90, 'Njaweb as ed. Nefka yas Yaêia, Nesseêla yas tameîîut is. Nitni, s tidep, izga izwar lxiô nnsen. Pnujun $uône£, s tugwdi d usirem. Unzen a£.'),
(2574, 21, 91, 'Ar tin i iqqimen zeddiget, Nûuv si ôôuê nne£. Nerra p, neppat akked mmi s, d assekni i imavalen.'),
(2575, 21, 92, 'Lois agi nnwen, war ccek, d lois yiwen. Nek d Mass nnwen, ihi âabdet iyI.'),
(2576, 21, 93, 'Gezmen lameô nnsen garasen. £uône£, akw, ara d u$alen.'),
(2577, 21, 94, 'Win ixeddmen ayen ilhan u irna iumen, ur ipôuêu laâtab is. Ih, Nekwni Nepparu fellas.'),
(2578, 21, 95, 'Ipwagdel asen a d u$alen $eô temdint i Nesqucc,'),
(2579, 21, 96, 'alamma serrêen d i Iaouo d Maouo. Nitni, si yal ti$ilt, a d azzlen.'),
(2580, 21, 97, 'Tqeôb ed lemâahda n tidep. Atan iqquô yiéôi n wid ijehlen: "a tawa$it nne$! Ni$ nella ne$fel $ef waya. U, aâer, nella d imednas.'),
(2581, 21, 98, 'Kunwi, s tidep, akked wayen tâabden, war Öebbi, d is$aôen n Loahennama. £ures, kunwi, teppeddum.'),
(2582, 21, 99, 'Lemmer llin widak d iôebbiten, ur p keççmen. Akw, ad wekkôen degs.'),
(2583, 21, 100, 'I nitni, degs, zzhir. Nitni, degs, ur sellen.'),
(2584, 21, 101, 'Ma d wid iwumi izwar ssaâd, s$uône£, widak, segs, ad baâden.'),
(2585, 21, 102, 'Ur sellen i ûûut is. Ad wekkôen deg wayen cihwant teôwiêin nnsen.'),
(2586, 21, 103, 'Ur ten i$webbel lweêc abarar. A ten magrent lmalayek: "assa, d ass nnwen, i wen ippuwaââden".'),
(2587, 21, 104, 'Ass ideg ara Nesnefvas igenni am tweôqep n tira, akken Nebda axlaq amezwaru, ad as Nales. D lemâahda fellane£. Akka, ih, ara Nexdem.'),
(2588, 21, 105, 'Ni$ Nura deg Ihellilen, deffir usmekti: "ara iweôten tamurt, d imdanen iW imaânen".'),
(2589, 21, 106, 'Deg wayagi, war ccekk, d asali i ugdud iâabbaden.'),
(2590, 21, 107, 'Ur k id Nuzen, siwa d aêunu i imavalen.'),
(2591, 21, 108, 'Ini: "iyi d ippuweêêan, siwa: Öebbi nnwen d Öebbi Yiwen kan. Kunwi ma d imvuâen"?'),
(2592, 21, 109, 'Ma wexxôen, ini: "âaggne$ awen, akken ma tellam; ur éôi$ ma iqôeb, ne$ ibâad, ayen i wen ippuwaââden.'),
(2593, 21, 110, 'Neppa, s tidep, Issen awal d iff$en, Issen ayen tessusmem.'),
(2594, 21, 111, 'Ur éôi$ ma, ayagi, ahat d ahewwel nnwen, u d zzhu n tallit kan.'),
(2595, 21, 112, 'Inna: "a Mass iw! Eêkem s tidep. Mass nne$, Aênin, i nepper d Amâiwen, mgal ayen teppandim".');
INSERT INTO `ber_mensur` (`index`, `sura`, `aya`, `text`) VALUES
(2596, 22, 1, 'A yimdanen! Ëezzbet i Mass nnwen, zzenzla n yimir, stidep, d tadyant tabarart.'),
(2597, 22, 2, 'Ass ideg ara p twalim, yal timôebbit a ppeppu win tessuîîuv, yal tadist a ppexseô. A pwaliv imdanen ssekôen, ur sskiôen. Maca, aâaqeb n Öebbi iwâaô.'),
(2598, 22, 3, 'Ger yimdanen, illa win ipnamaren $ef Öebbi, war tamusni. Iteddu d yal cciîan imcebbwel.'),
(2599, 22, 4, 'Iura fellas: "ar wagi, win i t irran d bab is, ara t itlef, s tidep, u a t inheô ar uâaqeb ujajiê".'),
(2600, 22, 5, 'A yimdanen! Ma di ccekk ay tellam f tnekra, ihi, Nekwni, s tidep, Nxelq ikwen seg wakal, sinna, si tiqqit n l$ella, sinna, seg urgan, sinna, si tecriêt, texleq ur texliq, iwakken ad awen Nbeggen. Neppara, di tâabbuvin, ayen i £ ihwan, alamma d lajel ipwassnen. Sinna, Nessuffu$ ikwen id d llufanat, sinna a ppim$uôem. Segwen llan wid ippemmten, u segwen win ara iawven d awessur, ard ur ippisin acemma seg wayen issen. A pwalid akal d a$uôaô. Ma Nesse$li d ageffur fellas, ad ikker, ad icuff, a d ifk tayuga n yal ûûenf uziyn n le$ôus.'),
(2601, 22, 6, 'Ayagi, acku Öebbi d Tidep. D Neppa id Issidiren lmeggtin. Neppa Izmer i yal cci.'),
(2602, 22, 7, 'U imir a d ias, war ccekk fellas. U Öebbi a d Issker wid illan di tneîlin.'),
(2603, 22, 8, 'Ger imdanen, illa win ipnamaren $ef Öebbi, war tamusni, ne$ nnhaya, ne$ Tazmamt ifeten.'),
(2604, 22, 9, 'Icuff aqenduô, iwakken ad itlef seg ubrid n Öebbi. Fellas xezzu di ddunit. Deg wass n tnekra, a Nessuk fellas aâaqeb n tmeô$iwt.'),
(2605, 22, 10, 'Ayagi, $ef wayen id urwen ifassen ik. U Öebbi ur Idennis imdanen.'),
(2606, 22, 11, 'Ger yimdanen, win iâabden Öebbi, $ef rrif. Ma iusa t id lxiô, ad ithenni yis. Ma iusa t id uhewwel, ad iswexxeô udem is. Öuêent as, ddunit, laxeôt. Ayagi d lexsaôa n ûûeê.'),
(2607, 22, 12, 'Ipnuju, war Öebbi, ar wayen ur t neîîuôôu, ur t neffaâ. D wagi ay d ttelfan u$miq.'),
(2608, 22, 13, 'Ipnuju ar bu vveôô izwaren aba$uô ines. Ay d bab ucmit, ay d acrik ucmit.'),
(2609, 22, 14, 'Öebbi, s tidep, ad Issekcem wid iumnen, i ixeddmen ayen ilhan, ar Loennet, ddaw as isaffen ppazzalen. Öebbi, s tidep, Ixeddem ayen Ib$a.'),
(2610, 22, 15, 'Win i oaâlen ur t Ipsellik ara Öebbi, di ddunit, di laxeôt, ad iâalleq amrar s igenni, sinna, ad igzem nnefs is. Ad iéeô ma tiêêeôci s temêa ayen i t irêan.'),
(2611, 22, 16, 'Akka ay t id Nessader, d issekniyen iberrzen. U Öebbi, s tidep, Inehhu win i S ihwan.'),
(2612, 22, 17, 'Ih, ass n tnekra, ad Iêudd Öebbi ger wid iumnen, udayen, iûabiyen, imasiêiyen, u iâabbaden n tmes, wid ipcaraken. Öebbi, s tidep, Iwala yal cci.'),
(2613, 22, 18, 'Ur twalav ara knan i Öebbi i illan deg igenwan, i illan di tmurt: iîij, aggur, itran, idurar, ttjuô, lêayawan, aîas n yimdanen. Aâaqeb d lewoeb $ef aîas. Win Isdull Öebbi, ur illi w ara t iâuzzen. Ih, Öebbi Ixeddem ayen i S ihwan.'),
(2614, 22, 19, 'Atnan sin ixûimen ppemqellaân $ef Mass nnsen. S tmes ay pwafeûlen iceîîiven n wid ijehlen. Ad mmiren, $ef iqweôôa nnsen, waman iô$an'),
(2615, 22, 20, 'ara issefsin ayen illan deg iâabbav nnsen, akked igwelman.'),
(2616, 22, 21, 'I nitni, ijekwaven n wuzzal.'),
(2617, 22, 22, 'Yal tikelt ara ssirmen a d ff$en segs, seg wakken meênen, a ten rren $uôes: "jeôôbet aâaqeb n tmeô$iwt"!'),
(2618, 22, 23, 'Öebbi, s tidep, ad Issekcem wid iumnen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan, ar Loennet, ddaw as isaffen ppazzalen. Degs ad qqnen imeqyasen n ddheb d lyaqut. Leêrir deg iceîîiven nnsen.'),
(2619, 22, 24, 'Pwanhan s awal umâin, pwanhan s abrid Umaâzuz.'),
(2620, 22, 25, 'Ih, i wid ijehlen i issefôa$en abrid n Öebbi, akked Loamaâ n Lêaôam, i Nerra i imdanen, ama d amezda$ n din, ama d abeôôani; i win ib$an degs tijehli, s ddens, a Nesâaddi aâaqeb aqeôêan.'),
(2621, 22, 26, 'Mi Nhegga i Ibôahim, amkan n Uxxam: "ur iyI pcarak acemma! Zizdeg axxam iW i wid idewwiôen, wid ibedden, wid iîîinizen, iknan.'),
(2622, 22, 27, 'Enced medden ar lêio. A d asen $uôek $ef uvaô, ne$ $ef yal amerkub ulîif. A d asen si yal abrid ibaâden.'),
(2623, 22, 28, 'Ad cehhden $ef l$it nnsen. A d smektin ism n Öebbi, deg ussan ipwassnen, $ef ubhim n lmal i sen Ifka. Eççet segs, cceççet ame$bun, aéawali.'),
(2624, 22, 29, 'Sinna, ad ssirden, ad qenâen asirem nnsen, ad dewwôen i Uxxam aqdim".'),
(2625, 22, 30, 'Akka. Win ippâuzzun ayen Igdel Öebbi, ilha yas kteô, ar Mass is. Ëellen awen lmal, siwa wid i wen mlan. Janbet lâaô n tâancuôin, janbet awal n ééuô;'),
(2626, 22, 31, 'am wid imalen ar tidep ar Öebbi, ur aS pcaraken. Win ipcaraken i Öebbi, amzun i$li d seg igenni, u iccelqef it ufôux, ne$ inheô it wavu, s amekkan lqayen.'),
(2627, 22, 32, 'Akka. Win ippâuzzun isekkiren n Öebbi, ihi, d aêezzeb n wulawen.'),
(2628, 22, 33, 'I kunwi degs aba$uô ar lajel ipwassnen, sinna, îêegga nnsen ar Uxxam aqdim.'),
(2629, 22, 34, 'I yal lois, Nefka asekkir, iwakken a d smektin ism n Öebbi, $ef ubhim n lmal is iten N$at. Öebbi nnwen d Öebbi Yiwen. Ihi, anzet aS. Becceô itubiyen,'),
(2630, 22, 35, 'wid iwumi ppergigin wulawen nnsen mara d mmektin Öebbi, wid iûebbôen i wayen iten iu$en, wid ipéallan u pseddiqen seg wayen is iten N$at.'),
(2631, 22, 36, 'Lmal iqebbwan, Nerra yawen ten, seg isekkiren n Öebbi. Degsen lfayda i kunwi. Bedret fellasen isem n Öebbi, mara d rsen. Mi $lin $ef ibeôdiyen nnsen, eççet segsen, cceççet aâîîaô, aéawali. Akka ay d Nenub fellawen yissen, amar a ppesnemmrem.'),
(2632, 22, 37, 'Ur ippawev ar Öebbi uksum nnsen, ne$ idamen nnsen, d awez$i. Ara T iawven, d aêezzeb nnwen. Am akka, Inub fellawen yissen, iwakken ad aS tgem ccan i Öebbi, ilmend n nnhaya nnwen s$uôeS. Becceô wid imaânen.'),
(2633, 22, 38, 'Ih, Öebbi Ipfukku wid iumnen. Ih, Öebbi ur Iêemmel ara yal lxayen ajehli.'),
(2634, 22, 39, 'Tsriê i wid ipwawwven imi pwadensen - Öebbi, s tidep, Izmer a ten Isellek -,'),
(2635, 22, 40, 'wid id ssuff$en seg ixxamen nnsen, war ssebba, imi kan qqaôen: "Mass nne$ d Öebbi". Lemmer ur Iswexxiô ara Öebbi imdanen, kra s kra, ara ipwahudden, war ccekk, d tiqwebtin, timezgida, lemûellat, lowamaâ ideg d smektayen, aîas, ism n Öebbi. Ih, Öebbi Ippaâwan win iT ippaâwanen. Öebbi, s tidep, d Uohid, d Uzmir.'),
(2636, 22, 41, 'Wid, ma Nessqâad iten di tmurt, bedden i téallit, pzekkin, ppamôen lewqama, gedlen tuccva. Ar Öebbi ara d gwrin lumuô.'),
(2637, 22, 42, 'Ma skaddben k, ni$ skaddben, uqbel nnsen, igduden n Nuê, Âad, akked Tamud,'),
(2638, 22, 43, 'agdud n Ibôahim, akked ugdud n Luî,'),
(2639, 22, 44, 'At Madyan. Skaddben Musa. Fki$ lmudda i ijehliyen, sinna, Zzi$ d fellasen. A tuzzma W imiren!'),
(2640, 22, 45, 'Acêal n temdinin ay Nesqucc imi densent. Haatent ppint. Xlan lebyar, akked lebruo uohiden.'),
(2641, 22, 46, 'Day ur unagen ara di tmurt? Ad sâun, $ef waya, ulawen ad fehmen yissen, imeééu$en ara islen yissen. Maca, maççi d allen, d ulawen deg idmaren i idre$len.'),
(2642, 22, 47, 'B$an k a d tesqeôbev aâaqeb. Öebbi ur Ipzeggil lemâahda S, d awez$i. Ni$ ass, ar Mass ik, am agim iseggwasen, s leêsab nnwen.'),
(2643, 22, 48, 'Acêal n temdinin iwumi Fki$ lmudda, u irna densent. Sinna, Zzi$ fellasent. £uôI tu$alin.'),
(2644, 22, 49, 'Ini: "a yimdanen! Nek, $uôwen, d aneddaô kan ipbegginen".'),
(2645, 22, 50, 'I wid iumnen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan, ssmaê akked ôôeéq ukyis.'),
(2646, 22, 51, 'Wid iaânan asfunneg issekniyen nne£, widak d at ujajiê.'),
(2647, 22, 52, 'Ur d Nuzen, uqbel ik, amazan ne$ nnbi, mebla ma ikecm ed Cciîan, deg wayen imenna, ma imenna. Itekkes Öebbi ayen d issekcam Cciîan, sinna, Itebbit issekniyen iS. Öebbi d Amusnaw, d Bab n ûûwab.'),
(2648, 22, 53, 'Iwakken ad Irr aggway n Cciîan d ahewwel, i at wulawen iblan akked at wulawen aquôan. Ih, imednas atnan di t$ennant tu$miqt.'),
(2649, 22, 54, 'Iwakken ad éôen wid iwumi teppunefk tmusni, ar neppa d tidep, s$uô Mass ik. Ad amnen yis. Ad as anzen wulawen nnsen. Öebbi, s tidep, Inehhu wid iumnen, s abrid uwqim.'),
(2650, 22, 55, 'Zgan wid ijehlen di ccekk fellas, ar ten id ias yimir, deqzalla, ne$ ibbwev iten id uâaqeb n wass abarar.'),
(2651, 22, 56, 'Assen, tagelda i Öebbi. Ad Iêudd garasen. Wid iumnen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan, ad ilin di Loennet n ssuâada.'),
(2652, 22, 57, 'I wid ijehlen, iskaddben issekniyen nne£, aâaqeb isdullun.'),
(2653, 22, 58, 'Wid iunagen, deg ubrid n Öebbi, sinna, pwan$an ne$ mmuten, a ten I$it Öebbi, war ccekk, s ôôeéq umâin. Ih, Öebbi Yif akw im$iten.'),
(2654, 22, 59, 'A ten Issekcem anekcum ara ôadin. Ih, Öebbi d Amusnaw, Iêellem.'),
(2655, 22, 60, 'Akka. Win iâaqben akken ippuâaqeb, sinna, ipwadnes, war ccekk, a t Isellek Öebbi. Ih, Öebbi Ipqili, Ipsemmiê.'),
(2656, 22, 61, 'Akka, acku Öebbi Issekcam iv deg wass, Issekcam ass deg yiv. U Öebbi Issel, Ipwali.'),
(2657, 22, 62, 'Akka, acku Öebbi d tidep, ma d ayen u$uô pnujun, war Neppa, d tikerkas. Ih, Öebbi d Aâlâyan, d Ameqwôan.'),
(2658, 22, 63, 'Day ur twalav ara Öebbi Isse$li d aman, seg igenni, d$a izzegzew wakal? Ih, Öebbi d Laîif, Iéôa.'),
(2659, 22, 64, 'IneS i illan deg igenwan, i illan di tmurt. Ih, Öebbi, ar Neppa d Asâay d Amaâzuz.'),
(2660, 22, 65, 'Ur twalav ara Öebbi Inub ed fellawen s wayen illan di tmurt, akked lbabur ippazalen di yill, s lameô iS. Iîîef igenni ur d i$elli f tmurt, siwa ma Iunef as. Ih, Öebbi, war ccekk, Issuruf u Ipêunu i imdanen.'),
(2661, 22, 66, 'D Neppa ikwen Issadren, sinna, ara kwen In$en, sinna, ara kwen id Issadren. Amdan, s tidep, d ajehli.'),
(2662, 22, 67, 'I yal lois, Nefka asekkir, teddun degs. Ulay$eô i k pna$en $ef lameô. Nuj ar Mass ik; ih, aql ak, keçç, di nnhaya tuwqimt.'),
(2663, 22, 68, 'Ma numren k, ini: "Öebbi Yif akw akken Issen ayen txeddmem.'),
(2664, 22, 69, 'Öebbi ad Iêudd garawen, ass n tnekra, $ef wayen tellam temgarradem".'),
(2665, 22, 70, 'Day ur teéôiv ara Öebbi Issen i illan deg igenni akked tmurt? Ayagi, s tidep, di Tezmamt. Ih, ayagi ishel i Öebbi.'),
(2666, 22, 71, 'La âabden, war Öebbi, ayen iwumi ur d Issers adabu, ayen ur ssinen. Imednas, ur illi wa ara ten isellken.'),
(2667, 22, 72, 'Ma mlan asen issekniyen nne£ iberrzen, a pâaqlev asmmummi deg udmawen n wid ijehlen. Qôib ad éevmen $ef wid i sen iqqaôen issekniyen nne£. Ini: "a kwen xebbôe$ af wayen i$elben aya: times i Iâahed Öebbi i wid ijehlen". A tu$alin tucmip!'),
(2668, 22, 73, 'A yimdanen! Ippunefk ed umedya, selt as d: ih, wid u$uô tepnujum, war Öebbi, ur zmiren, d awez$i, a d xelqen izi, xas mlalen $ef waya. Ma illa wayen i sen iuker yizi, ur zmiren ad as t id kksen. D uôhif umsuter, d uôhif win issuter.'),
(2669, 22, 74, 'Ur qudôen ara Öebbi, azal n lqedô iS. Ih, Öebbi d Uohid, d Uzmir.'),
(2670, 22, 75, 'Öebbi Iferren imazanen ger lmalayek, u ger imdanen. Ih, Öebbi Issel, Ipwali.'),
(2671, 22, 76, 'Issen i illan zdat sen, i illan deffir sen. Ar Öebbi ad u$alen lumuô.'),
(2672, 22, 77, 'A wid iumnen! Ïîinzet u knut, âabdet Mass nnwen, xedmet lxiô, amar a prebêem.'),
(2673, 22, 78, 'Jahdet ar Öebbi lêeqq ujahed iS. Neppa Ifren ikwen. Ur kwen Ihejjen ara di ddin, ddin ubabat wen Ibôahim. Neppa, i wen isemman, zik, imvuâen. Deg waya, ad yili Umazan d anagi nnwen, u a ppilim d inagan n medden. Ihi, ééallet, zekkit, teîîfem di Öebbi. Neppa d Bab nnwen. D Bab amxallef, d Asellak amxallef.');
INSERT INTO `ber_mensur` (`index`, `sura`, `aya`, `text`) VALUES
(2674, 23, 1, 'Ni$ lmumnin rebêen.'),
(2675, 23, 2, 'Wid ipéallan s wannuz;'),
(2676, 23, 3, 'wid ijunben yir awal;'),
(2677, 23, 4, 'wid ipzekkin;'),
(2678, 23, 5, 'wid iêurben af tuzzuft nnsen'),
(2679, 23, 6, '- siwa ar tlawin nnsen, ne$ taklatin nnsen. Akka, ur degsen tiyta;'),
(2680, 23, 7, 'wid ib$an sennig waya, widak zegren tilisa -,'),
(2681, 23, 8, 'wid ipqadaren lamanat nnsen, u lemâahda nnsen;'),
(2682, 23, 9, 'wid iwennâen tiéilla nnsen.'),
(2683, 23, 10, 'D wigi ay d iweôôaten,'),
(2684, 23, 11, 'wid ara iweôten Loennet, degs ad wekkôen.'),
(2685, 23, 12, 'Ni$ Nexleq amdan, seg ufûil n talaxt,'),
(2686, 23, 13, 'sinna, Nerra t d tiqqit deg umekkan n laman;'),
(2687, 23, 14, 'sinna, tiqqit Nxelq ip d argen; d$a, argen Nxelq it d acelleqluq; d$a, acelleqluq Nxelq it d i$san; d$a, Nessels aksum i yi$san. Sinna, Nxelq it d lxelq amaynut. Ad Ibarek Öebbi, Imxeyyeô ixellaqen!'),
(2688, 23, 15, 'Sinna, deffir waya, war ccekk, a ppemmtem.'),
(2689, 23, 16, 'Sinna, ih, ass n tnekra, a d tu$alem.'),
(2690, 23, 17, 'Ni$ Nexleq, sennig wen, ûa iberdan. Ur Nelli, $ef uxlaq, seg i$wefliyen.'),
(2691, 23, 18, 'Nessader ed, seg igenni, aman s lmizan. Naâteq iten di tmurt. Nezmer a ten Nessôuê.'),
(2692, 23, 19, 'Nxelq awen, yissen, leonanat n tezdayin akked téuôin; degsen, i kunwi, aîas n yizwayen, teppeppem segsen;'),
(2693, 23, 20, 'Akked ttejôa, id iff$en seg udrar n Sina. Teppak ed zzit u ddhin, i wid iteppen.'),
(2694, 23, 21, 'Ih, di lmal, aselmed i kunwi. Nesswa kwen s wayen illan deg iâabbav nnsen. Aîas n uba$uô degsen, i kunwi. Teppeppem segsen.'),
(2695, 23, 22, 'Fellasen, u $ef lbabuô, ppawin kwen.'),
(2696, 23, 23, 'Ni$ Nuzen ed Nuê i ugdud is. Inna: "a yagdud iw! Âabdet Öebbi. Ur awen illi ôebbi, war Neppa. Day ur tepêezziben ara"?'),
(2697, 23, 24, 'Nnan imvebbôen ijehliyen, n ugdud is: "wagi d amdan kan, am kunwi; ib$a a d ikk sennig wen. Lemmer i S ihwi i Öebbi, a d Issers lmalayek. Ur nesli s waya, ar lejdud nne$ imezwura.'),
(2698, 23, 25, 'Neppa d argaz kan aôehbani. Qaôaâet ep, tallit kan".'),
(2699, 23, 26, 'Inna: "a Mass iw! Awes iyi, skaddben iyi".'),
(2700, 23, 27, 'Nweêêa yas d: "eûnaâ lbabuô, ger wallen nne£, s uweêêi nne£. Mi d iusa lameô nne£, la pfeggiven igwefran, d ihedman, awi degs, tayuga n yal ûûenf, akked twacult ik, siwa wid, segsen, i$ef id izwar wawal. Ur iyI d steqsay af wid idensen, nitni, war ccekk, ad pwa$evsen.'),
(2701, 23, 28, 'Mi tâanncev di lbabur, keçç akked wid illan yidek, ini: ccekôan i Öebbi i $ Iselken seg ugdud imednas".'),
(2702, 23, 29, 'Ini: "a Mass iw! Ssers iyi deg umekkan iôqan; Keçç Tifev akw wid issrusun".'),
(2703, 23, 30, 'War ccekk, ayagi, d issekniyen, u Nekwni, Nezga d wid ipjeôôiben.'),
(2704, 23, 31, 'Sinna, Nxelq ed, deffir sen, isuta nniven.'),
(2705, 23, 32, 'Nuzen asen d amazan, segsen: "âabdet Öebbi, ur tesâim ôebbi, war Neppa. Day ur tepêezzibem ara"?'),
(2706, 23, 33, 'Nnan imvebbôen ijehliyen n ugdud is, wid iugin u inekôen timlilit n laxeôt, wid Ne$na di tmeddurt n ddunit: "wagi d amdan kan am kunwi, itepp seg wayen teppeppem, itess seg wayen teppessem.'),
(2707, 23, 34, 'Ma tessemêessem i umdan i kwen icban, war ccekk, kunwi seg imexsuôen.'),
(2708, 23, 35, 'Day i wen iâahed ard a d teff$em mara temmtem, tu$alem d akal, d i$san?'),
(2709, 23, 36, 'Ibâad, Ibâad, ayen i wen ippuwaââden.'),
(2710, 23, 37, 'I illan kan, d tameddurt n ddunit. A nemmet, a nidir, nekwni ur d neppenkar.'),
(2711, 23, 38, 'Neppa, d argaz kan id igren tikerkas $ef Öebbi. Nekwni, ur numin yis".'),
(2712, 23, 39, 'Inna: "a Mass iw! Awes iyi, skaddben iyi".'),
(2713, 23, 40, 'Inna: "garane$ d cwiî, a d gwrin di nndama".'),
(2714, 23, 41, 'Iwwet iten usu$u, s tidep. Nerra ten d rrmim. Err akin, agdud imednas!'),
(2715, 23, 42, 'Sinna, Nxelq ed, deffir sen, isuta nniven.'),
(2716, 23, 43, 'Lois ur d isseqôab, ur iswexxiô, lajel is.'),
(2717, 23, 44, 'Sinna, Nuzen ed imazanen nne£, wa deffir wa. Yal tikelt ideg ara d ias umazan, ar lois is, a t skiddben. Nerra ten mestebâan, Nerra ten d tidyanin. Err akin, agdud ur neppamen!'),
(2718, 23, 45, 'Sinna, Nuzen ed Musa akked gma s Haôun, s issekniyen nne£, akked udabu n ûûeê,'),
(2719, 23, 46, '$eô Ferâun akked imvebbôen is. Sme$wôen iman nnsen. Llan d agdud amzuxxi.'),
(2720, 23, 47, 'Nnan: "Day a namen sin imdanen am nekwni, u agdud nnsen d aklan nne$"?'),
(2721, 23, 48, 'Skaddben ten, d$a u$alen seg wid ipwan$an.'),
(2722, 23, 49, 'Ni$ Nefka Tazmamt i Musa, amar ad pwanhun.'),
(2723, 23, 50, 'Nerra mmi s n Meryem, akked imma s, d assekni. Nesduri ten di ti$ilt, degs laman d waman.'),
(2724, 23, 51, 'A yimazanen, eççet seg wayen imaânen, xedmet ayen ilhan, Nek, èôi$ ayen txeddmem.'),
(2725, 23, 52, 'Lois agi nnwen, s tidep, d lois yiwen. Nek, d Mass nnwen, ihi êezbet iyI.'),
(2726, 23, 53, 'Bvan lameô nnsen garasen, mi mfaôaqen. Yal akabar ifôeê s wayla s.'),
(2727, 23, 54, 'Eoo iten di maylellif nnsen, tallit kan.'),
(2728, 23, 55, 'Day $ilen mi sen Nefka ayla, tarwa,'),
(2729, 23, 56, 'ad asen Nezzazal lxiô? Xaîi, ur faqen.'),
(2730, 23, 57, 'Ih, wid, si tugwdi n Mass nnsen, pêadaren,'),
(2731, 23, 58, 'wid iumnen s issekniyen n Mass nnsen,'),
(2732, 23, 59, 'wid ur nepcarak i Mass nnsen,'),
(2733, 23, 60, 'wid ippaken ayen fkan, ulawen nnsen ugaden mi, nitni, ad u$alen ar Mass nnsen,'),
(2734, 23, 61, 'widak, pêirin ar lxiô u, $uôes, zeggwiren.'),
(2735, 23, 62, 'Ur Nepkellif taôwiêt, siwa ar wayen iwumi tezmer. £uône£ Tazmamt, tessawal tidep. Nitni ur twadensen.'),
(2736, 23, 63, 'Maca, ulawen nnsen di maylellif, $ef tagi. U rnan yir igiten i waya, a ten xedmen.'),
(2737, 23, 64, 'Alamma, mi Nesâadda aâaqeb $ef isâayen nnsen, a d su$en.'),
(2738, 23, 65, '"Ur psu$ut, ass agi, kunwi, segne$, ur tepwasellkem.'),
(2739, 23, 66, 'Ni$ mlan awen issekniyen iW, trewlem asen,'),
(2740, 23, 67, 'tesme$wôem iman nnwen fellasen. Teppaâwazem, tekkatem".'),
(2741, 23, 68, 'Day ur meyyzen ara Awal? Day ur ten id iusa ara, wayen ur d nusi ar lejdud nnsen imezwura?'),
(2742, 23, 69, 'Ne$ day ur ssinen ara amazan nnsen, imi t nekôen?'),
(2743, 23, 70, 'Ne$ qqaôen: "ikcem it loenn"? Xaîi, iusa ten id s tidep. Tegwti degsen, kerhen tidep.'),
(2744, 23, 71, 'Lemmer tedda tidep d lhawiyyat nnsen, war ccekk, tamurt, igenwan, akked wayen illan degsen, ad fesden. Xaîi, Nebbwi yasen d asmekti nnsen. Nitni asmekti nnsen ooan t.'),
(2745, 23, 72, 'Ne$, ad asen tessutrev taqdiât? Ppif taqdiât n Mass ik. Neppa Yif akw iôeééaqen.'),
(2746, 23, 73, 'Keçç, s tidep, la ten tneccdev s abrid uwqim.'),
(2747, 23, 74, 'Wid ur numin ara s laxeôt, s tidep, ff$en i ubrid.'),
(2748, 23, 75, 'Xas Nêun fellasen, u Nekkes asen ccqa nnsen, ad vellelen di leqheô nnsen, ad ddebdeben.'),
(2749, 23, 76, 'Ni$ Nesâadda fellasen aâaqeb. Ur knan i Mass nnsen, ur nujen.'),
(2750, 23, 77, 'Armi, mara asen Nelli tabburt uâaqeb iqesêen, imiren, degs, ad aysen.'),
(2751, 23, 78, 'Neppa i wen Ixelqen timesliwt, iéôi, ulawen. Drus ay tesnemmirem.'),
(2752, 23, 79, 'Neppa ikwen Iwezzâen di tmurt. £uôeS ara tepwafesrem.'),
(2753, 23, 80, 'Neppa i Issidiren, i Ineqqen. IneS afraz n yiv akked wass. Day ur tefhimem ara?'),
(2754, 23, 81, 'Xaîi. Nnan akken d nnan imezwura.'),
(2755, 23, 82, 'Nnan: "Ma nemmut, nu$al d akal, d i$san, day a $ d ssekren?'),
(2756, 23, 83, 'Ni$ ippuâahed wayagi i nekwni, akw, zik, i imezwura nne$. Ayagi, siwa d timucuha imezwura".'),
(2757, 23, 84, 'Ini: "wi p ilan tmurt, akked wayen illan degs, ma tessnem"?'),
(2758, 23, 85, 'A d inin: "d Öebbi". Ini: "ihi, day ur d tesmektayem ara"?'),
(2759, 23, 86, 'Ini: "anwa ay d Mass n ûa igenwan? Mass n usgeld ameqwôaêan"?'),
(2760, 23, 87, 'A d inin: "d Öebbi". Ini: "ihi, day ur tepêezzibem ara"?'),
(2761, 23, 88, 'Ini: "anwa i Isâan tagelda n yal cci, ger ifassen iS; Neppa Ipêarab, ur illi uêareb fellaS, ma teppissinem"?'),
(2762, 23, 89, 'A d inin: "d Öebbi". Ini: "ihi, acimi tepwamelkem"?'),
(2763, 23, 90, 'Xaîi! Nefka yasen tidep, nitni, war ccek, d ikeddaben.'),
(2764, 23, 91, 'Ur Isâi Öebbi mmi S. Ur illi ôebbi ar tama S. Mulac yal ôebbi ad iawi ayen id ixleq, wa ad iagwar wa. Gedha s Öebbi, seg wayen id snulfuyen!'),
(2765, 23, 92, 'Amusnaw n wayen iffren akked wayen ur neffir. D Aâlayan, sennig wayen pcaraken.'),
(2766, 23, 93, 'Ini: "a Mass iw! Lemmer a yi d Tesseknev acu i sen ippuâahden.'),
(2767, 23, 94, 'A Mass iw, ur iyi Ppara deg ugdud imednas".'),
(2768, 23, 95, '"S tidep, Nezmer ad ak Nessken acu i sen Nâahed".'),
(2769, 23, 96, 'Err akin tucmip s lfayeq. Nekwni Neéôa, sennig wiyav, ayen d snulfuyen.'),
(2770, 23, 97, 'Ini: "a Mass iw! Ëerz iyi seg u$wayen n ccwaîen. Êë'),
(2771, 23, 98, 'Ëerz iyi, a Mass iw! Ur dgi ppilin".'),
(2772, 23, 99, 'Armi, mi d tusa tmeppant yiwen degsen, inna: "a Mass iw! Err iyi,'),
(2773, 23, 100, 'amar ad xedme$ ayen ilhan deg wayen ooi$". Xaîi, d awal kan id inna. Tella, deffir es, tse$lit, alamma d ass n tnekra.'),
(2774, 23, 101, 'Ma ûuven di lbuq, assen, ur ppemyilin, ur pmesteqsayen.'),
(2775, 23, 102, 'Wid iwumi ééay lmizan nnsen, nitni rebêen.'),
(2776, 23, 103, 'Wid iwumi fessus lmizan nnsen, d nitni i issexsôen iman nnsen. Di Loahennama ad wekkôen.'),
(2777, 23, 104, 'A ppesser$ tmes udmawen nnsen, ad asen zelgen icenfiren.'),
(2778, 23, 105, 'Day ur awen qaren ara issekniyen iW, wanag la ten tnekôem?'),
(2779, 23, 106, 'Nnan: "a Mass nne$! I$leb ane$ ccum nne$. Nella d agdud im$eôqen.'),
(2780, 23, 107, 'A Mass nne$! Ssuffe$ ane$ segs. Ma nesnager, ihi, d imednas ay nella".'),
(2781, 23, 108, 'Ad Yini: "qqimet degs, ur pmeslayet"!'),
(2782, 23, 109, 'Ih, illa urbaâ n imdanen iW i iqqaôen: "a Mass nne$! Numen. Semmeê ane$, Ëun fella$, Keçç Tifev akw wid ipêunun".'),
(2783, 23, 110, 'Tettihim fellasen armi i wen sseppun asmekti W, u tdessem degsen.'),
(2784, 23, 111, 'Nek, assa, Kufa$ ten $ef wayen ûebôen. D nitni, war ccekk, ay d imerbaê.'),
(2785, 23, 112, 'Inna: "acêal iseggwasen i teqqimem deg wakal"?'),
(2786, 23, 113, 'Nnan: "Neqqim ass, ne$ ur ibbwiv wass, steqsi wid iêepben".'),
(2787, 23, 114, 'Inna: "cwiî kan ay teqqimen, lemmer, s tidep, day tessinem".'),
(2788, 23, 115, 'Day t$ilem Nxelq ikwen, kan, di rrayaâ; ar ur d teppu$alem $uône£?'),
(2789, 23, 116, 'Ay Meqqweô Öebbi, Agellid, Tidep! Ur illi ôebbi, siwa Neppa, Mass n usgeld ukyis.'),
(2790, 23, 117, 'Win inaâôen, ar tama n Öebbi, ôebbi nniven, ur isâi ppbut fellas, aqeîîi s ar Mass is kan. Ih, ur rebêen ara ijehliyen.'),
(2791, 23, 118, 'Ini: "a Mass iw! Semmeê u Ëun. Keçç, Tifev akw wid ipêunun".');
INSERT INTO `ber_mensur` (`index`, `sura`, `aya`, `text`) VALUES
(2792, 24, 1, 'Tasurep, Nessader ip id, Nêeppem ip id; Nessader ed, degs, issekniyen iberrzen, amar a d temmektim.'),
(2793, 24, 2, 'Tin ne$ win iznan, jekwvet, yal yiwen segsen, tawinest iberdan; ur kwen p$aven $ef udem n Öebbi, ma tellam tumnem s Öebbi akked wass aneggaru. Arbaâ n lmumnin, ad yili d anagi uâaqeb nnsen.'),
(2794, 24, 3, 'Win iznan ur ippa$ siwa tin iznan, ne$ tamcarekt. Tin iznan ur p ippa$ siwa win iznan, ne$ amcarek. Ipwagdel waya i lmumnin.'),
(2795, 24, 4, 'Wid itehmen tiâaôviyin, d$a ur d bbwin kué inagan, jekwvet pen îamet iberdan; ur qeblet ccada nnsen, d awez$i. Widen d iballa$en.'),
(2796, 24, 5, 'Kkes ed wid isteôoâen, deffir waya, u xedmen lfayeq. Öebbi, s tidep, Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu.'),
(2797, 24, 6, 'Wid itehmen tilawin nnsen, ur sâin inagan, siwa iman nnsen, yiwen segsen ad iggal s Öebbi, kué iberdan, ar neppa d bab n tidep,'),
(2798, 24, 7, 'akked ubrid wis smus ar a t Ixzu Öebbi ma iskaddeb.'),
(2799, 24, 8, 'Ur teppuâaqeb tmeîîut, ma teggul s Öebbi, kué iberdan, ar neppa seg wid iskadben,'),
(2800, 24, 9, 'akked ubrid, wis smus ar fellas zzâaf n Öebbi, ma issawel ed tidep.'),
(2801, 24, 10, 'A lemmer ur illi fellawen lfevl n Öebbi akked uêunu S! Öebbi, s tidep, Issuruf, d Bab n ûûwab.'),
(2802, 24, 11, 'Ih, wid isweûlen tikerkas, d agraw segwen. Ur p$ilit d cceôô i kunwi, xaîi, d lxiô nnwen. Yal yiwen, degsen, ibbwi ayen ibbwi ubekkav. Aâaqeb abarar i win, segsen, i ibbwin amur ameqwôaêan.'),
(2803, 24, 12, 'A lemmer lmumnin, argaz tameîîut, mi s slan, meyyzen lxiô, deg iman nnsen, u nnan: "wagi d tikerkas ibanen"!'),
(2804, 24, 13, 'A lemmer d bbwin, fellas, kué inagan! Ma ur d bbwin ara inagan, ar Öebbi, wigi, d ikeddaben.'),
(2805, 24, 14, 'Lemmer ur illi fellawen lfevl n Öebbi akked uêunu S, di ddunit akked laxeôt, a ppesâaddim aâaqeb abarar $ef wayen i$ef temcawaôem.'),
(2806, 24, 15, 'Mi p id teggarem s yilsawen nnwen, u teqqaôen s imawen nnwen ayen ur tessinem, t$ilem d ulac. Neppa, ar Öebbi, d abarar.'),
(2807, 24, 16, 'Lemmer, mi as teslam, tennam: "ur a$ issefk ara umeslay $ef waya! Gedha s yiseK! Wagi d acehrir abarar".'),
(2808, 24, 17, 'Inuba kwen Öebbi ur teppalsem, am akka, d awez$i, ma d lmumnin ay tellam.'),
(2809, 24, 18, 'Ipbeggin awen Öebbi issekniyen. Öebbi d Amusnaw, d Bab n ûûwab.'),
(2810, 24, 19, 'Ih, wid ib$an a d iazel lâaô, ar wid iumnen, fellasen aâaqeb aqeôêan di ddunit, di laxeôt. Öebbi Issen, kunwi ur tessinem.'),
(2811, 24, 20, 'A lemmer ur illi fellawen lfevl n Öebbi akked uêunu S! U Öebbi d Umâin, Ipêunu.'),
(2812, 24, 21, 'A wid iumnen! Ur teddut di lateô n Cciîan. Win iteddun di lateô n Cciîan, ar la iteddu di lâaô akked tuccva. Lemmer ur illi fellawen lfevl n Öebbi akked uêunu S, ur ippizdig degwen yiwen, d awez$i. Maca, Öebbi Izzizdig win i S ihwan. Öebbi Issel, d Amusnaw.'),
(2813, 24, 22, 'Wid, degwen, iwumi ippunefk lfevl akked terkunt, ur pgalan $ef tikci i llzem, i ime$ban, i wid iunagen deg ubrid n Öebbi. Ad semmêen, ad ssurfen. Day ur têemmlem ara mara awen Isemmeê Öebbi? Öebbi Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu.'),
(2814, 24, 23, 'Ih, wid ipqeôôiven tilawin zeddigen, istehzan, iumnen, ad pwaxzun di ddunit, di laxeôt. Fellasen aâaqeb abarar.'),
(2815, 24, 24, 'Ass ideg ara d cehhden $ef igiten nnsen, ilsawen nnsen, ifassen nnsen, ivaôen nnsen,'),
(2816, 24, 25, 'assen, ad asen Ifk Öebbi ayen ppalasen, s tidep. Ad éôen ar Öebbi d Tidep ibanen.'),
(2817, 24, 26, 'Yir tlawin i yir irgazen, yir irgazen i yir tlawin. Tilawin n lâali i irgazen n lâali, irgazen lâali i tlawin n lâali. Wigi ur ppkan deg wayen qqaôen. I nitni, ssmaê akked ôôeéq ukyis.'),
(2818, 24, 27, 'A wid iumnen! Ur keçmet ixxamen ur nelli nnwen, alamma s tsriê, u alamma tselmem $ef imawlan nnsen. Ppif akka i kunwi, amar a d tesmektim.'),
(2819, 24, 28, 'Ma ur tufim êedd degsen, ur keçmet alamma s tsriê. Ma nnan awen d: "u$alet", u$alet. Yif it wakka i ûûfawa nnwen. Öebbi Iéôa ayen txeddmem.'),
(2820, 24, 29, 'Ulac u$ilif fellawen ma tkecmem ixxamen ur nepwazde$, ma tella t$awsa nnwen degsen. Öebbi Iéôa acu d teqqaôem, u wacu teppeffrem.'),
(2821, 24, 30, 'Ini i wid iumnen ad brun i wallen nnsen, ad ssôen tuzzuft nnsen. Yif it wakka i ûûfawa nnsen. Öebbi, s tidep, Iéôa ayen xeddmen.'),
(2822, 24, 31, 'Ini i tid iumnen ad brunt i wallen nnsent, ad ssôent tuzzuft nnsent, ur d sskanent, di zzin nnsent, siwa ayen d ivehôen segs, ad $umment idmaren nnsent. Ur d sskanent ccbuê nnsent, siwa i irgazen nnsent, ne$ ibabaten nnsent, ne$ im$aôen nnsent, ne$ iqcicen nnsent, ne$ irbiben nnsent, ne$ atmaten nnsent, ne$ iqcicen n watmaten nnsent, ne$ wid n tsetmatin nnsent, ne$ tiqeddacin nnsent, ne$ taklatin nnsent, ne$ iqeddacen imudduzen, ne$ arrac ur nelleméi. Ur kkatent dderz, ad ipwassen zzin nnsent uffir. Steôoâet akw i Öebbi, a lmumnin, amar a prebêem.'),
(2823, 24, 32, 'Jewoet i iâzriyen nnwen, akked wid imaânen seg waklan nnwen, akked teklatin nnwen. Ma d ime$ban ay llan, a ten Iôéeq Öebbi, s lfevl iS. Öebbi d Ajemmal, d Amusnaw.'),
(2824, 24, 33, 'Wid ur nufa ara ar a$en, ad ûebôen ar ten id Iôéeq Öebbi, s lfevl iS. Wid, seg waklan nnwen, i ib$an ad asen tarum aserreê, arut asen ma teéôam ten, d at lxiô ay llan. Fket asen seg ayla i wen Ifka Öebbi. Ur pêeppimet $ef teklatin nnwen, tiquêbit, i rrbeê nnwen di tmeddurt n ddunit, ma b$ant tezdeg. Ma têeppmen, Öebbi, deffir uêeppem nnsent, Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu.'),
(2825, 24, 34, 'Ni$ Nessader awen ed issekniyen iberrzen, akked umedya n wid iâacen uqbel nnwen, d anabi i wid ipêezziben.'),
(2826, 24, 35, 'Öebbi d tafat n tmurt akked igenwan. Amedya n tafat iS d takwap degs taftilt. Taftilt daxel n tqeôâap. Taqeôâap, amzun d itri acôaôaq, tecâal it ttejôa iôqan, tazemmurt ur nelli n ugmuv ne$ n utaram. Qôib a pfet zzit is, ur p tennul tmes. Tafat $ef tafat. Ippawi Öebbi win i S ihwan ar tafat iS. Ippak ed Öebbi imedyaten i medden. Öebbi Iéôa yal cci.'),
(2827, 24, 36, 'Deg ixxamen i Ib$a Öebbi ad ufraren, ideg ara d immekti yisem iS, sbuccuâen T ssbeê, tameddit.'),
(2828, 24, 37, 'Irgazen ur tes$afal ttjaôa, ne$ ssuq, $ef usmekti n Öebbi, $ef téallit, $ef zzakat; ppagwaden ass, ideg ara nehwwalen wallen akked wulawen.'),
(2829, 24, 38, 'Iwakken a ten Ikafi Öebbi $ef wayen xeddmen d amxallef, ad asen Irnu si lfevl iS. Öebbi Ip$iti win i S ihwan, war aktili.'),
(2830, 24, 39, 'Igiten n wid ijehlen, am aylal deg uza$aô. Win ifuden, ad i$il d aman. Alamma mi ibbwev $uôes, ur ippaf acemma. A n iaf Öebbi, Issuli as leêsab is. Öebbi Ip$awal deg uqeîîi.'),
(2831, 24, 40, 'Ne$ am tillas di yill le$miq. T$umm it lmuja, sufella lmuja, sufella asigna. Tillas sennig tiyav. Ma issuffe$ ed afus is, ur issawev a t iwali. Win iwumi ur Iga ara Öebbi tafat, ur isâi tafat.'),
(2832, 24, 41, 'Day ur twalav ara, sbuccuâen Öebbi i illan di tmurt akked igenwan? Ifrax deg waffug. Issen taéallit akked usbuccaâ n yal yiwen. Öebbi Iéôa ayen xeddmen.'),
(2833, 24, 42, 'N Öebbi tagelda n tmurt akked igenwan. £uô öÖebbi tu$alin.'),
(2834, 24, 43, 'Ur twalav ara Öebbi Isselêay asigna, sinna, a t Izdi, sinna, a t Issem$weô? D$a a pwaliv ageffur a d iffe$ si zdaxel is. Isrusu d, seg idurar igenni, abruri. Ad Iwwet yis, win i S ihwan, a t Iveôôef $ef win i S ihwan. Tafat n lebôaq iS qôib a ppeglu s yiéôi.'),
(2835, 24, 44, 'Öebbi Ismizwar iv akked wass. Deg wayagi, s tidep, d aselmed i wid isâan iéôi.'),
(2836, 24, 45, 'Öebbi Ixleq akw lêayawan, seg waman. Garasen, illa win ippeênunufen $ef uâabbuv is, win ileêêun $ef sin ivaôôen, win ileêêun $ef kué. Ixelleq Öebbi ayen i S ihwan. Öebbi, s tidep, Izmer i yal cci.'),
(2837, 24, 46, 'Ni$ Nessader ed issekniyen iberrzen. Öebbi Inehhu win i S ihwan, ar ubrid uwqim.'),
(2838, 24, 47, 'Qqaôen: "numen s Öebbi akked Umazan, nu$ awal". Sinna, deffir waya, iwexxeô urbaâ segsen. Wigi ur llin d lmumnin.'),
(2839, 24, 48, 'Mi pwanecden ar Öebbi akked Umazan iS, ad Iêudd garasen, arbaâ segsen iwexxeô.'),
(2840, 24, 49, 'Ma sâan lêeqq, a d asen $uôes, d imvuâen.'),
(2841, 24, 50, 'Day helken wulawen nnsen, ne$ cukken, ne$ ugaden a ten Isneêyaf Öebbi akked Umazan iS? Xaîi, widak d imednas.'),
(2842, 24, 51, 'Timenna n lmumnin, mara ssutren aêuddu n Öebbi akked Umazan iS, ad Iêudd garasen, d tigi kan: "nesla, nôuva". D wigi ay d imerbaê.'),
(2843, 24, 52, 'Win iôuvan Öebbi akked Umazan iS, ippagwaden Öebbi, ipêezziben, nitni d isaâdiyen.'),
(2844, 24, 53, 'Ggulen s Öebbi, tagallit meqqwôen, ar ma tumôev asen, ard ad ff$en, war ccekk. Ini: "ur pgallat, annuz ipwassen. Öebbi, s tidep, Iéôa ayen txeddmem".'),
(2845, 24, 54, 'Ini: "ôavit Öebbi, ôavit Amazan". Ma wexxôen, fellas, neppa, ayen kan i s sbabben, fellawen kunwi ayen i wen sbabben. Ma tôuvam T, a ppeppwanhum. I iwatan i Umazan, siwa awal ipbegginen.'),
(2846, 24, 55, 'Iâahed Öebbi, i wid iumnen segwen, u xedmen ayen ilhan, ara ten Irr, war ccekk, d igensas di tmurt, akken Irra wid i ten id izwaren; ara ad asen Isseqâad ddin nnsen i$ef i ten Iôuva; ar ad asen Issegwri laman, deffir tugdi. Âabden iyI, ur iyI pcaraken acemma. Wid ijehlen, deffir waya, widak d iballa$en.'),
(2847, 24, 56, 'Beddet i téallit, zekkit, a$et awal i Umazan. Amar aêunu fellawen.'),
(2848, 24, 57, '£uôwat a p$ilem wid ijehlen sfunnugen di tmurt. Axxam nnsen d times. A tu$alin tucmip!'),
(2849, 24, 58, 'A wid iumnen! S uâammed nnwen ara d kecmen, $uôwen, waklan nnwen akw wid, degwen, ur nebli$ ara, krav iberdan ideg ur telsim ara: uqbel taéallit n tafrara, $ef îîhuô mara tekksem iceîîiven, deffir téallit n lâica. Ulac u$ilif fellawen ne$ fellasen, ma wa iéuô wa, deffir lewqat agi. Akka i wen d Ibeggen Öebbi issekniyen. Öebbi Iéôa, d Bab n ûûwab.'),
(2850, 24, 59, 'Ma bel$en warrac nnwen, s uâammed nnwen, am wid i ten id izwaren. Akka i wen d Ibeggen Öebbi issekniyen iS. Öebbi Iéôa, d Bab n ûûwab.'),
(2851, 24, 60, 'Ulac u$ilif $ef tâuqaô i iâaddan i jwao, ma kksent iceîîiven nnsent, mebla ma sseknent ccbuê nnsent. Ma setêant, yif it i nitenti. Öebbi Issel, d Amusnaw.'),
(2852, 24, 61, 'Ur telli tiyta deg uder$al, ne$ deg urejdal, ne$ deg umuvin, ne$ degwen, ma teççam deg ixxamen nnwen, deg wid n ibabaten nnwen, deg wid n tyimmatin nnwen, deg wid n watmaten nnwen, deg wid n tsetmatin nnwen, deg wid iâammiten nnwen, deg wid n tâammitin nnwen, deg wid ixaliten nnwen, deg wid n txaltitin nnwen, deg wid ideg tesâam tisura, ar uêbib nnwen. Ulac u$ilif fellawen ma teççam d agraw, ne$ d ifôiden. Mara tkecmen ixxamen, msalamet s wazul iôqan, aêmayan, s$uô Öebbi. Akka i wen d Ibeggen Öebbi issekniyen. Amar a pfehmem.'),
(2853, 24, 62, 'Lmumnin, siwa wid iumnen s Öebbi akked Umazan iS. Ma llan yides $ef lameô iten icerken, ur pôuêun alamma ssutren as tsriê. Ih, wid i k issuturen tsriê, d nitni i iumnen s Öebbi akked Umazan iS. Ma ssutren ak tsriê, $ef kra iten iaânan, serreê i win i k ihwan, segsen. Ssuter i Öebbi ad sen Isemmeê. Öebbi, s tidep, Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu.'),
(2854, 24, 63, 'Ur êepbet asiwwel garawen i Umazan, am mara temsawalem. Ih, Iéôa Öebbi wid, segwen, ippensaren s tuffra. Ad steêdren wid mgirrden lameô iS: ad ppuhewwlen, ne$ ad sâaddin aâaqeb aqeôêan.'),
(2855, 24, 64, 'Ih, day maççi n Öebbi, i illan di tmurt akked igenwan? Ni$ Iéôa amek tellam $uôeS. Ass n tu$alin nnsen $uôeS, ad asen Imel d acu xedmen. Öebbi Issen yal cci.');
INSERT INTO `ber_mensur` (`index`, `sura`, `aya`, `text`) VALUES
(2856, 25, 1, 'Ad Iôqu Win id Issadren afraz, i umdan iS, iwakken ad yili d aneddaô imavalen.'),
(2857, 25, 2, 'Win Ilan tagelda n tmurt akked igenwan; ur Isâi mmi S; ur aS illi ucrik di tgelda. Ixleq yal cci, Iwezn it s lmizan.'),
(2858, 25, 3, 'Ddmen, war Neppa, iôebbiten ur nexliq acemma. D nitni i ipwaxelqen. Ur pseyyin vveô ne$ aba$uô, i iman nnsen. Ur pseyyin di tmeppant ne$ di tmeddurt, ne$ di tnekra.'),
(2859, 25, 4, 'Nnan wid ijehlen: "ayagi, d tikerkas kan. Isnulfa tent id, iâawen it, fellas, ugdud nniven. Ni$ densen u skaddben".'),
(2860, 25, 5, 'Nnan: "d timucuha imezwura, i iura; qqaôen as tent ûûbeê, tameddit".'),
(2861, 25, 6, 'Ini: "Issader it id, Win Issnen sser n tmurt akked igenwan. Neppa, s tidep, Izga Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu".'),
(2862, 25, 7, 'Nnan: "d acut Umazan agi i iteppen lqut, iteddun ar leswaq? A lemmer id irs $uôes lmelk, ara yilin yides d aneddaô,'),
(2863, 25, 8, 'ne$ ippunefk as ugerruj, ne$ isâa aqwiô itepp segs"! Nnan imednas: "la teppeddum kan d urgaz iwumi sseêren".'),
(2864, 25, 9, 'Wali amek id ppaken fellak imedyaten. Nnetlafen, ur zmiren ad pwanhun.'),
(2865, 25, 10, 'Ad Iôqu Win ad ak Ifken, ma Irad, i ifen ayagi: leonanat, ddawat sen isaffen ppazzalen. Ad ak Issali lebôuo.'),
(2866, 25, 11, 'Xaîi, nekôen imir. Nhegga d times i win inekôen imir.'),
(2867, 25, 12, 'Mi ten twala si tama ibaâden, ad as slen s leêôaôa akked zzhir.'),
(2868, 25, 13, 'Mara $lin degs, nitni pwarzen deg umekkan uqmiv, ad siwlen, dinna, i wangar.'),
(2869, 25, 14, '"Ur ssawalet ara, assa, i yiwet n wangar, ssiwlet i waîas n wangaren".'),
(2870, 25, 15, 'Ini: "ppif ayagi, ne$ Loennet n lebda i Nâahed i wid ipêezziben? D neppat ay d arraz, ay d taggara, i nitni".'),
(2871, 25, 16, 'I nitni degs, ayen i sen ihwan, i lebda. D lemâahda i$ef Iuksan Mass ik.'),
(2872, 25, 17, 'Ass ideg ara ten Ifser, nitni akked wid âabden, war Öebbi, ad Yini: "d kunwi i itelfen imdanen iW agi, ne$ d nitni i iff$en abrid"?'),
(2873, 25, 18, 'A d inin: "gedha s yiseK! Ur a$ issefk a neddu d bab, war Keçç. Maca, T$atev ten, nitni akked imezwura nnsen, armi ppun asmekti, u$alen d agdud ixeûôen".'),
(2874, 25, 19, 'Atan nekôen kwen $ef wayen d tennam. Ihi ur tezmirem i tsensert, ne$ i leslak. Win idensen, degwen, a Nessukk fellas, aâaqeb ameqwôan.'),
(2875, 25, 20, 'Ur d Nuzen, uqbel ik, imazanen, mebla ma llan teppen lqut, u teddun ar leswaq. Nerra kwen, wa ihewwel wa, ma a pûebôem. Mass ik Izga la d Ismuqul.'),
(2876, 25, 21, 'Nnan wid ur nessarem ara timlilit yidne£: "a lemmer id ssersen lmalayek $uône$, ne$ nwala Mass nne$"! Ni$ sme$wôen aîas iman nnsen, u ffuhrin aîas.'),
(2877, 25, 22, 'Ass ideg ara walin lmalayek, ur ippili wassen d abecceô ibe$wviyen, s lxiô. A d inin: d aêdid ur nepwazgar.'),
(2878, 25, 23, 'Nezzi $eô igiten nnsen, Nerra ten d a$ebbaô immebruzzâen.'),
(2879, 25, 24, 'Imawlan n Loennet, assen, di tnezdu$t akked trusi iufraren.'),
(2880, 25, 25, 'Ass ideg ara iceqqeq igenni s usigna, ideg ara d ssersen lmalayek, ta deffir ta,'),
(2881, 25, 26, 'tagelda, assen, tidep, i Uênin. D ass uwâiô i ijehliyen.'),
(2882, 25, 27, 'Ass ideg ara i$eéé umednus ifassen is, ad yini: "a yamxix iw, a lemmer ddi$ d ubrid Umazan!'),
(2883, 25, 28, 'A tawa$it pwa$e$, a lemmer ur rri$ ara winnat d aêbib!'),
(2884, 25, 29, 'Ni$ itelf iyi seg usmekti i illan iusa yi d. Cciîan, i umdan, izga d axeddaâ".'),
(2885, 25, 30, 'Inna Umazan: "a Mass iw! Ar ugdud iw, s tidep, Leqwôan agi d askeôfeé".'),
(2886, 25, 31, 'Akka, i yal nnbi, Nefka acengu seg ibe$wviyen. Iqadd Mass ik, i nnhaya akked usellek.'),
(2887, 25, 32, 'Nnan wid ijehlen: "a lemmer i s d ssersen Leqwôan, deg yiwet n tikelt"! Akka, iwakken a Ntebbet ul ik, yis. Nesemderri t d idurra.'),
(2888, 25, 33, 'Ur ak d ppawin amedya, mebla ma Nuzen ak d tidep, akked ufesser amxallef.'),
(2889, 25, 34, 'Wid ara ipwafesren af udmawen nnsen, ar Loahennama, widak d at umkan n dir mavi, d at ubrid im$eôôeq mavi.'),
(2890, 25, 35, 'Ni$ Nefka yas Tazmamt i Musa, u Nerna $uôes gma s, Haôun, d am²âiwen.'),
(2891, 25, 36, 'Nenna: "ôuêet ar ugdud i inekôen issekniyen nne£". Nhudd iten qeccuc meccuc.'),
(2892, 25, 37, 'Agdud n Nuê, mi nekôen imazanen, Ne$ves iten, u Nerra ten d assekni i medden. Nhegga i imednas aâaqeb aqeôêan.'),
(2893, 25, 38, 'Âad, Tamud, At Öôas, u aîas isuta garasen.'),
(2894, 25, 39, 'I yal wa, Nefka imedyaten. Yal wa, Neôéa t wakali.'),
(2895, 25, 40, 'Ni$ âaddan $ef taddart i$ef id i$li ugeffur ageswaê. Day qqimen ur p walan ara? Xaîi, ur ssaramen ara tanekra.'),
(2896, 25, 41, 'Mi k walan, ppemsexxiôen kan fellak: "day d wagi id Iuzen Öebbi, d Amazan?'),
(2897, 25, 42, 'Qôib i $ itlef seg iôebbiten nne$, lemmer ur neûbiô fellasen". Deqqal ad éôen mara walin aâaqeb, anwa i innetlafen, kteô, seg ubrid.'),
(2898, 25, 43, 'Twalav win i irran lhawiyya s d ôebbi s? Day ad as tiliv, keçç, d awkil?'),
(2899, 25, 44, 'Day t$ilev tegwti, segsen, sellen ne$ fehmen? Nitni am lmal kan, aâer $elben ten akken nnetlafen seg ubrid.'),
(2900, 25, 45, 'Ma twalav Mass ik, amek id Ifka tili? Lemmer i S ihwi, Irra p d tusbiî. D$a Nefka yas itij d ppbut.'),
(2901, 25, 46, 'Sinna, Njebd ip id $uône£, ajbad isehlen.'),
(2902, 25, 47, 'D Neppa i wen Irran iv d aceîîiv, ives d areyyeê, u Irra ass d tanekra.'),
(2903, 25, 48, 'D Neppa i wen d Iuznen avu, d abecceô s uêunu S. Nessers ed, seg igenni, aman iûfan;'),
(2904, 25, 49, 'iwakken a Neêyu yissen tamurt immuten; a Nessew yissen aîas seg wid id Nexleq n lmal, akked imdanen.'),
(2905, 25, 50, 'Ni$ Nfeôq iten garasen, iwakken a d mmektin. Tegwti n yimdanen ugin; atnan kan di tijehli.'),
(2906, 25, 51, 'Lemmer i £ ihwi, yili Nuzen aneddaô, i yal tamdint.'),
(2907, 25, 52, 'Ur ppa$ awal i ijehliyen. Nna$ iten yis, amennu$ ameqwôan.'),
(2908, 25, 53, 'D Neppa i Issemfaôaqen sin ilellen, yiwen êlaw, d aéidan, wayev ôéag, d ameô$an. Irra, garasen, agadir, aêdid ur nepwazgar.'),
(2909, 25, 54, 'D Neppa i Ixelqen amdan seg waman. Ifka yas laâmum, lexwal. Mass ik Izga d Win Izemren.'),
(2910, 25, 55, 'La âabden, war Öebbi, ayen ur ten inefâan, ur ten ivuôôen. Ajehli, ar loiha n Mass is, izga d win issefôa$en.'),
(2911, 25, 56, 'Nuzen ik id kan, i ubecceô d uneddeô.'),
(2912, 25, 57, 'Ini: "ur awen ssutre$, $ef waya, kra n teqdiât. Ssutre$ kan, i win ib$an, ad ia$ abrid $eô Mass is".'),
(2913, 25, 58, 'Ppkel $ef Umuddir ur Nepmeppat. Sbuccaâ iT s ccekôan. Iqadd i tussna ibekkaven n imdanen iS.'),
(2914, 25, 59, 'I Ixelqen tamurt, igenwan, akked wayen illan garasen, di sdis wussan. Sinna, Aênin Iâannec af usgeld. Steqsi w iT issnen.'),
(2915, 25, 60, 'Ma pwanecden: "knut i Uênin"! A d rren: "d acu T Uênin? Day a neknu i w ara $ d tamôev"? D a$unfu i sen irna.'),
(2916, 25, 61, 'Ad Iôqu Win Irran itran deg igenni. Irna degs, lefnaô, akked waggur bu tziri.'),
(2917, 25, 62, 'D Neppa i Irran iv akked wass mestebâan, i win ib$an ad ismekti, ne$ ib$an ad isnemmer.'),
(2918, 25, 63, 'Ixdimen n Uênin, i ileêêun di tmurt di lehna, ma numren ten at war tussna, qqaôen: "tifrat"!'),
(2919, 25, 64, 'I ippaâwazen i Mass nnsen, knan ne$ bedden;'),
(2920, 25, 65, 'I iqqaôen: "a Mass nne$! Veôôef segne$ aâaqeb n Loahennama. Ih, aâaqeb is ipwaêeppem".'),
(2921, 25, 66, 'Neppat, s tidep, d tadirant, i tnezdu$t akked i$imi.'),
(2922, 25, 67, 'Wid, ma seôôfen, ur veggiâen, ur pcuêêun: igi iwulmen atan garasen.'),
(2923, 25, 68, 'Wid ur nenâaô ôebbi nniven, ar tama n Öebbi. Ur neqqen amdan, d ayen Igdel Öebbi, siwa $ef tidep. Ur zennun. Win ixedmen ayagi, ibbwi ibekkaven.'),
(2924, 25, 69, 'Ad ippuâaqeb berdayen, ass n tnekra. Ad iwekkeô d imdelli;'),
(2925, 25, 70, 'siwa win isteôoâen, iumnen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan. I wigi, ad Inûef Öebbi tucmitin nnsen, s yise$iyen. Öebbi Izga Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu.'),
(2926, 25, 71, 'Win isteôoâen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan, ihi, iutub Öebbi s ppuba n tidep.'),
(2927, 25, 72, 'Wid ur ncehhed ccada n rrya; u, ma mmugren tifukal, ddan d ukyisen.'),
(2928, 25, 73, 'Wid, mara asen d smmektin issekniyen n Mass nnsen, ur d neggar tiâéegt ne$ tider$elt fellasen.'),
(2929, 25, 74, 'Wid iqqaôen: "a Mass nne$! Err tilawin nne$, akked dderya nne$, d ssuâada n wallen. Err ane$ d wid inehhun wid ipêezziben".'),
(2930, 25, 75, 'Widak ad ppuoazin s t$uôfatin, ilmend n wayen ûebôen. Ad magren, dinna, azul, tifrat.'),
(2931, 25, 76, 'Dinna, ad wekkôen, d amkan amxalef i tnezdu$t d i$imi.'),
(2932, 25, 77, 'Ini: "ur d Irezzu Mass iw, degwen, ma ur tnujem $uôeS. Ni$ tnekôem? Ad iu$al waya d ayen ilezmen".');
INSERT INTO `ber_mensur` (`index`, `sura`, `aya`, `text`) VALUES
(2933, 26, 1, 'Ïsm.'),
(2934, 26, 2, 'Atnan issekniyen n Tezmamt ipbegginen.'),
(2935, 26, 3, 'Ahat tqelqev iman ik, imi ur ppilin d lmumnin.'),
(2936, 26, 4, 'Ma ihwa ya£, ad asen d Nessers assekni seg igenni, ad îinzent, zdat es, tmegôav nnsen, s wannuz.'),
(2937, 26, 5, 'Ur ten id ippas usmekti amaynut, s$uô Uênin, mebla ma u$alen as d inekkaôen.'),
(2938, 26, 6, 'Ni$ skaddben. Ihi, ad asen d asen isallen, $ef wayen i$ef pmmaâliken.'),
(2939, 26, 7, 'Day ur walan ara tamurt? Acêal i Nessenker degs n yal tayuga tukyist!'),
(2940, 26, 8, 'Deg wayagi, s tidep, assekni. Tegwti degsen, ur llin d lmumnin.'),
(2941, 26, 9, 'Mass ik, s tidep, Neppa, d Uzmir, Ipêunu.'),
(2942, 26, 10, 'Mi Issawel Mass ik, i Musa: "ôuê s agdud imednas,'),
(2943, 26, 11, 'agdud n Ferâun. Day ur ppezziben ara"?'),
(2944, 26, 12, 'Inna: "a Mass iw! Nek ugade$ ad iyi skiddben,'),
(2945, 26, 13, 'ad sekkwôen idmaren iw, ur ipserriê yiles iw. Ihi, Azen ar Haôun.'),
(2946, 26, 14, 'U denbe$ $uôsen. Ugade$ ad iyi n$en".'),
(2947, 26, 15, 'Inna: "Xaîi, ôuêet s issekniyen nne£. Aql a£ yidwen, Nessemêas en. Ôö'),
(2948, 26, 16, 'Öuêet ar Ferâun, tinem as: "nekwni d amazan n Mass imavalen.'),
(2949, 26, 17, 'Seddu, yidne$, At Isôail".'),
(2950, 26, 18, 'Inna: "day ur k nôebba ara $uône$, d llufan? U tesâaddav $uône$, iseggwasen di lâameô ik;'),
(2951, 26, 19, 'u txedmev igi txedmev. Keçç, seg ijehliyen".'),
(2952, 26, 20, 'Inna: "xedme$ t asmi lli$ seg im$eôôqen.'),
(2953, 26, 21, 'Rewle$ segwen, mi kwen ugade$. Ifka yi Mass iw, ûûwab. Irra yi seg imazanen.'),
(2954, 26, 22, 'D l$it agi, i$ef a yi teppezzmev, i k ibbwin a pperrev, At Isôail, d aklan"?'),
(2955, 26, 23, 'Inna Ferâun: "d acu T Mass imavalen"?'),
(2956, 26, 24, 'Inna: "d Mass n tmurt, igenwan, akked wayen illan garasen, ma tetebbtem".'),
(2957, 26, 25, 'Inna i wi s d izzin: "la tsellem"?'),
(2958, 26, 26, 'Inna: "Mass nnwen, u Mass n lejdud nnwen, imezwura".'),
(2959, 26, 27, 'Inna: "s tidep, amazan nnwen id ippuceggâen $uôwen, d aôehbani".'),
(2960, 26, 28, 'Inna: "Mass n ugmuv, utaram, akked wayen illan garasen, lemmer tefhimem".'),
(2961, 26, 29, 'Inna: "ma tedmev Öebbi, ur nelli d nek, a k nerr ar lêebs".'),
(2962, 26, 30, 'Inna: "i lemmer ad ak d awi$ ayen ipbegginen"?'),
(2963, 26, 31, 'Inna: "awi t id, ma d tidep ay tessawalev".'),
(2964, 26, 32, 'Iveggeô taâkwazt is, tu$al d azrem n ûûeê.'),
(2965, 26, 33, 'Issuffe$ ed afus is, d$a d amellal i imfeôoen,'),
(2966, 26, 34, 'Inna i imvebbôen i s d izzin: "wagi, s tidep, d aseêêar amusnaw;'),
(2967, 26, 35, 'ib$a a kwen issuffe$, s ssêur is, seg wakal nnwen. D acu t lameô nnwen"?'),
(2968, 26, 36, 'Nnan: "sgani t, neppa akked gma s; azen ineccaden ar temdinin,'),
(2969, 26, 37, 'ad ak d awin yal aseêêar amusnaw".'),
(2970, 26, 38, 'Mlalen iseêêaren, di lweqt akked wass ipwassnen.'),
(2971, 26, 39, 'Nnan i imdanen: "ma ad tenjemâam?'),
(2972, 26, 40, 'Ahat a neddu d iseêêaren, ma d nitni ara irebêen".'),
(2973, 26, 41, 'Mi d usan iseêêaren, nnan as i Ferâun: "ma ad a$ tili teqdiât, ma nerbeê"?'),
(2974, 26, 42, 'Inna: "ih, d$a, kunwi, war ccekk, a ppu$alem seg iqôiben".'),
(2975, 26, 43, 'Inna yasen Musa: "veggôet ayen ara tveggôem".'),
(2976, 26, 44, 'Veggôen imraren akked tâakwzin nnsen. Nnan: "s tezmert n Ferâun, ard nekwni ara irebêen"!'),
(2977, 26, 45, 'Iveggeô Musa taâkwazt is. Apan tesseblaâ ayen id snulfan.'),
(2978, 26, 46, 'Iseêêaren $lin, knan.'),
