(3194, 27, 35, 'Nek, ad asen azne$ tarzeft, ad aôou$ acu ara d awin imcegâan".'),
(3195, 27, 36, 'Mi tebbwev ar Sliman, inna: "day ad iyi tâawnem s terkunt? Ayen i yi Ifka Öebbi, yif ayen i wen Ifka. D kunwi kan i ifeôêen, s terzeft nnwen.'),
(3196, 27, 37, 'U$al $uôsen. Ih, a nôuê $uôsen s lâaskeô, iwumi ur zmiren. A ten id nessuffe$, syenna, ndellen, d imejîuêen".'),
(3197, 27, 38, 'Inna: "a yimvebbôen, anwa degwen, ara yi d iawin asgeld is, uqbel a yi d asen d imvuâen"?'),
(3198, 27, 39, 'Aâfrit si leonun, inna d: "ad ak t id awi$, uqbel ma tekkrev seg umekkan ik. I wayagi, war ccekk, nek d uzmir muman".'),
(3199, 27, 40, 'Inna d bab n tmusni si Tezmamt: "nek ad ak t id awi$, uqbel a pfukkev asmeômec". Mi t iwala irs ed $uôes, inna: "wagi si lfevl n Mass iw, ad iyi ijeôôeb ma ad snemmre$, ne$ ma ad jehle$. Win isnemmren, isnemmer kan i iman is. Win ijehl, ihi, Mass iw d Asâay, d Ukyis".'),
(3200, 27, 41, 'Inna: "bedlet as udem usgeld is, a néeô ma tepwanha, ne$ haap seg wid ur nepwanha".'),
(3201, 27, 42, 'Mi d tusa, nnan as: "day am wagi, usgeld inem"? Terra d: "amzun d neppa". "Tusa ya$ d tmusni, uqbel neppat, nuzen.'),
(3202, 27, 43, 'Isôuê ip wayen tunez, war Öebbi. Tella, s tidep, seg ugdud ijehliyen".'),
(3203, 27, 44, 'Nnan as: "ekcem ar lbeôo"! Mi t twala, t$il degs aman; tesban ed ifadden is. Inna: "s tidep, d lbeôo ulelluc imzin". Tenna: "a Mass iw! Ih, dense$ iman iw. Akked Sliman, unze$ aS i Öebbi, Mass imavalen".'),
(3204, 27, 45, 'Ni$ Nuzen ed, i Tamud, gmat sen Üaliê: "âabdet Öebbi"! Maca, rran snat n trebbuya$, ppemnamarent.'),
(3205, 27, 46, 'Inna: "a yagdud iw! Acimi tep$awalem ar tucmip, uqbel ise$? Lemmer a ppeste$fôem Öebbi, ahat aêunu fellawen".'),
(3206, 27, 47, 'Nnan: "tkeêêesev a$, keçç akked wi iddan yidek". Inna: "lfal nnwen ar Öebbi, u kunwi d agdud ara ippuhewwlen".'),
(3207, 27, 48, 'Llan, di temdint, tza iterrasen i issefsaden di tmurt, ur pleqqimen.'),
(3208, 27, 49, 'Nnan: "yyaw a nemmesgal s Öebbi, ard a neévem deg iv fellas, neppa akked twacult is. Sinna, a nini i bab is: ur nelli d inagan n tmen$iwt n tawacult is. Ih, nekwni, d imawlan n tidep".'),
(3209, 27, 50, 'Undin ticeôkep, Nundi ticeôkep, nitni ur faqen.'),
(3210, 27, 51, 'Wali amek tevôa di tceôkep nnsen. Nen$ed iten, nitni, akked ugdud nnsen, meôôa.'),
(3211, 27, 52, 'Atnan hudden ixxamen nnsen, ilmend n ddens nnsen. Deg wayagi, war ccekk, assekni i ugdud issnen.'),
(3212, 27, 53, 'Nsellek wid iumnen u llan pêezziben.'),
(3213, 27, 54, 'I Luî, mi inna i ugdud is: "teppeddum ar wayen n dir, u kunwi tepwalim.'),
(3214, 27, 55, 'Ih, kunwi teppeddum ar irgazen, teb$am ten, war tilawin. Ih, kunwi d agdud ur nessin".'),
(3215, 27, 56, 'Tiririt n ugdud is, siwa mi d nnan: "ssuff$et tawacult n Luî, si temdint nnwen, nitni d imdanen i ib$an tezdeg".'),
(3216, 27, 57, 'Nsellek it, neppa akked twacult is, siwa tameîîut is. Nseyya a ppili seg wid igwran.'),
(3217, 27, 58, 'Nesse$li d fellasen ageffur. I icmet ugeffur n wid ippunedôen!'),
(3218, 27, 59, 'Ini: "ccekôan i Öebbi. Talwit i imdanen iS, wid Ifren". Ppif Öebbi, ne$ ayen pcaraken?'),
(3219, 27, 60, 'Day Win Ixelqen tamurt akked igenwan, i wen d Isse$lin aman, seg igenni - Nessenkar, yissen, iqwiôen ippembehwaoen, ur teêwaoem a d tessem$im ttjuô is -, day illa ôebbi, ar tama n Öebbi? Maca, nitni d agdud issaâdalen.'),
(3220, 27, 61, 'Day Win Irran tamurt d tanezdu$t, Irra degs isaffen, Irra yas idurar, Irra agadir ger sin ilellen, day illa ôebbi ar tama n Öebbi? Xaîi, tegwti degsen, ur ssinen.'),
(3221, 27, 62, 'Day Win Issemêasen i umevôuô, mara S d isiwel; Itekksen ayen n dir; i kwen Ipparan d igensas di tmurt; day illa ôebbi, ar tama n Öebbi? Drus id tesmektayem.'),
(3222, 27, 63, 'Day Win i kwen Inehhun, di tillas n lberr akked yill, id Ippaznen avu, d abecceô n ccira uêunu S; day illa ôebbi, ar tama n Öebbi? Ay Aâlay Öebbi, sennig wayen pcaraken!'),
(3223, 27, 64, 'Day Win Ibeddun lxelq, sinna, Ippales as; ikwen I$aten seg igenni akked tmurt; day illa ôebbi ar tama n Öebbi? Ini: "awit ed atebbet nnwen, ma tessawalem tidep"!'),
(3224, 27, 65, 'Ini: "tabavnit, di tmurt akked igenwan, ur p issin yiwen siwa Öebbi. Ur éôin melmi ara d kkren".'),
(3225, 27, 66, 'Ih, tamusni nnsen ur tessawev ar laxeôt? Xaîi, nitni di ccekk fellas. Xaîi, nitni, fellas, dre$len.'),
(3226, 27, 67, 'Nnan wid ijehlen: "day ma nu$al d akal, am imezwura nne$, s tidep, fella$ tanekra?'),
(3227, 27, 68, 'Ni$ waââden a$ aya, i nekwni akw i imezwura nne$, zik. Ayagi, d timucuha kan imenza".'),
(3228, 27, 69, 'Ini: "iniget di tmurt, walit amek tevôa d ibe$wviyen".'),
(3229, 27, 70, 'Ur $webben fellasen, ur pxiqqi ilmend n nncub nnsen.'),
(3230, 27, 71, 'Nnan: "melmi lemâahda agi, ma d tidep ay tessawalem"?'),
(3231, 27, 72, 'Ini: "kra n wayen i$ef têarem, ahat atan ivfeô kwen id".'),
(3232, 27, 73, 'Mass ik, s tidep, meqqweô lfevl iS, $ef imdanen. Maca, tegwti degsen ur snemmiren.'),
(3233, 27, 74, 'Mass ik, s tidep, Iéôa ayen teffren idmaren nnsen, akked wayen d qqaôen.'),
(3234, 27, 75, 'Ur illi wayen iffren, deg igenni akked tmurt, ur nuri di Tezmamt ipbegginen.'),
(3235, 27, 76, 'Ih, Leqwôan agi iêekku d i At Isôail, tegwti n wayen i$ef mgarraden.'),
(3236, 27, 77, 'Neppa, war ccekk, ard nnhaya akked uêunu i lmumnin.'),
(3237, 27, 78, 'Mass ik, s tidep, ad Iseyyi garasen s uêuddu S. Neppa d Uzmir, d Amusnaw.'),
(3238, 27, 79, 'Ppkel $ef Öebbi, ih, aql ak di tidep ipbegginen.'),
(3239, 27, 80, 'Ih, keçç, ur tepparav lmeggtin ad slen, ur tepparav iâeééugen ad slen i wancad, ma wexxôen.'),
(3240, 27, 81, 'Ur fellak nnhaya ider$alen, mgal ttelfan nnsen. Ara islen, siwa wid iumnen s issekniyen nne£. Nitni d imvuâen.'),
(3241, 27, 82, 'Mi iûaô wawal fellasen, ad asen d Nessuffe$ lweêc si tmurt; ad asen yini ar imdanen ur metbutit $ef issekniyen nne£.'),
(3242, 27, 83, 'Ass ideg ara d Nefser, si yal lois, arbaâ n wid inekôen issekniyen nne£, d tirni,'),
(3243, 27, 84, 'alamma, mi d usan, ad Yini: "day tnekôem issekniyen iW, ur ten teskecmem di tmusni? Ne$ d acu tellam txeddmem"?'),
(3244, 27, 85, 'Iûaô wawal fellasen, imi densen. Ur d pmeslayen.'),
(3245, 27, 86, 'Day ur walan ara ar Nerra yasen iv i ureyyeê nnsen, ass iwakken ad walin? Deg wayagi, s tidep, issekniyen i ugdud iumnen.'),
(3246, 27, 87, 'Ass uûuvu n lbuq, ad iagwad i illan deg igenwan, i illan di tmurt, siwa wid i S ihwan i Öebbi. A d asen akw $uôeS, s uêiwet.'),
(3247, 27, 88, 'A pwaliv idurar i t$ilev sebken, la teddun am usigna. D igi n Öebbi i Iûegmen yal cci. Neppa, s tidep, Iéôa d acu txedmem.'),
(3248, 27, 89, 'Win id iusan s ise$, ad iawi it yifen. Widak, assen, mevmunit si tugdi.'),
(3249, 27, 90, 'Wid id iusan s tucmip, ad ppin wudmawen nnsen ar tmes. Ni$ a ppeppuqeîîim kan $ef wayen txeddmem?'),
(3250, 27, 91, 'Pwamôe$ kan ad âabde$ Mass n temdint agi, i Iôqa. IneS yal cci. Pwamôe$ d ad ili$ seg imduâen,'),
(3251, 27, 92, 'ad male$ Leqwôan. Win ipwanhan, ipwanha kan i iman is. Win innetlafen, ini: "nek d aneddaô kan".'),
(3252, 27, 93, 'Ini: "a neckeô Öebbi. Ad awen Issken issekniyen iS. A ten tâaqlem". Mass ik ur I$effel ara $ef wayen txeddmem.');
INSERT INTO `ber_mensur` (`index`, `sura`, `aya`, `text`) VALUES
(3253, 28, 1, 'Ïsm.'),
(3254, 28, 2, 'Atnan issekniyen n Tezmamt ipbegginen.'),
(3255, 28, 3, 'Ad ak d Neêku si teqûiî n Musa akked Ferâun, s tidep, i ugdud iumnen.'),
(3256, 28, 4, 'Ih, Ferâun issem$weô iman is di tmurt; imezda$ ifeôq iten d iêôumen. Isrewrew îayfa segsen, izellu arrac nnsen, issidir tilawin nnsen. Ih, neppa seg ifessaden.'),
(3257, 28, 5, 'Neb$a a Nfeôôeo $ef wid irewrwen di tmurt, a ten Nerr d imeqwôanen, a ten Nerr d iweôôaten.'),
(3258, 28, 6, 'A ten Nesseqâad di tmurt. A Nessken i Ferâun, Haman, akked iâsekôiwen nnsen, ayen ppagwaden segsen.'),
(3259, 28, 7, 'Nweêêa i imma s n Musa: "ssuîîev it, sinna, ma tugadev fellas, err it ar wasif. Ur ppagwad, ur $webben. Ad am t id Nerr, u a t Nerr seg imazanen".'),
(3260, 28, 8, 'Teddem it twacult n Ferâun. Ad asen iu$al d acengu, d a$ilif. Ih, Ferâun, Haman, akked iâsekôiwen nnsen llan d imsaben.'),
(3261, 28, 9, 'Tenna tmeîîut n Ferâun: "d nnûib n tiî, i nek akked keçç. Ur tneqq, ahat ad a$ infaâ, ne$ a t nerr d mmit nne$". Nitni ur faqen ara.'),
(3262, 28, 10, 'Temmar ed tasa n yimma s n Musa. Qôib it id tessken, lemmer ur Nzeyyeô ara ul is, iwakken a ppili si lmumnin.'),
(3263, 28, 11, 'Tenna i ultma s: "evfeô it"! Teqquôa t si mbâid, nitni ur faqen.'),
(3264, 28, 12, 'Uqbel, Negdel as tid iûûuîuven. Tenna: "ad awen ssekne$ axxam ar awen itkwelfen fellas, u nitni ad as bedden"?'),
(3265, 28, 13, 'Nerra t id i imma s, iwakken ad as kkawent wallen is, ur t$webben, iwakken a péeô ar lemâahda n Öebbi d tidep. Maca, tegwti degsen, ur ssinen.'),
(3266, 28, 14, 'Mi meqqweô, ittaâqel, Nefka yas tussna, ûûwab. Akka ay Nepkafi imdanen lâali.'),
(3267, 28, 15, 'Ikcem tamdint, di lweqt ideg stehzan imezda$ is. Iufa n sin irgazen pna$en, yiwen seg uêôum is, wayev seg icenga s. Win n uêôum is, issuter as d afus, mgal win n icenga s. Iwwet it Musa s lbunia, in$a t. Inna: "ayagi, seg igi n Cciîan. Neppa, s tidep, d acengu n ûûeê, itellifen".'),
(3268, 28, 16, 'Inna: "a Mass iw! Nek dense$ iman iw, Semmeê iyi". Isemmeê as. Ih, Neppa Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu.'),
(3269, 28, 17, 'Inna: "a Mass iw! S l$it iK felli, ur ppili$, d awez$i, si loiha ibe$wviyen".'),
(3270, 28, 18, 'Iufa d iman is di temdint, iugad, iquôaâ. Atan a d ipâaggiv $uôes, win i s d issutren afus, ass izeryen. Inna yas Musa: "keçç, s tidep, d im$eôôeq n ûûeê".'),
(3271, 28, 19, 'Acengu nnsen, mi ib$a a t iwwet, inna d: "a Musa! Day teb$iv ad iyi ten$ev, akken ten$iv yiwen, ivelli? Teb$iv kan a ppiliv d aqehhaô di tmurt, ur teb$iv ara a ppiliv seg iâaôviyen".'),
(3272, 28, 20, 'Iusa d urgaz si îîerf n temdint, ippazal. Inna d: "a Musa! S tidep, imvebbôen mlalen $ef loal ik, a k n$en. Effe$, nek, seg wid ik ipweûûin".'),
(3273, 28, 21, 'Iffe$ segs, iugad, iquôaâ. Inna: "a Mass iw! Sellek iyi seg ugdud imednas".'),
(3274, 28, 22, 'Mi ibbwi tikli ar Madian, inna: "ahat Mass iw ad iyi Iawi d ubrid umâin".'),
(3275, 28, 23, 'Mi ibbwev s aman n Madian, iufa n arbaâ n l$aci, la sswan. Iufa, di îîerf nnsen, snat n tlawin, îîfent lmal nnsent. Inna: "d acu txeddmemt"? Nnant ed: "ur nesswa alamma wexxôen imeksawen. Babat ne$ d am$aô ameqwôan".'),
(3276, 28, 24, 'Issew asent, iu$al ar tili, inna: "a Mass iw! Nek ôe$be$ $ef yal lxiô, ar iyi d Tessersev".'),
(3277, 28, 25, 'Tusa t id yiwet segsent, s tikli ikukran, tenna: "atan ak d issawal baba, a k ikafi imi $ tesswev". Mi iôuê $uôes, u iêka yas i ivôan, inna: "ur ppagwad, tepwasellkev seg ugdud imednas".'),
(3278, 28, 26, 'Yiwet segsent, tenna: "a baba! Eîîef it d acrik, ih, yif icriken ik, iohed, muman".'),
(3279, 28, 27, 'Inna: "b$i$, nek, ad ak fke$ yiwet si yissi yagi, s cceôt a pxedmev $uôi îam iseggwasen. Ma tessawdev mraw, s leb$i k. Ur b$i$ a k hejjne$. Ad ak ili$, ma Irad Öebbi, seg iâaôviyen".'),
(3280, 28, 28, 'Irra: "ayagi, gari yidek. A tin sâadda$ ger snat n tallitin, ur ippili felli u$ilif. Öebbi d Awkil, $ef wayen id nenna".'),
(3281, 28, 29, 'Mi ifukk Musa tallit, u iseyyeê akked twacult is, iwala times ar tama n udrar. Inna i twacult is: "qqimet, wala$ times, ahat ad awen d awi$, segs, asali ne$ asafu, amar a ppesseêmum".'),
(3282, 28, 30, 'Mi ibbwev $uôes, ipwanced ed si ttejôa, di rif ayeffus n te$zut, deg umviq iôqan: "a Musa! S tidep, Nek d Öebbi, Mass imavalen.'),
(3283, 28, 31, 'Veggeô taâkwazt ik". Mi p iwala, la tesseêôiîiw amzun d azrem, ibren ur iwexxeô. "A Musa! Qeddem, ur ppagwad, aql ak, ih, di laman.'),
(3284, 28, 32, 'Err afus ik di loib ik, a d iffe$ d amellal, ur ihlik. Sseqôeb ed $uôek i$il ik, ad ak tekkes tugwdi. Tigi d sin n ppbut s$uô Mass ik, i Ferâun akked imvebbôen is. Ih, nitni d agdud iballa$en".'),
(3285, 28, 33, 'Inna: "a Mass iw! Nek n$i$ yiwen segsen, ugade$ ad iyi n$en.'),
(3286, 28, 34, 'Gma Harun yif iyi afeûûeê umeslay. Azen it id yidi d amâiwen, ad iyi tebbet. Nek ugade$ ad iyi nekôen".'),
(3287, 28, 35, 'Inna: "a Nesseohed tayepp ik s gma k. Ad awen Nefk, i sin, adabu; ur kwen id ppawven. S issekniyen nne£, d kunwi akked wid iddan yidwen ara irebêen".'),
(3288, 28, 36, 'Mi ibbwev $uôsen Musa, s issekniyen iberrzen, nnan: "ayagi, siwa ssêur id innulfan. Ur nesli s waya, $uô ibabaten nne$ imezwura".'),
(3289, 28, 37, 'Inna Musa: "Mass iw Iéôa sennig wiyav, anwa iwumi Ifka nnhaya s$uôeS, anwa ara d igwrin deg Uxxam. Imednas, s tidep, ur rebêen".'),
(3290, 28, 38, 'Inna Ferâun: "a yimvebbôen, ur awen mli$ ara kra n ôebbi, war nekkini. Ecâal iyi times ar talaxt, a Haman; bnu yi lbeôo aâlayen; ahat ad ali$ ar ÖÔebbi n Musa. Nek, s tidep, êesbe$ t seg wid iskiddiben".'),
(3291, 28, 39, 'Neppa, akked iâsekôiwen is, sme$wôen iman nnsen di tmurt, war ssebba. £ilen, ar nitni, ur d ppu$alen $uône£.'),
(3292, 28, 40, 'Neppa, akked iâsekôiwen is, Neîîef iten. Nger iten ar yill. Wali amek tevôa d imednas.'),
(3293, 28, 41, 'Nerra ten d imeqwôanen i ineccden ar tmes. Ass n tnekra, ur ppusellken.'),
(3294, 28, 42, 'Neqqen asen xezzu di ddunit agi. Ass n tnekra, nitni seg ucmiten.'),
(3295, 28, 43, 'Ni$ Nefka Tazmamt i Musa, mbaâd ma Nesqucc isuta imezwura. D tafat i imdanen, d nnhaya u d aêunu. Amar a d mmektin.'),
(3296, 28, 44, 'Ur telliv ara di loiha utaram, mi Nseyya lameô i Musa. Ur telliv seg inagan.'),
(3297, 28, 45, 'Maca, Nxelq ed tisuta, $wezzif laâmeô nnsent. Ur tellid seg imezda$ n Madian, la sen teqqarev issekniyen nne£. Maca, Nella Neppazen.'),
(3298, 28, 46, 'Ur telliv ar tama n udrar, mi d Nessawel. Maca d aêunu s$uô Mass ik, iwakken a pnedrev agdud, u$uô ur d iusi uneddaô, uqbel ik. Amar a d mmektin.'),
(3299, 28, 47, 'Mulac, ma têuza ten tiyta id urwen ifassen nnsen, a d inin: "a Mass nne$! A lemmer i $ d Tuznev amazan, a neddu d issekniyen iK, a nili seg wid iumnen"!'),
(3300, 28, 48, 'Mi ten id tusa tidep s$uône£, nnan: "a lemmer id iusi am wayen id iusan i Musa"! Day ur ugin ara, zik, ayen id iusan i Musa? Nnan: "d sin ssêurat". Mwafaqen, nnan: "nekwni nugi ten i sin".'),
(3301, 28, 49, 'Ini: "awit ed Tazmamt, s$uô Öebbi, i yifen snat agi, i nnhaya, ad ddu$ yides, ma tessawalem tidep".'),
(3302, 28, 50, 'Ma ur ak d rran ara, efhem ar ddan kan d lhawiyyat nnsen. Anwa innetlafen, sennig win iteddun d lhawiyya s, war nnhaya s$uô Öebbi? Öebbi, s tidep, ur Inehhu agdud imednas.'),
(3303, 28, 51, 'Aql a£ Nessawwev asen awal, amendeô ma d mmektin.'),
(3304, 28, 52, 'Umnen yis wid iwumi Nefka Tazmamt, uqbel tagi.'),
(3305, 28, 53, 'Ma $ôan asen t, ad inin: "numen yis. Ih, ar neppa d tidep, s$uô Mass nne$. Uqbel is, s tidep, nella d imvuâen".'),
(3306, 28, 54, 'Wigi a ten id ias ukafi nnsen berdayen, $ef wayen ûebôen, swexxiôen tucmip s yise$, u seg wayen iten N$at, pseddiqen.'),
(3307, 28, 55, 'Mi slan i yir awal, ad as veôfen, u qaôen: "i nekwni igiten nne$, i kunwi igiten nnwen. Fellawen talwit. Ur neô$eb $ef at war tussna".'),
(3308, 28, 56, 'Keçç, s tidep, ur tnehhuv win têemlev. Maca, Öebbi Inehhu win i S ihwan. Neppa, Yif akw akken Iéôa wid ipwanhan.'),
(3309, 28, 57, 'Nnan: "ma nedda d nnhaya yidek, a nepwaxvef seg wakal nne$". Day ur ten Nesseqâad ara di loamaâ n laman, u$uô d ppawvent yal l$ellat? D l$it s$uône£. Maca, tegwti degsen, ur éôin.'),
(3310, 28, 58, 'Acêal Nesqucc n temdininn, cerrâent di temâict nnsent. Atnan ixxamen nnsen, ay ten ized$en, deffir sen, siwa ixeîîayen. D Nekwni ay d iweôôaten.'),
(3311, 28, 59, 'Ur Isquccu Mass ik timdinin, alamma iuzen i imezda$ nnsent, amazan i sen immalen issekniyen nne£. Ur Nesquccu timdinin, mebla ma llan imezda$ nnsent, d imednas.'),
(3312, 28, 60, 'Kra n wayen i wen ippunefken n cci, d zzhu n tmeddurt n ddunit, akked ccbuê is. Ayen illan $eô Öebbi, yif it, ad idum kter. Day ur pmeyyizen ara?'),
(3313, 28, 61, 'Day win iwumi Nefka lemâahda igerzen, u immuger ip, am win i Nezha s l$it n tmeddurt n ddunit; sinna, ass n tnekra, neppa seg wid ara d irsen?'),
(3314, 28, 62, 'Ass ideg ara sen d Isiwel, ad Yini: "anda ten wid iyY tepcarakem, u tellam tepkabarem"?'),
(3315, 28, 63, 'A d inin wid i$ef iûaô wawal: "a Mass nne$! Wigi i njeggeê, njeggeê iten, akken i nepwajeggeê. A nzekki $ureK: maççi d nekwni ay âabden".'),
(3316, 28, 64, 'Ad asen inin: "naâôet wid tepcarakem". Ad ten naâôen, ur asen d pparan. Walan aâaqeb. A lemmer llan pwanhan!'),
(3317, 28, 65, 'Ass ideg ara sen d Isiwel, ad Yini: "acu d terram i imazanen"?'),
(3318, 28, 66, 'Assen, ad dergen fellasen isalen, nitni ur pmesteqsayen.'),
(3319, 28, 67, 'Ma d win isteôoâen, iumnen, ixedmen ayen ilhan, ahat ad yili seg imerbaê.'),
(3320, 28, 68, 'Mass ik Ixelleq ayen i S ihwan, u Ismenyafa. Ur ten id iûaê usmenyif. Gedha s Öebbi! I Aâlay sennig wayen pcaraken!'),
(3321, 28, 69, 'Mass ik Iéôa ayen iffren deg idmaren nnsen, akked wayen cennâen.'),
(3322, 28, 70, 'Neppa d Öebbi, ur illi ôebbi siwa Neppa. I Neppa, annuz di tmezwarut, u di tneggarut. I Neppa aêuddu, $uôeS tu$alin nnwen.'),
(3323, 28, 71, 'Ini: "acu tmeyyzem, ma Isse$li d Öebbi iv imezgi, fellawen, alamma d ass n tnekra? Anwa ôebbi, war Öebbi, ara wen d iawin tafat? Day ur tsellem ara"?'),
(3324, 28, 72, 'Ini: "acu tmeyyzem, ma Issuli Öebbi ass imezgi, fellawen, alamma d ass n tnekra? Anwa ôebbi, war Öebbi, ara wen d iawin iv, a ppestaâfum degs? Day ur tepwalim ara"?'),
(3325, 28, 73, 'Seg uêunu S, Iga yawen iv akked wass, i ustaâfu nnwen, akked unadi n lfevl iS. Amar a ppesnemmrem.'),
(3326, 28, 74, 'Ass ideg ara sen d Isiwel, ad asen Yini: "anda ten wid iyY tepcarakem, u tellam tepkabarem"?'),
(3327, 28, 75, 'A d Nawi anagi, si yal lois. A Nini: "awit ed atebbet nnwen". Ad éôen ar tidep n Öebbi. Itelf iten wayen d snulfuyen.'),
(3328, 28, 76, 'Ih, Qaôun illa seg ugdud n Musa. Iqehô iten. Nefka yas igerrujen; s tezmert ugraw ioehden, arfad n tsura nnsen. Mi s inna ugdud is: "ur zehhu! Öebbi, s tidep, ur Iêemmel ara izehwaniyen.'),
(3329, 28, 77, 'Deg wayen i k Ifka Öebbi, nadi axxam aneggaru. Ur teppu amur ik, di ddunit. Elhu, akken i Ilha Öebbi $uôek. Ur ssaram lefsad di tmurt. Öebbi, s tidep, ur Iêemmel ifessaden".'),
(3330, 28, 78, 'Inna: "ippunefk iyi kan, ilmend n tmusni i sâi$". Day ur iéôa ara ar Öebbi Isqucc, uqbel is, ger isuta, wid i t iugaren di tezmert, isemmden kteô? Ur illi usteqsi ibe$wviyen, af ibekkaven nnsen.'),
(3331, 28, 79, 'Iffe$ ed s agdud is, s ôôêuê is. Wid ib$an tameddurt n ddunit, nnan: "awufan nesâa am wayen ippunefken i Qaôun! Ih, neppa d bab n terkunt tabarart".'),
(3332, 28, 80, 'Wid, iwumi teppunefk tmusni, nnan: "a ssexv nnwen! Ppwab n Öebbi yif it, i win iumnen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan. Ara d iûaê siwa win iûebôen".'),
(3333, 28, 81, 'Nger it seddaw tmurt, neppa akked uxxam is. Ur as telli terbaât ara t isellken, war Öebbi. Ur illi seg wid ipselliken iman nnsen.'),
(3334, 28, 82, 'Wid issaramen amkan is, ivelli nni, u$alen nnan: "zi$ Öebbi Issugut ôôeéq i win i S ihwan, deg imdanen iS, u iwezzen. Lemmer ur a$ I$at ara Öebbi, yili Iger a$ seddaw tmurt. Ih, ur rebêen ijehliyen".'),
(3335, 28, 83, 'Axxam nni aneggaru, a t Nerr i wid ijunben tem$weô akked usefsed, di tmurt. Tirect i wid ipêezziben.'),
(3336, 28, 84, 'Win id iusan s yise$, ad iawi ayen it yifen. Win id iusan s tucmip, ihi, ad ppuqeîîin wid ixedmen tucmitin, $ef wayen kan xeddmen.'),
(3337, 28, 85, 'Ih, Win Ilezmen fellak Leqwôan, war ccekk, a k id Irr s axxam. Ini: "Mass iw Yif akw akken Issen anwa id iusan s nnhaya, anwa i illan di ttelfan n ûûeê".'),
(3338, 28, 86, 'Ur tessarmev ara, ad ak ed ters Tezmamt, lemmer maççi d aêunu s$uô Mass ik. Ur ppili d amâiwen ijehliyen.'),
(3339, 28, 87, 'Ur k swexxiôen seg issekniyen n Öebbi, deffir trusi nnsen $uôek. Nuj ar Mass ik, ur ppili seg wid ipcaraken.'),
(3340, 28, 88, 'Ur nâaô, ar tama n Öebbi, ôebbi nniven. Ur illi ôebbi, siwa Neppa. Yal cci ad inger, siwa udem iS. IneS aêuddu. £ureS ara tu$alem.');
INSERT INTO `ber_mensur` (`index`, `sura`, `aya`, `text`) VALUES
(3341, 29, 1, 'Alm.'),
(3342, 29, 2, 'Day $ilen imdanen a ten ooen qqaôen: "numen", u nitni ur ppuhewwlen?'),
(3343, 29, 3, 'Ni$ Nhewwel wid i ten id izwaren. War ccekk, ad Yissin Öebbi wid iqqaôen tidep, ad Yissin ikeddaben.'),
(3344, 29, 4, 'Ne$ $ilen ad a£ zwiren wid ixedmen tucmitin? Dir it wayen pêuddun.'),
(3345, 29, 5, 'Win iggunin timlilit akked Öebbi, s tidep, a d ias, war ccekk, lajel n Öebbi. Neppa, Issel, d Amusnaw.'),
(3346, 29, 6, 'Win ijuhden, ijuhed kan i iman is. Öebbi, s tidep, ur Iêwao ara imavalen.'),
(3347, 29, 7, 'Wid iumnen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan, war ccekk, ad asen Nekkes tucmitin nnsen, a ten Nkafi $ef wayen xeddmen ifuqen.'),
(3348, 29, 8, 'Nweûûa amdan ar lewqama, s imawlan is. Ma lezmen fellak, ad iyI tcarkev ayen ur tessinev, ur asen ppa$ awal. Tu$alin nnwen, $uôI. Ad awen Mle$ acu txeddmem.'),
(3349, 29, 9, 'Wid iumnen, ixedmen ayen ilhan, war ccekk, a ten Nessekcem ar iâaôviyen.'),
(3350, 29, 10, 'Ger imdanen, wid iqqaôen: "numen s Öebbi". Ma meênen, deg ubrid n Öebbi, ad êesben ahewwel n medden, d aâaqeb n Öebbi. Mi d iusa l$elb, s$uô Mass ik, ar ad inin: "ih, nella yidwen". Day ur Iéôa ara Öebbi, i illan deg idmaren imavalen?'),
(3351, 29, 11, 'War ccekk, Öebbi Issen wid iumnen, Issen ixabiten.'),
(3352, 29, 12, 'Nnan wid ijehlen, i wid iumnen: "ddut d ubrid nne$, a nbibb tuccva nnwen". Nitni ur pbibbin acemma, si tuccva nnsen. S tidep, nitni d ikeddaben.'),
(3353, 29, 13, 'War ccekk, ad bibben tiâekkwmin nnsen, akked tiâekkwmin nniven. Ih, ad ppusteqsin, ass n tnekra, af wayen id snulfuyen.'),
(3354, 29, 14, 'Ni$ Nuzen ed Nuê, i ugdud is. Izde$ yides, agim kkes ed smuset iseggwasen. Ibbwi ten uêemmal, nitni d imednas.'),
(3355, 29, 15, 'Nsellek it, neppa akked wid iddan di lbabuô. Nerra t d assekni i imavalen.'),
(3356, 29, 16, 'Ibôahim, mi inna i ugdud is: "âabdet Öebbi, êezzbet aS. Yif it wakka, i kunwi, lemmer teéôim.'),
(3357, 29, 17, 'Tâabdem kan tiâancuôin, war Öebbi. Tesnulfam d tikerkas. Ih, wid tâabdem, war Öebbi, ur zmiren a kwen $iten. Ssutret l$it i Öebbi, âabdet eP, snemmret aS. £uôeS ara tu$alem.'),
(3358, 29, 18, 'Ma tnekôem, ihi, uqbel nnwen, nekôen leoyus". I iwatan, i umazan, siwa assiwev ubeggen.'),
(3359, 29, 19, 'Day ur walan ara, amek id Inezzu Öebbi lxelq, sinna, Ippales as. Ih, ayagi, i Öebbi, d ushil.'),
(3360, 29, 20, 'Ini: "iniget di tmurt, walit amek id Inza lxelq. Sinna, Öebbi a d Iawi lxelq aneggaru. Ih, Öebbi Izmer i yal cci".'),
(3361, 29, 21, 'Ikkat win i S ihwan; Ipêunu $ef win i S ihwan. £ureS jebbu nnwen.'),
(3362, 29, 22, 'Ur tesfunnugem, kunwi, di tmurt, ne$ deg igenni. Ur tesâim, war Öebbi, bab ne$ asettaô.'),
(3363, 29, 23, 'Wid iugin issekniyen n Öebbi, akked temlilit yideS, widak ad aysen aêunu W. I widak, aâaqeb aqeôêan.'),
(3364, 29, 24, 'Tiririt n ugdud is, siwa mi d nnan: "en$et ep, ne$ sseô$et ep". Isellek it Öebbi, si tmes. Deg waya, s tidep, d assekni i ugdud iumnen.'),
(3365, 29, 25, 'Inna: "teddmem kan tiâancuôin, war Öebbi. Temêemmalem di tmeddurt n ddunit, sinna, ass n tnekra, kra degwen ad nekôen wiyav, kra ad xzun wiyav. Axxam nnwen d times, ur awen illi usellak".'),
(3366, 29, 26, 'Iumen it Luî. Inna: "nek, d iminig ar Mass iw. Ih, Neppa, d Uzmir, d Bab n ûûwab".'),
(3367, 29, 27, 'N$at it s Isêaq akked Yaâqub. I tarwas, Nefka lambiyya, Tazmamt. Nefka yas taqviât is, di ddunit; u neppa, di laxeôt, war ccekk, seg iâaôviyen.'),
(3368, 29, 28, 'Luî, mi inna i ugdud is: "ih, aql akwen la txedmem lâaô, ur ixdim yiwen, zik, deg imavalen.'),
(3369, 29, 29, 'La teppeddum, ih, ar irgazen, tgezzmem abrid, txeddmem ayen icemten, deg igrawen nnwen". Tiririt n ugdud is, siwa mi nnan: "awi a$ d aâaqeb n Öebbi, ma telliv seg wid issawalen tidep".'),
(3370, 29, 30, 'Inna: "a Mass iw! Efk iyi afus, mgal agdud ifessaden".'),
(3371, 29, 31, 'Mi d usan imceggâen nne£, ar Ibôahim, s ubecceô, nnan as: "ih, a Nesqucc imezda$ n temdint agi. Imezda$ is, s tidep, d imednas".'),
(3372, 29, 32, 'Inna d: "ni$ degs Luî". Nnan as: "Nekwni, Neéôa sennig akw, i illan degs. A t Naâteq, neppa akked twacult is, siwa tameîîut is, ara yilin seg wid igwran".'),
(3373, 29, 33, 'Mi usan imceggâen nne£, ar Luî, i$wbel ilmend nnsen, ur izmir a ten ifukk. Nnan as: "ur ppagwad, ur $webbel. Nekwni a k Naâteq, keçç d twacult ik, siwa tameîîut ik, ara yilin seg wid igwran.'),
(3374, 29, 34, 'Ih, nekwni a d Nesse$li ssxev seg igenni, $ef imezda$ n temdint agi, ilmend n lâaô nnsen".'),
(3375, 29, 35, 'Ni$ Neooa d segs, assekni iberrzen, i ugdud ipmeyyizen.'),
(3376, 29, 36, 'Ar Madian, gmat sen Cuâayeb. Inna: "a yagdud iw! Âabdet Öebbi, gganit ass aneggaru, ur oouôut di tmurt d ifessaden!".'),
(3377, 29, 37, 'Nekôen t. Tewwet iten zzenzla. Gwran d, d loeppat, deg ixxamen nnsen.'),
(3378, 29, 38, 'Âad akked Tamud - ni$ iban awen d seg ixxamen nnsen -, icebbeê asen Cciîan igiten nnsen. Issuffe$ iten seg ubrid, nitni pfeôôioen.'),
(3379, 29, 39, 'Qaôun, Ferâun, Haman, ni$ iusa ten id Musa, s ubeggen. Sme$wôen iman nnsen, di tmurt, ur rbiêen.'),
(3380, 29, 40, 'Yal wa, Newwet it $ef ubekkav is. Llan wid iwumi Nuzen tabucivant. Llan wid i iwwet usu$u. Llan wid i Nger seddaw wakal. Llan wid i Ne$meq. Maççi d Öebbi iten idensen, d nitni i idensen iman nnsen.'),
(3381, 29, 41, 'Wid iteddun d imawlan, war Öebbi, cban rtila. Tebna tissist. Ihi, axxam ahcican mavi, d tissist n rtila, lemmer ssinen.'),
(3382, 29, 42, 'Ih, Öebbi Iéôa akw ayen u$uô naâôen, war Neppa. Neppa, d Uzmir, d Bab n ûûwab.'),
(3383, 29, 43, 'Imedyaten agi, Neppawi ten id, i l$aci. Siwa imusnawen ara ten ifehmen.'),
(3384, 29, 44, 'Ixleq Öebbi tamurt akked igenwan, s tidep. Ih, deg waya, assekni i lmumnin.'),
(3385, 29, 45, 'Mel ayen i k id ippuweêêan si Tezmamt. Bedd i téallit. Ih, taéallit teppekkes lâaô, tuccva. War ccek, iugar ip usmekti n Öebbi. Öebbi Iéôa acu tûenâam.'),
(3386, 29, 46, 'Ur pnamaret At Tezmamt, siwa s wawal aéidan, siwa wid degsen idensen. Init: "numen s wayen id irsen $uône$, id irsen $uôwen. Öebbi nne$, akked Öebbi nnwen, Yiwen. Nekwni $uôeS d imvuâen".'),
(3387, 29, 47, 'Akka ay ed Nessers, $uôek, Tazmamt. Wid iwumi Nefka Tazmamt, umnen yis. Ger wigi, kra umnen yis. I inekôen issekniyen nne£, siwa ijehliyen.'),
(3388, 29, 48, 'Ur telliv temmalev kra n Tezmamt, uqbel tagi; ur p tepparuv, s uyeffus ik. Yili ad cukken inekkaôen.'),
(3389, 29, 49, 'Xaîi, neppa d issekniyen iberrzen, deg idmaren n wid iwumi teppunefk tmusni. Siwa imednas, i inekôen issekniyen nne£.'),
(3390, 29, 50, 'Nnan: "a lemmer id rsen fellas, issekniyen s$uô Mass is"! Ini: "issekniyen ar Öebbi kan. Nek, d aneddaô kan, ipbegginen".'),
(3391, 29, 51, 'Ne$, ur steqnaâen ara s trusi $uôek, s$uône£, n Tezmamt, malen asen p. Deg waya, s tidep, aêunu, akked usmekti i ugdud iumnen.'),
(3392, 29, 52, 'Ini: "Iqadd Öebbi, d anagi gari yidwen. Issen i illan di tmurt akked igenwan. Wid iumnen di tkerkas, u ugin Öebbi, widak d imexsuôen".'),
(3393, 29, 53, 'Sêirin k $ef uâaqeb. Lemmer maççi d lajel ipwassnen, a ten id ias uâaqeb. Ih, a ten id ias, deqzalla, ur bnin.'),
(3394, 29, 54, 'Sêirin k $ef uâaqeb. Ih, Loahennama a ppezzi i ijehliyen'),
(3395, 29, 55, 'Ass ideg ar asen isbur uâaqeb, sennig sen, akw seddaw ivaôen nnsen, ad Yini: "jeôôbet ayen txeddmem".'),
(3396, 29, 56, 'A yimdanen iW iumnen, ni$ tamurt iW tewsaâ. Ihi, âabdet iyI, Nek.'),
(3397, 29, 57, 'Yal iman, ad ijeôôeb tameppant; sinna, $uône£ a d tu$alem.'),
(3398, 29, 58, 'Wid iumnen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan, ad asen Nerr tanezdu$t di Loennet m t$uôfatin, ddaw as isaffen ppazzalen, degs ad wekkôen. D asaâdi warraz n wid ixedmen lxiô,'),
(3399, 29, 59, 'wid iûebôen, ippeklen $ef Mass nnsen.'),
(3400, 29, 60, 'Acêal n lewêuc, ur d neppawi ôôeéq nnsen. Öebbi Iôeéq iten, u Iôeéq ikwen. Neppa, Issel, d Amusnaw.'),
(3401, 29, 61, 'Ma testeqûav ten: "anwa i Ixelqen tamurt akked igenwan, i Inuben s yiîij akked waggur"? A d inin, war ccekk: "d Öebbi". Ihi, acimi wexxôen?'),
(3402, 29, 62, 'Öebbi Issugut l$it i win i S ihwan, deg imdanen iS, u Iwezzen as. Ih, Öebbi Issen yal cci.'),
(3403, 29, 63, 'Ma testeqûav ten: "anwa id Isse$layen aman seg igenni, Issidir yissen akal, deffir tmeppant is"? A d inin, war ccekk, "d Öebbi". Ini: "ccekôan i Öebbi". Maca, tegwti degsen, ur fhimen.'),
(3404, 29, 64, 'Tameddurt agi, di ddunit, siwa lhawiyya, d wurar. D axxam aneggaru, war ccekk, ay d amuddir, lemmer éôin.'),
(3405, 29, 65, 'Mara rekben di lbabuô, ad naâôen Öebbi, d idiniyen zeddigen $uôeS. Mi ten Isellek ar lberr, atnan la pcaraken.'),
(3406, 29, 66, 'Ad nekôen ayen i sen Nefka, ad zhun, deqqal ad éôen.'),
(3407, 29, 67, 'Day ur walan ara, Nerra loamaâ n laman, wanag la pwaxvafen imdanen i sen d izzin? Day ad amnen di tkerkas, u ad nekôen l$it n Öebbi?'),
(3408, 29, 68, 'Anwa i idensen kteô: win id isnulfan tikerkas af Öebbi, ne$ win irran tidep d tikerkas, mi t id tusa? Day maççi d Loahennama ay d tanezdu$t i ijehliyen?'),
(3409, 29, 69, 'Wid ijuhden ar loiha nne£, a ten Nenhu, war ccekk, s iberdan nne£. Ih, Öebbi Ippili ar lâuûam.');
INSERT INTO `ber_mensur` (`index`, `sura`, `aya`, `text`) VALUES
(3410, 30, 1, 'Alm.'),
(3411, 30, 2, 'IôÔöumiyen rnan ten,'),
(3412, 30, 3, 'deg wakal aqôib mavi. Deffir lexsaôa nnsen, ad rnun,'),
(3413, 30, 4, 'di kra iseggwasen. Lameô ar Öebbi, uqbel aya, u ssyen $eô da. Assen, ad feôêen lmumnin'),
(3414, 30, 5, 's rrbeê n Öebbi. Isserbaê win i S ihwan. Neppa, d Uzmir, Ipêunu.'),
(3415, 30, 6, 'D lemâahda n Öebbi. Öebbi ur Ipxallaf ara lemâahda S, maca, tegwti n medden ur ssinen.'),
(3416, 30, 7, 'Ssnen ayen id innunnten, di tmeddurt n ddunit. £ef laxeôt nitni stehzan.'),
(3417, 30, 8, 'Day ur meyyzen ara deg iman nnsen? Ur Ixliq Öebbi tamurt, igenwan, akked wayen illan garasen, siwa s tidep, akked lajel ipwassnen. Ih, aîas n medden i inekôen timlilit d Mass nnsen.'),
(3418, 30, 9, 'Day ur unagen ara di tmurt, ad walin amek tevôa d wid i ten id izwaren? Llan ifen ten tazmert, $zan tamurt, $elben ten akken i p âamôen. Usan ten id imazanen nnsen, s ubeggen. Ur ten Idnis Öebbi. Maca d nitni i idensen iman nnsen.'),
(3419, 30, 10, 'D$a teqseê taggara n laâôuô. Skaddben issekniyen n Öebbi. Pmmaâliken fellasen.'),
(3420, 30, 11, 'Öebbi Inezzu lxelq; sinna, Ippales it id. Sinna, $uôeS ara tu$alem.'),
(3421, 30, 12, 'Ass ideg ara d ijbu yimir, ad feqâen ibe$wviyen.'),
(3422, 30, 13, 'Ur ten pselliken wid pcaraken. Ad nekôen wid pcaraken.'),
(3423, 30, 14, 'Ass ideg ara d ijbu yimir, assen ad mfaôaqen.'),
(3424, 30, 15, 'Wanag wid iumnen u xeddmen ayen ilhan, ad zhun di tebêirt.'),
(3425, 30, 16, 'Ma d wid ijehlen, inekôen issekniyen nne£, akked temlilit n laxeôt, widak ar uâaqeb ara rsen.'),
(3426, 30, 17, 'Gedha s Öebbi, tameddit nnwen, taûebêit nnwen!'),
(3427, 30, 18, 'I Neppa ccekôan, di tmurt akked igenwan, tameddit u di pnaûfa n wass.'),
(3428, 30, 19, 'Issuffu$ ed amuddir si lmegget. Issuffu$ ed lmegget seg umuddir. Issidir akal, deffir tmeppant is. Akka ara d teff$em.'),
(3429, 30, 20, 'Seg issekniyen iS: Ixelq ikwen seg wakal. Aql akwen d imdanen tembwezzâam.'),
(3430, 30, 21, 'Seg issekniyen iS: Ixelq awen, segwen, tiâggaltin nnwen, a pzed$em yidsent. Irra garawen tayri, lmaênana. Deg waya, s tidep, issekniyen i ugdud ipmeyyizen.'),
(3431, 30, 22, 'Seg issekniyen iS: lxelq n tmurt akked igenwan, amgirred ger tutlayin nnwen, akked initen nnwen. Deg waya, s tidep, issekniyen i imusnawen.'),
(3432, 30, 23, 'Seg issekniyen iS: ives nnwen deg iv, deg wass, anadi nnwen n lfevl iS. Deg waya, s tidep, issekniyen i ugdud isellen.'),
(3433, 30, 24, 'Seg issekniyen iS: Issenâat awen lebôaq, degs tugdi, asirem. Issadar ed aman seg igenni, Issidir yissen akal, deffir tmeppant is. Deg waya, s tidep, issekniyen i ugdud ifehmen.'),
(3434, 30, 25, 'Seg issekniyen iS: s lameô iS, igenni akked tmurt bedden. Sinna, ma Isawel awen d, yiwen usiwel, seg wakal kunwi a d teff$em.'),
(3435, 30, 26, 'IneS i illan di tmurt akked igenwan. Akken ma llan, unzen aS.'),
(3436, 30, 27, 'D Neppa i Inezzun lxelq, sinna Ippales it id. D ayen i S isehlen mavi. IneS umedya aâlayan, di tmurt akked igenwan. Neppa d Uzmir, d Bab n ûûwab.'),
(3437, 30, 28, 'Ibbwi yawen d amedya, seg iman nnwen: day tcerkem d waklan nnwen, ayen i s ikwen N$at, d$a tâadlem yidsen? Day ten teppagwadem, akken teppemyagwadem garawen? Akka ay Nepfeûûil issekniyen i ugdud ipxemmimen.'),
(3438, 30, 29, 'Xaîi! Wid idensen teddun d lhawiyyat nnsen, ur ssinen. Anwa ara inhun wid Itlef Öebbi? Ur sâin imâiwnen.'),
(3439, 30, 30, 'Smil udem ik adini ar tidep, d lxelq n Öebbi akken id Ixleq imdanen. Ur illi ubeddel, di lxelq n Öebbi. Wagi d ddin amxallef, maca, tegwti n medden ur ssinen.'),
(3440, 30, 31, 'D imvuâen iS, êezzbet aS, beddet i téallit, ur ppilit seg wid ipcaraken,'),
(3441, 30, 32, 'seg wid ifeôqen ddin nnsen. U$alen d îayfat, yal akabar icôeê s wayen isâa.'),
(3442, 30, 33, 'Imdanen, ma iwwet iten wugur, ad naâôen Mass nnsen, d imvuâen iS. Sinna, ma Isêess asen aêunu, s$uôeS, a pwaliv arbaâ degsen pcaraken i Mass nnsen,'),
(3443, 30, 34, 'iwakken ad nekôen i sen Nefka. Zhut! Deqqal a ppeéôem.'),
(3444, 30, 35, 'Ne$ Nessader asen ed amvebbeô, i ipmeslayen $ef wayen i S pcaraken.'),
(3445, 30, 36, 'Mi Nesêess aêunu i imdanen, ad ceôêen yis. Ma têuza ten tucmip, seg wayen id urwen ifassen nnsen, ad aysen.'),
(3446, 30, 37, 'Day ur walan ara ar Öebbi Issugut ôôeéq i win i S ihwan, u Iwezzen. Deg waya, s tidep, issekniyen i ugdud iumnen.'),
(3447, 30, 38, 'Efk as leêqq is i llezm ik, i ume$bun, i win id ibbwi ubrid. Ppif akka i wid ib$an udem n Öebbi. D widak ay d imerbaê.'),
(3448, 30, 39, 'Ayen teppakem n rrba, iwakken ad issem$weô ayla n medden, ar Öebbi ur issim$uô ara. Ayen tepzekkim $ef udem n Öebbi, d ayen ara ibuôekten.'),
(3449, 30, 40, 'Öebbi, ikwen id Ixelqen, sinna, ikwen I$aten, sinna, ara kwen In$en, sinna, ara kwen id Issidren. Day ara ixdem kra, seg waya, yiwen seg wid tepcarakem? Gedha s yiS, Aâlayan sennig wid pcaraken!'),
(3450, 30, 41, 'Ivehô ed lefsad di lberr u di yill seg wayen id urwen ifassen n medden, iwakken ad Isukk fellasen kra seg wayen xedmen, amar a d u$alen s abrid.'),
(3451, 30, 42, 'Ini: "iniget di tmurt, muqlet amek tevôa d imezwura. Tegwti, segsen, pcaraken".'),
(3452, 30, 43, 'Err udem ik ar ddin amxallef, uqbel a d ias s$uô Öebbi, ass ur nepwexxiô. Assen, ad pwaferzen.'),
(3453, 30, 44, 'Win ijehlen, tijehli s mgal is; wid ixeddmen ayen ilhan, gemren i iman nnsen.'),
(3454, 30, 45, 'Iwakken ad Ikafi, s lfevl iS, wid iumnen u xeddmen ayen ilhan. Neppa, s tidep, ur Iêemmel ara ijehliyen.'),
(3455, 30, 46, 'Seg issekniyen iS: Ippazen ed avu abcir, ad awen Isêess, cwiî, seg uêunu S; ad iaâjel lbabuô, s lameô iS. A pnadim lfevl iS, amar a ppesnemmrem.'),
(3456, 30, 47, 'Ni$ Nuzen ed, uqbel ik, imazanen i igduden nnsen. Usan ten id, s ubeggen. Nerra d ppaô seg wid ibe$wven. Aslak n lmumnin d lwaoeb nne£.'),
(3457, 30, 48, 'Öebbi, id Ippaznen avu isselêayen asigna, a t ifser, deg igenni, akken i S ihwa, a t Issemfaôeq, a pwaliv ageffur a d iteffe$ segs. Mi t Issawev ar wid i S ihwan, deg imdanen iS, a ten tafev ceôêen.'),
(3458, 30, 49, 'Wanag, iu$ lêal, llan uysen, uqbel ad asen d i$li.'),
(3459, 30, 50, 'Wali lateô uêunu n Öebbi: amek id Issidir akal, deffir tmeppant is. Ih, d Win, s tidep, i Issidiren lmeggtin. Neppa Izmer i yal cci.'),
(3460, 30, 51, 'Mara Nazen avu, ara walin ippiwôi$, a pdum, deffir es, tjehli nnsen.'),
(3461, 30, 52, 'Ma d keçç, s tidep, ur tezmirev a pperrev lmeggtin ad slen, ne$ iâeééugen ad slen i tnaâôit, ma u$alen $er deffir.'),
(3462, 30, 53, 'Ur tezmirev a penhuv ider$alen, mgal ttelfan nnsen. Ara terrev ad ak slen, siwa wid iumnen s issekniyen nne£. Nitni d imvuâen.'),
(3463, 30, 54, 'Öebbi, ikwen Ixelqen si ôehfan; sinna, deffir ôehfan, Irra tazmert; sinna, deffir tezmert, Irra ôehfan, akked ccib. Ixelleq ayen i S ihwan. Neppa d Amusnaw, d Aêernuk.'),
(3464, 30, 55, 'Ass ideg ara d ijbu yimir, ad gallen ibe$wviyen, ar siwa saâa segmi mmuten. Akka ay skiddiben.'),
(3465, 30, 56, 'Ad inin wid iwumi teppunefk tussna, akked liman: "ni$ teqqimem di Tezmamt n Öebbi, ar ass n tnekra. Wagi d ass n tnekra, maca tellam ur tessinem".'),
(3466, 30, 57, 'Assen, wid idensen, ur ten tepsellik nndama ne$ asuter n ssmaê.'),
(3467, 30, 58, 'Ni$ Nefka, i medden, yal amedya di Leqwôan agi. Maca, mi sen d tebbwiv assekni, ad ak inin, war ccekk, wid ijehlen: "kunwi d wid ireoonen".'),
(3468, 30, 59, 'Akka i Iselle$ Öebbi ulawen n wid ur nessin.'),
(3469, 30, 60, 'Eûbeô, ih, lemâahda n Öebbi d tidep. Ur k sêirin, wid ur nepputebbet!');
INSERT INTO `ber_mensur` (`index`, `sura`, `aya`, `text`) VALUES
(3470, 31, 1, 'Alm.'),
(3471, 31, 2, 'Wigi d issekniyen n Tezmamt tuûwibt;'),
(3472, 31, 3, 'd nnhaya u d aêunu i iâaôviyen,'),
(3473, 31, 4, 'wid ibedden i téallit, ipzekkin, ipputebbten af laxeôt.'),
(3474, 31, 5, 'Wigi, di nnhaya s$uô Mass nnsen. Wigi, d isaâdiyen.'),
(3475, 31, 6, 'Ger yimdanen, wid ippa$en awal n zzhu, iwakken ad nnetlafen seg ubrid n Öebbi, war tamusni. U fellas ttihin. I wigi, aâaqeb isdullun.'),
(3476, 31, 7, 'Ma mlan as issekniyen nne£, ad ibren s tem$weô, amzun ur asen isli, amzun âaégen as imeééu$en. Xebbeô it s uâaqeb aqeôêan.'),
(3477, 31, 8, 'Ih, i wid iumnen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan, leonanat isaâdiyen.'),
(3478, 31, 9, 'Degsen ad wekkôen. Lemâahda n Öebbi d tidep. Neppa d Uzmir, d Bab n ûûwab.'),
(3479, 31, 10, 'Ixleq igenwan, war tigejda ara twalim. Irra di tmurt idurar, iwakken ur tepzenzil ara yiswen. Iwezzaâ, degs, yal lxelq. Nessader ed aman seg igenni. Nessem$i d degs, yal tayuga tukyist.'),
(3480, 31, 11, 'Wagi d lxelq n Öebbi. Sseknet iyi d, acu d xelqen wid ur nelli d Neppa. Xaîi, imednas atnan di ttelfan n ûûeê.'),
(3481, 31, 12, 'Ni$ Nefka i Luqman ûûwab: "snemmer Öebbi. Win isnemmiren, isnemmir kan i iman is. Ma d wid ijehlen, ihi, Öebbi d Asâay, d Amaâzuz".'),
(3482, 31, 13, 'Mi inna Luqman i mmi s, la t isselmad: "a mmi! Ur pcarak i Öebbi. Ccerk, s tidep, d ddens abarar".'),
(3483, 31, 14, 'Nweûûa amdan $ef imawlan is. Imma s temêen s tadist is. Tuîva s, sin iseggwasen. Snemmer iyI, u i imawlan ik. Tu$alin $uôI.'),
(3484, 31, 15, 'Ma êeppmen fellak, ad iyI tcarkev ayen ur tessinev, ur asen teddu di leb$i. Illi yidsen d uwqim di ddunit. Ddu d ubrid n wid isteôoâen $uôI. Sinna, tu$alin nnwen $uôI, ad awen Mle$ ayen txeddmem.'),
(3485, 31, 16, '"Ih, a mmi, xas am taéeyt uâaqqa ucceryad, ara yilin di teéôut, ne$ deg igenwan, ne$ di tmurt, a p id Iawi Öebbi. Ih, Öebbi d Laîif, Iéôa.'),
(3486, 31, 17, 'A mmi, bedd i téallit, ameô lewqama, îîixxeô i wayen n dir, eûbeô i wayen ara k id iasen! Aya, s tidep, seg uâzzem i lumuô.'),
(3487, 31, 18, 'Ur sxunzuô ar medden, ur teddu di tmurt s îî$aya! Öebbi, s tidep, ur Iêemmel yal imnefxi, amzuxi.'),
(3488, 31, 19, 'Iôqiq di tikli k, ssers ûûut ik! Ni$ ûûut ucmit mavi, d win n ye$yal".'),
(3489, 31, 20, 'Day ur twalam ara, Inub Öebbi fellawen s wayen akw illan deg igenwan, akked wayen illan di tmurt? Isserwa yawen l$it iS, uvhiô, uffir. U llan l$aci i ipnamaren $ef Öebbi, war tamusni, ne$ nnhaya, ne$ Tazmamt timnewweôt.'),
(3490, 31, 21, 'Ma nnan asen: "ddut akked wayen id Issader Öebbi", a d inin: "xaîi, a neddu akked wayen id nufa ar imezwura nne$". I ma Cciîan atan la ten inecced ar uâaqeb n tmes?'),
(3491, 31, 22, 'Win ifkan i Öebbi udem amvuâ, u neppa d aâeôvi, iîîef deg ufus iûeêêan mavi. Ar Öebbi, tu$alin n lumuô.'),
(3492, 31, 23, 'Win ijehlen, ur k t$webben tjehli s! £uône£, tu$alin nnsen; ad asen Nini acu xedmen. Öebbi, s tidep, Iéôa i illan deg idmaren.'),
(3493, 31, 24, 'A ten Neoo ad zhun cwiî, sinna, a Nêeppem fellasen aâaqeb iwaâôen.'),
(3494, 31, 25, 'Ma testeqûav ten: "anwa i Ixelqen tamurt akked igenwan"? A d inin, war ccekk: "d Öebbi". Ini: "ccekôan i Öebbi". Maca, tegwti degsen, ur ssinen.'),
(3495, 31, 26, 'I Öebbi i illan akw di tmurt akked igenwan. Ih, Öebbi d Asâay, d Amaâzuz.'),
(3496, 31, 27, 'Xas lukan ttjuô akw n ddunit d leqlamat, u yill, ernu yas ûa ilellen nniven, d lmidad nnsen, ur pqamen awalen n Öebbi. Ih, Öebbi d Uzmir, d Bab n ûûwab.'),
(3497, 31, 28, 'Lxelq nnwen, tanekra nnwen, amzun d yiman yiwen kan. Ih, Öebbi Issel, Ipwali.'),
(3498, 31, 29, 'Day ur twalav ara, Öebbi Issekcam iv deg wass, Issekcam ass deg yiv. Iêeppem i yiîij akked waggur ad lêun, ar lajel ipwassnen. Ih, Öebbi Iéôa ayen txeddmem.'),
(3499, 31, 30, 'Akka, acku Öebbi d Tidep. Ayen u$uô naâôen, war Neppa, d tikerkas. Öebbi, d Aâlayan, d Ameqwôan.'),
(3500, 31, 31, 'Day ur twalav ara ssfina, teppazal di yill s lqwedôa n Öebbi, iwakken ad awen d Issenâat seg issekniyen iS. Ih, deg wayagi, issekniyen i yal aûebôi isnemmiren.'),
(3501, 31, 32, 'Ma tesbur asen lmuja, am tillas, ad nujen ar Öebbi, $uôeS s ddin azedgan. Mi ten Isellek ar lberr, kra, degsen, îîfen deg wawal nnsen. I inekôen issekniyen nne£, siwa yal axeddaâ ajehli.'),
(3502, 31, 33, 'A yimdanen! Ëezzbet i Mass nnwen. Agwadet ass ideg ababat ur d ilehhu d mmi s, u mmi s ur d ilehhu d baba s, s wacemma. Ih, lemâahda n Öebbi, d tidep. Ur kwen tep$uôôu tmeddurt n ddunit. Ur kwen issefôa$ im$weôôi, $ef Öebbi.'),
(3503, 31, 34, 'Öebbi, s tidep, $uôeS tamusni n yimir. Issadar ed ageffur. Iéôa i illan di tâabbuvin. Ur iéôi yiwen acu ara ikseb azekka; ur iéôi yiwen anwa akal ideg ara immet. Öebbi, s tidep, Iéôa, d Amusnaw.');
INSERT INTO `ber_mensur` (`index`, `sura`, `aya`, `text`) VALUES
(3504, 32, 1, 'Alm.'),
(3505, 32, 2, 'Tarusi n Tezmamt, ur illi degs ccekk, s$uô Mass imavalen.'),
(3506, 32, 3, 'Ne$ a d inin: "isnulfa p id". Xaîi, neppat, d tidep s$uô Mass ik, iwakken a pnedôev agdud u$uô ur d iusi ara uneddaô, uqbel ik, amar ad pwanhun.'),
(3507, 32, 4, 'Öebbi i Ixelqen tamurt, igenwan, akked wayen illan garasen, di sdis wussan; sinna, Iâannec $ef usgeld. Ur tesâim, war Neppa, bab, ne$ amcafaâ. Day ula d tesmektayem ara?'),
(3508, 32, 5, 'A d Iseyyi lameô seg igenni ar tmurt; sinna, ad iu$al $uôeS deg ibwass, lmudda s: agim iseggwasen, s leêsab nnwen.'),
(3509, 32, 6, 'Akka, Umusnaw n wayen iffren, u n wayen ur neffir, Uzmir Ipêunun.'),
(3510, 32, 7, 'I Iûûegmen akw ayen Ixleq. Inza d lxelq n umdan, si talaxt.'),
(3511, 32, 8, 'Sinna, Issuffe$ ed tarwa s si l$ella, degs cwiî n waman.'),
(3512, 32, 9, 'Sinna, Imesl it, Iûûuv degs, si ôôuê iS. Irra yawen timesliwt, iéôi, ul. Drus ay tesnemmirem.'),
(3513, 32, 10, 'Nnan: "ma nweddeô di tmurt, day a d nepwaxleq tikelt nniven"? Xaîi, nekôen timlilit akked Mass nnsen.'),
(3514, 32, 11, 'Ini: "ad iddem ôôuê nnwen, lmelk n tmeppant i ippukelfen fellawen. Sinna, ar Mass nnwen a ppu$alem".'),
(3515, 32, 12, 'Lemmer a pwaliv ibe$wviyen, ad brun i iqweôôa nnsen, zdat Mass nnsen: "a Mass nne$! Nwala, nesla; Err ane$ a nexdem ayen ilhan. S tidep, numen".'),
(3516, 32, 13, 'Lemmer i £ ihwi, yili Nefka, i yal ôôuê, nnhaya s. Maca, ad ivôu wayen Nni$: "war ccekk, ad Acaôe$ Loahennama s leonun akked yimdanen, mejmulen".'),
(3517, 32, 14, 'Ihi, jeôôbet imi teppum a d temlilem d wass nnwen agi! Nekwni, ih, Neppu kwen. Jeôôbet aâaqeb, n lebda, ilmend n wayen txeddmem.'),
(3518, 32, 15, 'I iumnen kan, s issekniyen nne£, d wid, mara ten id mmektin, ara weddin ad knun, ara isbucuâen Mass nnsen s ccekôan, nitni ur pzuxxun.'),
(3519, 32, 16, 'Ppensaren d ibeôdiyen nnsen, seg imîeôêen, pnujun $eô Mass nnsen, s tugwdi d usirem. Seg wayen iten N$at, pseddiqen.'),
(3520, 32, 17, 'Ur iéôi yiwen acu i sen Ffre$ n lfeôê. D arraz n wayen llan xeddmen.'),
(3521, 32, 18, 'Win illan d lmumen, day am win illan d amed$ul? Ur aâdilen.'),
(3522, 32, 19, 'Ihi, i wid iumnen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan, leonanat imôaêbiyen, ara zed$en, ilmend n wayen xeddmeùn.'),
(3523, 32, 20, 'Wanag wid ide$wlen, di tmes ara zed$en. Yal tikelt ideg ara b$un a d ff$en segs, a ten rren $uôes, ad asen inin: "jeôôbet aâaqeb n tmes i tnekkôem".'),
(3524, 32, 21, 'Ih, a Nessukk fellasen aâaqeb aqôib mavi, war aâaqeb abarar. Ahat a d u$alen s abrid.'),
(3525, 32, 22, 'Anwa i idensen sennig n win iwumi d dekôen issekniyen n Mass is, iu$al iwexxeô asen? Ih, a d Nerr ppaô seg ibe$wviyen.'),
(3526, 32, 23, 'Ni$ Nefka yas Tazmamt i Musa. Ur ppili di ccekk af temlilit yideS! Nerra p d nnhaya i At Isôail.'),
(3527, 32, 24, 'Nesbedd, segsen, iselmaden; nnehun s lameô nne£, mi ûebôen, u llan pputebbten $ef issekniyen nne£.'),
(3528, 32, 25, 'Ih, Mass ik, Neppa, ad Iêudd garasen, ass n tnekra, $ef wayen i$ef mgarraden.'),
(3529, 32, 26, 'Day ur ten inha ara wayen Nesqucc isuta, uqbel nnsen? La leêêun $ef tnezdu$in nnsen. Deg waya, s tidep, issekniyen. Day ur sellen ara?'),
(3530, 32, 27, 'Day ur zôin ara Neppawi aman s akal aquôan; Nessuffu$ ed, yissen, iâaqqayen; teppen, segsen, nitni akked lmal nnsen. Day ur pwalin ara?'),
(3531, 32, 28, 'Qqaôen: "melmi l$elb agi, ma tessawalem tidep"?'),
(3532, 32, 29, 'Ini: "ass n l$elb, liman n wid ijehlen, ur ten infaâ; ur pganin".'),
(3533, 32, 30, 'Ihi, wexxeô asen, ggani. Nitni, s tidep, la pganin.');
INSERT INTO `ber_mensur` (`index`, `sura`, `aya`, `text`) VALUES
(3534, 33, 1, 'A Nnbi! Ëezzeb i Öebbi, ur ppa$ awal i ijehliyen akked ixabiten. Öebbi, s tidep, Izga d Amusnaw, d Bab n ûûwab.'),
(3535, 33, 2, 'Ddu akked wayen i k d Ippuweêêan, s$uô Mass ik. Ih, Öebbi Ippuxebbeô $ef wayen txedmem.'),
(3536, 33, 3, 'Ppkel $ef Öebbi. Iqadd Öebbi d Awkil.'),
(3537, 33, 4, 'Ur Irra ara Öebbi sin wulawen di tfekka n urgaz. Ur Irra ara tilawin nnwen, i tmetlem ar iârar n tyimmatin nnwen, d tiyimmatin nnwen. Ur irra ara wid id tessekrem, d tarwa nnwen. Ayagi, d awal nnwen, seg imawen nnwen. Öebbi Issawal tidep. Neppa Ippawi d ubrid.'),
(3538, 33, 5, 'Ssiwlet asen am ibabaten nnsen; akka i iwqem ar Öebbi. Ma ur tessinen ara anwi ay d ibabaten nnsen, atmaten nnwen di ddin, d iqôiben nnwen. Ur illi u$ilif $ef wayen teffalîam degs, siwa ayen âammden wulawen nnwen. Öebbi Izga Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu.'),
(3539, 33, 6, 'Nnbi iqôeb ar lmumnin, sennig iman nnsen. Tilawin is, d tiyimmatin nnsen. Wid ippemyilin, mqaôaben di Tezmamt n Öebbi, sennig lmumnin akked iminigen. Siwa ma tgam tajmilt i imeddukwal nnwen. Ayagi iura di Tezmamt.'),
(3540, 33, 7, 'Mi Neîîef si lambiyya lmitaq nnsen, u si keçç, si Nuê, Ibôahim, Musa, u si Âisa, mmi s n Meryem, Neîîef segsen lmitaq lfayeq,'),
(3541, 33, 8, 'iwakken ad Iêtec imawlan n tidep, af tidep nnsen. Ihegga d, i ijehliyen, aâaqeb aqeôêan.'),
(3542, 33, 9, 'A wid iumnen! Mmektit ed l$it ikwen I$at Öebbi. Mi d usan $uôwen iâsekôiwen, Nuzen asen d avu, akked iâsekôiwen ur twalam. Öebbi Izga Ipwali ayen txeddmem.'),
(3543, 33, 10, 'Mi wen d kkan sennig wen, seddawat wen, mi zzint wallen, ulawen bbwven s ijuxax, tepmeyyizem yal ameyyez $ef Öebbi.'),
(3544, 33, 11, 'Dinna, ppwajeôôben lmumnin, enhezzen s leqseê.'),
(3545, 33, 12, 'Mi d nnan ixabiten, akked imehzulen n wul: "ay $ d Iwaââed Öebbi, akked Umazan iS, siwa a$uôôu".'),
(3546, 33, 13, 'Mi d inna urbaâ segsen: "a yAt Yatrib, ur illi umekkan i kunwi, u$alet"! Kra segsen ssutren tsriê i Nnbi, nnan: "ih, ixxamen nne$ aâran". Nitni, ur llin aâran, b$an kan ad rewlen.'),
(3547, 33, 14, 'Ma kecmen ten id, si leriaf is, sinna, ssutren asen ad xubten, ad xubten. Cwiî kan ara kukrun fellas.'),
(3548, 33, 15, 'Ni$ llan âuhden s Öebbi, uqbel, ar ur ppu$alen ar deffir. Aâahed s Öebbi ad ippuqeîîi!'),
(3549, 33, 16, 'Ini: "ur kwen tenfaâ trewla, ma trewlem si tmeppant, ne$ si îôad. Ara tezhum, siwa tallit wezzilen".'),
(3550, 33, 17, 'Ini: "anwa wa, ara kwen ikksen seg ufus n Öebbi, ma Ib$a yawen cceôô, ne$ Ib$a yawen aêunu"? Ur asen ppafen, war Öebbi, bab, ne$ asettaô.'),
(3551, 33, 18, 'Ni$ Öebbi Iéôa wid degwen, i ipâawwiqen, wid iqqaôen i watmaten nnsen: "Yyat $uône$"! Drus kan degsen, i ikecmen îôad.'),
(3552, 33, 19, 'D imceêêiyen ar loiha nnwen. Ma tusa d tugdi, a ten twaliv la k pmuqulen, tezzint wallen nnsen, am win tessexciwit tmeppant. Ma tekkes tugdi, a kwen gezren s yilsawen uqviâen. D imceêêiyen $ef lxiô. Wigi, ur uminen ara. Ihi, Imêa Öebbi igiten nnsen. Ayagi, d ayen isehlen i Öebbi.'),
(3553, 33, 20, '£ilen ikabaren ur ôuêen ara. Lemmer a d asen ikabaren, ad ssirmen, ar nitni, di ûûeêôa ay llan, ar Waâôaben n ucluê, steqsayen fellawen. Lemmer llan yidwen, cwiî kan ara nna$en.'),
(3554, 33, 21, 'Ni$, i kunwi, Amazan n Öebbi d amedya amxallef i win ippaôoun Öebbi, akked was aneggaru, id ismektayen aîas Öebbi.'),
(3555, 33, 22, 'Mi walan lmumnin ikabaren, nnan: "ayagi d ayen i $ d Iwaââed Öebbi, akked Umazan iS. Öebbi, akked Umazan iS, Ssawlen tidep". Ay sen irna kan, siwa liman akked wannuz.'),
(3556, 33, 23, 'Ger lmumnin, llan irgazen i iîîfen deg wayen i$ef âuhden Öebbi. Garasen, wid iêellen timeôoiwt nnsen, garasen wid ipganin. Ur bedlen mavi.'),
(3557, 33, 24, 'Iwakken ad Ikafi Öebbi imawlan n tidep, $ef tidep nnsen, u ad Iâaqeb ixabiten, ma ihwa yaS, ne$ ad asen Issuref. Ih, Öebbi Izga Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu.'),
(3558, 33, 25, 'Iééaâ Öebbi wid ijehlen, s iêecciô nnsen. Ur ppaddamen lxiô. Issuli Öebbi îôad i lmumnin. Öebbi Izga d Uohid, d Uzmir.'),
(3559, 33, 26, 'Issers ed, si lebôuj nnsen, wid i sen ifkan afus, seg wAt Tezmamt. Issekcem tugdi deg ulawen nnsen. Arbaâ ten$am ten, arbaâ têebsem ten.'),
(3560, 33, 27, 'Irra kwen tweôtem akal nnsen, ixxamen nnsen, ayla nnsen. D akal ur taâfisem. Ih, Öebbi Izmer i yal cci.'),
(3561, 33, 28, 'A Nnbi! Ini i tlawin ik: "maday teb$amt tameddurt n ddunit, akked ccbuê is, yyamt a kwent $ite$, ad a kwent bru$, berru umâin.'),
(3562, 33, 29, 'Ma illa teb$amt Öebbi, Amazan iS, akked uxxam aneggaru, ihi, Ihegga d Öebbi, i tâaôviyin, segkwent, arraz ameqwôaêan".'),
(3563, 33, 30, 'A tilawin n Nnbi! Tid segkwent ara iawin abekkav ufviê, a ppeppuâaqeb berdayen. Ayagi d ayen isehlen i Öebbi.'),
(3564, 33, 31, 'Tin segkwent i iunzen i Öebbi, akked Umazan iS, u txeddem ayen ilhan, ad as Nefk arraz berdayen, u Nhegga yas d l$it ukyis.'),
(3565, 33, 32, 'A tilawin n Nnbi! Ur tellimt am tlawin nniven. Ma têezzbemt, ur teppeccvemt deg wawal, a kwent isirem umuvin n wul. Inimt awal uwqim.'),
(3566, 33, 33, 'Ilimt deg ixxamen nnkwent. Ur pcebbiêemt acebbeê n at war tussna imenza. èÈéalemt, zekkimt, ôavimt Öebbi akked Umazan iS. Ib$a kan Öebbi a kwent ipwakkes nnkel, a tawacult n Uxxam. U, a kwent Izzizdeg nezzeh.'),
(3567, 33, 34, 'Mmektitemt ed ayen i kwent $ôan, deg ixxamen nnkwent, n issekniyen n Öebbi, akw n ûûwab. Ih, Öebbi Izga d Laîif, Ippuxebbeô.'),
(3568, 33, 35, 'Ih, imvuâen, timvuâin, lmumnin argaz tameîîut, itubiyen, titubiyin, wid akked tid issawalen tidep, iûebôiyen, tiûebôiyin, wid akked tid ippagwaden, wid akked tid ipseddiqen, wid akked tid ippuéumen, wid akked tid ipêaraben $ef tuzzuft nnsen, wid akked tid id immektayen aîas Öebbi; i wigi, Ihegga d Öebbi ssmaê akked warraz abarar.'),
(3569, 33, 36, 'Ur issefk ara i win, ne$ tin iumnen, ad smenyafen lameô nnsen, ma Iseyya d lameô Öebbi, akked Umazan iS. Win inuqmen Öebbi, akked Umazan iS, ni$ innetlaf ttelfan n ûûeê.'),
(3570, 33, 37, 'Mi tenniv i win I$at Öebbi, u t$atev: "jmaâ $uôek, tameîîut ik, êezzeb i Öebbi"; teffrev deg iman ik, ayen ara d Isban Öebbi. Tugadev medden. D Öebbi, i iwatan a T tagwadev. Mi s ibra Zayed, Njewo ik yides, iwakken ur teppili lhejna i lmumnin, ma u$en tilawin n wid id ssekren, mara ad sent brun. Ad iûaô lameô n Öebbi.'),
(3571, 33, 38, 'Ur telli lhejna f Nnbi, deg wayen Iêeppem fellas Öebbi; d tannumi n Öebbi $ef imezwura. Lameô n Öebbi izga ipwafta.'),
(3572, 33, 39, 'Wid issawaven tibôatin n Öebbi, i T ippagwaden, ur ppagwaden yiwen, siwa Öebbi. Öebbi Iqadd i uqeîîi.'),
(3573, 33, 40, 'Ur illi Muêemmed d ababat n yiwen seg irgazen nnwen, maca, d Amazan n Öebbi, u d aneggaru n lambiyya. Öebbi Izga Issen yal cci.'),
(3574, 33, 41, 'A wid iumnen! Mmektit ed Öebbi, maççi d izli.'),
(3575, 33, 42, 'Sbuccuâet eP, ûûbeê, tameddit.'),
(3576, 33, 43, 'D Neppa i d Inuben fellawen, akked lmalayek, iwakken a kwen Issuffe$ si tillas ar tafat. Izga Ipêunu $ef lmumnin.'),
(3577, 33, 44, 'Asmi ara T magren, azul nnsen d: "tifrat"! Ihegga yasen d arraz ukyis.'),
(3578, 33, 45, 'A Nnbi! Nuzen ik id d anagi, d abcir u d aneddaô,'),
(3579, 33, 46, 'i ineccden ar Öebbi, s tsriê iS; d asavef icaâlen.'),
(3580, 33, 47, 'Becceô lmumnin s lfevl ameqwôan i nitni, s$uô Öebbi.'),
(3581, 33, 48, 'Ur ppa$ awal i ijehliyen akked ixabiten. Ur ssemêas, i ccum nnsen. Ppkel $ef Öebbi, Iqadd Öebbi d Awkil.'),
(3582, 33, 49, 'A wid iumnen! Ma tu$em tid iumnen, sinna, tebram asent, uqbel ma tennulem tent, ur fellawen ad asent têesbem tallit. £itet pent, serrêet asent, s wudem uwqim.'),
(3583, 33, 50, 'A Nnbi! Nêell ak tilawin iwumi tefkiv tiqviâen nnsent, tiklatin ik, si tid i k Iqsed Öebbi, iss is n âam ik, tid n tâamtin ik, tid n xal ik, tid n txaltin ik iunagen yidek, tameîîut iumnen, ma tefka iman is i Nnbi, ma ib$a Nnbi a p ya$. D lemziyya i keçç, war lmumnin. Ni$ Neéôa acu i sen Nseyya af tlawin nnsen, akked teklatin nnsen. Iwakken ur teppili fellak lhejna. Öebbi Izga Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu.'),
(3584, 33, 51, 'A ppesganiv tin i k ihwan segsent. A d tawiv $uôek tin i k ihwan, ne$ tin teb$iv si tid tâazlev. Ur fellak tuzzma. Akka i iwulem, iwakken ad qenâant, ur $webbnent, ad ôavint akw, ayen i sent tefkiv. Öebbi Iéôa i illan deg ulawen nnwen. Öebbi Izga d Amusnaw, Iêellem.'),
(3585, 33, 52, 'Ur ak êellent tlawin, sya d asawen, ne$ abeddel n tlawin, xas tâaoeb ik ûûifa nnsent, siwa tiklatin ik. Öebbi Izga Issikid yal cci.'),
(3586, 33, 53, 'A wid iumnen! Ur keççmet ar texxamin n Nnbi, ar awen iâammed, d inebgawen ar wuççi, ur teggunim. Maca, ma tepwâaôvem, kecmet. Mi teççam, sahlet; ur ssiôxiset ameslay. Ayagi, s tidep, iqelleq Nnbi. Isetêa segwen. Öebbi ur Ipsetêi $ef tidep. Ma tessutrem asent ta$awsa, ssutret ep deffir tsabert. Yif it wakka, i tezdeg n wulawen nnwen, akked wulawen nnsent. Ur awen ilaq ara a pjjerim Amazan n Öebbi, ne$ a ppa$em tilawin is, deffir es, d awez$i. Ayagi, ad yili, ar Öebbi, d lefviêa.'),
(3587, 33, 54, 'Ama tessknem d lêaoa, ne$ teffrem p, Öebbi, s tidep, Iéôa yal cci.'),
(3588, 33, 55, 'Ur telli tiyta degsent af ibabaten nnsent, arraw nnsent, atmaten nnsent, arraw n wamaten nnsent, arraw n tsetmatin nnsent, tilawin nnsent, ticrikin nnsent. Ad êezzbent i Öebbi. Öebbi, s tidep, d Anagi n yal cci.'),
(3589, 33, 56, 'Öebbi akked lmalayek iS, s tidep, Nuban $ef Nnbi. A wid iumnen! Nubet fellas, ternum as azul aêmayan.'),
(3590, 33, 57, 'Ih, wid ijjerin Öebbi akked Umazan iS, Ixza ten Öebbi, di ddunit, di laxeôt. Ihegga yasen d aâaqeb isdullun.'),
(3591, 33, 58, 'Wid ijjerin lmumnin, argaz tameîîut, $ef wayen ur ksiben, ni$ bbwin acehrir akked ubekkav n ûûeê.'),
(3592, 33, 59, 'A Nnbi! Ini i tlawin ik, i iss ik, i tlawin n lmumnin, ad jemâant ijufaô nnsent. Ppif akka, a tent âaqlen, ur tent pooerin. Öebbi Izga Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu.'),
(3593, 33, 60, 'Ma ur êbisen ara ixabiten, imehzulen n wul, akked wid ipxeôôiven di Lmadina, ad ak Nebges $uôsen. Sinna, siwa cwiî n tallit ara yilin, degs, d loiran ik.'),
(3594, 33, 61, 'Ad pwaxzun anda ten nufan, ad pwaîîfen, ad pwan$en akw.'),
(3595, 33, 62, 'D tannumi n Öebbi ar wid iâaddan zik. Ur teppafev, d awez$i, abeddel, di tannumi n Öebbi.'),
(3596, 33, 63, 'Steqsan k imdanen, af yimir. Ini: "it Issnen siwa Öebbi". Anwa ad ak imlen, amar imir iqeôb ed?'),
(3597, 33, 64, 'Öebbi, s tidep, Ixza ijehliyen, Ihegga yasen d u$ud.'),
(3598, 33, 65, 'Ad wekkôen degs, i lebda; ur ppafen bab, ne$ asettaô.'),
(3599, 33, 66, 'Ass ideg ara zzin wudmawen nnsen, ar tmes, ad inin: "a yamxix nne$! A lemmer nunez i Öebbi, u nunez i Umazan!'),
(3600, 33, 67, 'Ad inin: "a Mass nne$! Nekwni nunez i igeldan nne$, i imeqwôanen nne$, telfen a$ ar yir abrid.'),
(3601, 33, 68, 'A Mass nne$! Aâqeb iten berdayen, u Xzu ten s leqseê"!'),
(3602, 33, 69, 'A wid iumnen! Ur ppilit am wid i ijjerin Musa. Izekka t Öebbi, seg wayen id nnan. Illa ar Öebbi d amxallef.'),
(3603, 33, 70, 'A wid iumnen! Ëezzbet i Öebbi, tinim awal umâin.'),
(3604, 33, 71, 'Ad awen Iûeggem igiten nnwen, ad Isemmeê ibekkaven nnwen. Win iôuvan Öebbi akked Umazan iS, ni$ ibbwi arraz ameqwôaêan.'),
(3605, 33, 72, 'Naâôev a nefk lamana i igenwan, i tmurt, i idurar. Ugin a p îîfen. Ugaden p. Ibubb ip umdan. Neppa ard amednus ur nessin.'),
(3606, 33, 73, 'Ihi, ad Isâaddi Öebbi aâaqeb af ixabiten akked txabitin, wid akked tid ipcaraken. Ad Issuref Öebbi i wid akked tid iumnen. Öebbi Izga Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu.');
INSERT INTO `ber_mensur` (`index`, `sura`, `aya`, `text`) VALUES
(3607, 34, 1, 'Ccekôan i Öebbi, i iIan i illan deg igenwan, i illan di tmurt. I Neppa, ccekôan di laxert. Neppa, d Bab n ûûwab, Ippuxebbeô.'),
(3608, 34, 2, 'Iéôa ayen ikeççmen di tmurt, ayen id iteff$en segs, ayen id iprusun seg igenni, ayen ippalin $uôes. Neppa Ipêunu, Ipsemmiê.'),
(3609, 34, 3, 'Nnan wid ijehlen: "ur a$ d ippas yimir". Ini: "xaîi, s Mass iw, ara kwen id ias"! Amusnaw n tbavnit, ur idrig fellaS ubruy ubelkim, ama deg igenwan, ama di ddunit; ama seddaw wannect is, ama sennig es; akw, di Tezmamt ipbegginen.'),
(3610, 34, 4, 'Ad Ikafi wid iumnen, ixedmen ayen ilhan. I wigi, ssmaê akked ôôeéq ukyis.'),
(3611, 34, 5, 'Wid ikkaten deg issekniyen nne£, sfunnugen, widak, fellasen aâaqeb n twa$it taqeôêant.'),
(3612, 34, 6, 'Wid iwumi teppunefk tmusni, walan ar ayen id irsen $uôek, s$uô Mass ik, d tidep. Ippawi s abrid n Uzmir, Amaâzuz.'),
(3613, 34, 7, 'Nnan wid ijehlen: "day ad awen nessken argaz, ar awen d yinin ar ma teftutsem, yal aftutes, i kunwi lxelq amaynut?'),
(3614, 34, 8, 'Iger ed tikerkas $ef Öebbi, ne$ d aôehbani"? Xaîi, wid ur numin ara s laxeôt, haaten deg uâaqeb, akked ttelfan u$miq.'),
(3615, 34, 9, 'Day ur walan ara ayen illan zdat sen, u deffir sen, di tmurt akked igenwan? Ma ihwa ya£, a ten Nger seddaw tmurt, ne$ a d Nesse$li fellasen igezzim seg igenni. Deg wayagi, ih, d assekni i yal amdan ucâif.'),
(3616, 34, 10, 'Ni$ Nefka s$uône£ lfevl i Dawed. A yidurar, alset yides akked ifrax. Nerra yas uzzal d aleqqaq.'),
(3617, 34, 11, 'Eûnaâ tibedâiyin n wuzzal, qiss tindar. Xeddmet ayen ilhan. Nek, Pwali$ ayen txeddmem.'),
(3618, 34, 12, 'I Sliman: avu. Win n ûûbeê, aggur; win n tmeddit, aggur. Nelli yas taâwint n nnêas. Kra n leonun ad xedmen fellas, s tsriê n Mass is. Win degsen, iveôfen i lameô nne£, Nessukk fellas, aâaqeb ujajiê.'),
(3619, 34, 13, 'Xeddmen as ayen ib$a: leowamaâ, tiâancuôin, loefnat am iêvunen, ticcuytin iqaâden. Exdem s tnemmirt, a tawacult n Dawed, drus n yimdanen iW i isnemmiren!'),
(3620, 34, 14, 'Mi Nseyya fellas tameppant, ur as faqen ara immut, armi içça taâkwazt is, ubaââuc n wakal. Mi i$li, êulfan leonun ar, lemmer day ssinen tabavnit, ur qqimen deg uâaqeb isdullun.'),
(3621, 34, 15, 'Ni$, i Saba, assekni di tnezdu$in nnsen. Snat tebêirin, ta yeffus, ta zelmev. Eççet si l$it n Mass nnwen, u snemmret aS. Tamurt ilhan, Mass Ipsemmiêen.'),
(3622, 34, 16, 'Wexxôen. Nuzen asen aêemmal n Âarim. Tibêirin nnsen, nerra tent d tibêirin id ippaken l$ella ôéagen, tammemayt, akked tzegwart taxeîîayt.'),
(3623, 34, 17, 'Akka ay ten Nqeîîi $ef tijehli nnsen. Day a Nqeîîi wur nejhil?'),
(3624, 34, 18, 'Nerra garasen u ger temdinin i$ef Nburek, timdinin id ivehôen. Nektal tikli garasent: "merêet degsent di laman, am yiv, am ass"!'),
(3625, 34, 19, 'Nnan: "a Mass nne$! Zzi$wzef tallit ger zziaôat nne$"! Densen iman nnsen. Nerra ten d tiqûivin. Nesqucc iten wakali. Ih, deg wayagi, war ccek, d issekniyen i yal aûebôi isnemmiren.'),
(3626, 34, 20, 'Ni$ Iblis itebbet ed, segsen, ameyyez is. Vefôen t, siwa arbaâ si lmumnin.'),
(3627, 34, 21, 'Ur isâi kra udabu fellasen. Iwakken kan, a Nissin anwa iumnen s laxeôt, u anwa i illan, fellas, di ccekk. Mass ik Ipêarab af yal cci.'),
(3628, 34, 22, 'Ini: "naâret wid i tepkabarem, war Öebbi. Ur sâin taéeyt ubelkim, deg igenwan ne$ di tmurt; ur criken degsen; ur aS illi, garasen, umâiwen".'),
(3629, 34, 23, 'Cafuâa, s$uôeS, tenfaâ kan win iwumi ip Irad. Alamma, ma tekkes tugdi seg wulawen nnsen, a d inin: "acu id Inna, Mass nnwen"? A d inin: "d tidep, u Neppa d Aâlayen, d Ameqwôan".'),
(3630, 34, 24, 'Ini: "anwa ikwen ip$aten, si tmurt akked igenwan"? Ini: "d Öebbi". Nekwni am kunwi, amendeô ma nella di nnhaya, ne$ di ttelfan n ûûeê.'),
(3631, 34, 25, 'Ini: "ur teppuqeîîim $ef wayen nfalîa, ur neppuqeîîi $ef wayen txeddmem".'),
(3632, 34, 26, 'Ini: "ad a$ Issemlil Mass nne$, sinna, ad Iêudd garane$, s tidep. Neppa d Amêaddi Amusnaw".'),
(3633, 34, 27, 'Ini: "sseknet iyi d wid i tqeônem $uôeS, d icriken"! Xaîi, Neppa d Öebbi Uzmir, Bab n ûûwab.'),
(3634, 34, 28, 'Ur k id Nuzen, i imdanen, armi d uqniâ; a pbecôôev, a pnedôev. Maca, tegwti n yimdanen, ur ssinen.'),
(3635, 34, 29, 'Qqaôen: "melmi lemâahda agi, ma tessawalem tidep"?'),
(3636, 34, 30, 'Ini: "$uôwen ppaâud ass, ur tezmirem a t teswexxôem, ne$ a t id tesqeôbem, s saâa".'),
(3637, 34, 31, 'Nnan wid ijehlen: "ur neppamen, d awez$i, s Leqwôan agi, ne$ s wayen it id izwaren". Lemmer a pwaliv mara bedden imednas, ar Mass nnsen, pmeslayen garasen. Ad inin uôhifen i imzuxiyen: "lemmer maççi d kunwi, yili nella d lmumnin".'),
(3638, 34, 32, 'Ad inin imzuxiyen i uôhifen: "day d nekwni ikwen isfeô$en af nnhaya, mi kwen id iusa? Xaîi, tellam d ibe$wviyen".'),
(3639, 34, 33, 'Ad inin uôhifen, i imzuxiyen: "xaîi! Nncub, iv akked wass, mi têeppmem, fellane$, a nagwi Öebbi, u ad aS negg tanudda". Ffren nndama mi walan aâaqeb. Nerra tiqwlavin $ef imegôav n wid ijehlen. Day ara ppuqeîîin $ef wayen ur xdimen?'),
(3640, 34, 34, 'Ur Nuzen ara kra uneddaô ar temdint, mebla ma nnan imeôkantiyen is: "nekwni, ih, nugwi ayen is id teppuceggâam".'),
(3641, 34, 35, 'Nnan: "nekwni, n$elb ik ayla, tarwa. Ur nelli d wid ara ippuqeîîin".'),
(3642, 34, 36, 'Ini: "ihi Mass iw Ip$iti win i S ihwan u Iwezzen; maca, tegwti n imdanen, ur ssinen".'),
(3643, 34, 37, 'Maççi d ayla nnwen, ne$ d tarwa nnwen, ara kwen id iééiéen nezzeh $uône£, siwa wid iumnen, ixedmen ayen ilhan. I nitni arraz berdayen, ilmend n wayen xedmen. Ad ilin, di laman, di t$uôfatin.'),
(3644, 34, 38, 'Ma d wid ikkaten deg issekniyen nne£, sfunnugen, widak a d rsen i uâaqeb.'),
(3645, 34, 39, 'Ini: "ih, Mass iw Ip$iti win i S ihwan, deg imdanen iS. Iwezzen as. Ayen akw ara tefkem n cci, ad awen t id Irr. Neppa, Yif akw im$iten".'),
(3646, 34, 40, 'Ass ideg ara ten Ifser, akken ma llan, imiren ad Yini i lmalayek: "wigi, day llan âabden kwent"?'),
(3647, 34, 41, 'A d inint: "gedha s yiseK! D Keçç ay d Bab nne$, war nitni. Xaîi, llan âabden leonun. Tegwti degsen umnen yissen".'),
(3648, 34, 42, 'Assa, ur imlik yiwen i wayev, segwen, aba$uô ne$ ccqa. A Nini i wid idensen: "jeôôbet aâaqeb n tmes, i tellam tnekôem t"!'),
(3649, 34, 43, 'Ma $ôan asen issekniyen nne£ ipbegginen, ad inin: "wagi d argaz kan, i ib$an a kwen istixeô, seg wayen llan âabden imezwura nnwen". Ad inin: "ayagi, siwa d tikerkas id innulfan". Wid ijehlen i tidep, mi ten id tusa, ad inin: "ayagi d ssêur n ûûeê kan"!'),
(3650, 34, 44, 'Ur asen Nefki tizmamin, ara lemden; ur asen d Nuzen, uqbel ik, aneddaô.'),
(3651, 34, 45, 'Skaddben wid i ten id izwaren. Ur asen tebbwiv ara tis mraw n wayen i ippunefken mi skaddben imazanen iW. A tuzzma W, imiren!'),
(3652, 34, 46, 'Ini: "ar yiwet kan, ara kwen nabi$: a pbeddem zdat Öebbi, di sin, ne$ weêêedwen; sinna, a d tesmektim. Ameddakwel nnwen ur illi d aôehbani. Neppa d aneddaô nnwen kan, uqbel aâaqeb uqsiê".'),
(3653, 34, 47, 'Ini: "ur awen ssutre$ kra n teqdiât; apan nnwen. Ih, taqdiât iw, ar Öebbi kan. Neppa, $ef yal cci, d Anagi".'),
(3654, 34, 48, 'Ini: "ih, Mass iw Ipqeddim tidep, d Amusnaw n tbavnit".'),
(3655, 34, 49, 'Ini: "tusa d tidep, ur d nezzunt tkerkas, ur d ppalsent".'),
(3656, 34, 50, 'Ini: "ma nnetlafe$, nnetlafe$ kan i iman iw. Ma pwanha$, d ayen iyi d Iweêêa Mass iw. Neppa, ih, d Aqôib, Isell".'),
(3657, 34, 51, 'Lemmer a pwaliv mi xelâan, tarewla ur telli. Pwaîîfen, si tama iqeôben.'),
(3658, 34, 52, 'Nnan: "numen yis". Amek ara d ssiwven, si tama ibaâden?'),
(3659, 34, 53, 'Ni$ llan zik, nekôen t. Rran akin tabavnit, si tama ibaâden.'),
(3660, 34, 54, 'Ad yili ufûil, garasen d wayen ctaqen, akken tevôa, zik, d wid i ten icban. Ih, nitni llan di ccekk imcebbwel.');
INSERT INTO `ber_mensur` (`index`, `sura`, `aya`, `text`) VALUES
(3661, 35, 1, 'Ccekôan i Öebbi, Axellaq n tmurt akked igenwan, i Irran lmalayek d timersulin sut sin, krav, akked kué iferrawen. Irennu, di lxelq, ayen i S ihwan. Öebbi, s tidep, Izmer i yal cci.'),
(3662, 35, 2, 'Ayen Ifka Öebbi uêunu, i medden, ur t itekkes yiwen. Ayen Iîîef, ur izmir yiwen a t id iazen, deffir eS. Neppa d Uzmir, d Bab n ûûwab.'),
(3663, 35, 3, 'A yimdanen! Mmektit ed a$iti nnwen s$uô Öebbi. Day illa uxellaq, war Öebbi, ikwen iôeéqen seg igenni akked tmurt? Ur illi ôebbi siwa Neppa, ihi acimi tessaâwajem?'),
(3664, 35, 4, 'Ma nekôen k, ni$ pwanekôen imazanen, uqbel ik. Ar Öebbi, ara qqlen lumuô.'),
(3665, 35, 5, 'A yimdanen! Ih, lemâahda n Öebbi d tidep. Ur kwen tep$uôôu tmeddurt n ddunit! Ur kwen ipkellix um$weôôi, af Öebbi!'),
(3666, 35, 6, 'Cciîan, s tidep, d acengu nnwen. Ëesbet ep d acengu. Issawal kan, i ukabar is, ad ilin seg wat tmes.'),
(3667, 35, 7, 'I wid ijehlen, aâaqeb uqsiê. I wid iumnen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan, ssmaê akked warraz meqqwôen.'),
(3668, 35, 8, 'Day win iwumi Icebbeê yir igiten is, iwakken ad ioâal gerzen…? S tidep, Öebbi Itellif win i S ihwan, Inehhu win i S ihwan. Ur hellek ara iman ik, fellasen. Ih, Öebbi Iéôa acu la ûûenâen.'),
(3669, 35, 9, 'Öebbi i Ippaznen avu, issalayen asigna. Neppawi t ar tmurt immuten, Nessidir ed, yis, akal, deffir tmeppant is. Akka, tanekra.'),
(3670, 35, 10, 'Win ib$an tazmert, tazmert akw ar Öebbi. Awal ukyis ippali $uôeS. Igi ilhan, Iteg as ccan. Aâaqeb uqsiê i wid ippandin tucmitin. A ppemêu tandit nnsen.'),
(3671, 35, 11, 'Ixelq ikwen Öebbi seg wakal; sinna, si tiqqit; sinna, Irra kwen d tiyugiwin. Ur treffed tadist, ur tepparew nnta, siwa ma Iéôa t. Ur Izzi$wzif laâmeô i umuddir, ur as t Issenqas, siwa ma di tezmamt. Ayagi, ih, d ayen isehlen i Öebbi.'),
(3672, 35, 12, 'Ur aâdilen sin ilellen: wa zeddig, éid, iwata i tissit; wayev d ameô$an, d aôéagan. Segsen teppeppem aksum aleqqaq, teppekksem d iâqqucen i teppeqnem. Twalav sfina tepcerrig iten, iwakken a pnadim lfevl iS. Amar a ppesnemmrem.'),
(3673, 35, 13, 'Issekcam iv deg wass, Issekcam ass deg yiv. Iêeppem i yiîij akked waggur, ad lêun ar lajel ipwassnen. D wagi ay d Öebbi, Mass nnwen. IneS tagelda. Wid i tnaâôem, war Neppa, ur rebêen iclem utemôiw.'),
(3674, 35, 14, 'Ma tnaâôem ten, ur sellen i tnaâôit nnwen. Xas slan, ur awen d pparan. Ass n tnekra, ad nekôen ccerk nnwen. Ur k ipxebbiô yiwen am Win Ippuxebbôen.'),
(3675, 35, 15, 'A yimdanen! Kunwi d ime$ban zdat Öebbi. Öebbi d Asâay, d Amaâzuz.'),
(3676, 35, 16, 'Ma ihwa yaS, a kwen Ikkes, a d Iawi lxelq amaynut.'),
(3677, 35, 17, 'I Öebbi, ayagi, ur illi d aéayan.'),
(3678, 35, 18, 'Win ibubben ur ipbibbi taâkkwemt n wayev. Ma isuter ed afus win iâabban, ur s ipwakkas wacemma, xas ma si llezm is. Nabi kan wid ippagwaden Mass nnsen di tbavnit, u péallan. Win ipzekkin, i iman is kan i ipzekki. Tu$alin ar Öebbi.'),
(3679, 35, 19, 'Ur iaâdil uder$al akked win ipwalin,'),
(3680, 35, 20, 'ne$ tillas akked tafat,'),
(3681, 35, 21, 'ne$ tili akked una$uô.'),
(3682, 35, 22, 'Ur aâdilen imuddiren akked lmeggtin. Öebbi, s tidep, Issel i win i S ihwan. Keçç, ur tezmirev a ppeslev i wid illan di tneîlin.'),
(3683, 35, 23, 'Keçç, d aneddaô kan.'),
(3684, 35, 24, 'Ih, Nuzen ik id, s tidep, d abeccaô, d aneddaô. Ur illi lois, mebla ma iusa t id uneddaô.'),
(3685, 35, 25, 'Ma skaddben k, ni$ skaddben wid i ten id izwaren. Usan ten id imazanen nnsen, s ubeggen, s Ihellilen, s Tezmamt timnewweôt.'),
(3686, 35, 26, 'D$a Ssemêalqe$ i wid ijehlen. Amek tuzzma W imiren!'),
(3687, 35, 27, 'Ur twalav ara Öebbi Isse$li d aman seg igenni? Nessuffe$ ed, yissen, ppemôa n yal ini. Deg idurar, isôiden icebêanen, izegwa$en n yal ini, akked iberkanen mavi.'),
(3688, 35, 28, 'Imdanen, lewêuc, lmal, n yal ini ula d nitni. Akka, ger imdanen iS, d imusnawen kan i ippagwaden Öebbi. Ih, Öebbi d Uzmir, Ipsemmiê'),
(3689, 35, 29, 'Ih, wid iqqaôen Tazmamt n Öebbi, ipéallan, ipseddiqen seg wayen iten N$at, s tuffra ne$ âinani, ad ssirmen ttjaôa ur nepquccu.'),
(3690, 35, 30, 'Akken ad asen Ifk tiqvaâin nnsen, ad asen Irnu si lfevl iS. Neppa, s tidep, Ipsemmiê, Ippara tajmilt.'),
(3691, 35, 31, 'Ayen i k Nweêêa, si Tezmamt, d tidep id itebbten ayen ip id izwaren. Ih, Öebbi, $ef imdanen iS, Ippuxebbeô, Ipwali ten.'),
(3692, 35, 32, 'Sinna, Nerra d iweôôaten n Tezmamt, wid Nefren, ger imdanen nne£. Garasen, llan win idensen iman is, garasen alemmas, garasen win izeggwiren ar lxiô, s wannuf n Öebbi. Wagi d lfevl ameqwôan.'),
(3693, 35, 33, 'Loennet n Âaden, ara kecmen. Din, ad qqnen imeqyasen n ddheb, akked tyuqat. Leêrir, di lebsa nnsen.'),
(3694, 35, 34, 'Ad inin: "cekôan i Öebbi i Issaferen fella$ le$wben. Ih, Mass nne$ Ipsemmiê, Ippara tajmilt.'),
(3695, 35, 35, 'I a$ Irran, s lefvl iS, axxam i tnezdu$t; ur a$ ipnal, degs, wugur; ur a$ ipnal, degs, âaggu".'),
(3696, 35, 36, 'I wid ijehlen, times n Loahennama. Ur tepfukku fellasen, ad mmten; ur ippifsus, fellasen, uâaqeb is. Akka, ay Nepqeîîi yal ajehli.'),
(3697, 35, 37, 'Degs, ad ppu$un: "a Mass nne$! Ssuffe$ ane$, a nexdem ayen ilhan, maççi am akken nella nxeddem"! Day ur awen Nesse$wzef ara laâmeô, akken a d immekti win id ismektayen? Iusa kwen id uneddaô. Ihi jeôôbet. I imednas, ur illi umâiwen.'),
(3698, 35, 38, 'Öebbi Issen tabavnit n tmurt akked igenwan. Neppa, s tidep, Iéôa i illan deg idmaren.'),
(3699, 35, 39, 'D Neppa i kwen Iran d igensas di tmurt. Win ijehlen, tijehli s mgal iman is. Tijehli ijehliyen, siwa a$unzu i trennu ar Mass nnsen. Tijehli ijehliyen, siwa taxessaôt i trennu.'),
(3700, 35, 40, 'Ini: "twalam icriken nnwen, la tnaâôem, war Öebbi; sseknet iyi d acu xelqen, si tmurt, ne$ ma sâan amur deg igenwan, ne$ ma Nefka yasen Tazmamt i sen d ipbegginen? Xaîi, aâahed imednas, garasen, d a$uôôu kan.'),
(3701, 35, 41, 'D Öebbi, s tidep, i Iîfen tamurt akked igenwan, ur $ellin ara. Lemmer ad $lin, ur illi yiwen, deffir eS, ara ten iîîfen. Neppa, ih, Izga Iêellem, Ipsemmiê.'),
(3702, 35, 42, 'Gullen s Öebbi, tagalit meqwôen, ar ma iusa ten id uneddaô, ar ad ddun d ubrid, sennig akw leoyus. Mi ten id iusa uneddaô, i asen d irna, siwa tugin,'),
(3703, 35, 43, 'tem$weô di tmurt, akked tnaâuôt tucmip. Ur teppaîîaf tnaâuôt tucmip, siwa bab is. Day ur muqlen ara ar tannumi imezwura? Ur teppafev, d awez$i, abeddel di tannumi n Öebbi. Ur teppafev ara adewwel di tannumi n Öebbi.'),
(3704, 35, 44, 'Day ur unagen ara di tmurt, ad walin amek tevôa d wid i ten id izwaren? Llan $elben ten tazmert. Ur illi win ara sfunngen Öebbi, s wacemma, deg igenwan, ne$ di tmurt. Neppa, ih, Izga d Amusnaw, d Uzmir.'),
(3705, 35, 45, 'Lemmer Ipqeîîi Öebbi imdanen, $ef wayen kesben, ur Ippaooa kra n lxelq sufella n tmurt. Maca, Iswexxiô iten, ar lajel ipwassnen. Ma iusa d lajel nnsen, ihi, Öebbi, deg imdanen iS, Izga Ipwali.');
INSERT INTO `ber_mensur` (`index`, `sura`, `aya`, `text`) VALUES
(3706, 36, 1, 'Is.'),
(3707, 36, 2, 'S Leqwôan uûwib!'),
(3708, 36, 3, 'Keçç, d ûûeê, ar seg imazanen,'),
(3709, 36, 4, '$ef ubrid uwqim.'),
(3710, 36, 5, 'Tarusi n Uzmir Ipêunun,'),
(3711, 36, 6, 'iwakken a pnedôev agdud; ur pwanedôen imezwura nnsen, d$a stehzan.'),
