(3719, 36, 14, 'Mi sen Nuzen sin, nekôen ten. Null s wis krav. Nnan: "nekwni d imazanen $uôwen".'),
(3720, 36, 15, 'Nnan: "kunwi d imdanen kan, am nekwni. Aênin ur d Issers acemma. Kunwi, teskiddibem kan".'),
(3721, 36, 16, 'Nnan: "Mass nne$ Iéôa, s tidep, ar $uôwen id neppuceggaâ.'),
(3722, 36, 17, 'Ay fella$ kan d timenna ipbegginen".'),
(3723, 36, 18, 'Nnan: "war ccekk, tesskeêsem a$. Ma ur teêbisem ara, a kwen neôoem, u a nessuk fellawen, aâaqeb aqeôêan".'),
(3724, 36, 19, 'Nnan: "lkeês nnwen yidwen. Day imi i kwen smektin? Maca, kunwi d agdud amaâfun".'),
(3725, 36, 20, 'Iusa d si îeôf ibaâden n temdint, urgaz s tazzla. Inna: "a yagdud iw! Ddut d imazanen!'),
(3726, 36, 21, 'Ddut d wid ur awen d nessuter taqviât, nitni pwanhan.'),
(3727, 36, 22, 'Amek ur âabde$ ara Win iyi d Ixelqen, u $uôeS tu$alin nnwen?'),
(3728, 36, 23, 'Day ad sâu$, war Neppa, iôebbiten? Ur iyi d teppawi acemma cafuâa nnsen, ma Irad iyi Uênin ccqa; ur iyi pselliken.'),
(3729, 36, 24, 'Yili nek, war ccekk, di ttelfan n ûûeê.'),
(3730, 36, 25, 'Nek, umne$ s Mass nnwen. Ihi selt iyi d".'),
(3731, 36, 26, 'Nnan as: "ekcem ar Loennet"! Inna: "anna$, a lemmer ad iéeô ugdud iw,'),
