(3758, 36, 53, 'Asu$u yiwen kan: a d rsen akw, zdat nne£.'),
(3759, 36, 54, 'Assa, ur ipwadennes ôôuê, s wacemma. A ppeppuqeîîim kan, $ef wayen txeddmem.'),
