(3768, 36, 63, 'Tagi d Loahennama i wen ippuwaââden.'),
(3769, 36, 64, 'Eô$et degs, assa, ilmend n tijehli nnwen.'),
(3770, 36, 65, 'Assa, a Neskweô imawen nnsen, a £ d hedôen ifassen nnsen, a d cehhden ivaôen nnsen, af wayen kesben.'),
(3771, 36, 66, 'Lemmer i £ ihwi, ad asen nergel allen nnsen, ad mzizlen s abrid. Amek ara walin?'),
(3772, 36, 67, 'Lemmer i £ ihwi, ad asen nbeddel udem deg imukan nnsen, ur zmiren ad qqedmen, ne$ ad wexxôen.'),
(3773, 36, 68, 'Win iwumi Nessi$wzef laâmeô, Neppara yas lxelq amengal. Day ur pxemmimen ara?'),
(3774, 36, 69, 'Ur as Nesseêfev tamedyazt, ur as tlaq. Ayagi, siwa asmekti akked Leqwôan ipbegginen.'),
