(3993, 38, 23, 'Ihi, gma yagi, isâa tza u tzat n wulli, nek tixsi yiwet. Inna yi d: kwellef iyi p. Irna yi s wawal".'),
(3994, 38, 24, 'Inna: "ni$ idens ik s usuter n texsi inek, a p irnu ar wulli ines. Aîas n yicriken i ippemjuôen, siwa wid iumnen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan, drus nnsen ay llan". Ifhem Dawed Njeôôeb it kan; iste$feô Mass is, i$li, iîîanez, indem.'),
