(4062, 39, 4, 'Lemmer Ib$i Öebbi ad Isâu aqcic, yili Ifren, deg wayen Ixelleq, ayen i S ihwan. Gedha s yiS! Neppa d Öebbi Yiwen, Aqehhaô.'),
(4063, 39, 5, 'Ixleq tamurt akked igenwan, s tidep. Innev Iv i wass, Innev ass i yiv. Iêeppem i yiîij akked waggur, ad lêun, yal wa, ar lajel ipwassnen. Day Neppa maççi d Uzmir Ipsemmiêen?'),
(4064, 39, 6, 'Ixelq ikwen si yiwen n lxelq. Irra, segs, tislit is. Issers awen d îam n tyugiwin n lmal. Ixelq ikwen di tâabbuvin n tyimmatin nnwen, lxelq deffir lxelq, di krav n tellisat. D wagi ay d Öebbi, Mass nnwen. IneS tagelda, ur illi ôebbi siwa Neppa. Amek ihi tugim?'),
(4065, 39, 7, 'Ma tjehlem, Öebbi ur kwen Iêwao ara. Ur Ipôadi tijehli i imdanen iS. Ma tesnemmrem, a kwen Iôavi. Ur ipbibbi yiwen taâkkwemt n wayev; sinna, ar Mass nnwen tu$alin nnwen; ad awen Imel acu txeddmem. Ih, Neppa, Issen i illan deg idmaren.'),
(4066, 39, 8, 'Amdan, ma iêuza t ccqa, ad inuj ar Mass is, d ucâif $uôes; sinna, ma I$at it s$uôeS, ad ippu ayen i$ef inuj $uôeS, uqbel; ad irr i Öebbi tanudda, ad innetlaf seg ubrid iS. Ini: "zzhu cwiî di tijehli k, ihi, keçç seg wat tmes".'),
(4067, 39, 9, 'Day win ippanzen deg iv, ikna u ibedd, ipêebbiô i laxeôt, issaram aêunu n Mass is…? Ini: "day âadlen wid issnen akked wid ur nessin? Ay d ismektayen, kan, d uâqilen".'),
(4068, 39, 10, 'Ini: "a yimdanen iW iumnen, êezzbet i Mass nnwen. Ayen ilhan i wid imaânen di ddunit agi. Tamurt n Öebbi tewsaâ. Ihi, arraz, war aktili, ad ippunefk i iûebôiyen".'),
(4069, 39, 11, 'Ini: "nek pwamôe$ d ad âabde$ Öebbi, s laâqida i Neppa.'),
(4070, 39, 12, 'Pwamôe$ d, ad ili$ d amvuâ amenzu".'),
(4071, 39, 13, 'Ini: "nek, ugade$, ma aâûa$ Mass iw, aâaqeb n wass ameqwôaêan".'),
(4072, 39, 14, 'Ini: "ad âabde$ Öebbi, s laâqida i Neppa.'),
(4073, 39, 15, 'Ihi, âabdet i wen ihwan, war Neppa". Ini: "imexsuôen d wid iwedôen iman nnsen, akked twacult nnsen, ass n tnekra". Ni$ d tagi ay d taxessaôt n ûûeê.'),
(4074, 39, 16, 'A$embabu n tmes, sennig sen, wayev seddawat sen. Ayagi, Issagwad yis Öebbi imdanen iS: a yimdanen iW, êezzbet iyI!'),
(4075, 39, 17, 'Wid ijunben aâbad iôebbiten n tkerkas, u iutuben Öebbi, a ten id ias lfeôê. Ihi, ssefôeê imdanen iW'),
(4076, 39, 18, 'i issemêasen i wawal, teddun d ûûam ines. D wigi i Inha Öebbi, d wigi ay d uâqilen.'),
(4077, 39, 19, 'Day win i$ef ippuseyya ad isâaddi aâaqeb, day a psellkev keçç, win illan di tmes?'),
(4078, 39, 20, 'Ma d wid iêezzben i Mass nnsen, ad sâun ti$uôfatin, bnant ta sennig ta, isaffen seddawat sent ppazzalen, d lemâahda n Öebbi. Öebbi ur Ixeîîu i lemâahda.'),
(4079, 39, 21, 'Ur twalav ara, Öebbi Isse$li d aman, seg igenni, Issekcem iten ad sswen akal. Sinna, yissen, a d Issuffe$ im$an n yal ini, ara iu$alen ad isliwen. A ten twaliv d iwôa$en, sinna, a ten Irr d iquôanen. Deg waya, s tidep, asmekti i uâqilen.'),
(4080, 39, 22, 'Day win iwumi Illi Öebbi, idmaren is, ar wannuz, d$a neppa di tafat s$uô Mass is…? A ssxev n at wulawen iqquôen, ur d smektayen Öebbi! Widak di ttelfan n ûûeê.'),
(4081, 39, 23, 'Issader ed Öebbi ûûam n wawal. Tazmamt, degs acbi, allus. Ad ccirwen segs igwelman akked wulawen n wid ippagwaden Mass nnsen, sinna, igwelman akked wulawen nnsen ad iêninen ar usmekti n Öebbi. D tagi ay d nnhaya n Öebbi. Inehhu yis, win i S ihwan. Win Itlef Öebbi, ur illi wa ara t inhun.'),
(4082, 39, 24, 'Day win ipêezziben, s wudem is, seg uâaqeb ucmit, ass n tnekra…? Ad inin i imednas: "jeôôbet ayen tkeppbem"!'),
(4083, 39, 25, 'Skaddben wid i ten id izwaren. Iusa ten id uâaqeb, seg wanda ur bnin.'),
(4084, 39, 26, 'Issukk fellasen Öebbi aâaqeb, di tmeddurt n ddunit; war ccekk, aâaqeb n laxeôt iugar it, lemmer éeôôen!'),
(4085, 39, 27, 'Ni$ Nefka i imdanen, di Leqwôan agi, yal amedya, amar a d mmektin.'),
(4086, 39, 28, 'Leqwôan s taâôabt, ur degs tiââawji; amar ad êezzben.'),
(4087, 39, 29, 'Ifka d Öebbi amedya n urgaz icerken akked wid ipmeréan, u argaz di tifrat akked yiwen urgaz. Day âadlen sin imedyaten? Ccekôan i Öebbi. Xaîi, tegwti degsen ur ssinen.'),
(4088, 39, 30, 'War ccekk, keçç a ppemmtev, nitni ad mmten.'),
(4089, 39, 31, 'Sinna, kunwi, ass n tnekra, ar Mass nnwen, a ppemqellaâm.'),
(4090, 39, 32, 'Anwa i idensen sennig win iskaddben af Öebbi, iskaddben tidep ma tusa t id? Day maççi di Loahennama, i illa uxxam ijehliyen?'),
(4091, 39, 33, 'Wid id iusan s tidep, u pputebbten yis, wigi d wid ipêezziben.'),
(4092, 39, 34, 'Ad sâun ayen b$an, ar Mass nnsen. D wagi ay d arraz iâaôviyen.'),
(4093, 39, 35, 'Iwakken ad asen Ikkes Öebbi, ayen xedmen adiran mavi; a ten I$it s wayen xeddmen d amxallef.'),
(4094, 39, 36, 'Day ur Ipqam ara Öebbi amdan iS? La k ssagwaden s wid, war Neppa. Win Itlef Öebbi, ur illi w ara t inhun.'),
(4095, 39, 37, 'Win Inha Öebbi, ur illi w ara t itelfen. Ni$ Öebbi d Uzmir, Bab n ppaô.'),
(4096, 39, 38, 'Ma testeqsav ten: "anwa i Ixelqen tamurt akked igenwan? Ad inin, war ccekk: d Öebbi". Ini: "ma twalam wigi tnaâôem, war Öebbi, day zemren, ma Ib$a yi Öebbi ccqa, ad kksen ccqa S? Ne$, ma Ib$a yi aêunu, ad ssbeîlen aêunu S"? Ini: "Iqennaâ iyi Öebbi; fellaS ay ppeklen wid ipkalen".'),
(4097, 39, 39, 'Ini: "a yagdud iw! Xedmet akken tennumen, nek la xeddme$". Deqqal a ppeéôem'),
(4098, 39, 40, 'anwa u$uô ara d ias uâaqeb ara t isdullen, u$uô ara d irs uâaqeb imezgi.'),
(4099, 39, 41, 'Ih, Nessader ed $uôek, Tazmamt i medden, s tidets. Win ipwanhan, i iman is, win innetlafen, innetlaf kan, mgal is. Ur telliv, keçç, d awkil nnsen.'),
(4100, 39, 42, 'Öebbi Ippaddam leôwaê mara mmten, akked wid ur nemmut, deg ives nnsen. Iâatteq wid i$ef Iseyya tameppant, Ippara d wiyav, ar lajel ipwassnen. Ih, deg wayagi, ard issekniyen i ugdud ipmeyyizen.'),
(4101, 39, 43, 'Ne$ ad ddmen, war Öebbi, imcafâan? Ini: "i ma ur sâin acemma, ur fhimen"?'),
(4102, 39, 44, 'Ini: "akw ccafuâa n Öebbi. IneS tagelda n tmurt akked igenwan. Sinna, $uôeS ara tu$alem".'),
(4103, 39, 45, 'Mara d Ipwadder Öebbi Yiwen, ad zemven wulawen n wid ur numin ara s laxeôt. Ma pwadren d wid, war Neppa, imiren nitni ad ceôêen.'),
(4104, 39, 46, 'Ini: "a Öebbi! Axellaq n tmurt akked igenwan, Amusnaw n wayen iffren d wayen ivehôen, d Keçç ara Iêudden ger imdanen iK, $ef wayen llan mgarraden".'),
(4105, 39, 47, 'Wid idensen, lemmer nnsen ayen akw i illan di tmurt, rnu yas am neppa, ur ten id ifeddu, seg uâaqeb ucmit, ass n tnekra. Ad asen d iban, s$uô Öebbi, ayen i$ef ur bnin.'),
(4106, 39, 48, 'Ad asen d banent tucmitin kesben, ad asen innev wayen i$ef ttahan.'),
(4107, 39, 49, 'Ma iêuza umdan ccqa, ad a£ d inâaô. Sinna, ma Nezger tacvaî nne£ fellas, ad yini: "tusa yi d kan si tmusni". Xaîi! D ajeôôeb, maca aîas degsen ur ssinen.'),
(4108, 39, 50, 'Ni$ nnan t id imezwura nnsen. Acu i sen d ibbwi wayen keppben?'),
(4109, 39, 51, 'Iwwet iten wayen kesben n tucmitin. Wid idensen, seg wigi, a ten iwwet wayen kesben n tucmitin. Ur zmiren ad sfunngen.'),
(4110, 39, 52, 'Day ur éôin ara ar Öebbi Ip$iti win i S ihwan, u Iwezzen? Ih, deg waya, ard issekniyen i ugdud iumnen.'),
(4111, 39, 53, 'Ini: "a yimdanen iw i ipêawalen mgal iman nnsen! Ur ppayset aêunu n Öebbi. Ih, Öebbi Ipsemmiê akw ibekkaven. Ih, Neppa Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu.'),
(4112, 39, 54, 'Steôoâet i Mass nnwen, anzet aS, uqbel a kwen id ias uâaqeb, d$a ula ikwen isellken.'),
(4113, 39, 55, 'Ddut d ûûam n wayen i wen d irsen, s$uô Mass nnwen, uqbel a kwen id ias uâaqeb, deqzalla, kunwi ur tebnim";'),
(4114, 39, 56, 'u a d yini ôôuê: "a ssexv iw, $ef wayen stehza$ ar loiha n Öebbi! Lli$, s tidep, seg wid ittihin".'),
(4115, 39, 57, 'Ne$ a d yini: "lemmer iyi Inha Öebbi, yili lli$ seg wid ipêezziben".'),
(4116, 39, 58, 'Ne$ a d yini mara iwali aâaqeb: "lemmer iyi illi wallus, ad ili$ si lâuûam".'),
(4117, 39, 59, 'Xaîi! Usan k id issekniyen iW, teskaddbev ten, tzuxxev, telliv seg ijehliyen.'),
(4118, 39, 60, 'Ass n tnekra, a pwaliv berrikit wudmawen n wid id igren tikerkas af Öebbi. Day maççi di Loahennama, i illa uxxam imzuxiyen?'),
(4119, 39, 61, 'Ad Isellek Öebbi wid iêezzben; ar rebêen. Ur ten ikkat wugur, ur $webbnen.'),
(4120, 39, 62, 'Öebbi Ixleq yal cci. Neppa d Awkil n yal cci.'),
(4121, 39, 63, 'IneS tsura n tmurt akked igenwan. Wid inekôen issekniyen n Öebbi, widak d imexsuôen.'),
(4122, 39, 64, 'Ini: "day ad yi tamôem ad âabde$, war Öebbi, a wid ur nessin"?'),
(4123, 39, 65, 'Ni$ iusa k id uweêêi, u $eô wid i k izwaren. Ma tcurkev, ad mêun igiten ik, a ppiliv seg imexsuôen.'),
(4124, 39, 66, 'Xaîi! Aâbed Öebbi. Ili seg wid isnemmiren.'),
(4125, 39, 67, 'Ur qudôen ara Öebbi, azal n lqedô iS. Akw tamurt, ass n tnekra, di tumeét iS. Igenwan ad nnefvasen deg ufus iS ayeffus. Gedha s yiS! I Aâlay sennig wayen pcaraken!'),
(4126, 39, 68, 'Aûuvu di lbuq: ad ixsef i illan deg igenwan, i illan di tmurt, kkes ed i S ihwan i Öebbi. Aûuvu nniven: nitni a d kkren pmuqulen.'),
(4127, 39, 69, 'A pfeooeo tmurt, si tafat n Mass is. A d ters Tezmamt, a d awin lambiyya akked inagan. Ad âaddin di ccôaâ, s tidep, ur pwadensen.'),
(4128, 39, 70, 'Yal yiwen ad i$ellet ayen ixdem. Neppa, Yif akw akken Issen, d acu xeddmen.'),
(4129, 39, 71, 'Ad pwanehôen wid ijehlen, d igrawen, ar Loahennama. Mi bbwven $uôes, u llint tebbura s, ad asen inin iâssasen is: "day ur kwen in usan ara imazanen, segwen, mmalen awen issekniyen n Mass nnwen, nedôen kwen af temlilit n wass nnwen agi"? A d inin: "Ih. Maca, ad iûaô wawal uâaqeb, af ijehliyen".'),
(4130, 39, 72, 'A d inin: "kecmet si tebbura, ar Loahennama! Degs, wekkôet". Ay d ucmit uxxam n imzuxiyen!'),
(4131, 39, 73, 'Wid iêezzben i Mass nnsen, ad pwanehôen ar Loennet, d igrawen. Mi bbwven $uôes, u llint tebbura s, ad asen inin iâssasen is: "tifrat fellawen, tgerzem; kecmet ep, twekkôem"!'),
(4132, 39, 74, 'Ad inin: "ccekôan i Öebbi i $ Issawven lemâahda S. Ifka ya$ tamurt d lweôt; a nili, di Loennet, anda i $ ihwa. A yarraz asaâdi n wid ixeddmen lxiô!'),
(4133, 39, 75, 'A pwaliv lmalayek zzint ed i usgeld, sbuccuâent s ccekôan Mass nnsent. Iâadda ccôaâ garasen, s tidep. Ad inin: "a neckeô Öebbi, Mass imavalen".');
INSERT INTO `ber_mensur` (`index`, `sura`, `aya`, `text`) VALUES
(4134, 40, 1, 'Ëm.'),
(4135, 40, 2, 'Tarusi n Tezmamt, s$uô Öebbi, Uzmir, Amusnaw;'),
(4136, 40, 3, 'Ipsemmiêen tuccva, Iqeblen nndama, Ipâaqaben s teqseê, Bab n terkunt. Ur illi ôebbi siwa Neppa. £uôeS taggara.'),
(4137, 40, 4, 'Siwa wid ijehlen i ipnamaren $ef issekniyen n Öebbi. Ur k ip$uôôu ucali nnsen, di tmurt.'),
(4138, 40, 5, 'Uqbel nitni, agdud n Nuê, akked ikabaren deffir sen, skaddben. Yal lois iclaâ ad ixvef amazan is. Ipnamar s tkerkas, iwakken, s yissent, ad iveggeô tidep. Ëekme$ ten. A tiyta W imiren!'),
(4139, 40, 6, 'Akka iûaô wawal n Mass ik, af wid ijehlen. Nitni, war ccekk, d at tmes.'),
(4140, 40, 7, 'Tid irefden asgeld, akked tid i s izzin, sbuccuâen s ccekôan Mass nnsent, umnent yiS. Ssuturent ad pwasemmêen wid iumnen: "a Mass nne$! Terriv yal cci d aêunu, u d tamusni. Semmeê i wid isteôoâen u ddan d ubrid iK; Sellek iten seg uâaqeb n wu$ud.'),
(4141, 40, 8, 'A Mass nne$! Ssekcem iten ar leonanat n Âaden, i Tâahdev, i nitni, u i iâaôviyen seg ibabaten nnsen, tilawin nnsen, tarwa nnsen. Keçç, ih, d Uzmir, d Bab n ûûwab.'),
(4142, 40, 9, 'Aâteq iten si tucmitin. Win Tâatqev, assen, si tucmitin, ni$ Têunev fellas. D wagi ay d rrbeê ameqwôaêan".'),
(4143, 40, 10, 'Ad pwanecden wid ijehlen: "taâdawt n Öebbi te$leb taâdawt bbwaygarawen. Mi tepwanecdem ar liman, tugim".'),
(4144, 40, 11, 'A d inin: "a Mass nne$! Ten$iv a$ berdayen, Tessidrev a$ berdayen. Nqaôô s ibekkaven nne$. Day illa ubrid n tuff$a"?'),
(4145, 40, 12, 'Akka, imi mara ipwanâaô Öebbi Yiwen, kunwi tjehlem. Mara S pcaraken, kunwi tumnem. Aêuddu ar Öebbi Aâlayen, Ameqwôan.'),
(4146, 40, 13, 'D Neppa i wen Issnaâtan issekniyen iS. Issadar awen d l$it, seg igenni. Siwa win isteôoiâen, id ismektayen.'),
(4147, 40, 14, 'Nujet $uô Öebbi, s laâqida i Neppa, xas ugin ijehliyen.'),
(4148, 40, 15, 'Aâlayen nnig idurra, Bab n usgeld, Ippak ôôuê s lameô iS, i win i S ihwan, deg imdanen iS, iwakken ad indeô af wass umlili,'),
(4149, 40, 16, 'ass ideg ara d awven, ur illi wayen iffren, degsen, i Öebbi. W ip ilan tgelda, assen? D Öebbi, Yiwen, Aqehhaô.'),
(4150, 40, 17, 'Ass ideg ara ippuqeîîi yal iman $ef wayen ikseb; ur ippili ddens assen. Ih, Öebbi Ip$awal deg uqeîîi.'),
(4151, 40, 18, 'Nabi ten af ass aqôib, ideg ulawen ad rewlen s igerjumen, ad qebôen. Ur ippilli i imednas, uêbib ne$ amcafaâ, iwumi ara ssemêessen.'),
(4152, 40, 19, 'Issen nncub n yiéôi, akked wayen teffren idmaren.'),
(4153, 40, 20, 'Öebbi Iferru s tidep. Wid ipnujun ar war Neppa, ur qeîîun acemma. Ih, Öebbi d Win Isellen, Ipwalin.'),
(4154, 40, 21, 'Day ur nudan ara tamurt, ad walin amek tevôa d wid i ten id izwaren. Llan ifen ten tazmert, akked lateô, di tmurt. Issemêelleq asen Öebbi, ilmend ibekkaven nnsen. Ur asen illi umêareb, mgal Öebbi.'),
(4155, 40, 22, 'Akka, acku ppasen $uôsen, imazanen nnsen, s ubeggen, u nitni jehlen. Issemêelleq asen Öebbi. Ih, Neppa, d Uzmir, d Bab uâaqeb uqsiê.'),
(4156, 40, 23, 'Ni$ Nuzen ed Musa s issekniyen nne£, s udabu iberrzen,'),
(4157, 40, 24, 'ar Ferâun, Haman, akked Qaôun. Nnan: "d aseêêar, d akeddab".'),
(4158, 40, 25, 'Mi sen d iusa, s tidep s $uône£, nnan: "en$et arrac n wid iumnen yides, ssidret tilawin nnsen". Tandit ijehliyen siwa di ttelfan.'),
(4159, 40, 26, 'Inna Ferâun: "anfet iyi ad n$e$ Musa, xas ad inuj ar Mass is. Ugade$, nek, ad ibeddel ddin nnwen, ne$ a d issekcem lefsad di tmurt".'),
(4160, 40, 27, 'Inna Musa: "nek, ad iyi Iûûeô Mass iw u Mass nnwen, si yal amzuxi, ur numin s wass uqeîîi".'),
(4161, 40, 28, 'Inna urgaz lmumen, i iffren liman is, si twacult n Ferâun: "day a ppen$em argaz, imi d iqqaô: Mass iw d Öebbi, u irna ibbwi yawen d abeggen, s$uô Mass nnwen? Ma iskaddeb, lkedb is fellas. Ma issawel tidep, a kwen iêaz kra seg wayen ikwen issagwad. Öebbi ur Inehhu amaâfun iskiddiben.'),
(4162, 40, 29, 'A yagdud iw! Assa, nnwen tagelda, tufrarem di tmurt. W ad a$ isellken si tiyta n Öebbi, ma tusa ya$ d"? Inna d Ferâun: "i wen ssekne$ ayen kan wala$; s anda i kwen nehhu$, siwa ar ubrid imaânen".'),
(4163, 40, 30, 'Inna d win iumnen: "a yagdud iw! Nek, ugade$ fellak tin n wass ikabaren,'),
(4164, 40, 31, 'akken tevôa d ugdud n Nuê, Âad, Tamud, akked wid i ten id ivefôen. Öebbi ur Ib$a ara ddens i imdanen.'),
(4165, 40, 32, 'A yagdud iw! Nek ugade$, ay kwen ippa$en, ass umnamar,'),
(4166, 40, 33, 'ass ideg ara trewlem ar deffir. Ur awen illi umêareb mgal Öebbi. Ur illi nnahi i win Itlef Öebbi".'),
(4167, 40, 34, 'Ni$ iusa kwen id Yusef, zik, s ubeggen. Tezgam di ccekk, $ef wayen i wen d ibbwi. Armi immut, tennam: "ur d Ippazen ara Öebbi amazan, deffir es, d awez$i". Akka i Itellif Öebbi amaâfun amcekki.'),
(4168, 40, 35, 'Wid ipnamaren issekniyen n Öebbi, ur ten id iusi udabu, nezzeh ara ten i$unfu Öebbi, akked wid iumnen. Akka ara Icemmaâ Öebbi, yal ul amzuxi, aâfrit.'),
(4169, 40, 36, 'Inna Ferâun: "a Haman, bnu yi lbeôo, amar ad awve$ ar iberdan,'),
(4170, 40, 37, 'iberdan igenwan. Ad ali$ ar Öebbi n Musa. Nek êesbe$ t d akeddab". Akka i s ippucebbeê i Ferâun, igi s ucmit. Ippuveôôef seg ubrid. Tandit n Ferâun, siwa taxeûûart.'),
(4171, 40, 38, 'Inna d win iumnen: "a yagdud iw! Ddu yidi, a k nhu$ s abrid umâin.'),
(4172, 40, 39, 'A yagdud iw! Tameddurt agi, di ddunit, d zzhu kan; wanag laxeôt d axxam n leqôaô.'),
(4173, 40, 40, 'Win ixedmen tucmip, ad ippuqeîîi, kan, s tin i p icban. Wid ixedmen ayen ilhan, d ddkeô ne$ d nnta, u nitni umnen, widak ad kecmen Loennet; din, ad aten $iten, war aktili.'),
(4174, 40, 41, 'A yagdud iw! Acu iyi bbwin, a kwen neccde$ ar leslak; kunwi, a yi tneccdem ar tmessi?'),
(4175, 40, 42, 'A yi tneccdem ad aâûu$ Öebbi, ad aS carke$ ayen ur ssine$. Nek, neccde$ kwen ar Uzmir Ipsemmiêen'),
(4176, 40, 43, 'War ccekk, ayen u$uô a yi tneccdem, ur as iwata unuju di ddunit, u di laxeôt. Ih, tu$alin nne$ ar Öebbi. Imaâfan ard at tmes.'),
(4177, 40, 44, 'A d tesmektim ayen i wen qqaôe$. Öôay iw fki$ t i Öebbi. Ni$ Öebbi Ipwali imdanen".'),
(4178, 40, 45, 'Isellek it Öebbi si tucmitin i undin. I$wellef lois n Ferâun, s uâaqeb iugaren wiyav:'),
(4179, 40, 46, 'times. Ad pwafessren degs, ûûbeê, tameddit. Ass ideg ara d ias yimir: "ekcem, a lois n Ferâun, aâaqeb uwâiô mavi"!'),
(4180, 40, 47, 'Mara ppemqellaâen di tmes, ad inin uôhifen i imzuxiyen: "ni$ nella nedda yidwen. Ma tzemrem, kunwi, ad a$ tesneqsem cwiî, si tmes"?'),
(4181, 40, 48, 'A d inin imzuxiyen: "aql a$, akw, degs. S tidep, Öebbi Iêudd ger imdanen".'),
(4182, 40, 49, 'Ad inin wid illan di tmes, i iâessasen n Loahennama: "naâôet Mass nnwen, ad a$ Issifes ibwass uâaqeb".'),
(4183, 40, 50, 'Ad inin: "day ur kwen id usan ara imazanen nnwen, s ubeggen"? Ad inin: "ih". Ad inin: "naâret"! Ar ttelfan, kan, tanaârit ijehliyen.'),
(4184, 40, 51, 'War ccekk, a Nsellek imazanen nne£, akked wid iumnen, di tmeddurt n ddunit, u deg wass ideg ara d bedden inagan,'),
(4185, 40, 52, 'ass ideg ur infaâ uste$feô imednas. Ad pwaxzun, ad zed$en deg uxxam ucmit mavi.'),
(4186, 40, 53, 'Ni$ Nefka, i Musa, nnhaya. Nefka, i At Isôail, Tazmamt d lweôt.'),
(4187, 40, 54, 'D nnhaya, u d asmekti i uâqilen.'),
(4188, 40, 55, 'Eûbeô. Ih, lemâahda n Öebbi, d tidep. Ssuter ssmaê ubekkav ik. Sbuccaâ s ccekôan Mass ik, tameddit, taûebêit.'),
(4189, 40, 56, 'Ih, wid ipnamaren issekniyen n Öebbi, ur ten id iusi udabu, d tem$weô kan i illan deg idmaren nnsen; ur as ssawven. Ggani Öebbi, Neppa, s tidep, Isell, Ipwali.'),
(4190, 40, 57, 'Ih, lxelq n tmurt akked igenwan iugar lxelq n imdanen, maca aîas n imdanen ur éôin.'),
(4191, 40, 58, 'Ur iaâdil ara uder$al akked win ipwalin, wid iumnen u xeddmen ayen ilhan, akked bu tucmitin. Cwiî id tesmektayem.'),
(4192, 40, 59, 'Ihi, imir a d ias, ur illi ccekk fellas, maca tegwti n imdanen ur uminen.'),
(4193, 40, 60, 'Inna Mass nnwen: "naâret iyI, ad awen d Jawbe$. Wanag wid igelzen aâbed iW, ad kecmen Loahennama, d imedlulen".'),
(4194, 40, 61, 'Öebbi i wen Irran iv, i ureyyeê degs, ass i tmu$li. Öebbi, ih, d Bab n lfevl i imdanen, maca tegwti n imdanen, ur snemmiren.'),
(4195, 40, 62, 'D wagi ay d Öebbi, Mass nnwen. Ixleq yal cci, ur illi ôebbi, siwa Neppa. Ihi, acimi tezzim akin?'),
(4196, 40, 63, 'Akka ay wexxôen wid iugin issekniyen n Öebbi.'),
(4197, 40, 64, 'Öebbi i wen Irran tamurt d leqôaô, igenni d ssqef; ikwen Imeslen. Iûeggem udem nnwen. I$at ikwen s wayen ilhan. D wagi ay d Öebbi, Mass nnwen. D Asaâdi Öebbi, Mass imavalen.'),
(4198, 40, 65, 'Neppa d Amuddir, ur illi ôebbi siwa Neppa. Ihi, naâôet eP, s lâaqida i Neppa. Ccekôan i Öebbi, Mass imavalen.'),
(4199, 40, 66, 'Ini: "nek, ipwakkes iyi uâbad n wid tnaârem war Öebbi, mi yi d iusa ubeggen, s$uô Mass iw. Pwamôe$ d, ad anze$ i Mass imavalen.'),
(4200, 40, 67, 'Neppa, ikwen Ixelqen seg wakal; sinna, si tiqqit; sinna, seg urgen; sinna, Issuffe$ ikwen id d igwerdan; sinna, a ppim$uôem; sinna, a ppu$alem d im$aôen. Kra segwen, pmeppaten uqbel. Iwakken a ppawvem ar lajel ipwassnen. Amendeô ma a pfehmem.'),
(4201, 40, 68, 'D Neppa i Issidiren, i Ineqqen. Ma Iseyya d lameô, ad as Yini kan: "ili"! Ad yili.'),
(4202, 40, 69, 'Day ur twalav ara amek ssuff$en i ubrid, wid ipnamaren issekniyen n Öebbi?'),
(4203, 40, 70, 'Wid iskaddben Tazmamt, akked wayen i$ef id Nuzen imazanen nne£, deqqal ad éôen.'),
(4204, 40, 71, 'Mara pwazu$ôen, s teqlavin d slasel,'),
(4205, 40, 72, 'ar waman ippayzagen; sinna, ar tmes, ad pwaveggôen;'),
(4206, 40, 73, 'sinna, ad asen inin: "anda t wayen tepcarakem'),
(4207, 40, 74, 'war Öebbi"? A d inin: "dergen fella$. Xaîi! Ur illi wayen u$uô nepnuju, zik". Akka i Itellif Öebbi ijehliyen.'),
(4208, 40, 75, 'Akka, $ef wayen tzehhum di tmurt, ur teklalem, akked wayen tqebêem.'),
(4209, 40, 76, 'Kecmet Loahennama, si tebbura; degs twekkôem. Ay dir tanezdu$t imzuxiyen!'),
(4210, 40, 77, 'Eûbeô, war ccekk, lemâahda n Öebbi d tidep. Ad ak Nessken kra n wayen i sen Nâahed, ne$ a Neddem ôôuê ik. £uône£ ara d u$alen.'),
(4211, 40, 78, 'Ni$ Nuzen ed imazanen uqbel ik. £ef kra segsen, Neêka yak d. £ef kra nniven, ur ak d Neêka ara. Ur iwata ara i umazan, a d iawi assekni, siwa ma s tsriê n Öebbi. Ma iusa d lameô n Öebbi, aseyyi s tidep. Ad xesôen, imiren, laâôuô.'),
(4212, 40, 79, 'Öebbi i wen Ifkan lmal i rekba nnwen. Segsen teppeppem.'),
(4213, 40, 80, 'Degsen, i kunwi, aba$uô akked agwav ar wayen id ssuturen idmaren nnwen. Fellasen, akw f ssfinat, teppâabbim.'),
(4214, 40, 81, 'Issenâat awen d issekniyen iS. Anwi issekniyen n Öebbi ara tnekôem?'),
(4215, 40, 82, 'Day ur nudan ara tamurt ad walin amek tevôa d wid i ten id izwaren. Llan ifen ten akken îîuqten, ifen ten tazmert akked lateô di tmurt. Ulay sen d ibbwi wayen la keppben.'),
(4216, 40, 83, 'Mi ten id usan imazanen nnsen s ubeggen, feôêen s tmusni i illan $uôsen. Izzi fellasen wayen i$ef ppemsexxiôen.'),
(4217, 40, 84, 'Mi walan tamnirt nne£, nnan: "numen s Öebbi Yiwen, nveggeô ayen i nella ncurek aS".'),
(4218, 40, 85, 'Ur izmir ara a ten infaâ liman nnsen, mi walan tamnirt nne£. D tannumi n Öebbi, si zik, i imdanen iS. Akka ay xesôen ijehliyen.');
INSERT INTO `ber_mensur` (`index`, `sura`, `aya`, `text`) VALUES
(4219, 41, 1, 'Ëm.'),
(4220, 41, 2, 'Tarusi s$uô Uênin Ipêunun,'),
(4221, 41, 3, 'Tazmamt, feûûlen issekniyen is; Leqwôan s taâôabt, i ugdud issnen,'),
(4222, 41, 4, 'ipbecciôen, ineddôen. Tegwti degsen numren, d$a ur sellen.'),
(4223, 41, 5, 'Nnan: "ulawen nne$ ddurin i wayen i$eô la $ tneccdev; di tmejjin nne$: tiâéegt; garane$ yidek: sîeô. Ihi, exdem, nekwni la nxeddem".'),
(4224, 41, 6, 'Ini: "nek d amdan kan, am kunwi. Weêêan iyi d kan ar Öebbi nnwen, d Öebbi Yiwen. Sweqmet $uôeS, ssutret aS ssmaê". A tawa$it n imcurak,'),
(4225, 41, 7, 'wid ur nepzekki, u nitni nekôen laxeôt!'),
(4226, 41, 8, 'Ih, i wid iumnen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan: arraz ur nepnegzay.'),
(4227, 41, 9, 'Ini: "kunwi aql akwen la tnekôem Win Ixelqen tamurt, di sin wussan. La S tepparam nned. Wagi d Mass imavalen.'),
(4228, 41, 10, 'Irra degs idurar sufella. Iôqa p, Iwzen degs tagwella s, di kué wussan. Akka i wid isteqsayen.'),
(4229, 41, 11, 'Sinna, Izzi ar igenni i illan d abbu. Inna yas, u i tmurt: "aset ed, teb$am ne$ tugim"! Nnan: "a n nas, d imvuâen".'),
(4230, 41, 12, 'Iseyya ten d ûa igenwan, di sin wussan. Iweêêa lameô is, i yal igenni. Ncebbeê igenni aqôib mavi, s teftilin, u d laânaya. D aya ay d Iqeddeô n Uzmir, Amusnaw.'),
(4231, 41, 13, 'Ma numren, ini: "ssagwde$ kwen s ssiâqa, am ssiâqa n Âad u Tamud".'),
(4232, 41, 14, 'Mi ten id usan imazanen, zdat sen, u deffir sen: "ur âabdet, siwa Öebbi"! Nnan: "lemmer i S ihwi i Mass nne$, a d Issers lmalayek. Nekwni, ihi, nenkeô ayen i s id teppuceggâam".'),
(4233, 41, 15, 'Wanag Âad, sme$wôen iman nnsen di tmurt, ur klalen. Nnan: "anwa i $ i$elben di tezmert"? Day ur walan ara, Öebbi, iten id Ixelqen, I$elb iten di tezmert? Llan la nekôen issekniyen nne£.'),
(4234, 41, 16, 'Nuzen asen aûeôûaô, deg ussan imevyaôen, iwakken a Nessukk fellasen, aâaqeb imdelli di tmeddurt n ddunit. Aâaqeb n laxeôt, war ccekk, isdullu kteô. Ur asen ippili umâiwen.'),
(4235, 41, 17, 'Wanag Tamud, Nebbwi ten d ubrid. Smenyafen tider$elt i nnhaya. Tewwet iten ssiâqa n uâaqeb issrusun, ilmend n wayen keppben.'),
(4236, 41, 18, 'Nsellek wid iumnen, i illan pêezziben.'),
(4237, 41, 19, 'Ass ideg ara ssemlilen ar tmessi, icenga n Öebbi, nitni ad pwajemmlen.'),
(4238, 41, 20, 'Alamma, mara awven $uôes, ad cehhden fellasen, $ef wayen xeddmen, imeééu$en nnsen, allen nnsen, d igwelman nnsen.'),
(4239, 41, 21, 'Ad inin i igwelman nnsen: "acimi id tcuhhdem fella$"? A d inin: "Issenîeq a$ d Öebbi, id Issentaqen yal cci. Neppa, Ixelq ikwen tikelt tamezwarut, u $uôeS ara tu$alem".'),
(4240, 41, 22, 'Ur tezmirem ara a ppeffrem, ur cehhden fellawen imeééu$en nnwen, allen nnwen, akked igwelman nnwen. Maca, t$ilem ur Iéeô ara Öebbi, aîas n wayen txeddmem.'),
(4241, 41, 23, 'Akka ameyyez nnwen $ef Mass nnwen. Isqucc ikwen, tegwram d d imexsuôen.'),
(4242, 41, 24, 'Xas ûebôen, di tmes ara zed$en. Ma ssutren ssmaê, ur llin d wid ara ipwaqeblen.'),
(4243, 41, 25, 'Nefka yasen imeddukwal i sen icebbêen ayen illan zdat sen, akked wayen illan deffir sen. Iûaô fellasen wawal ger leoyus n yimdanen akw n leonun, i i$aben, uqbel nnsen. Ih, nitni d imexsuôen.'),
(4244, 41, 26, 'Nnan wid ijehlen: "ur ssemêaset i Leqwôan agi. Ssekret fellas, ta$wegwa, ahat a prebêem".'),
(4245, 41, 27, 'A Nessukk $ef wid ijehlen, aâaqeb uqsiê. A ten Nqeîîi sennig wayen xeddmen.'),
(4246, 41, 28, 'D wagi ay d aqeîîi icenga n Öebbi: times; i nitni degs axxam n lebda; d aqeîîi, imi la nekôen issekniyen nne£.'),
(4247, 41, 29, 'Ad inin, wid ijehlen: "a Mass nne$! Essken a$ wid i $ i$elîen, d loenn ne$ d amdan; a ten neôkev, ad u$alen seg wid indellen mavi".'),
(4248, 41, 30, 'Ih, wid innan: "Mass nne$ d Öebbi", sinna, nudan lewqama, a d rsent $uôsen lmalayek: "ur ppagwadet, ur $webblet; ppubeccôet s Loennet i wen ippuwaââden".'),
(4249, 41, 31, 'Nekwni d imawlan nnwen di tmeddurt n ddunit u di laxeôt. Dinna, i kunwi, ayen i cedhant teôwiêin nnwen. Dinna, i kunwi, ayen tessutrem.'),
(4250, 41, 32, 'D tarusi s$uô Win Ipsemmiêen, Ipêunun.'),
(4251, 41, 33, 'Anwa yifen awal umâin n win inaâôen Öebbi, ixeddmen ayen ilhan, id innan: "nek, ih, seg imvuâen".'),
(4252, 41, 34, 'Ur iaâdil ise$ akked tucmip. Err ip akin, s wayen ip yifen. Ma tella cceêna, garak d yiwen, ad iu$al d aêbib i k iêemmlen.'),
(4253, 41, 35, 'Ur teppunefk siwa i wid iûebbôen. Ur teppunefk, siwa i bu sser abarar.'),
(4254, 41, 36, 'Ma iccacev ak Cciîan tuccva, ssuter laânaya n Öebbi. Ih, Neppa d win Isellen, d Amusnaw.'),
(4255, 41, 37, 'Seg issekniyen iS, ass akked yiv, iîij akked waggur. Ur kennut ara i yiîij, ne$ i waggur. Knut i Öebbi, iten id Ixelqen, ma d Neppa ay tâabbdem.'),
(4256, 41, 38, 'Ma zuxxen, ihi, wid illan ar Mass ik, sbuccuâen T iv akked wass, ur âaggun.'),
(4257, 41, 39, 'Seg issekniyen iS: a pwaliv, keçç, akal iqquô; lemmer ad as Nesse$li aman, a d iakwi, ad icuff. Win it id Issadren, d Win ara d Issidren lmeggtin. Ih, Neppa, Izmer i yal cci.'),
(4258, 41, 40, 'Ih, wid issexûaôen issekniyen nne£, ur drigen fellane£. Menyif win ara ipwaveggôen ar tmes, ne$ win ara iasen di laman, ass n tnekra? Xedmet ayen i wen ihwan. Neppa, s tidep, Ipwali ayen txeddmem.'),
(4259, 41, 41, 'Akka, wid inekôen asmekti, mi ten id iusa, u neppat ard Tazmamt tuzmirt.'),
(4260, 41, 42, 'Ur d iusi le$wlav zdat es, ne$ deffir es. D tarusi s$uô Bab n ûûwab, Amaâzuz.'),
(4261, 41, 43, 'Awal i k id iusan, d win kan id iusan imazanen, uqbel ik. Mass ik, ih, ard Bab n ssmaê, d Bab uâaqeb aqeôêan.'),
(4262, 41, 44, 'Lemmer Nerri Leqwôan s tmeslayt tabeôôanit, a d inin: "lemmer feûûlen issekniyen iS s wawal abeôôani, u s taâôabt"? Ini: "neppa, i wid iumnen, d nnhaya u d ccafuâa. Wid ur numin ara, âaégent tmejjin nnsen. Neppa, i nitni, d tider$elt. Widak pwanecden seg umkan ibaâden".'),
(4263, 41, 45, 'Ni$ Nefka yas Tazmamt i Musa. Mgarraden fellas. Lemmer ur d izwar ara wawal s$uô Mass ik, yili tefra garasen. Nitni, fellas, di ccekk imcebbwel.'),
(4264, 41, 46, 'Win ixedmen ayen ilhan, i iman is; win iccven, mgal iman is. Mass ik ur Idennis ara imdanen.'),
(4265, 41, 47, '£uôeS ay tella tmusni n yimir. Ur d iteffe$ uzway si txeddact is, ur treffed nnta tadist, ur tepparew, siwa ma Iéôa. Ass ideg ar asen Isiwel: "anda ten icriken iW"? A d inin: "ad aK nini, ur illi garane$ unagi".'),
(4266, 41, 48, 'Iooa ten wayen u$uô pnujun zik. Fehmen, ur asen illi ssôan.'),
(4267, 41, 49, 'Ur ifeccel ara umdan di tuppra n lxiô. Ma inul it lqeôê, ad iayes, ad innu$ben.'),
(4268, 41, 50, 'Ma Nseêess as aêunu nne£, deffir ccqa i t iêuzan, war ccekk, ad yini: "ayagi inu. Ur cukke$ ara imir a d ias. Ma bbwve$ s afus n Mass iw, ad afe$ $uôeS ûûam". Ih, a Nbeggen ayen xedmen, i wid ijehlen, u, ih, ad Nsâaddi fellasen aâaqeb iwaâôen.'),
(4269, 41, 51, 'Ma N$at amdan ad iwexxeô, izzi akin. Ma iêuza t lêif, ad ipnuju, irennu.'),
(4270, 41, 52, 'Ini: "tmeyyzem ma iusa d s$uô Öebbi, u kunwi tnekôem t"? Anwa innetlafen sennig win illan di ticuîna tu$miqt?'),
(4271, 41, 53, 'Ad asen Nessken issekniyen nne£ di tmurt akked igenwan, u deg iman nnsen, alamma pputebbten ar neppa d tidep. Day ur Iqadd ara Mass ik mi Neppa, war ccekk, d Anagi n yal cci?'),
(4272, 41, 54, 'Day, s tidep, cukken timlilit d Mass nnsen? Day Neppa, s tidep, ur Izzi ara i yal cci?');
INSERT INTO `ber_mensur` (`index`, `sura`, `aya`, `text`) VALUES
(4273, 42, 1, 'Ëm.'),
(4274, 42, 2, 'Âsq.'),
(4275, 42, 3, 'Akka i Iweêêa i keçç, akked wid ik id izwaren, Öebbi, Uzmir, Bab n ûûwab.'),
(4276, 42, 4, 'IneS i illan deg igenwan, i illan di tmurt. Neppa, d Aâlayen, d Ameqwôahan.'),
(4277, 42, 5, 'Qôib ad ccergen igenwan seg ixfawen nnsen, mara d lhint lmalayek deg usbuccaâ s ccekôan n Mass nnsent, u ssuturent ad pwassemêen kra illan di tmurt. War ccekk, Öebbi Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu?'),
(4278, 42, 6, 'Wid irran imawlan, war Neppa, Iquôaâ ten Öebbi. Ur telliv, keçç, d awkil nnsen.'),
(4279, 42, 7, 'Akka ay k n Nweêêa Leqwôan, s taâôabt, iwakken a pnedôev tayimmap n temdinin, akked wayen i s d izzin; a pnedôev af ass n temlilit, ur degs ccekk; arbaâ di Loennet, arbaâ deg ujajiê.'),
(4280, 42, 8, 'Lemmer i S ihwi i Öebbi, yili Izdukkel iten d yiwen n lois. Maca, ad Issekcem win i S ihwan ar uêunu S. Imednas, ur sâin bab ne$ asettaô.'),
(4281, 42, 9, 'Ne$ rran imawlan, war Neppa. Öebbi d Neppa ay d Bab, d Neppa i Issidiren lmeggtin, d Neppa i Izemren i yal cci.'),
(4282, 42, 10, 'Ayen akw i$ef temgarradem, aêuddu s ar Öebbi. Akka Öebbi, Mass iw; fellaS ppekle$, $eô Neppa ay steôoiâe$.'),
(4283, 42, 11, 'Axellaq n tmurt akked igenwan. Seg iman nnwen Irra yawen tiyugiwin; si lmal nnwen, tiyugiwin. Isfukti kwen yisent. Ur illi wayen i T icban. Neppa Issel, Ipwali.'),
(4284, 42, 12, 'IneS tisura n tmurt akked igenwan. Issugut ôôeéq i win i S ihwan, Iwezzen. Ih, Neppa Issen yal cci.'),
(4285, 42, 13, 'Issers awen d, di ddin, ayen i$ef Iweûûa Nuê. Ayen i k Nweêêa, d ayen i$ef Nweûûa Ibôahim, Musa, akked Âisa: "sbeddet ddin, ur ppemgarradet fellas". èÈÈéay, i imcurak, wayen u$uô la ten tneccdev. Öebbi Ippawi $uôeS, win i S ihwan; Inehhu $uôeS, win isteôoiâen.'),
(4286, 42, 14, 'Ur mfaôaqen armi ten id tusa tussna. Ppemvuddun. Lemmer ur d izwar wawal s$uô Mass ik $ef lmijal ipwassnen, yili myefran. Ih, wid iweôten Tazmamt deffir sen, haaten, fellas, di ccekk imcebbwel.'),
(4287, 42, 15, 'Ilmend n waya, enced, ssewqem akken i tepwamôev, ur teddu d cchawi nnsen. Ini: "umne$ s wayen id Issader Öebbi n Tira. Pwamôe$ d ad wezne$ garawen. Öebbi d Mass nne$, u d Mass nnwen. I nekwni igiten nne$, i kunwi igiten nnwen. Ur teppili nnmara garane$. Öebbi ad a$ Issemlil. Tu$alin $uôeS".'),
(4288, 42, 16, 'Wid ipnamaren af Öebbi, deffir wagwav n loawab $uôsen, ur teswi nnmara nnsen, ar Mass nnsen. Fellasen zzâaf, fellasen aâaqeb uqsiê.'),
(4289, 42, 17, 'Öebbi id Issadren Tazmamt, s tidep, akked lmizan. W ad ak imlen, ahat imir iqeôb ed?'),
(4290, 42, 18, 'Ëaren $uôes wid ur numin ara yis. Ma d wid iumnen, ugaden t; éôan ar neppa d tidep. Ih, wid icukken deg imir, haaten, war ccekk, di ttelfan u$miq.'),
(4291, 42, 19, 'Öebbi d Laîif i imdanen iS. Ip$iti win i S ihwan. Neppa d Uohid, d Uzmir.'),
(4292, 42, 20, 'Win ib$an tayerza n laxeôt, ad as Nernu di tyerza ines. Win ib$an tayerza n ddunit, ad as Nefk segs. Ur as illi umur di laxeôt.'),
(4293, 42, 21, 'Ne$ sâan icriken, sse$ôen ten di ddin ur Iqbil Öebbi? Lemmer ur d izwir ara wawal n ufraz, a p fru garasen. I imednas, war ccekk, aâaqeb aqeôêan.'),
(4294, 42, 22, 'A pwaliv imednas feqâen ilmend n wayen kesben, u neppa iddehm ed fellasen. Wid iumnen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan, ad ilin di tebêirin n leonanat. Nnsen i sen ihwan $uô Mass nnsen. D wagi ay d lfevl ameqwôan.'),
(4295, 42, 23, 'D wagi is Ipbecciô Öebbi imdanen iS, wid iumnen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan. Ini: "ur awen ssutre$ taqdiât, af waya, siwa lmaênana i llezm nnwen". Win ixedmen ise$, ad as Nernu degs lehhu. Öebbi, ih, Ipsemmiê, Ippara tajmilt.'),
(4296, 42, 24, 'Ne$ a d inin: "isnulfa d tikerkas af Öebbi". Ma ihwa yaS i Öebbi, ad Icemmaâ ul ik. S wawal iS, ad Isqucc Öebbi tikerkas, ad Iêeqqeq tidep. Ih, Neppa Iéôa tababnit n idmaren.'),
(4297, 42, 25, 'D Neppa i Iqeblen nndama n yimdanen iS. Ipsemmiê tucmitin. Issen ayen txeddmem.'),
(4298, 42, 26, 'Issemêas i wid iumnen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan. Ad asen Irnu si lfevl iS. I ijehliyen, aâaqeb uqsiê.'),
(4299, 42, 27, 'Ma Issuget Öebbi l$it i imdanen iS, ad be$wven di tmurt. Maca, Issrusu d, s lmizan, ayen i S ihwan. Ih, Neppa Ippuxebbeô $ef imdanen iS, Ipwali ten.'),
(4300, 42, 28, 'D Neppa id Isse$layen ageffur mara aysen. Iweppaâ aêunu S. Neppa d Bab, d Amaâzuz.'),
(4301, 42, 29, 'Seg issekniyen iS, lxelq n tmurt, igenwan, akked wayen illan n lewêuc, degsen. Izmer Neppa, ma ihwa yaS, a ten id Issemlil.'),
(4302, 42, 30, 'Kra n tiyta ikwen iwwten, siwa ayen d bbwin ifassen nnwen. Aîas i Ipsemmiê.'),
(4303, 42, 31, 'Ur tezmirem a ppesfunngem di tmurt. Ur awen illi, war Öebbi, bab ne$ asettaô.'),
(4304, 42, 32, 'Seg issekniyen iS, ssfinat di yill, amzun d idurar.'),
(4305, 42, 33, 'Ma ihwa yaS ad Issens avu, ad êebsent, d tusbivin sufella s. War ccekk, ayagi d issekniyen i yal aûebôi isnemmiren.'),
(4306, 42, 34, 'Ne$ a ten Issenger ilmend n wayen kesben. Aîas i Ipsemmiê.'),
(4307, 42, 35, 'Ad éôen wid ipnamaren $ef issekniyen nne£, ar ur asen illi ssôan.'),
(4308, 42, 36, 'Ayen akw i wen ippunefken n wayla, d zzhu n tmeddurt di ddunit. Ayen illan ar Öebbi, yif it; ad idum kteô, i wid iumnen, ippeklen $ef Mass nnsen;'),
(4309, 42, 37, 'wid ijunben ibekkaven ibararen, akked lâaô, u ssurufen i wid i ten isserfan;'),
(4310, 42, 38, 'wid id ipjawaben i Mass nnsen, péallan, ppemcawaôen $ef lameô nnsen, pseddiqen seg wayen iten N$at;'),
(4311, 42, 39, 'wid, ma iusa ten lbe$wv, ad qablen.'),
(4312, 42, 40, 'Aqeîîi n tucmip, d tucmip i p icban. Win isemmêen, issweqmen, arraz is ar Öebbi. Neppa, ih, ur Iêemmel ara imednas.'),
(4313, 42, 41, 'Ma d wid id irran ppaô mi pwadensen, ur telli tiyta degsen.'),
(4314, 42, 42, 'Tiyta, kan, deg wid ivuôôen imdanen, iqehôen di tmurt, war ssebba. I wigi, aâaqeb aqeôêan.'),
(4315, 42, 43, 'Ma d win iûebôen, isemmêen, ayagi, s tidep, d aseyyi n lumuô.'),
(4316, 42, 44, 'Win Itlef Öebbi, ur isâi bab, deffir eS. A pwaliv imednas, mara éôen aâaqeb, ad inin: "ma illa ubrid n tu$alin"?'),
(4317, 42, 45, 'A ten twaliv pwafessren fellas, ndellen, ggaren tiî s tugwdi. Ad inin wid iumnen: "imexsuôen, s tidep, d wid i sxesôen iman nnsen, akked twacult nnsen, ass n tnekra". War ccekk, deg uâaqeb imezgi, ara yilin imednas.'),
(4318, 42, 46, 'Ur asen llin imawlan, ara ten isellken, war Öebbi. Win Itlef Öebbi, ur isâi abrid.'),
(4319, 42, 47, 'Jawbet i Mass nnwen, uqbel a d ias, s$uô Öebbi, ass ur nepwexxiô. Ur awen ippili ssôan assen, ur tezmirem a pnekôem.'),
(4320, 42, 48, 'Ma numren, ur k id Nuzen ara d amêareb nnsen. Ay fellak, siwa timenna. Ih, mara Nesêess i umdan aêunu s$uône£, ad ifôeê yis. Mara t tsami tucmip, id bbwin ifassen is, s tidep, amdan ad ikaraâ.'),
(4321, 42, 49, 'N Öebbi, tagelda n tmurt akked igenwan. Ixelleq ayen i S ihwan. Ippak nnta i win i S ihwan, Ippak ddkeô i win i S ihwan.'),
(4322, 42, 50, 'Ne$ Ipcarak ddkeô d nnta. Isaâqaô win i S ihwan. Ih, Neppa Issen, Izmer.'),
(4323, 42, 51, 'Ur ippunefk ara i umdan, ad as Immeslay Öebbi, siwa aweêêi, ne$ deffir ucembir, ne$ a d iazen amazan iwumi ara Iweêêi, s tsriê iS, ayen Ib$a. Ih, Neppa d Aâlayen, d Bab n ûûwab.'),
(4324, 42, 52, 'Akka ik d Nweêêa ôôuê, si lameô nne£; ur telliv d win issnen d acu p Tezmamt, ne$ liman. Maca, nerra p d tafat. Yis Nenehhu win i £ ihwan, seg imdanen nne£. Ih, d Keçç i ippawin d ubrid uwqim;'),
(4325, 42, 53, 'abrid n Öebbi, i Isâan i illan di tmurt, i illan deg igenwan. War ccekk, ar Öebbi ay teddun lumuô.');
INSERT INTO `ber_mensur` (`index`, `sura`, `aya`, `text`) VALUES
(4326, 43, 1, 'Ëm.'),
(4327, 43, 2, 'S Tezmamt ipbegginen!'),
(4328, 43, 3, 'Nerra p d Leqwôan s taâôabt, amar a pfehmem.'),
(4329, 43, 4, 'Neppa, ih, ata $uône£, ar Tyimmap n Tezmamt, d aâlayan, d uûwib.'),
(4330, 43, 5, 'Day a kwen Nêewwej seg usmekti, imi kunwi d agdud ipêawalen?'),
(4331, 43, 6, 'Acêal id Nuzen d nnbi i imezwura!'),
(4332, 43, 7, 'Ur ten id ippas nnbi, mebla ma mmaâlken fellas.'),
(4333, 43, 8, 'Nemêa wid i ten yifen tazmert. U iûaô umedya imezwura.'),
(4334, 43, 9, 'Ma testeqûav ten: "anwa i Ixelqen tamurt akked igenwan"? A d inin, war ccekk: "Ixelq iten Uzmir, Amusnaw";'),
(4335, 43, 10, 'i wen Irran tamurt d dduê; i wen Igan, degs, iberdan - amendeô ma a ppeppwanhum -;'),
(4336, 43, 11, 'id Isse$layen, seg igenni, aman s lmizan - Nessakway yissen tamurt immuten; akka ara d tekkrem -;'),
(4337, 43, 12, 'id Ixelqen akw tiyugiwin, i wen Ifkan, si sfinat akked lmal, ara trekbem.'),
(4338, 43, 13, 'A pâanncem $ef iârar nnsen; sinna, a d tesmektim l$it n Mass nnwen, mara pâanncem fellasen. A ppinim: "gedha s Win i d Inuben fella$ s waya, ur t nemlik!'),
(4339, 43, 14, 'Ih, a nu$al ar Mass nne$".'),
(4340, 43, 15, 'Ëesben ay T iâabden d amur segS. Amdan, s tidep, d anekkaô n ûûeê.'),
(4341, 43, 16, 'Ne$ day d Iddem tullas seg wayen Ixleq, u Ifren awen d arrac?'),
(4342, 43, 17, 'Ma ibbwev ed usali yiwen segsen, $ef wayen id ifka d amedya i Uênin, ad yibrik wudem is, ad ikkufer:'),
(4343, 43, 18, '"ayen d ikren di rrêuê, ur nessifrir anamer"!'),
(4344, 43, 19, 'Ëesben lmalayek, i illan d ixdimen n Uênin, d nnta. Day êevôen i uxlaq nnsent? Tira $ef ccada nnsen; fellasen asteqsi.'),
(4345, 43, 20, 'Nnan: "lemmer Irad Uênin, yili ur ten naâbbid". Ur sâin kra n tmusni $ef waya. Nitni la pxeôôiven kan.'),
(4346, 43, 21, 'Ne$ Nefka yasen Tazmamt, uqbel Tagi, d$a, degs, îîfen.'),
(4347, 43, 22, 'Xaîi! Nnan: "nufa d, ih, imezwura nne$, di laâqida. D$a, nekwni, Nedda di lateô nnsen".'),
(4348, 43, 23, 'Am akka, ur d Nuzen, uqbel ik, aneddaô ar temdint, mebla ma nnan isâiyen is: "nufa d imezwura nne$ di laâqida. D$a, nedda d lateô nnsen".'),
(4349, 43, 24, 'Inna: "i ma bbwi$ awen d nnhaya yifen tin id tufam ar imezwura nnwen"? Nnan: "nekwni, ihi, nugwi ayen is id teppuceggâam".'),
(4350, 43, 25, 'Nerra d ppaô, segsen. Muqel amek tevôa d inekkaôen.'),
(4351, 43, 26, 'Mi inna Ibôahim i baba s, akked ugdud is: "nek, ur pkka$ deg wayen la tâabdem,'),
(4352, 43, 27, 'kkes ed Win iyi d Ixelqen. D Neppa, s tidep, ara iyi Inhun".'),
(4353, 43, 28, 'Irra t d awal imezgi i texlift is, amar a d u$alen s abrid.'),
(4354, 43, 29, 'U £ate$ ten, nitni akked imezwura nnsen, armi ten id tusa tidep, akked umazan ipbegginen.'),
(4355, 43, 30, 'Mi ten id tusa tidep, nnan: "wagi d ssêur, ihi, nekwni nugi t".'),
(4356, 43, 31, 'Nnan: "A lemmer id ssadren Leqwôan agi ar urgaz ameqwôaêan n snat temdinin"!'),
(4357, 43, 32, 'Day d nitni i ifeôôqen aêunu n Mass ik? D Nekwni i sen Ifeôôqen tamâict nnsen, di tmeddurt n ddunit, u Nessuli kra segsen, tidekkaôin sennig wiyav, iwakken kra, ad sxedmen wiyav. Aêunu n Mass ik yif ayen jemâan.'),
(4358, 43, 33, 'Lemmer maççi yiwen n lois kan ara yilin imdanen, a Nerr tiseddura n lfeîîa i ixxamen n wid inekôen Aênin, akw i tiseddaôin i$ef ara alin;'),
(4359, 43, 34, 'i ixxamen nnsen, tibbura; imîeôêen ideg ara élen;'),
(4360, 43, 35, 'akked uzewweq. Maca, ayagi akw, d astumen i tmeddurt n ddunit. Laxeôt, ar Mass ik, i wid ipêezziben.'),
(4361, 43, 36, 'Win iooan asmekti n Uênin, ad as Nqelled Cciîan, ad as yili d amsaâef.'),
(4362, 43, 37, 'Ih, Nitni veôôifen ten seg ubrid, u $ilen ar nitni pwanhan.'),
(4363, 43, 38, 'Alamma ma iusa d $uône£, inna d: "ah, awufan gari yidek, amecwaô illan ger ugmuv d wayev". A yir amsaâef!'),
(4364, 43, 39, 'Ur kwen infaâ, assa, d awez$i, ma tdensem. Aql akwen tcerkem aâaqeb.'),
(4365, 43, 40, 'Day a pperrev, keçç, aâeééug ad issel, ne$ a ppenhuv ader$al, akked win illan di ttelfan n ûûeê?'),
(4366, 43, 41, 'Amar a k id Nekkes, d$a a d Nerr ppaô segsen;'),
(4367, 43, 42, 'ne$ ak Nessken ayen i sen d Nhegga. £uône£, ih, adabu fellasen.'),
(4368, 43, 43, 'Ïîef deg wayen i k d ippuweêêan. Keçç, war ccekk, aql ak deg ubrid uwqim.'),
(4369, 43, 44, 'Wagi, ih, d asmekti i keçç, akked ugdud ik; deqqal fellawen asteqsi.'),
(4370, 43, 45, 'Steqsi wid id Nuzen, uqbel ik, seg imazanen nne£. Day Nerra, war Aênin, iôebbiten ara âabden?'),
(4371, 43, 46, 'Ni$ Nuzen ed Musa s issekniyen nne£, ar Ferâun akked imvebbôen is. Inna: "nek d amazan n Mass imavalen".'),
(4372, 43, 47, 'Mi sen d ibbwi issekniyen nne£, nitni la ppavsan degsen.'),
(4373, 43, 48, 'Ur asen Nessenâata assekni, siwa ma i$leb gma s. Nesâadda fellasen aâaqeb, amar a d u$alen s abrid.'),
(4374, 43, 49, 'Nnan: "a yaseêêar, nâaô a$ Mass ik, s lemâahda i k Ifka. Nekwni ara nepwanhu".'),
(4375, 43, 50, 'Mi Nessafer aâaqeb fellasen, imiren ad xedâan.'),
(4376, 43, 51, 'Imdeê Ferâun i ugdud is, inna: "a yagdud iw, day maççi inu tagelda n Maseô, akked isaffen agi, i ippazalen seddaw i. Day ur twalam ara?'),
(4377, 43, 52, 'Ne$ nek ur ife$ ara imdelli agi, ur nezmir ad ibeggen?'),
(4378, 43, 53, 'Acimi ur as qqnen ara imeqyasen n uwôe$, ne$ ur d usint ara yides lmalayek, pwazdan t"?'),
(4379, 43, 54, 'Issefqaâ agdud is. Unzen as. Wigi, ih, d agdud ucmit.'),
(4380, 43, 55, 'Mi £ zzaâfen, Nerra d ppaô segsen, Ne$meq iten meôôa.'),
(4381, 43, 56, 'Nerra ten d asmekti u d amedya, i ineggura.'),
(4382, 43, 57, 'Mi sen d ippunefk mmi s n Meryem, d amedya, agdud ik iugwi t.'),
(4383, 43, 58, 'Qqaôen: "ppif iôebbiten nne$, ne$ Neppa"? Qqaôen ak d akka, i nnmara. Ih, nitni d agdud ipmeôéan.'),
(4384, 43, 59, 'Neppa d amdan kan. N$at it, Nerra t d amedya i At Isôail.'),
(4385, 43, 60, 'Lemmer i£ £ ihwi, a Nerr lmalayek di tmurt, deg umkan nnwen.'),
(4386, 43, 61, 'Neppa, s tidep, d ppbut n yimir. Ur ppilit di ccekk fellas. Ddut yidi; wagi d abrid uwqim.'),
(4387, 43, 62, 'Ur kwen issefra$ Cciîan! Ih, neppa d acengu nnwen n ûûeê.'),
(4388, 43, 63, 'Mi n iusa Âisa s issekniyen, inna: "usi$ d $uôwen s ûûwab, ad awen beggne$ kra, seg wayen i$ef temgarradem. Ihi, êezzbet i Öebbi, ta$em iyi awal.'),
(4389, 43, 64, 'Öebbi, s tidep, d Mass iw u d Mass nnwen. Ihi, âabdet eÏ, d wagi ay d abrid uwqim".'),
(4390, 43, 65, 'Mgarraden ikabaren garasen. A tawa$it n wid idensen, ilmend uâaqeb n wass aqeôêan!'),
(4391, 43, 66, 'Day a pôaoun imir, ad asen d ias, deqzalla, nitni ur bnin?'),
(4392, 43, 67, 'Iêbiben, assen, ad u$alen wa d acengu n wa, kkes ed wid ipêezziben.'),
(4393, 43, 68, 'A yimdanen iW, assa, ur telli tugdi fellawen, ur $webblet!'),
(4394, 43, 69, '- Wid iumnen s issekniyen nne£, u llan d imvuâen -'),
(4395, 43, 70, 'Kecmet Loennet, kunwi akked tlawin nnwen, a ppezhum.'),
(4396, 43, 71, 'Ad asen ddewwiôen, s sniwat n uwôe$, akked ibuqalen; degsen ayen cihwant teôwiêin, ayen iqennâen allen. Kunwi, din, ad twekkôem.'),
(4397, 43, 72, 'D tagi ay d Loennet i tweôtem, ilmend n wayen txeddmem.'),
(4398, 43, 73, 'Degs, i kunwi, aîas n izwayen, segsen a ppeççem.'),
(4399, 43, 74, 'Ibe$wviyen, s tidep, deg uâaqeb n Loahennama, ad wekkôen.'),
(4400, 43, 75, 'Ur ipfukku fellasen. Nitni, degs, ad kkufferen.'),
(4401, 43, 76, 'Ur ten Nednis, maca llan, nitni, d imednas.'),
(4402, 43, 77, 'Ad necden: "a Malik, xas ad a$ Iqfeô Mass ik"! A d ini: "war ccekk, a pwellfem"!'),
(4403, 43, 78, 'Ni$ Nusa n $uôwen, s tidep, maca tegwti, degwen, keôhen tidep.'),
(4404, 43, 79, 'Ne$ undin ticeôkep. Ula d Nekwni Neppandi.'),
(4405, 43, 80, 'Ne$ $ilen ur Nsell ara i lesrar nnsen, akked tumlin nnsen. Ihi, imceggâen nne£, $uôsen, pparun.'),
(4406, 43, 81, 'Ini: "lemmer illi mmi s i Uênin, nek d aâbad amenzu".'),
(4407, 43, 82, 'Gedha s Mass n tmurt akked igenwan, Mass n usgeld, mgal ayen pxeôôiven!'),
(4408, 43, 83, 'Anef asen ad nexxôen, ad uraren, alamma mmugren ass nnsen, i sen ippuwaââden.'),
(4409, 43, 84, 'D Neppa ay d Öebbi deg igenni, d Öebbi di tmurt, u d Bab n ûûwab, d Amusnaw.'),
(4410, 43, 85, 'Iôqa Win Ilan tagelda n tmurt, igenwan, akked wayen illan garasen. Iéôa melmi ay d imir. £uüôeS, ara tu$alem.'),
(4411, 43, 86, 'Wid i la naâôen, war Neppa, ur $uôsen kra n ccafuâa, kkes ed inagan n tidep, u nitni éôan.'),
(4412, 43, 87, 'Ma testeqûav ten anwa iten Ixelqen, a d inin, war ccekk, "d Öebbi". Ihi, acimi zzin akin?'),
(4413, 43, 88, 'Timenna s: "a Mass iw! Wigi, s tidep, d agdud ur numin".'),
(4414, 43, 89, 'Wexxeô asen, ini: "tifrat"! Deqqal ad éôen.');
INSERT INTO `ber_mensur` (`index`, `sura`, `aya`, `text`) VALUES
(4415, 44, 1, 'Ëm.'),
(4416, 44, 2, 'S Tezmamt ipbegginen!'),
(4417, 44, 3, 'Nessader ip id, ih, deg iv iôqan. Ih, Nekwni, Nella d ineddaôen!'),
(4418, 44, 4, 'Iban ed degs, yal lameô uûwib.'),
(4419, 44, 5, 'Lameô s$uône£. Ih, Nekwni Nella d wid Ippaznen.'),
(4420, 44, 6, 'Aêunu s$uô Mass ik. Ih, Neppa Isell, d Amusnaw.'),
(4421, 44, 7, 'Mass n tmurt, igenwan akked wayen illan garasen, ma tepputebbtem.'),
(4422, 44, 8, 'Ur illi ôebbi siwa Neppa. Issidir, Ineqq. D Mass nnwen, u Mass n lejdud nnwen, imezwura.'),
(4423, 44, 9, 'Xaîi! Nitni, di ccekk, ppuraren.'),
(4424, 44, 10, 'Qaôaâ ass, ideg ara d iawi igenni, abbu ipbegginen.'),
(4425, 44, 11, 'Ad i$umm imùdanen. Wagi d aâaqeb aqeôêan.'),
(4426, 44, 12, '"A Mass nne$! Kkes a$ aâaqeb; nekwni d lmumnin"!'),
(4427, 44, 13, 'Amek ara sâun asmekti, wanag iusa ten id Umazan ipbegginen?'),
(4428, 44, 14, 'D$a wexxôen as, u nnan: "d aselmad aôehbani". ²'),
(4429, 44, 15, 'Ma Nessenqes awen cwiî uâaqeb, ihi, kunwi, a ppu$alem ar din.'),
(4430, 44, 16, 'Ass ideg ara Neédem fellasen, ééedma tabarart, war ccekk, a d Nerr ppaô.'),
(4431, 44, 17, 'Ni$ Njeôôeb, uqbel nnsen, agdud n Ferâun. Iusa ten id umazan ukyis.'),
(4432, 44, 18, '"Seddut yidi imdanen n Öebbi; nek, $uôwen, d amazan muman.'),
(4433, 44, 19, 'Ur ssem$waôet iman nnwen, zdat Öebbi. Nek, usi$ d $uôwen, s udabu n ûûeê.'),
(4434, 44, 20, 'Nek, ad iyi Isseô Mass iw u d Mass nnwen, ur iyi tôeoomem.'),
(4435, 44, 21, 'Ma ur iyi tuminem ara, aâzlet iyi".'),
(4436, 44, 22, 'Inuj $eô Mass is ar wigi d agdud ibe$wviyen.'),
(4437, 44, 23, '"Awi imdanen iW deg iv. War ccekk, a kwen in vefôen.'),
(4438, 44, 24, 'Eoo ill ildi; nitni, ih, d lâaskeô ara i$emqen".'),
(4439, 44, 25, 'Ay ooan di tebêirin, akked tliwa,'),
(4440, 44, 26, 'igran, ixxamen ukyisen,'),
(4441, 44, 27, 'l$it swayes zehhun!'),
(4442, 44, 28, 'Akka ay ten Nefka d lweôt i ugdud nniven.'),
(4443, 44, 29, 'Ur d run, fellasen, igenni akked tmurt. Ur ggunin.'),
(4444, 44, 30, 'Ni$ Nsellek At Isôail, seg uâaqeb isdullun,'),
(4445, 44, 31, 'si Ferâun, i illan, s tidep, d amnefxi ger imaâfan.'),
(4446, 44, 32, 'S tmusni ay ten Nefren deg imavalen.'),
(4447, 44, 33, 'Nefka yasen seg issekniyen, wid ujeôôeb ipbegginen.'),
(4448, 44, 34, 'Ih, widak la qqaôen:'),
(4449, 44, 35, '"Siwa tameppant nne$ tamezwarut, ur fella$ tanekra.'),
(4450, 44, 36, 'Awit ed imezwura nne$, ma tessawalem tidep"!'),
(4451, 44, 37, 'Menyif nitni ne$ agdud n Tubbaâ, akked wid i ten id izwaren? Nessenger iten. S tidep, nitni llan d ibe$wviyen.'),
(4452, 44, 38, 'Ur Nexliq ara tamurt, igenwan, akked wayen illan garasen, i wurar.'),
(4453, 44, 39, 'Nxelq iten kan s tidep, maca, tegwti degsen, ur ssinen.'),
(4454, 44, 40, 'S tidep, ass n ufraz, ad mlilen meôôa.'),
(4455, 44, 41, 'Ass ideg aêbib ur i$ennu aêbib, s wacemma; nitni ur pwasellken.'),
(4456, 44, 42, 'Kkes ed wid i$ef Iêun Öebbi. Neppa, s tidep, d Uzmir, Ipêunu.'),
(4457, 44, 43, 'Ih, ttejôa n Zaqqum,'),
(4458, 44, 44, 'uççi umednub,'),
(4459, 44, 45, 'am nnêas ifsin, ippayzag di tâabbuvin,'),
(4460, 44, 46, 'akken ppayzagen waman.'),
(4461, 44, 47, '"Ddemt ep, zu$ôet ep, ar pnaûfa ujajiê,'),
(4462, 44, 48, 'sinna, smiret sufella uqeôôu s, aâaqeb ippayzagen".'),
(4463, 44, 49, '"Jeôôeb! Ni$ keçç d uzmir, d ukyis"!'),
(4464, 44, 50, 'Ih, wagi d ayen i la tepcukkum.'),
(4465, 44, 51, 'Wanag wid iêezzben, deg umekkan n laman;'),
(4466, 44, 52, 'di leonanat akked tliwa;'),
(4467, 44, 53, 'lebsa nnsen s leêrir, leêrir iêewwcen. Mqabalen.'),
(4468, 44, 54, 'Akka, a ten Njewweo akked têuôtin lâin.'),
(4469, 44, 55, 'A d ssutren, dinna, yal izwayen, di laman.'),
(4470, 44, 56, 'Ur pjeôôiben, dinna, tameppant, siwa tameppant tamezwarut. Isellek iten seg uâaqeb ujajiê.'),
(4471, 44, 57, 'D lfevl n Mass ik, d wagi ay d rrbeê ameqwôaêan.'),
(4472, 44, 58, 'Nsehhel it kan, s tmeslayt ik, amendeô ma a d mmektin.'),
(4473, 44, 59, 'Ggani, ula d nitni la pganin.');
INSERT INTO `ber_mensur` (`index`, `sura`, `aya`, `text`) VALUES
(4474, 45, 1, 'Ëm.'),
(4475, 45, 2, 'Tarusi n Tezmamt s$uô Öebbi, Uzmir, Bab n ûûwab.'),
(4476, 45, 3, 'Di tmurt akked igenwan, s tidep, llan issekniyen i lmumnin.'),
(4477, 45, 4, 'Di lxelq nnwen, akked wayen id Issefôuôex n lewêuc, d issekniyen i ugdud ipputebbten.'),
(4478, 45, 5, 'Di lemgarda n yiv akked wass, akked wayen id Issrusu Öebbi n ôôeéq, seg igenni - Issidir yis tamurt, deffir tmeppant is -, deg udewwel n wavu, issekniyen i ugdud ipmeyyizen.'),
(4479, 45, 6, 'D wigi ay d issekniyen n Öebbi; Nemmal ak ten, s tidep. Anwa ameslay ara amnen, deffir Öebbi akked issekniyen iS?'),
(4480, 45, 7, 'A ssxev n yal akeddab amednub!'),
(4481, 45, 8, 'Issemêas i issekniyen n Öebbi, qqaôen as ten, sinna, iggernen di tem$weô, amzun ur asen isli. Ihi, becceô it s uâaqeb aqeôêan.'),
(4482, 45, 9, 'Ma illa wayen iwumi isla, seg issekniyen nne£, ad ittihi fellas. I widak, aâaqeb isdullun.'),
(4483, 45, 10, 'Deffir sen Loahennama. Ur ten i$ennu s wacemma wayen kesben akked wayen rran d imawlan, war Öebbi. I nitni, aâaqeb abarar.'),
(4484, 45, 11, 'Tagi d nnhaya. Wid iugin issekniyen n Mass nnsen, fellasen aâaqeb n daâwessu taqeôêant.'),
(4485, 45, 12, 'Öebbi i Inuben fellawen s yill; ipcali, fellas, lbabuô, s lameô iS; a pnadim l$it iS. Amar a ppesnemrem!'),
(4486, 45, 13, 'Inub fellawen s wayen akw illan deg igenwan, akked wayen illan di tmurt. Akw s$uôeS. S tidep, deg waya, d issekniyen i ugdud ismektayen.'),
(4487, 45, 14, 'Ini i wid iumnen ad semmêen i wid ur negguni ara ussan n Öebbi, iwakken ad Ikafi agdud $ef wayen keppben.'),
(4488, 45, 15, 'Win ixedmen ayen ilhan, i iman is; win ifalîan, mgal is. Sinna, ar Mass nnwen tu$alin nnwen.'),
(4489, 45, 16, 'Ni$ Nefka, i At Isôail, Tazmamt, ûûwab, lambiyya. Nôeéq iten s wayen ilhan. Nesmenyaf iten i imavalen.'),
(4490, 45, 17, 'Nefka yasen abeggen si Lameô. Ur mgarraden, armi i ten id tusa tmusni, wa iqheô wa. Ih, Mass ik ad Iêudd garasen, ass n tnekra, $ef wayen i$ef mgarraden.'),
(4491, 45, 18, 'Sinna, Nebbwi k deg ubrid n Lameô. Ddu degs, ur teddu akked chawi n wid ur nessin.'),
(4492, 45, 19, 'Ih, nitni ur ak d ppawin acemma s$uô Öebbi. Imednas, ih, d imawlan wa n wa. Öebbi d Bab n wid ipêezziben.'),
(4493, 45, 20, 'Ayagi d assekni i l$aci, d nnhaya u d aêunu i ugdud ipputebbten.'),
(4494, 45, 21, 'Ne$ $ilen wid imôôeôen iman nnsen s tucmitin, a ten Neêseb am wid iumnen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan, d imuddiren ne$ d lmeggtin. Dir it uêuddu nnsen.'),
(4495, 45, 22, 'Öebbi Ixleq tamurt akked igenwan, s tidep, iwakken yal amdan ad ippuqeîîi af wayen ikseb. Nitni ur pwadensen.'),
(4496, 45, 23, 'Twalav win irran lhawiyya s d ôebbi is? Itelf it Öebbi, asali $uôeS. Iskweô as ul, timejjin, Irra yas aâbôuq af allen is. Anwa ara t inhun, deffir Öebbi? Day u la tesmektayem ara?'),
(4497, 45, 24, 'Nnan: "i illan kan, d tudert nne$, di ddunit. A nemmet, a nidir. Ad a$ in$en kan d akud". £ef ayagi, ur sâin kra n tmusni. Nitni $ilen kan.'),
(4498, 45, 25, 'Ma mlan asen issekniyen nne£ iberrzen, anamer nnsen, siwa mara d inin: "erret ed imezwura nne$, ma tessawalem tidep"!'),
(4499, 45, 26, 'Ini: "Öebbi Issidir ikwen, sinna, Ineqq ikwen. Sinna a kwen Issemlil ass n tnekra, ur illi degs ccekk". Maca, tegwti n yimdanen ur ssinen.'),
(4500, 45, 27, 'N Öebbi, tagelda n tmurt akked igenwan. Ass ideg ara d ias yimir, ass nni, ad xesôen ucmiten.'),
(4501, 45, 28, 'A pwaliv yal lois $ef tgwecrar, yal lois ipwanced ar tezmamt is. Assa, a p$eltem ayen txeddmem.'),
(4502, 45, 29, 'Tagi d tazmamt nne£, tessawal tidep fellawen. Nella Nepjerrid ayen akw txeddmem.'),
(4503, 45, 30, 'Ihi, wid iumnen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan, a ten Issekcem, Mass nnsen, s aêunu S. Wagi d rrbeê n ûûeê.'),
(4504, 45, 31, 'Wanag wid ijehlen: "day ur awen $ôan ara issekniyen iW? Tesme$wôem iman nnwen, tellam d agdud ibe$wviyen".'),
(4505, 45, 32, 'Mi nnan: "ih, lemâahda n Öebbi, d tidep; imir, ur degs ccekk", tennam: "ur neéôi d acu ay d imir; $uône$ d nnwaya kan, ur nepputebbet".'),
(4506, 45, 33, 'Ad asen d vehôent tucmitin xedmen, ad asen izzi wayen i$ef ttihin.'),
(4507, 45, 34, 'Ad asen Inin: "assa, a kwen Neppu, akken teppum timlilit n wass nnwen agi. Axxam nnwen d times, ur awen illi useîîaô.'),
(4508, 45, 35, 'Ayagi, acku kunwi la tettihim $ef issekniyen n Öebbi. T$uôô ikwen tudert n ddunit. Assa, ur d teff$en segs". Ur isti$fiô êedd fellasen.'),
(4509, 45, 36, 'I Öebbi annuz, Mass igenwan, Mass n tmurt, Mass imavalen.'),
(4510, 45, 37, 'I Neppa akw ayen iufraren, di tmurt akked igenwan. Neppa, d Uzmir, d Bab n ûûwab.');
INSERT INTO `ber_mensur` (`index`, `sura`, `aya`, `text`) VALUES
(4511, 46, 1, 'Ëm.'),
(4512, 46, 2, 'Tarusi n Tezmamt s$uô Öebbi, Uzmir, Bab n ûûwab.'),
(4513, 46, 3, 'Ur Nexliq tamurt, igenwan, akked wayen illan garasen, siwa s tidep, ar lajel ipwassnen. Wid ijehlen numren ayen u$uô pwanedôen.'),
(4514, 46, 4, 'Ini: "day ur twalam ara wigi u$uô la tepnujum, war Öebbi? Sseknet iyi d, d acu xelqen si tmurt, ne$ ma sâan amur deg igenwan? Awit iyi d tazmamt id izwaren tagi, ne$ lateô n tmusni, ma tessawalem tidep".'),
(4515, 46, 5, 'Anwa innetlafen sennig wid ipnujun, war Öebbi, $eô wayen ur asen d nepparra, ar ass n tnekra, u nitni stehzan deg unuju nnsen?'),
(4516, 46, 6, 'Mara twafesrem imdanen, ad ilin d icenga nnsen, ad skiddben aâbad nnsen.'),
(4517, 46, 7, 'Ma $ôan asen issekniyen nne£ iberrzen, wid iugin tidep, mi ten id tusa, ad inin: "wagi d ssêur n ûûeê".'),
(4518, 46, 8, 'Ne$ ad inin: "isnulfa t id". Ini: "lemmer it id snulfa$, ur tezmirem ad iyi tsellkem, s wacemma, si Öebbi. Neppa, Yif akw akken Issen, acu têekkum fellas. Iqadd Neppa d Anagi gari yidwen. Neppa, Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu.'),
(4519, 46, 9, 'Ini: "ur lli$, ger imazanen, d win id isnulfuyen. Ur éôi$ acu ara ivôun yidi, ne$ yidwen. La îîafaôe$, kan, ayen iyi d ippuweêêan. Aql i, kan, nek, d aneddaô ipbegginen".'),
(4520, 46, 10, 'Ini: "meyyzet ma, ayagi, s$uô Öebbi, u tnekôem t? Icehhed unagi n At Isôail, $ef lmetl is, d$a iumen. Tesme$wrem iman nnwen". Ih, Öebbi ur Inehhu agdud imednas.'),
(4521, 46, 11, 'Nnan wid ijehlen, i wid iumnen: "lemmer d ayen ilhan, ur a$ zeggwiren $uôes". Imi ur pwanhan ara syis, qqaôen: "ayagi d tikerkas n zik".'),
(4522, 46, 12, 'Uqbel is, Tazmamt n Musa, d nnhaya u d aêunu. Tagi d Tazmamt itebbiten, s wawalen n taâôabt, a ppendeô wid idensen, a ppessefôeê lâuûam.'),
(4523, 46, 13, 'Ih, wid iqqaôen: "Mass nne$ d Öebbi, d$a îfen degs, ur ppagaden, ur $weblen".'),
(4524, 46, 14, 'Widak d at Loennet, degs ad wekkôen, d arraz n wayen xeddmen.'),
(4525, 46, 15, 'Nweûûa amdan ar lewqama s imawlan is. Imma s temêen s tadist, temêen di tinnufra. Ger tadist akked ujumi, caret wagguren. Armi ibbwev d anqaqôi, issawev kuéet isegwasen, inna: "a Mass iw! Eoo iyi a K snemmre$ af l$it i $ T$atev, nek akked lwaldin iw; ad xedme$ ayen ilhan ara K iôavin. Efk iyi d tarwa ilhan. Aql i utube$ K, aql i seg imvuâen".'),
(4526, 46, 16, '£uô wigi, Nqebbel lmefruz igiten nnsen, a Nessuref i tucmitin nnsen, ger at Loennet; d lemâahda n tidep, i sen ippuwaââden.'),
(4527, 46, 17, 'Win innan i imawlan is: "tfuh nnwen! Day yi tâahdem a d kkre$? Ni$ âaddan isuta uqbel i". Nitni teppren tacvaî n Öebbi: "a ssexv ik, amen! Ih, lmâahda n Öebbi, d tidep". A d yini: "ayagi, siwa tiêkayin imezwura".'),
(4528, 46, 18, 'D wigi i$ef iûaô wawal iaânan leoyus n leonun akked yimdanen, i ten id izwaren. Ih, nitni d imexsuôen.'),
(4529, 46, 19, 'I akw tiseddarin n wayen xedmen, iwakken ad yili warraz igiten nnsen. Nitni ur pwadensen.'),
(4530, 46, 20, 'Ass ideg ara kecmen ar tmes, wid ijehlen: "tvegâam tiéidanin i s tezham, di tmeddurt nnwen di ddunit. Assa, a ppeppuqeîîim s uâaqeb isdullun, imi tessem$waôem iman nnwen di tmurt, ur teklalem; imi tellam tbe$wlem".'),
(4531, 46, 21, 'Mmekti d agmat n Âad, mi indeô agdud is deg igidan, u, s tidep, âaddan d ineddaôen zdat es, u zdeffir es: "siwa Öebbi ara tâabdem. Nek ugade$, fellawen, aâaqeb n wass abarar".'),
(4532, 46, 22, 'Nnan d: "day a$ d tusiv, ad a$ tfaôqev akked iôebbiten nne$? Awi a$ d ayen i$ef la $ tessagwadev, ma tessawalev tidep"!'),
(4533, 46, 23, 'Inna: "tamusni ar Öebbi kan. Ssawve$ awen ayen i$ef id ppuceggâa$. Maca, wala$ kwen d agdud ur nessin".'),
(4534, 46, 24, 'Mi t walan d asigna id ileêêun ar t$wezza nnsen, nnan: "wagi d asigna ar a$ d iawin ageffur". Xaîi! D ayen i$ef têarem, d avu, degs aâaqeb aqeôêan;'),
(4535, 46, 25, 'ad isqucc yal cci, s lameô n Mass is. Gwran d ur tepwaliv siwa ixxamen nnsen. Akka i Nepqeîîi igduden ibe$wviyen.'),
(4536, 46, 26, 'Ni$ Nessakrer asen ayen ur awen Nessakrer. Nefka yasen imeééu$en, allen, akked wulawen. Ula i sen d bbwin deg wacemma imeééu$en, allen, akked wulawen, mi skaddben issekniyen n Öebbi. Ayen i$ef ttihin, izzi d fellasen.'),
(4537, 46, 27, 'Ni$ nessenger akw timdinin i wen d izzin, u Nenewwel asent issekniyen, amar a d u$alent s abrid.'),
(4538, 46, 28, 'Acimi ur ten sellken ara wid rran d iôebbiten iééaéan, war Öebbi? Xaîi! Ooan ten. D ayagi ay d tikerkas nnsen, u d wayen id snulfuyen.'),
(4539, 46, 29, 'Mi k ed Nebbwi agraw n leonun, ad ssemêessen i Leqwôan; mi s êedôen, nnan: "êesset"! Mi ifukk, u$alen s agdud nnsen d ineddaôen.'),
(4540, 46, 30, 'Nnan: "a yagdud nne$, aql a$ nesla i Tezmamt id irsen, deffir Musa, id itebbten ayen ip id izwaren, i inehhun ar tidep akked ubrid uwqim.'),
(4541, 46, 31, 'A yagdud nne$, erret awal i uberraê n Öebbi, amnet yiS, ad awen Isemmeê seg ibekkaven nnwen, a kwen Isellek seg uâaqeb aqeôêan".'),
(4542, 46, 32, 'Win isâaweégen i uberraê n Öebbi, ur ipsellik di tmurt, ur ippaf imawlan, war Neppa. Widak di ttelfan n ûûeê.'),
(4543, 46, 33, 'Day ur walan ara ar Öebbi d Win Ixelqen tamurt akked igenwan, ur Ifcil seg uxlaq nnsen? Izmer a d Issider lmeggtin. Ih, Neppa Izmer i yal cci.'),
(4544, 46, 34, 'Ass ideg ara d rsen, ar tmes, wid ijehlen: "maççi s tidep ayagi"? A d inin: "ih, s Mass nne$"! A d Yini: "jeôôbet aâaqeb $ef wayen la tnekôem"!'),
(4545, 46, 35, 'Eûbeô akken ûebôen wid iôeûmen seg imazanen. I nitni, ur p$awal. Ass ideg ara walin acu i sen ippuwaââden, amzun ur kminen siwa saâa n wass. D aberreê: "anwa ara ipwakksen, siwa agdud icemten"?');
INSERT INTO `ber_mensur` (`index`, `sura`, `aya`, `text`) VALUES
(4546, 47, 1, 'Wid ijehlen, u ssefôa$en abrid n Öebbi, Itlef igiten nnsen.'),
(4547, 47, 2, 'Wid iumnen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan, umnen s wayen id irsen ar Muêemmed, u neppa d tidep s$uô Mass nnsen; Issemsa yasen tucmitin nnsen, Iûeggem asen lêala nnsen.'),
(4548, 47, 3, 'Ayagi, acku wid ijehlen îîafaôen tikerkas; ma d wid iumnen, îîafaôen tidep n Mass nnsen. Akka id Ippak Öebbi imedyaten nnsen i imdanen.'),
(4549, 47, 4, 'Mara d temlilem akked wid ijehlen, ewwtet ar tmegrav ar ten t$elbem. Arzet pen nezzeh. Sinna, d aserreê ne$ d feddu, alamma isers îôad tiâekkwmin is. Akka, lemmer i S ihwi i Öebbi, yili I$leb iten, maca a kwen Ijeôôeb, kra s kra. Wid ipwan$an deg ubrid n Öebbi, ur pôuêun igiten nnsen, d awez$i.'),
(4550, 47, 5, 'A ten Inhu, ad Iûeggem lêala nnsen.'),
(4551, 47, 6, 'A ten Issekcem di Loennet i sen Imla.'),
(4552, 47, 7, 'A wid iumnen! Ma tefkam afus i Öebbi, ad awen Ifk afus, ad awen itebbet isurifen.'),
(4553, 47, 8, 'Wid ijehlen, ay amxix nnsen, ad weddôen igiten nnsen.'),
(4554, 47, 9, 'Ayagi, acku ugwin ayen id Issers Öebbi; ihi, Imêa igiten nnsen.'),
(4555, 47, 10, 'Aâni ur nudan ara tamurt, ad walin amek tevôa d imezwura nnsen? Issexv iten Öebbi. Am akka i ijehliyen.'),
(4556, 47, 11, 'Ayagi, acku Öebbi d bab n wid iumnen. Ijehliyen, ur asen illi bab.'),
(4557, 47, 12, 'Ih, Öebbi ad Issekcem wid iumnen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan, di leonanat, ddawat sen isaffen ppazzalen. Wid ijehlen zehhun, teppen akken itepp lmal. D times ay d leqôaô nnsen.'),
(4558, 47, 13, 'Acêal n at temdinin i yifen, di tezmert, tamdint i k id iéâan! Nesqucc iten, ur asen illi useîîaô.'),
(4559, 47, 14, 'Day win illan ar ubeggen n Mass is, am win, iwumi ppucebbêen yir igiten is, u iîîafaôen chawi nnsen?'),
(4560, 47, 15, 'Amek tga Loennet i ippuwaââden i wid ipêezziben: degs isaffen n waman ur nxeppeô, isaffen n yi$i ur tfessed lbenna s, isaffen n ccôab aéidan i wid itessen, isaffen n tament ippuneqqan. Degs, i nitni, yal ppemôa, akked ssmaê n Mass nnsen. Day am wid iwekkôen di tmes; sswan ten s waman ippayzagen, ara icergen afwad nnsen?'),
(4561, 47, 16, 'Llan garasen wid i k issemêasen. Sifat ff$en d s$uôek, ad inin i wid iwumi teppunefk tmusni: "d acu id inna kan, llinna"? Wigi d wid iwumi Isle$ Öebbi ulawen, teddun kan d chawi nnsen.'),
(4562, 47, 17, 'Wid ipwanhan, Irna asen nnhaya, Ifka yasen aêezzeb nnsen.'),
(4563, 47, 18, 'Day la pôaoun kan imir, a ten id ias, deqzalla? Ni$ usant ed licaôat is. Ma iusa d $uôsen, iwumi t usmekti nnsen?'),
(4564, 47, 19, 'Cfu ar, s tidep, ur illi ôebbi siwa Öebbi; ssuter ssmaê ubekkav ik, akked wid n lmumnin, argaz tameîîut. Öebbi Iéôa anda têebkem, akked wanda tberrkem.'),
(4565, 47, 20, 'La qqaôen wid iumnen: "a lemmer a d ters tsuôep"! Maca, mi d ters tsuôep tuêkimt, ideg id ipwader umennu$, a pwaliv at wul iblan, la k id pmuqulen s tiî n win tessexcawat tmeppant. Yif it i nitni'),
(4566, 47, 21, 'wannuz, akked wawal uwqim. Mi ipwagzem ôôay, ma ssawlen tidep ar Öebbi yif it i nitni.'),
(4567, 47, 22, 'Day maççi, ma twexxôem, ahat a ppesfesdem tamurt, a pfaôqem alag nnwen?'),
(4568, 47, 23, 'Wigi d wid i Ixza Öebbi; Isgugem iten, Isder$el iéôi nnsen.'),
(4569, 47, 24, 'Day ur pmeyyizen ara Leqwôan, ne$ u$alent tsergal $ef wulawen?'),
(4570, 47, 25, 'Ih, wid ixedâan, deffir ubeggen n nnhaya $uôsen, ikellex iten Cciîan. Iooa ten tallit.'),
(4571, 47, 26, 'Ayagi, acku nitni nnan i wid iugin ayen d Issader Öebbi: "ad awen na$ awal di kra n lumuô". Öebbi Iéôa lesrar nnsen.'),
(4572, 47, 27, 'Amek ihi, ma ddment lmalayek leôwaê nnsen, la ten kkatent ar udmawen nnsen, iârar nnsen?'),
(4573, 47, 28, 'Akka, ihi, ddan akked wayen isserfayen Öebbi. Ugin llza S. D$a Isseôxes igiten nnsen.'),
(4574, 47, 29, 'Ne$ $ilen at wul amehzul, ard awez$i, ur d Issuffu$ ara Öebbi leb$wev nnsen?'),
(4575, 47, 30, 'Lemmer i £ ihwi, ad ak ten id Nessken, war ccekk, a ten tâaqlev ar udem nnsen, a ten tâaqlev ar ûûenf umeslay. Öebbi Issen igiten nnwen.'),
(4576, 47, 31, 'S tidep, a kwen Njeôôeb, alamma Nessen imjuhad, akked iûebôiyen, segwen. A Njeôôeb isallen nnwen.'),
(4577, 47, 32, 'Ih, wid ijehlen, issefôa$en abrid n Öebbi, i inuqmen Amazan, deffir ubeggen n nnhaya $uôsen, ur vuôôen Öebbi s wacemma. Ad Isseôxes igiten nnsen.'),
(4578, 47, 33, 'A wid iumnen! A$et awal i Öebbi, a$et awal i Umazan, ur ssiôxiset igiten nnwen!'),
(4579, 47, 34, 'Ih, wid ijehlen, issefôa$en abrid n Öebbi, sinna, mmuten d ijehliyen, war ccekk, ur sen Ipsemmiê Öebbi, d awez$i.'),
(4580, 47, 35, 'Ur ppiôhifet, ur ssuturet tifrat, mara tilim d ine$laben! U Öebbi yidwen, ur kwen Ipêewwio, d awez$i, seg igiten nnwen.'),
(4581, 47, 36, 'Tameddurt di ddunit, d urar kan, akked lhawiyya. Ma tumnem u têezbem, ad awen d Ifk arrazen nnwen. Ur awen issutur ayla nnwen.'),
(4582, 47, 37, 'Ma Issuter awen t, a kwen Icebbwel, a pcuêêem, a d iffe$ leb$wev nnwen.'),
(4583, 47, 38, 'D kunwi i ipwanecden a pseddqem deg ubrid n Öebbi. Llan degwen wid ipcuêêun. Win ipcuêêun, ipcuêêu kan $ef yiman is. Öebbi d Asâay, kunwi d igellilen. Ma twexxôem, a kwen Ineûûef s ugdud ur nelli segwen. D$a ur ppemcabin $uôwen.');
INSERT INTO `ber_mensur` (`index`, `sura`, `aya`, `text`) VALUES
(4584, 48, 1, 'Ih, Nefya yak l$elb iberrzen,'),
(4585, 48, 2, 'iwakken ad Isemmeê Öebbi ibekkaven ik id izwaren akked wid igwran. Ad ak Itim l$it iS, a k Iawi d ubrid uwqim.'),
(4586, 48, 3, 'A k Iall Öebbi tallalt tuzmirt.'),
(4587, 48, 4, 'D Neppa id Issersen talwit deg ulawen n lmumnin, iwakken ad yim$uô liman nnsen. N Öebbi Iâsekôiwen n tmurt akked igenwan. Öebbi Izga Iééeô, d Bab n ûûwab.'),
(4588, 48, 5, 'Iwakken ad Issekcem wid akked tid iumnen, ar leonanat, ddawat sen isaffen ppazzalen, degsen ad wekkôen. Ad asen Issemsu tucmitin nnsen. D wagi, ar Öebbi, ay d rrbeê abarar.'),
(4589, 48, 6, 'Ad Iâaqeb ixabiten, tixabitin, imcurak, timcurak, wid id ipfekkiôen Öebbi yir afekkeô. Izzi yasen ddens. Irfa Öebbi fellasen, Ixza ten. Ihegga yasen d Loahennama. A tu$alin tucmip!'),
(4590, 48, 7, 'N Öebbi iâsekôiwen n tmurt akked igenwan. Öebbi Izga d Uzmir, d Bab n ûûwab.'),
(4591, 48, 8, 'Ih, Nuzen ik id d anagi, d abcir, d aneddaô,'),
(4592, 48, 9, 'iwakken a ppamnem s Öebbi akked Umazan iS, a T kfum, ad aS tanzem, a T tesbuccuâem taûebêit, tameddit.'),
(4593, 48, 10, 'Wid iâaqden yidek âaqden kan d Öebbi. Afus n Öebbi nnig ufus nnsen. Win iêenten, d imanis kan i isseênet. Win iîîfen deg wayen i$ef iâuhed Öebbi, ad as Ifk arraz abarar.'),
(4594, 48, 11, 'Ad ak inin wid igwran, seg uâôaben n ucluê: "i $ ice$wlen, d ayla nne$ akked twaculin nne$. Ssuter a neppusemmeê". Qqaôen s yilsawen nnsen, ayen ur nelli deg ulawen nnsen. Ini: "anwa ara kwen iselken si Öebbi, s wacemma, ma Ib$a yawen vveôô, ne$ ma Ib$a yawen aba$uô? Xaîi, Izga Öebbi Ippuxebbeô af wayen txeddmem.'),
(4595, 48, 12, 'Xaîi, t$ilem Amazan akked lmumnin ur d ppu$alen ara, d awez$i, ar twaculin nnsen. Ayagi, issefôeê ulawen nnwen. Nnwaya nnwen dir ip. Kunwi d agdud imsenger.'),
(4596, 48, 13, 'Wid ur numin s Öebbi, akked Umazan iS, ihi, aql a£ Nhegga d ajajiê i ijehliyen.'),
(4597, 48, 14, 'N Öebbi, tagelda n tmurt akked igenwan. Ipsemmiê i win i S ihwan, Ipâuqub win i S ihwan. Öebbi Izga Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu.'),
(4598, 48, 15, 'A d inin wid igwran: "ma tôuêem a d t$eltem, ooet a$ a neddu yidwen". B$an ad bedlen awalen n Öebbi. Ini: "ur teppeddum yidne$, d awez$i. Akka ay d izwar wawal n Öebbi". A d inin: "teêsedm a$"! Xaîi, cwiî kan ay fehhmen.'),
(4599, 48, 16, 'Ini i wid igwran, seg uâôaben n ucluê: "a ppepwanecdem s agdud amaâwaôu, uqsiê; a t tenna$em, ne$ ad anzen. Ma tu$em awal, ad awen Ifk Öebbi arraz igerzen. Ma twexxôem, akken twexxôem uqbel, a kwen Iâaqeb s lqeôê".'),
(4600, 48, 17, 'Ur telli tiyta deg uder$al, ne$ deg urejdal, ne$ deg umuvin. Win iunzen i Öebbi akked Umazan iS, a t Issekcem di leonanat, ddawat sen isaffen ppazzalen. Win iwexxôen, a t Iâaqeb s lqeôê.'),
(4601, 48, 18, 'Ni$ Iôuva Öebbi lmumnin, mi âaqden yidek, seddaw ttejôa. Iéôa i illan deg ulawen nnsen, Issers d fellasen talwit, I$na ten s l$elb aqôib,'),
(4602, 48, 19, 'akked waîas n lerbaê, ara îîfen. Öebbi Izga d Uzmir, d Bab n ûûwab.'),
(4603, 48, 20, 'Iwaââed awen Öebbi a d teîîfem lerbaê aîas. I$awel awen d deg waya. Ikkes fellawen afus n medden. Akken ad yili ussekni i lmumnin, a kwen iawi d ubrid uwqim.'),
(4604, 48, 21, 'Tayev, iwumi ur tezmirem, ihi, Izzi as Öebbi. Öebbi Izga Izmer i yal cci.'),
(4605, 48, 22, 'Lemmer i kwen nnu$en wid ijehlen, ad rewlen, sinna, ur ppafen bab, ne$ asettaô.'),
(4606, 48, 23, 'D tannumi n Öebbi i illan si zik. Ur teppafev abeddel, d awez$i, di tannumi n Öebbi.'),
(4607, 48, 24, 'D Neppa i Ikksen afus nnsen segwen, akked ufus nnwen segsen, di te$zut n Mekka, siwev Iss$elb ikwen fellasen. Öebbi Izga Ipwali ayen txeddmem.'),
(4608, 48, 25, 'D nitni i ijehlen. Swexxôen kwen si Loamaâ n Lêaôam, ugin ad iawev usfel s amkan is. Lemmer maççi d lmumnin, argaz tameîîut, ur ten tessinem, a ten têazem ur teéôim; segsen a d tegwrim di le$ôuô - ni$ Öebbi Issekcam s aêunu S, win i S ihwan - lemmer mfaôaqen, yili, war ccekk, Nesâadda, $ef wid segsen ijehlen, aâaqeb aqeôêan.'),
(4609, 48, 26, 'Mi rran wid ijehlen, aêernun deg ulawen nnsen, aêernun n war tussna, Issers ed Öebbi talwit iS af Umazan iS, akked lmumnin. Iqqen asen awal uêezzeb. Iwata ten, klalen t. Öebbi Izga Iéôa yal cci.'),
(4610, 48, 27, 'Ni$ Issawev Öebbi, i Umazan iS, tamu$li s tidep: war ccekk, a pkecmem Loamaâ n Lêaôam, ma Irad Öebbi, di laman, iqweôôa nnwen ûûeîlen u qeôcen, ur teppagwadem. Iéôa ayen ur teéôim. Ihegga yawen d, ugwar aya, l$elb aqôib.'),
(4611, 48, 28, 'Neppa id Iuznen Amazan iS s nnhaya, akked ddin n tidep, iwakken a t Issifrer $ef ddin meôôa. Iqadd Öebbi d Anagi.'),
(4612, 48, 29, 'Muêemmed d Amazan n Öebbi. Wid illan yides, qesêen ar ijehliyen, êninit garasen. A ten twaliv îîinizen, kennun, ssuturen lfevl s$uô Öebbi akked llza. Ccama nnsen, deg udmawen nnsen, d lateô n lekni. Ata wayen i ten icban di Tuôa akked wayen i ten icban di Linoil: am uâaqqa, iger ed im$i s, isoehd it. Ad iuzur, ad iâaooeô $ef yile$ is. Ippaâoab ifellaêen; i$webben yissen ijehliyen. Iwaââed Öebbi ssmaê akked warraz abarar, i wid degsen iumnen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan.');
INSERT INTO `ber_mensur` (`index`, `sura`, `aya`, `text`) VALUES
(4613, 49, 1, 'A wid iumnen! Ur zeggwiret zdat Öebbi akked Umazan iS. Ëezzbet i Öebbi. Öebbi, s tidep, Issel, d Amusnaw.'),
(4614, 49, 2, 'A wid iumnen! Ur zzuhriyet tu$ac nnwen, sennig ta$wect n Nnbi. Ur zaââvet $uôes, akken tepzaââvam garawen, mulac ad mêun igiten nnwen, kunwi ur tfaqem.'),
(4615, 49, 3, 'Ih, wid issrusun ûut n ta$wect nnsen, ar Umazan n Öebbi, d wid iwumi Issefsi Öebbi ulawen nnsen, ar uêezzeb. Ad asen ippunefk ssmaê akked warraz abarar.'),
(4616, 49, 4, 'Ih, tegwti n wid ik n issawlen, deffir texxamin, ur pmeyyizen.'),
(4617, 49, 5, 'Lemmer ûbiôen ard teff$ev $uôsen, ppif i nitni. Öebbi Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu.'),
(4618, 49, 6, 'A wid iumnen! Aballa$ ma ibbwi yawen d asali, ppuêeqqeqet, mulac a pvuôôem agdud, war tamusni, a ppu$alem tnedmem deg wayen txedmem.'),
(4619, 49, 7, 'Cfut illa garawen Umazan n Öebbi. Ma issemêes awen deg waîas n lumuô, a pjafem. Maca, Öebbi Issaâzez awen liman, Imelleê it deg ulawen nnwen, Isseôéeg awen tijehli, dd$el, lmaâûegga. Widak d wid ipwanhan.'),
(4620, 49, 8, 'D lfevl s$uô Öebbi, d l$it. Öebbi Iéôa, d Bab n ûûwab.'),
(4621, 49, 9, 'Ma nnu$ent snat n îayfat n lmumnin, êuddet pent. Ma tebw$ev yiwet degsent, $ef tayev, nna$et tin ibwe$ven alamma tevfeô lameô n Öebbi. Ma tevfeô it, ssemûalêet pent, s lmizan. Wezznet. Öebbi Iêemmel wid iwezznen.'),
(4622, 49, 10, 'Lmumnin d atmaten kan i illan. Ssemûalêet atmaten nnwen, êezzbet i Öebbi, amar fellawen aêunu.'),
(4623, 49, 11, 'A wid iumnen! £uôwat ad imaâlek ugdud $ef wayev, ahat d widen i ten yifen. Ne$ tilawin $ef tiyav, ahat d tiden i tent yifen. Ur pqeôôidet iman nnwen, ur pmirgamet s tselleqwbin. Dir it isem n dd$el, anda illa liman. Wid ur nutub ara, d widak ay d imednas.'),
(4624, 49, 12, 'A wid iumnen! Janbet aîas n nnwaya. Ih, nnwaya, tikwal, d abekkav. Ur ppemâassat ara. Ur kkatet wa deg wa. Day ib$u yiwen, degwen, ad içç aksum n gmas lmegget? A t tagwim. Ëezzbet i Öebbi. Ih, Öebbi Issuruf, Ipêunu.'),
(4625, 49, 13, 'A yimdanen! Ni$ Nxelq ikwen si ddker akked nnta. Nerra kwen d igduden, d laâôac, a ppemyussanem. Ihi, ukyis nnwen amxallef, ar Öebbi, d win degwen ipêezziben sennig wiyav. Ih, Öebbi Iéôa, Ippuxebbeô.'),
(4626, 49, 14, 'Nnan uâôaben n ucluê: "numen". Ini: "ur tuminem". Maca init ed: "nunez"; ur ikcim ara liman ar wulawen nnwen. Ma tôuvam Öebbi akked Umazan iS, ur awen Isôuêu acemma seg igiten nnwen. Öebbi, s tidep, Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu.'),
(4627, 49, 15, 'Lmumnin d wid kan iumnen s Öebbi akked Umazan iS, d$a, ur pcukun. Pna$en s wayla nnsen akked yiman nnsen, deg ubrid n Öebbi. D widak ay d imawlan n tidep.'),
(4628, 49, 16, 'Ini: "day ad aS temlem i Öebbi, ddin nnwen"? Öebbi Iéôa i illan deg igenwan, i illan di tmurt. Öebbi Issen yal cci.'),
(4629, 49, 17, 'Rran ak annuz nnsen, d tajmilt. Ini: "ur iyi telli tejmilt deg annuz nnwen. Xaîi, d Öebbi ikwen I$aten mi kwen Inha ar liman, ma d imawlan n tidep ay tellam".'),
(4630, 49, 18, 'Ih, Öebbi Issen tabavnit n tmurt akked igenwan. Öebbi Ipwali ayen txeddmem.');
INSERT INTO `ber_mensur` (`index`, `sura`, `aya`, `text`) VALUES
(4631, 50, 1, 'Q. S Leqwôan, mucaâ!'),
(4632, 50, 2, 'Xaîi! Wehmen mi ten id iusa uneddaô, segsen. Nnan ijehliyen: "ayagi d lwehma!'),
(4633, 50, 3, 'Ma nemmut, nu$al d akal, ayagi d tu$alin si mbâid"!'),
(4634, 50, 4, 'Ni$ Neéôa acêal, segsen, i issenqes wakal. £uône£ Tazmamt iêerrzen.'),
(4635, 50, 5, 'Xaîi! Nekôen tidep, mi ten id tusa, d$a terwi lêala nnsen.'),
(4636, 50, 6, 'Day ur muqlen ara igenni, sennig sen, amek i t Nebna? Ncebbeê it, ur isâi i$isan.'),
(4637, 50, 7, 'Tamurt, Nvelq ip, Nerra degs idurar, Nessem$i d degs tayuga n yal ûûenf amxallef,'),
(4638, 50, 8, 'i tmu$li akked usmekti n yal amdan isteôoiâen.'),
(4639, 50, 9, 'Nesse$li d seg igenni aman iôqan. Nessem$i d yissen leonanat akked uâqqa n tmegra,'),
(4640, 50, 10, 'akked tezdayin ti$wezfanin, s ijeooigen mbabben,'),
(4641, 50, 11, 'd ôôeéq i imdanen. Nessider d yissen tamurt immuten. Akka tanekra.'),
(4642, 50, 12, 'Inkeô, uqbel nnsen, ugdud n Nuê, At Rrass, Tamud,'),
(4643, 50, 13, 'Âad, Ferâun, atmaten n Luî,'),
(4644, 50, 14, 'At Laika, akked ugdud n Tubbaâ. Nekôen akw imazanen. Iûaô ussigwed iW.'),
(4645, 50, 15, 'Day £ issefcel uxlaq amezwaru? Wanag nitni di ccekk $ef uxlaq amaynut.'),
(4646, 50, 16, 'Ni$ Nxelq ed amdan. Neéôa s wacu i t t$ewwu, teôwiêt is. Neqôeb $uôes, sennig iéuôan n temgaôt is.'),
(4647, 50, 17, 'Mara îîfen wid ippaîîafen; qqimen, wa $eô yeffus, wa $eô zelmev,'),
(4648, 50, 18, 'ur d iqqaô awal, siwa ma illa $uôes, uâssas imêelles.'),
(4649, 50, 19, 'Iusa d ddux n tmeppant, ibbwi d tidep: "atan wayen iseg la treggwlev".'),
(4650, 50, 20, 'Aûuvu di lbuq. D wagi ay d ass n ussigwed.'),
(4651, 50, 21, 'Yal iman a d ias s unehhaô, akked unagi.'),
(4652, 50, 22, 'Ni$ telliv testehzav $ef waya. Nekkes ak taduli k. Iéôi k, assa, d uzzal.'),
(4653, 50, 23, 'Ad yini umsaâef is: "ata $uôi wayen id ippuheggan".'),
(4654, 50, 24, 'Veggôet, ar Loahennama, yal ajehli amâaûi,'),
(4655, 50, 25, 'i iugwin lxiô, amjuô, imcebbwel,'),
(4656, 50, 26, 'i irran ar tama n Öebbi, ôebbi nniven. Ihi, veggôet ep s aâaqeb uqsiê!'),
(4657, 50, 27, 'A d yini umsaâef is: "a Mass nne$! Ur t rri$ d amjuô, d neppa i illan di ttelfan u$miq".'),
(4658, 50, 28, 'Inna: "ur ppemnamaret ara $uôI, imi wen d Zzewre$ aâggen.'),
(4659, 50, 29, 'Ur ipbeddil $uôI wawal. Nek, ur Ïîuôôu$ imdanen".'),
(4660, 50, 30, 'Ass ideg ara Nini i Loahennama: "ma teççuôev"? A d tini: "ma tella tmerna"?'),
(4661, 50, 31, 'Tqeôb ed Loennet, ar wid ipêezziben, ur tebâad.'),
(4662, 50, 32, '"D tagi i wen ippuwaââden; i yal atubi iêerzen,'),
(4663, 50, 33, 'ippagwaden Aênin di tbavnit, iteddun s wul ucâif.'),
(4664, 50, 34, 'Ekcemt ep, di tifrat, d wagi ay d ass uwekkeô"!'),
(4665, 50, 35, 'Nnsen, dinna, ayen i sen ihwan; s$uône£, timerna.'),
(4666, 50, 36, 'Acêal isuta ay Nesqucc uqbel nnsen! Llan $elben ten di loehd. Qelben, di tmurt, anda t ssôan?'),
(4667, 50, 37, 'Deg waya, s tidep, asmekti i win isâan ul, ne$ ifkan tameééu$t, u d anagi.'),
(4668, 50, 38, 'Ni$ Nxelq ed tamurt, igenwan, akked wayen illan garasen, di sdis wussan, ur Naâyi.'),
(4669, 50, 39, 'Eûbeô i wayen d qqaôen, sbuccaâ s ccekôan Mass ik, uqbel ad inqeô yiîij, uqbel ad i$li.'),
(4670, 50, 40, 'Deg iv sbuccaâ iT, akked deffir lekni.'),
(4671, 50, 41, 'Ssemêes, ass ideg ara d iberreê uberraê, si tama iqeôben.'),
(4672, 50, 42, 'Ass ideg ara slen i usu$u, s tidep, ass nni, d ass n tuff$a.'),
(4673, 50, 43, 'Ih, Nekwni Nessidir u Nneqq. £uône£ tu$alin.'),
(4674, 50, 44, 'Ass ideg ara tceqqeq tmurt $uôsen s tazla. Afesser agi d ayen isehlen fellane£.'),
(4675, 50, 45, 'Nekwni Nif akw akken Neéôa acu id qqaôen. Ur telliv fellasen d aqehhaô. Mmekti d, s Leqwôan, wid ippagwaden aâggen iW.');
INSERT INTO `ber_mensur` (`index`, `sura`, `aya`, `text`) VALUES
(4676, 51, 1, 'S wavu iwezzâen!'),
(4677, 51, 2, 'I ibubben taâkkwemt!'),
(4678, 51, 3, 'Wid ippazalen s shala!'),
(4679, 51, 4, 'Tid ifeôqen lameô!'),
(4680, 51, 5, 'Ar ayen i wen ippuâahden, d tidep.'),
(4681, 51, 6, 'Aqeîîi, ih, ad iûaô.'),
(4682, 51, 7, 'S igenni bu idurra!'),
(4683, 51, 8, 'Kunwi temgarradem $ef wawal.'),
(4684, 51, 9, 'Iooa t win iooan.'),
(4685, 51, 10, 'Tameppant i ikeddaben!'),
(4686, 51, 11, 'Nitni, di maylellif, stehzan,'),
(4687, 51, 12, 'steqsayen: "anda t wass uqeîîi"?'),
(4688, 51, 13, 'Ass ideg, ara ppuhewlen di tmes:'),
(4689, 51, 14, '"Jeôôbet ahewwel nnwen agi i$ef têarem"!'),
(4690, 51, 15, 'Ih, wid ipêezziben, di leonanat akked tliwa;'),
(4691, 51, 16, 'Ïîfen ayen i sen Ifka Mass nnsen. Ih, nitni llan, iu$ lêal, d lâuûam.'),
(4692, 51, 17, 'Deg iv, cwiî ay gganen.'),
(4693, 51, 18, 'Di tafrara, nitni ste$fiôen;'),
(4694, 51, 19, 'deg wayla nnsen: amur i umappar akked ume$bun.'),
(4695, 51, 20, 'U di tmurt, issekniyen i wid ipputebbten.'),
(4696, 51, 21, 'Llant deg iman nnwen. Aâni ur tepwalim ara?'),
(4697, 51, 22, 'U deg igenni, ôôeéq nnwen, akked wayen i wen ippuwaââden.'),
(4698, 51, 23, 'S Mass n tmurt akked igenwan, ar neppa d tidep, am akken kunwi tepmeslayem!'),
(4699, 51, 24, 'Ma tebbwev ik id tedyant inebgawen ukyisen n Ibôahim?'),
(4700, 51, 25, 'Kecmen $uôes, nnan as: "tifrat"! Inna: "tifrat a wid ur nessin!"'),
(4701, 51, 26, 'Inser ar twacult is, ibbwi d aâjmi iqebbwan.'),
(4702, 51, 27, 'Iqeôb asen t id; inna: "day ur teppeppem ara"?'),
(4703, 51, 28, 'Iêus iugad iten. Nnan as: "ur ppagwad"! D$a beccôen t s uqcic amusnaw'),
(4704, 51, 29, 'Tqeôb ed tmeîîut is, tsu$, tewwet deg udem is, tenna d: "tam$aôt tiâiqeôt?"'),
(4705, 51, 30, 'Nnan: "akka id Inna Mass im. Ih, Neppa, d Bab n ûûwab, d Amusnaw".'),
(4706, 51, 31, 'Inna: "anwa ay d awal nnwen, a yimceggâan"?'),
(4707, 51, 32, 'Nnan: "nekwni neppuceggaâ d ar ugdud ibe$wviyen.'),
(4708, 51, 33, 'Iwakken a ten neôoem s uéôu n talaxt'),
(4709, 51, 34, 'i ipwaôecmen s$uô Mass ik i ucmiten".'),
(4710, 51, 35, 'Nessuffe$ kra illan, degs, n lmumnin.'),
(4711, 51, 36, 'Nufa kan degs, yiwen uxxam n imvuâen.'),
(4712, 51, 37, 'Neooa p id d assekni i wid iugaden aâaqeb aqeôêan.'),
(4713, 51, 38, 'I di Musa, mi t id Nuzen i Ferâun, s udabu n ûûeê.'),
(4714, 51, 39, 'Iaâûa, akked imalalen is, inna: "d aseêêar, ne$ d aôehbani".'),
(4715, 51, 40, 'Neddem it, neppa akked iâsekriwen is, Nveggeô iten ar yill. Tiyta degs.'),
(4716, 51, 41, 'I di Âad, mi sen Nuzen avu asexvi.'),
(4717, 51, 42, 'Ur ippaooa ayen immuger, alamma irra t am rrmim.'),
(4718, 51, 43, 'I Tamud, mi pwanecden: "siwa tallit ara tezhum".'),
(4719, 51, 44, 'Âuûan lameô n Mass nnsen. Tewwet iten id ssiâqa, nitni la pwalin.'),
(4720, 51, 45, 'Ur zmiren a d kren, ur pwasellken.'),
(4721, 51, 46, 'Agdud n Nuê, uqbel, llan, s tidep, d agdud iballa$en.'),
(4722, 51, 47, 'Igenni, Nebna t s loehd, d Nekwni it Issewsaân.'),
(4723, 51, 48, 'Tamurt, Nessa p. Ay gerzen Wid Itessun!'),
(4724, 51, 49, 'Di yal cci, Nexleq tayuga, ahat a d tesmektim.'),
(4725, 51, 50, 'Ihi, srifget ar Öebbi. Nek, ih, s$uôeS ar $uôwen, d aneddaô ipbegginen.'),
(4726, 51, 51, 'Ur sâut, ar tama n Öebbi, ôebbi nniven! Nek, ih, s$uôeS ar $uôwen, d aneddaô ipbegginen.'),
(4727, 51, 52, 'Akka, ur iusi umazan ar wid i ten id izwaren, mebla ma nnan as: "d aseêêar ne$ d aôehbani".'),
(4728, 51, 53, 'Day ppuweûûan $ef waya? Xaîi, nitni d agdud izegren tilas.'),
(4729, 51, 54, 'Ïîixxeô asen; ur deg k tiyta.'),
(4730, 51, 55, 'Smektay ed. Asmekti, s tidep, infaâ lmumnin.'),
(4731, 51, 56, 'Xelqe$ leonun akked imdanen, iwakken kan ad iyI âabden.'),
(4732, 51, 57, 'Ur b$i$ segsen ôôeéq, ur b$i$ ad iyi cceççen.'),
(4733, 51, 58, 'Öebbi, s tidep, d Aôeééaq, d Bu tezmert n ûûeê.'),
(4734, 51, 59, 'Ih, i wid idensen, amur am umur imeddukwal nnsen. Ulay$eô iyI $eûben.'),
(4735, 51, 60, 'A tawa$it n wid ijehlen, ilmend n wass i sen ippuwaââden!');
INSERT INTO `ber_mensur` (`index`, `sura`, `aya`, `text`) VALUES
(4736, 52, 1, 'S udrar!'),
(4737, 52, 2, 'S Tezmamt ippujerrden'),
(4738, 52, 3, 'di lka$ev ivelqen!'),
(4739, 52, 4, 'S texxamt iâamôen!'),
(4740, 52, 5, 'S tseddarit aâlayen!'),
(4741, 52, 6, 'S yill icebbwlen!'),
(4742, 52, 7, 'Aâaqeb n Mass ik, s tidep, ad ivôu.'),
(4743, 52, 8, 'Ur isâi ara t sfunngen.'),
(4744, 52, 9, 'Ass ideg ara imbwiwel igenni, d ambwiwel,'),
(4745, 52, 10, 'Ad lêun idurar, d tikli.'),
(4746, 52, 11, 'A ssexv, assen, n wid iskiddiben!'),
(4747, 52, 12, 'Wid inexôen deg uraren.'),
(4748, 52, 13, 'Ass ideg ara pwaveggôen ar tmes n Loahennama, d aveggeô.'),
(4749, 52, 14, 'Apan tmes nni i la tnekôem!'),
(4750, 52, 15, 'D ssêur waya, ne$ d kunwi ur nwala ara?'),
(4751, 52, 16, 'Kecmet ep. Iâuva fellawen, tûebôem, ne$ ur teûbiôem. A ppeppuqeîîim kan $ef wayen txeddmem.'),
(4752, 52, 17, 'Wanag wid ipêezziben, di leonanat, akked zzhu.'),
(4753, 52, 18, 'Feôêen s wayen i sen Ifka Mass nnsen. Isellek iten, Mass nnsen, seg uâaqeb ujajiê.'),
(4754, 52, 19, 'àçet, teswem, di lehna, ilmend n wayen txeddmem!'),
(4755, 52, 20, 'èélen af imîeôêen, d idurra; d tiêuôiyin lâin ukud iten Njewweo.'),
(4756, 52, 21, 'Wid iumnen, u âanden ten, warraw nnsen, ar liman nnsen, a ten Nessemlil akked warraw nnsen. Ur Nessenqas acemma seg igiten nnsen. Yal amdan ad immager ayen ikseb.'),
(4757, 52, 22, 'Ad asen d Nefk izwayen akked uksum seg wayen cedhan.'),
(4758, 52, 23, 'Dinna ad ppemyeppaken lkas, ideg ur illi usîeômel, ne$ ssebba n tuccva.'),
(4759, 52, 24, 'Garasen, ddewiôen ilmeéiyen i nitni, amzun d tiyaqutin mesîuôen.'),
(4760, 52, 25, 'Zzin, kra $er kra, pmesteqsayen.'),
(4761, 52, 26, 'Nnan d: "ni$ nella, zik, di twacult nne$, nugad.'),
(4762, 52, 27, 'I$at a$ Öebbi, Isellek a$ seg ujajiê n tmes.'),
(4763, 52, 28, 'Ni$ nella, zik, nepnuju $uôeS. Neppa, s tidep, d A$eyyat Ipêunun".'),
(4764, 52, 29, 'Ihi, ccfu ar keçç, s l$it n Mass ik, ur telliv d agezzan, ne$ d aôehbani.'),
(4765, 52, 30, 'Ne$, ad inin: "d amedyaz. A naôou asali s akud".'),
(4766, 52, 31, 'Ini: "gganit! Nek, yidwen, seg wid ipganin".'),
(4767, 52, 32, 'Ne$ d tirga nnsen i sen iumôen aya, ne$ nitni d agdud izegren tilas.'),
(4768, 52, 33, 'Ne$ ad inin: "isnulfa t id". Xaîi! Ur uminen.'),
(4769, 52, 34, 'Ihi, a d awin ameslay i t icban, ma d tidep ay ssawalen!'),
(4770, 52, 35, 'Ne$ pwaxelqen seg ulac, ne$ d nitni ay d ixellaqen?'),
(4771, 52, 36, 'Ne$ xelqen tamurt akked igenwan? Xaîi, ur pputebbten!'),
(4772, 52, 37, 'Ne$ $uôsen lexzayen n Mass ik, ne$ nitni d imvebbôen?'),
(4773, 52, 38, 'Ne$ sâan sellum ad ssemêessen, segs. Ihi, win islan segsen, a d iawi adabu n ûûeê!'),
(4774, 52, 39, 'Ne$ i Neppa tullas, i kunwi arrac?'),
(4775, 52, 40, 'Ne$ tessutrev asen taqdiât, fellasen d îîlaba ééayen?'),
(4776, 52, 41, 'Ne$ $uôsen tabavnit, d$a la pparun?'),
(4777, 52, 42, 'Ne$ b$an ad andin? D wid ijehlen ara ipwaîîfen.'),
(4778, 52, 43, 'Ne$ sâan ôebbi, ur Nelli d Öebbi? Gedha s Öebbi, seg wayen pcaraken!'),
(4779, 52, 44, 'Lemmer ad walin amur igenni i$li, ad as inin: "d asigna i izdin".'),
(4780, 52, 45, 'Ihi, eoo iten, ard mlilen d wass n ssiâqa nnsen,'),
(4781, 52, 46, 'Ass, ideg ur asen d teppawi acemma, tandit nnsen; ur asen illi usettaô.'),
(4782, 52, 47, 'I wid idensen, s tidep, aâaqeb nniven, maca tegwti degsen, ur éôin.'),
(4783, 52, 48, 'Eûbeô i wayen d Iêudd Mass ik, aql ak, s tidep, ger wallen nne£. Sbuccaâ s ccekôan Mass ik, mara d tekkrev.'),
(4784, 52, 49, 'Sbuccaâ iT deg iv, u mara xsin yitran.');
INSERT INTO `ber_mensur` (`index`, `sura`, `aya`, `text`) VALUES
(4785, 53, 1, 'S yitri mara ixeppi!'),
(4786, 53, 2, 'Ur innetlaf, ur i$liv umeddakwel nnwen.'),
(4787, 53, 3, 'Ur d iqqaô akken i s ihwan.'),
(4788, 53, 4, 'D aweêêi kan, id ippuweêêan.'),
(4789, 53, 5, 'Islemd it bab n tezmert iqwan.'),
(4790, 53, 6, 'D bab n tezmert irs ed'),
(4791, 53, 7, 'u neppa di lejba aâlayen.'),
(4792, 53, 8, 'Sinna iqeôb ed, ippucengel,'),
(4793, 53, 9, 'atan tasurift n sin ixtucen, ne$ ur tebbwiv.'),
(4794, 53, 10, 'D$a iweêêa i umdan iS, ayen iweêêa.'),
(4795, 53, 11, 'Ur iskaddeb wul deg wayen iwala.'),
(4796, 53, 12, 'Day a t tnaqwmem, $ef wayen iwala?'),
(4797, 53, 13, 'Ni$ iéôa t di trusi s nniven,'),
(4798, 53, 14, 'ar tedxwent n talast,'),
(4799, 53, 15, 'u$uô illa leonan usemlili.'),
(4800, 53, 16, 'Mi tesbur tedxwent ta$wlaft,'),
(4801, 53, 17, 'ur iwweônenni yiéôi, ur izgir.'),
(4802, 53, 18, 'Ni$ iwala kra issekniyen imeqwôaêanen, n Mass is.'),
(4803, 53, 19, 'Twalam Allat akked Lâuzza?'),
(4804, 53, 20, 'Akked Manat, tis krav nniven?'),
(4805, 53, 21, 'Day i kunwi ddkeô, i Neppa nnta?'),
(4806, 53, 22, 'Wagi, ihi, d beîîu aneêyaf.'),
(4807, 53, 23, 'Wigi d ismawen kan i sent tefkam, kunwi akked imezwura nnwen. Ur sent d Issers Öebbi kra udabu. Ïîafaôen kan nnwaya, akked wayen cehwant teôwiêin. Ni$ tusa ten id nnhaya s$uô Mass nnsen.'),
(4808, 53, 24, 'Aâni, i umdan, ayen issaram?'),
(4809, 53, 25, 'Tamezwarut akked tneggarut, n Öebbi.'),
(4810, 53, 26, 'Acêal n lmalayek deg igenwan, ur d teppawi acemma ccafuâa nnsent, siwa deffir tsriê n Öebbi, $ef win Ib$a u Iôuva.'),
(4811, 53, 27, 'Ih, wid ur numin ara di laxeôt, ppaken i lmalayek ismawen n nnta.'),
(4812, 53, 28, 'Ur sâin fellas kra n tmusni. Ïîafaôen kan nnwaya. Wanag nnwaya ur tebbwi acemma si tidep.'),
(4813, 53, 29, 'Ihi, eoo win iwexxôen i usmekti nne£, i ib$an kan tudert n ddunit.'),
(4814, 53, 30, 'D aya ay sen tefka tmusni. Mass ik, war ccekk, Iéôa sennig akw, anwa innetlafen seg ubrid iS; Iéôa sennig akw, anwa i ipwanhan.'),
(4815, 53, 31, 'N Öebbi ayen akw illan deg igenwan, illan di tmurt. Ad Iqeîîi wid ifalîan $ef wayen xedmen, ad Ioazi wid issweqmen, s ûûam.'),
(4816, 53, 32, 'Wid ijunben ibekkaven ibararen akked tucmitin, siwa lfalîat fessusen, ihi, d uwsiâ ssmaê n Mass ik. Neppa Issen ikwen sennig akw, mi kwen id Ixleq seg wakal, mi tellam d icelleqluqen, deg iâabbav n tyimmatin nnwen. Ur staâmilet tezdeg deg iman nnwen! Neppa Iéôa sennig akw, anwa iêezzben.'),
(4817, 53, 33, 'Twalav win iwexxôen,'),
(4818, 53, 34, 'i ifkan cwiî, iccuêen?'),
(4819, 53, 35, 'Day isâa tamusni n tbavnit, d$a iwala?'),
(4820, 53, 36, 'Ne$ ur ippuxebbeô $ef tewôiqin n Musa?'),
(4821, 53, 37, 'Akked Ibôahim ineûêen?'),
(4822, 53, 38, 'Ur ipbibbi yiwen taâkkwemt n wayev.'),
(4823, 53, 39, 'I umdan, siwa ayen inki.'),
(4824, 53, 40, 'Ankay is a t iwali.'),
(4825, 53, 41, 'Sinna, a t Ikafi s lufa.'),
(4826, 53, 42, 'Ih, ar Mass ik, taggara.'),
(4827, 53, 43, 'D Neppa i Issevûan, i Issruyen.'),
(4828, 53, 44, 'D Neppa i Ineqqen, i Issidiren.'),
(4829, 53, 45, 'D Neppa i Ixelqen tayuga, ddkeô akked nnta,'),
(4830, 53, 46, 'Si tiqqit n l$ella ma tuzzel.'),
(4831, 53, 47, 'FellaS, axlaq nniven.'),
(4832, 53, 48, 'D Neppa i I$ennun, i Iqenâan.'),
(4833, 53, 49, 'D Neppa i d Mass n Ciâra.'),
(4834, 53, 50, 'D Neppa i Isnegren Âad imezwura.'),
(4835, 53, 51, 'Si Tamud, ur d Iooi ara.'),
(4836, 53, 52, 'Agdud n Nuê, uqbel nnsen, war ccekk, iugar iten ddens, lbbwe$v.'),
(4837, 53, 53, 'Issenger tid inneqlaben;'),
(4838, 53, 54, 'Idel iten s wayen idellen.'),
(4839, 53, 55, 'Anta talalt n Mass ik ara tnamerev?'),
(4840, 53, 56, 'Wagi d aneddaô seg ineddaôen n zik.'),
(4841, 53, 57, 'A d taéé tin d ippaééen.'),
(4842, 53, 58, 'War Öebbi, ur illi ara p id issdehôen.'),
(4843, 53, 59, 'Iswehm ikwen wawal a?'),
(4844, 53, 60, 'La tdessem ur la tepprum!'),
(4845, 53, 61, 'Kunwi di zzhu.'),
(4846, 53, 62, 'Knut i Öebbi, âabdet.');
INSERT INTO `ber_mensur` (`index`, `sura`, `aya`, `text`) VALUES
(4847, 54, 1, 'Iqeôb ed yimir; ifelleq waggur.'),
(4848, 54, 2, 'Ma walan assekni, ad wexxôen, ad inin: "ipkemmil ssêur"!'),
(4849, 54, 3, 'Nekôen, îîafaôen lemcihwat nnsen. Ad iûaô yal lameô.'),
(4850, 54, 4, 'Ni$ usan ten id kra isallen, u wayen degsen iswexxiôen.'),
(4851, 54, 5, 'Üûwab issakwayen. Maca ula iwumi aâaggen.'),
(4852, 54, 6, 'Ihi, îîixxeô asen! Asmi ara d isiwel, uberraê, ar wayen iwaâôen,'),
(4853, 54, 7, 's wallen ibran, ara d ff$en si tneîlin, am ujôad iwezzâen.'),
(4854, 54, 8, 'Ad éedmen, âaooôen, ar uberraê, ad inin ijehliyen: "wagi d ass uwâiô".'),
(4855, 54, 9, 'Agdud n Nuê, uqbel nnsen, iskaddeb. Skaddben amdan nne$. Nnan: "d aôehbani". Rran t id.'),
(4856, 54, 10, 'Inuj ar Mass is: "nek pwa$elbe$, Awes"!'),
(4857, 54, 11, 'Nelli tibbura igenni, i waman d ihedman,'),
(4858, 54, 12, 'Nesgguffaâ d laânaûeô n tmurt, mlalen waman akken ipwagzem lameô;'),
(4859, 54, 13, 'Nebbwi t af tencirin, akked tavuî n tiffest.'),
(4860, 54, 14, 'Teppeddu zdat wallen nne£, d arraz i win ipwanekôen.'),
(4861, 54, 15, 'Ni$ Neooa p id d assekni. Day llan wid id ismektayen?'),
(4862, 54, 16, 'Amek illa uqeîîi W u llant licaôat iW!'),
(4863, 54, 17, 'Ni$ Nsehhel Leqwôan i usmekti. Day llan wid id ismektayen?'),
(4864, 54, 18, 'Âad skaddben. Amek illa uqeîîi W u llant licaôat iW!'),
(4865, 54, 19, 'Ih, Nuzen asen aûeôûaô, ass amekêus, imezgi.'),
(4866, 54, 20, 'Ippawi medden amzun d iqeôôumen n tezdayin ipwaqelâen.'),
(4867, 54, 21, 'Amek illa uqeîîi W u llant licaôat iW!'),
(4868, 54, 22, 'Nsehhel Leqwôan i usmekti. Day llan wid id ismektayen?'),
(4869, 54, 23, 'Tamud skaddben aâeggen.'),
(4870, 54, 24, 'Nnan: "day a neddu d yiwen n umdan segne$? Ihi, nekwni, war ccekk, di ttelfan, akked tisselbi.'),
(4871, 54, 25, 'Day d neppa, garane$, u$uô id iusa uneddeô? Wanag neppa, d akeddab uqbiê".'),
(4872, 54, 26, 'Ad walin azekka, anwa ay d akeddab uqbiê!'),
(4873, 54, 27, 'A Nazen, ih, tal$wemt i ujeôôeb nnsen. Qaôaâ ten, ili k d aûebôi.'),
(4874, 54, 28, 'Xebbeô iten ar aman ad pwafeôqen. Mkul tissit s tidwelt.'),
(4875, 54, 29, 'Ssawlen i umeddakwel nnsen. Iusa d, igezm as ivaôen.'),
(4876, 54, 30, 'Amek illa uqeîîi W u llant licaôat iW!'),
(4877, 54, 31, 'Nuzen asen d, s tidep, yiwen usu$u. U$alen am alim di tbergent.'),
(4878, 54, 32, 'Nsehhel Leqwôan i usmekti. Day llan wid id ismektayen?'),
(4879, 54, 33, 'Agdud n Luî skaddben aâeggen.'),
(4880, 54, 34, 'Ihi, Nuzen asen ajebwani, kkes ed tawacult n Luî, i Nsellek qbel tafara,'),
(4881, 54, 35, 'd l$it s$uône£. Akka ay Nepkafi wid isnemmiren.'),
(4882, 54, 36, 'Ni$ iâaggen asen, Newâaô. Rran aâeggen di ccekk.'),
(4883, 54, 37, 'Ni$ ssutren t $ef inebgawen is. Nesder$el allen nnsen: "jeôôbet aâaqeb iW, akked uâaggen iW".'),
(4884, 54, 38, 'Iusa ten id, ssbeê zik, uâaqeb imezgi.'),
(4885, 54, 39, 'Jeôôbet aâaqeb iW, akked uâeggen iW!'),
(4886, 54, 40, 'Nsehhel Leqwôan i usmekti. Day llan wid id ismektayen?'),
(4887, 54, 41, 'Ni$ iusa n uâeggen ar twacult n Ferâun.'),
(4888, 54, 42, 'Skaddben issekniyen nne£, meôôa. Naâtad iten s ufus ioehden, izemren.'),
(4889, 54, 43, 'Aâni ijehliyen nnwen ifen wigi? Ne$ tesâam laânaya deg Ihellilen?'),
(4890, 54, 44, 'Ne$ a d inin: "nekwni d agraw ara irebêen"?'),
(4891, 54, 45, 'Agraw ad ixseô, ad wexxôen.'),
(4892, 54, 46, 'Ih, imir d ppaâud nnsen. Imir d lhejna, u ôéag kteô.'),
(4893, 54, 47, 'Ih, ibe$wdiyen di ttelfan akked tisselbi.'),
(4894, 54, 48, 'Asmi ara kkerkren ar tmes, $ef udmawen nnsen: "jeôôbet tanalit ujajiê"!'),
(4895, 54, 49, 'Ih, yal cci, Nxelq it s lmizan.'),
(4896, 54, 50, 'Lameô nne£ siwa yiwen, am unqej n tiî.'),
(4897, 54, 51, 'Ni$ Nesqucc wid i kwen icban. Day llan wid ara d ismektin?'),
(4898, 54, 52, 'Yal igi nnsen deg Ihellilen.'),
(4899, 54, 53, 'Akw, meééi meqqweô, ppujerrden.'),
(4900, 54, 54, 'Wid ipêezziben, s tidep, di leonanat akked isaffen,'),
(4901, 54, 55, 'deg umekkan n tidep, ar Ugellid Uzmir.');
INSERT INTO `ber_mensur` (`index`, `sura`, `aya`, `text`) VALUES
(4902, 55, 1, 'Aênin.'),
(4903, 55, 2, 'Isseêfev Leqwôan.'),
(4904, 55, 3, 'Ixleq amdan.'),
(4905, 55, 4, 'Isselmed as ôôkuz.'),
(4906, 55, 5, 'Iîij akked waggur, s leêsab.'),
(4907, 55, 6, 'Itran akked ttjuô, knan.'),
(4908, 55, 7, 'Igenni, Issuli t; Issers ed lmizan.'),
(4909, 55, 8, 'Ur xedâat di lmizan.'),
(4910, 55, 9, 'Weznet s tidep, ur ssexsaôet lmizan.'),
(4911, 55, 10, 'Issewsaâ tamurt i imexlaq.'),
(4912, 55, 11, 'Degs izwayen, tizdayin sut tkummiwin;'),
(4913, 55, 12, 'iâqqayen s usa$uô, iferrawen utebtil.'),
(4914, 55, 13, 'Anwa seg i$iten n Mass nnwen ara teskiddben, i sin?'),
(4915, 55, 14, 'Ixleq amdan si talaxt, am ujeqduô.'),
(4916, 55, 15, 'Ixleq loenn seg ujajiê n tmessi.'),
(4917, 55, 16, 'Anwa seg i$iten n Mass nnwen ara teskiddben, i sin?'),
(4918, 55, 17, 'Mass n sin igmav, Mass n sin ituram.'),
(4919, 55, 18, 'Anwa seg i$iten n Mass nnwen ara teskiddben, i sin?'),
(4920, 55, 19, 'Iooa sin ilellen ad mqaôaben.'),
(4921, 55, 20, 'Garasen agadir, ur zegren.'),
(4922, 55, 21, 'Anwa seg i$iten n Mass nnwen ara teskiddben, i sin?'),
(4923, 55, 22, 'Teff$ent ed, segsen, tyuqat akked lmeôoan.'),
(4924, 55, 23, 'Anwa seg i$iten n Mass nnwen ara teskiddben, i sin?'),
(4925, 55, 24, 'IneS lembwabeô pwabnan di yill, am idurar.'),
(4926, 55, 25, 'Anwa seg i$iten n Mass nnwen ara teskiddben, i sin?'),
(4927, 55, 26, 'Ad ifut degs kra illan.'),
(4928, 55, 27, 'A d igwri udem n Mass ik, Bab n ccan akked cciâa.'),
(4929, 55, 28, 'Anwa seg i$iten n Mass nnwen ara teskiddben, i sin?'),
(4930, 55, 29, 'Teppren T, yal ass, kra illan di tmurt akked igenwan, Neppa la Ixelleq.'),
(4931, 55, 30, 'Anwa seg i$iten n Mass nnwen ara teskiddben, i sin?'),
(4932, 55, 31, 'A d Nelhi yidwen, a sin iéayanen!'),
(4933, 55, 32, 'Anwa seg i$iten n Mass nnwen ara teskiddben, i sin?'),
(4934, 55, 33, 'A yagraw n leonun akked imdanen, ma tzemrem a pzegrem akin i tmurt akked igenwan, zegret! Ur tepzeggirem siwa ma s udabu.'),
(4935, 55, 34, 'Anwa seg i$iten n Mass nnwen ara teskiddben, i sin?'),
(4936, 55, 35, 'A d teppewwtem s ijujaê n tmes akked nnêas. Ur tepsellikem iman nnwen.'),
(4937, 55, 36, 'Anwa seg i$iten n Mass nnwen ara teskiddben, i sin?'),
(4938, 55, 37, 'Ma ifelleq igenni, iu$al d azeggwa$ am u$eggwad,'),
(4939, 55, 38, '- Anwa seg i$iten n Mass nnwen ara teskiddben, i sin? -'),
(4940, 55, 39, 'assen, amdan ne$ loenn, ur fellas asteqsi $ef ubekkav is.'),
(4941, 55, 40, 'Anwa seg i$iten n Mass nnwen ara teskiddben, i sin?'),
(4942, 55, 41, 'Ibe$wviyen, a d banen ar ccwami nnsen. Ad pwaîîfen seg icebbuben akked ivaôen.'),
(4943, 55, 42, 'Anwa seg i$iten n Mass nnwen ara teskiddben, i sin?'),
(4944, 55, 43, 'D tagi ay d Loahennama i skaddben ibe$wviyen.'),
(4945, 55, 44, 'Ad ddewwiôen garas akked wayen ippayzagen.'),
(4946, 55, 45, 'Anwa seg i$iten n Mass nnwen ara teskiddben, i sin?'),
(4947, 55, 46, 'I win iugaden ibeddi zdat Mass is, sin leonanat.'),
(4948, 55, 47, 'Anwa seg i$iten n Mass nnwen ara teskiddben, i sin?'),
(4949, 55, 48, 'S tzegzew, d imselîen.'),
(4950, 55, 49, 'Anwa seg i$iten n Mass nnwen ara teskiddben, i sin?'),
(4951, 55, 50, 'Degs sin i$bula pfeggiven.'),
(4952, 55, 51, 'Anwa seg i$iten n Mass nnwen ara teskiddben, i sin?'),
(4953, 55, 52, 'Degs yal izwayen, d tiyugiwin.'),
(4954, 55, 53, 'Anwa seg i$iten n Mass nnwen ara teskiddben, i sin?'),
(4955, 55, 54, 'èélen af imîeôêen ippuêewcen; izwayen n sin leonanat wâan asen.'),
(4956, 55, 55, 'Anwa seg i$iten n Mass nnwen ara teskiddben, i sin?'),
(4957, 55, 56, 'Dinna, sut usekkud ipsetêin, ur tent innul yiwen, uqbel nnsen, d loenn ne$ d amdan.'),
(4958, 55, 57, 'Anwa seg i$iten n Mass nnwen ara teskiddben, i sin?'),
(4959, 55, 58, 'Amzun nitenti d lyaqut akked lmeôoan.'),
(4960, 55, 59, 'Anwa seg i$iten n Mass nnwen ara teskiddben, i sin?'),
(4961, 55, 60, 'Nni$ arraz n wayen ilhan, d ayen ilhan?'),
(4962, 55, 61, 'Anwa seg i$iten n Mass nnwen ara teskiddben, i sin?'),
(4963, 55, 62, 'Sin leonanat nniven.'),
(4964, 55, 63, 'Anwa seg i$iten n Mass nnwen ara teskiddben, i sin?'),
(4965, 55, 64, 'S tzegzewt isemmxen.'),
(4966, 55, 65, 'Anwa seg i$iten n Mass nnwen ara teskiddben, i sin?'),
(4967, 55, 66, 'Degsen snat n tliwa gguffant.'),
(4968, 55, 67, 'Anwa seg i$iten n Mass nnwen ara teskiddben, i sin?'),
(4969, 55, 68, 'Degsen izwayen, tizdayin, ôemman.'),
(4970, 55, 69, 'Anwa seg i$iten n Mass nnwen ara teskiddben, i sin?'),
(4971, 55, 70, 'Degsen tiferni akked ûûam.'),
(4972, 55, 71, 'Anwa seg i$iten n Mass nnwen ara teskiddben, i sin?'),
(4973, 55, 72, 'Tiêuôiyin ized$en di texxamin.'),
(4974, 55, 73, 'Anwa seg i$iten n Mass nnwen ara teskiddben, i sin?'),
(4975, 55, 74, 'Ur tent innul yiwen, uqbel nnsen, d loenn ne$ d amdan.'),
(4976, 55, 75, 'Anwa seg i$iten n Mass nnwen ara teskiddben, i sin?'),
(4977, 55, 76, 'Ad élen af imîeôêen izegzawen akked d tôakniwin ilhan.'),
(4978, 55, 77, 'Anwa seg i$iten n Mass nnwen ara teskiddben, i sin?'),
(4979, 55, 78, 'Iôqa ism n Mass ik, Bab n ccan akked cciâa.');
INSERT INTO `ber_mensur` (`index`, `sura`, `aya`, `text`) VALUES
(4980, 56, 1, 'Mara d tas, tin ara d iasen,'),
(4981, 56, 2, '$ef tisin is, ur illi ucehrir.'),
(4982, 56, 3, 'Tessrusu, treffed.'),
(4983, 56, 4, 'Ma tenhez tmurt, lhezz iqesêen,'),
(4984, 56, 5, 'idurar ftutsen,'),
(4985, 56, 6, 'u$alen d a$ebbaô ippuwezzâen,'),
(4986, 56, 7, 'a d tevêum krav leûnaf:'),
(4987, 56, 8, 'at uyeffus. At uyeffus, anwi ten?'),
(4988, 56, 9, 'At uzelmav. At uzelmav, anwi ten?'),
(4989, 56, 10, 'Akked imezwura, imezwura,'),
(4990, 56, 11, 'Widak d iqôiben;'),
(4991, 56, 12, 'di leonanat isaâdiyen.'),
(4992, 56, 13, 'Seg imenza, deg waîas idsen.'),
(4993, 56, 14, 'Seg ineggura, drus nnsen.'),
(4994, 56, 15, '£ef imîeôêen iévan,'),
(4995, 56, 16, 'éélen fellasen, mqabalen.'),
(4996, 56, 17, 'Tezzin asen ilmeéiyen iwekkôen,'),
(4997, 56, 18, 's tbuqalin, iqbucen, akked lkas n tissit iûfan.'),
(4998, 56, 19, 'Yis, ur ppavnen, ur sekkôen.'),
(4999, 56, 20, 'Izwayen, seg wid smenyafen.'),
(5000, 56, 21, 'Aksum n yifôax, seg win cedhan.'),
(5001, 56, 22, 'Tiêuôiyin lâin,'),
(5002, 56, 23, 'am tyaqutin iffren.'),
(5003, 56, 24, 'D arraz n wayen xeddmen.'),
(5004, 56, 25, 'Ur din sellen awal n leqbaêa, ne$ n tuccva;'),
(5005, 56, 26, 'siwa awal n tifrat, tifrat!'),
(5006, 56, 27, 'At uyeffus, at uyeffus, d acu ten?'),
(5007, 56, 28, 'Ar tzegwart, war isennanen.'),
(5008, 56, 29, 'Tulmatin iurwen.'),
(5009, 56, 30, 'Tili iwsâen.'),
(5010, 56, 31, 'Aman ippazalen.'),
(5011, 56, 32, 'Aîas n yizwayen,'),
(5012, 56, 33, 'ur zegzawit, ur ppugedlen.'),
(5013, 56, 34, 'Imîeôêen aâlayen.'),
(5014, 56, 35, 'D Nekwni itent Ixelqen,'),
(5015, 56, 36, 'Nerra tent d tiêuôiyin;'),
(5016, 56, 37, 'pêemmilent, d tizyiwin,'),
(5017, 56, 38, 'i at uyeffus.'),
(5018, 56, 39, 'Seg imenza, deg aîas idsen.'),
(5019, 56, 40, 'Seg ineggura, deg aîas idsen.'),
(5020, 56, 41, 'At uzelmav, at uzelmav, d acu ten?'),
(5021, 56, 42, 'Deg wavu, akked waman iô$an.'),
(5022, 56, 43, 'Tili n wabbu iô$an.'),
(5023, 56, 44, 'Ur degs tasmuvi, lekyasa.'),
(5024, 56, 45, 'Ih, nitni zik, llan ôwan.'),
(5025, 56, 46, 'Zgan deg ubekkav abarar.'),
(5026, 56, 47, 'Llan qqaôen: "ma nemmut, nu$al d akal, akked i$san, day a d a$ d rren?'),
(5027, 56, 48, 'Akked imezwura nne$ imenza"?'),
(5028, 56, 49, 'Ini: "ih, imezwura akked ineggura,'),
(5029, 56, 50, 'ad ppujemmlen ar temlilit n wass ipwassnen".'),
(5030, 56, 51, 'D$a, ih, a yim$eôôqen, i illan d inekkaôen,'),
(5031, 56, 52, 'a ppeççem, war ccekk, si ttejôa n Zaqqum.'),
(5032, 56, 53, 'A ppacaôem segs ifwaden.'),
(5033, 56, 54, 'Sinna, a ppernum tissit seg waman iô$an.'),
(5034, 56, 55, 'A ppetessem tissit ile$wman.'),
(5035, 56, 56, 'D wagi ar asen d irsen, ass uqeîîi.'),
(5036, 56, 57, 'D Nekwni ikwen Ixelqen. Lemmer a ppamnem.'),
(5037, 56, 58, 'Twalam l$ella id iteff$en segwen?'),
(5038, 56, 59, 'D kunwi ip ixelqen, ne$ d Nekwni ay d ixellaqen?'),
(5039, 56, 60, 'Nseyya tameppant garawen. Ur a£ izeggwir yiwen'),
(5040, 56, 61, 'iwakken a Nerr deg umkan nnwen wid i kwen icban; u kunwi, a kwen Nexleq d ayen ur tessinem.'),
(5041, 56, 62, 'Ni$ tesnem axlaq amenzu, lemmer tesmektayem!'),
(5042, 56, 63, 'Twalam ayen tkerrzem?'),
(5043, 56, 64, 'D kunwi i t ikerzen, ne$ d Nekwni ay d imekrazen?'),
(5044, 56, 65, 'Ma ihwa ya£, a t Nerr d uêvim, d$a a kwen tekkat lwehma:'),
(5045, 56, 66, '"Aql a$ nepwalas!'),
(5046, 56, 67, 'Sennig waya: aql a$ neppuêeôôem"!'),
(5047, 56, 68, 'Twalam aman i teppessem?'),
(5048, 56, 69, 'D kunwi iten id isse$layen seg usigna, ne$ d Nekwni?'),
(5049, 56, 70, 'Ma ihwa ya£, a ten Nerr d imeô$anen. A lemmer tesnemmiren!'),
(5050, 56, 71, 'Twalam times i tesskarem s uêukku?'),
(5051, 56, 72, 'D kunwi i s d ixelqen ttjuô is, ne$ d Nekwni ay d Ixellaqen?'),
(5052, 56, 73, 'D Nekwni i p Irran d asmekti, u d lâafia i wid ineêwwaoen.'),
(5053, 56, 74, 'Sbuccaâ, s ccekôan, isem n Mass ik, Ameqwôaêan!'),
(5054, 56, 75, 'Ih, gulle$ seg wanda llan itran!'),
(5055, 56, 76, 'U, tagi, lemmer a ppeéôem, ard tagallit tameqwôaêant!'),
(5056, 56, 77, 'Ar neppa d Leqwôan ukyis,'),
(5057, 56, 78, 'di Tezmamt iffren.'),
(5058, 56, 79, 'Ur t pnalen, siwa wid zeddigen.'),
(5059, 56, 80, 'D tarusi s$uô Mass imavalen.'),
(5060, 56, 81, 'S usali agi, amendeô ma a ppiéidem?'),
(5061, 56, 82, 'S ôôeéq nnwen, kunwi tnekôem?'),
(5062, 56, 83, 'Mara d tawev s agerjum,'),
(5063, 56, 84, 'kunwi, imiren, teppaôoum,'),
(5064, 56, 85, 'Nekwni, sennig wen, i Neqôeb $uôes, maca, ur twalam ara.'),
(5065, 56, 86, 'Xas ma ur tellim d wid ur nepwalas,'),
(5066, 56, 87, 'erret p id, ma tessawalem tidep!'),
(5067, 56, 88, 'Ma illa seg iqôiben,'),
(5068, 56, 89, 'ihi, abeêri, laâîeô, di leonan n ssuâada.'),
(5069, 56, 90, 'Ma illa seg iyeffusen:'),
(5070, 56, 91, '"i keçç tifrat, seg iyeffusen"!'),
(5071, 56, 92, 'Ma illa seg inekkaôen innetlafen,'),
(5072, 56, 93, 'axxam is seg waman ippayzagen,'),
(5073, 56, 94, 'ad iô$ deg ujajiê.'),
(5074, 56, 95, 'Ayagi, ih, d tidep itebbten.'),
(5075, 56, 96, 'Sbuccaâ, s ccekôan, isem n Mass ik Ameqwôaêan!');
INSERT INTO `ber_mensur` (`index`, `sura`, `aya`, `text`) VALUES
(5076, 57, 1, 'Sbuccuâen, s ccekôan Öebbi, ayen akw illan di tmurt akked igenwan. Neppa d Uzmir, d Bab n ûûwab.'),
(5077, 57, 2, 'IneS tagelda n tmurt akked igenwan; Issidir, Ineqq; u Neppa Izmer i yal cci.'),
(5078, 57, 3, 'D Neppa ay d amezwaru, ay d aneggaru; d ayen d ibanen akked wayen iffren. Neppa Iéôa yal cci.'),
(5079, 57, 4, 'D Neppa i Ixelqen tamurt akked igenwan di sdis wussan. Sinna, Iâannec af usgeld. Iéôa i ikeççmen ar tmurt, akked wayen id iteff$en segs, ayen id ippadren seg igenni, akked wayen ippalin $uôes. Neppa yidwen, anda ma tellam. Öebbi Ipwali ayen txedmem.'),
(5080, 57, 5, 'IneS tagelda n tmurt akked igenwan. Ar Öebbi ara u$alen lumuô.'),
(5081, 57, 6, 'Issekcam iv deg wass, Issekcam ass deg yiv. Iéôa ayen illan deg idmaren.'),
(5082, 57, 7, 'Amnet s Öebbi akked Umazan iS! Efket seg wayen i$ef i kwen Irra, degs, d igensas. Wid iumnen segwen, iseddqen, d ameqwôan warraz nnsen.'),
(5083, 57, 8, 'Acu ikwen iu$en, ur tuminem ara s Öebbi? Amazan ipnabi kwen a ppamnem s Mass nnwen. Ni$ $uôes nnesba nnwen, ma tellam d lmumnin.'),
(5084, 57, 9, 'D Neppa id Issadren i umdan iS, issekniyen iberrzen, iwakken a kwen Issuffe$ si tillas ar tafat. Ih, Öebbi, fellawen, d Umâin Ipêunun.'),
(5085, 57, 10, 'Acu ikwen iu$en, ur tepseddiqem deg ubrid n Öebbi? N Öebbi lweôt n tmurt akked igenwan. Ur taâdilem ara: wid iseddqen uqbel l$elb, u nnu$en, widak, ad aâlayen, nezzeh, sennig wid iseddqen sin $er da, u nnu$en. Iwaââed asen akw Öebbi ûûam. Öebbi Iéôa ayen txedmem.'),
(5086, 57, 11, 'Win iôevlen i Öebbi aôeîîal umâin, ad as d Irr s lufa, u ines warraz ukyis.'),
(5087, 57, 12, 'Asmi ara twaliv lmumnin, argaz tameîîut, teddun tafat nnsen zdat sen, u yeffus nnsen: "a lxiô nnwen, assa, di leonanat, ddawat sen isaffen ppazzalen, degsen a pwekkôem! D wagi ay d rrbeê ameqwôaêan".'),
(5088, 57, 13, 'Ass ideg ixabiten, argaz tameîîut, ad inin i wid iumnen: "arout a$, a neddem si tafat nnwen"! A d inin: "u$alet ar deffir, a d tqelbem tafat"! Ad yili garasen lêiv, s tebburt. Zdaxel d aêunu, beôôa, zdat es: aâaqeb.'),
(5089, 57, 14, 'Ad sen d siwlen: "day ur nella ara yidwen"? Ad inin: "ih! Maca, thewwlem iman nnwen, tekkukram, tcukkem, $elvent kwen lemcihwat, armi d iusa lameô n Öebbi. I$elv ikwen af Öebbi, u$ellav".'),
(5090, 57, 15, 'Assa, ur ipwaîîaf feddu segwen, ne$ seg wid ijehlen. Axxam nnwen d times; d neppat ay d bab nnwen. A tu$alin tucmip!'),
(5091, 57, 16, 'Âani maççi d lawan, i wid iumnen, ad rgagin wulawen nnsen ar usmekti n Öebbi, akked wayen id Issers n tidep? Ur ppilin am wid iwumi teppunefk Tezmamt, zik, u tvul fellasen lmudda. D$a qquôen wulawen nnsen; aîas degsen d iballa$en.'),
(5092, 57, 17, 'Ecfut ar Öebbi Issidir tamurt, deffir tmeppant is. Ni$ Nbeggen awen d issekniyen, amendeô ma a pfehmem?'),
(5093, 57, 18, 'Ih, wid akked tid ipseddiqen, iôeîlen i Öebbi aôeîîal umâin, ad asen d Irr s lufa, u nnsen arraz ukyis.'),
(5094, 57, 19, 'Wid iumnen s Öebbi akked imazanen iS, d nitni ay d iêeqqiyen, u d inagan ar Mass nnsen. Ad awin arraz nnsen akked tafat nnsen. Wid ijehlen u skaddben issekniyen nne£, widak d at ujajiê.'),
(5095, 57, 20, 'Cfut ar tameddurt n ddunit d urar kan, d zzhu, d acebbeê, d zzux garawen, asuget n wayla akked derya. Am umedya ugeffur. Im$an is âaoben ijehliyen; sinna, ad isliwen, a ten twaliv ppiwôi$en; d$a ad êevmen. Di laxeôt, aâaqeb uqsiê akked ssmaê s$uô Öebbi, akked llza. Tameddurt n ddunit d zzehwa kan ip$uôôun.'),
(5096, 57, 21, '£iwlet ar ssmaê n Mass nnwen, akked Loennet iwesâan am tmurt akked igenni, teppuhegga d i wid iumnen s Öebbi akked imazanen iS. D wagi ay d lfevl n Öebbi. Ippak it i win i S ihwan. Öebbi d Bab n lfevl ameqwôaêan.'),
(5097, 57, 22, 'Ur d tveôôu twa$it di tmurt, ne$ deg iman nnwen, siwa ma tura di Tezmamt, uqbel a p id Nawi. Ayagi, s tidep, d ayen isehlen i Öebbi.'),
(5098, 57, 23, 'Iwakken ur kwen ip$av wayen tzeglem, ur kwen issefôaê wayen i wen Ifka. Öebbi ur Iêemmel ara yal amzuxi, imnefxi,'),
(5099, 57, 24, 'wid ipcuêêun, iêeppmen ccêa af medden. Win i iwexxôen…ihi, Öebbi d Asâay, d Amaâzuz.'),
(5100, 57, 25, 'Nuzen ed imazanen nne£, s ubeggen. Nessader ed yidsen Tazmamt akked lmizan, iwakken ad ddun imdanen s lêeqq. Nessader ed uzzal, degs vveôô uqsiê, akked uba$uô i medden, iwakken ad Iéeô Öebbi anwa ara ifken afus i Neppa akked imazanen iS, di tbavnit. Ih, Öebbi d Uohid, d Uzmir.'),
(5101, 57, 26, 'Ni$ Nuzen ed Nuê akked Ibôahim. Nerra, si tarwa nnsen, Lambiyya, Tira. Degsen llan wid ipwanhan; aîas segsen d iballa$en.'),
(5102, 57, 27, 'Sinna, Nessevfeô ed, deffir sen, imazanen nne$. Nessevfeô ed Âisa, mmi s n Meryem, Nefka yas Linoil. Nessekcem deg ulawen n wid iddan yides leênana akked tiéeî. Taxelwit, ur p Nuri fellasen; snulfan p id i llza n Öebbi. Ur qumen ara yis, akken iwata. Nefka arraz nnsen i wid iumnen segsen. Aîas, segsen, d iballa$en.'),
(5103, 57, 28, 'A wid iumnen! Ëezzbet i Öebbi. Amnet s Umazan iS. Ad awen Ifk sin imuren seg uêunu S, ad awen Irr tafat a ppeddum yis, ad awen Isemmeê. Öebbi Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu.'),
(5104, 57, 29, 'Akken ad éôen At Tezmamt, ar ur zmiren acemma di lfevl n Öebbi. Ih, lfevl deg ufus n Öebbi; Ippak it i win i S ihwan. Öebbi d Bab n lfevl ameqwôaêan.');
INSERT INTO `ber_mensur` (`index`, `sura`, `aya`, `text`) VALUES
(5105, 58, 1, 'Ni$ Isla Öebbi i wawal n tin i k d ihedôen $ef urgaz is. Tepcetkay i Öebbi. Öebbi Isla i umeslay nnwen. Öebbi, s tidep, Isell, Iéeô.'),
(5106, 58, 2, 'Wid ipmettilen tilawin nnsen ar izugar n tyimmatin nnsen, ur llint d tiyimmatin nnsen - imi tiyimmatin d tid, kan, i ten id iurwen -, ihi, ar d nnan yir awal, akked tikerkas. Ih, Öebbi ard Win Ipsemmiêen, Ipqilin.'),
(5107, 58, 3, 'Wid imetlen, akka, tilawin nnsen, sinna, wexxôen i wayen d nnan, ad brun i wakli, uqbel a tent nnalen. D ayen u$uô i kwen nuban. Öebbi Iéôa ayen txedmem.'),
(5108, 58, 4, 'Win ur newâa ara, ilaq ad iuéum sin wagguren, wa deffir wa, uqbel a p innal. Win, da$en, ur nezmir ara, ad icceçç sdiset igellilen. Akka, iwakken a ppamnem s Öebbi akked Umazan iS. D tigi ay d tilisa n Öebbi. I ijehliyen aâaqeb aqeôêan.'),
(5109, 58, 5, 'Ih, wid ipqamaôen Öebbi akked Umazan iS, ad nneqlaben, akken nneqlaben wid i ten id izwaren. Ni$ Nessers ed issekniyen iberrzen. I ijehliyen, aâaqeb isdullun.'),
(5110, 58, 6, 'Ass ideg ara ten id Issker Öebbi, meôôa, ad asen Issken ayen xedmen. Öebbi Iêesb iten, nitni ppun ten. Öebbi d Anagi n yal cci.'),
(5111, 58, 7, 'Day ur twalav ara ar Öebbi Iéôa i illan di tmurt, i illan deg igenwan? Ur ippili wawal ger krav, mebla ma Illa, Neppa, d wis kué; ne$ ger smus, u Neppa, d wis sdis. Ama seddaw, ne$ sennig waya, ad Yili yidsen, anda ma llan. D$a, ad asen Imel acu xedmen, ass n tnekra. Ih, Öebbi Iéôa yal cci.'),
(5112, 58, 8, 'Ur twalav ara wid i$ef tepwagdel temlilit i umeslay, sinna, u$alen ar wayen i sen ipwagedlen? Ppemlilin i ubekkav, i wanfal, i âaûûu i Umazan. Ma usan k id, ad sellmen fellak s wayen ur d Ipsellim fellak Öebbi. Qqaôen deg ulawen nnsen: "awi d kan ur a$ Ipâuqub ara Öebbi $ef wayen neqqaô"! Loahennama beôka ten. Ad ô$en degs. A tu$alin icemten!'),
(5113, 58, 9, 'A wid iumnen! Ma temlalem i wawal, ur ppemlilit ara i ubekkav, i wanfal, i âaûûu i Umazan. Ppemlilit i tezdeg akked uêezzeb. Ëezzbet i Öebbi u$uô ara tepwafesrem.'),
(5114, 58, 10, 'Timlilit i wawal si Cciîan kan, iwakken ad $weblen wid iumnen. Acemma ur ten iîîuôôu, siwa ma Irad Öebbi. £ef Öebbi ara ppeklen lmumnin.'),
(5115, 58, 11, 'A wid iumnen! Ma nnan awen: "get amkan" di temliliyin, get amkan! Öebbi ad awen Ig amkan. Ma nnan awen: "ooet amkan", ooet amkan! Ad Issali Öebbi tidekkaôin, wid iumnen segwen, akked wid iwumi teppunefk tmusni. Öebbi Iéôa ayen txedmem.'),
(5116, 58, 12, 'A wid iumnen! Ma temlalem i wawal akked Umazan, seddqet uqbel timlilit. Akka i wen ilha, i wen iûfa. Ma ur tewâam ara, ihi, Öebbi Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu.'),
(5117, 58, 13, 'Tekukram a pseddqem uqbel timlilit nnwen? Ma ur tseddqem ara, u Issuref awen Öebbi, ééallet, zekkit, a$et awal i Öebbi akked Umazan iS. Öebbi Iéôa ayen txedmem.'),
(5118, 58, 14, 'Day ur twalav ara wid idduklen akked ugdud i$ef Izzaâf Öebbi? Ur llin segwen ne$ segsen. Pgalan s tkerkas, u nitni éôan.'),
(5119, 58, 15, 'Ihegga yasen d Öebbi aâaqeb uqsiê. Ih, ar dir it wayen xeddmen!'),
(5120, 58, 16, '£ilen tagallit nnsen d ssôan. Swexxiôen seg ubrid n Öebbi. Fellasen aâaqeb isdullun.'),
(5121, 58, 17, 'Ur sen d ippawi acemma wayla nnsen, ne$ dderya nnsen, mgal Öebbi, d awez$i. Widak d at tmes. Degs, nitni, ad wekkôen.'),
(5122, 58, 18, 'Ass ideg ara ten id Issker Öebbi, meôôa, ad aS gallen akken i wen pgallan. Ad $ilen ar ad yili wacu ideg ara îîfen. Aâni maççi, war ccekk, nitni d ikeddaben?'),
(5123, 58, 19, 'Imelk iten Cciîan armi ppun asmekti n Öebbi. Widak d akabar n Cciîan. Ni$ akabar n Cciîan d imexsuôen.'),
(5124, 58, 20, 'Ih, wid ipqamaôen Öebbi akked Umazan iS, widak, ad ndellen sennig wiyav.'),
(5125, 58, 21, 'Iura Öebbi: war ccekk, d Nek akked imazanen iW, ara irebêen. Öebbi, s tidep, d Uohid, d Uzmir.'),
(5126, 58, 22, 'Ur teppafev ara agdud iumnen s Öebbi akked wass aneggaru, ad iddukwel akked wid ipqamaôen Öebbi akked Umazan iS. Xas ma llan d ibabaten nnsen, ne$ d arraw nnsen, d atmaten nnsen, d alag nnsen. Widak, Iura yasen liman deg ulawen nnsen, Iul iten s ôôuê s$uôeS. A ten Issekcem di leonanat, ddawat sen isaffen ppazzalen, degsen ad wekkôen. Öuvan Öebbi, Iôuva ten. Widak d akabar n Öebbi. Day akabar n Öebbi maççi d win ara irebêen?');
INSERT INTO `ber_mensur` (`index`, `sura`, `aya`, `text`) VALUES
(5127, 59, 1, 'Sbuccuâen Öebbi kra illan deg igenwan, akked kra illan di tmurt. Neppa d Uzmir, d Bab n ûûwab.'),
(5128, 59, 2, 'D Neppa i Issuff$en seg ixxamen nnsen wid ijehlen seg At Tezmamt, i ujemmal amezwaru. Ur tuminem ara ad ff$en. £ilen leswaô nnsen a ten sellken si Öebbi. Ikka yasen d Öebbi seg wanda ur bnin. Issekcem tugdi deg ulawen nnsen. Hudden ixxamen nnsen, s ifassen nnsen, akked ifassen n lmumnin. Meyyzet a wid ipwalin!'),
(5129, 59, 3, 'Lemmer ur asen Iura ara Öebbi neffu, yili Iqeîîa ten di ddunit, u, di laxeôt, fellasen aâaqeb n tmes.'),
(5130, 59, 4, 'Ayagi, acku numren Öebbi akked Umazan iS. Win inumren Öebbi, ihi, Öebbi, Iwâaô i uqeîîi.'),
(5131, 59, 5, 'Ayen tgezmem n tezdayin akked wayen teooam beddent af iéuôan nnsent, s wannuf n Öebbi, iwakken a d Isdull iballa$en.'),
(5132, 59, 6, 'Ayen i s Ifka Öebbi, s$uôsen, i Umazan iS, ur tebgisem fellas s ioedâen akked lemrakeb. Maca, Öebbi Ippak adabu i Umazan iS, $ef wid i S ihwan. Öebbi Izmer i yal cci.'),
(5133, 59, 7, 'Ayen Ifka Öebbi i Umazan iS, s$uô at tuddar, n Öebbi akked Umazan iS, llezm is, igujilen, ime$ban, akked win d ibbwi ubrid. Iwakken ur ippu$al ara ger ifassen imeôkantiyen nnwen. Ayen i wen ifka Umazan, ddmet ep. Ayen i wen ikkes, kkset ep. Ëezzbet i Öebbi. Ih, Öebbi, Iwâaô i uqeîîi.'),
(5134, 59, 8, 'I igellilen iminigen, id ssuff$en seg ixxamen nnsen akked seg wayla nnsen, ssaramen lfevl n Öebbi akked llza, fkan afus i Öebbi akked Umazan iS, d widak ay d imawlan n tidep.'),
(5135, 59, 9, 'Wid ized$en ixxamen, iumnen uqbel nnsen, êemmlen wid id iunagen $uôsen. Ur néifen idmaren nnsen af wayen i sen ippunefken, smenyafen ten i iman nnsen, xas ma gwran d xuûûen. Wid irran akin ccêa af yiman nnsen, widak d imerbaê.'),
(5136, 59, 10, 'Wid id iusan deffir sen, qqaôen: "a Mass nne$! Semmeê a$, akked wamaten nne$, i $ d izwaren ar liman. Ur Ppara deg ulawen nne$, a$ullu n wid iumnen. A Mass nne$! Keçç, s tidep, d Umâin Ipêunun".'),
(5137, 59, 11, 'Ur twalav ara ixabiten, la qqaôen i watmaten nnsen ijehlen, seg wAt Tezmamt: "ma ssuff$en kwen, ard a neffe$ yidwen, ur nessemêas i yiwen, d awez$i, mgal nnwen. Ma nnu$en kwen, ar ad awen nefk afus". Ad Icehhed Öebbi, ar nitni d ikeddaben.'),
(5138, 59, 12, 'Ma ssuff$en ten, ur teff$en yidsen. Ma nnu$en ten, ur asen ppaken afus. Ma âawnen ten, ad rewlen; ihi, ur ppâawanen!'),
(5139, 59, 13, 'D kunwi, sennig Öebbi, ay ugaden idmaren nnsen, ayagi, acku nitni d agdud ur nefhim.'),
(5140, 59, 14, 'Ur kwen pna$en, ddukwlen, siwa ma di temdinin ippwaéeôben, ne$ deffir leswaô. Lbe$wv garasen qesseê. A pxilev dduklen, wanag rwin wulawen nnsen. Ayagi, acku nitni d agdud ur nepxemmim.'),
(5141, 59, 15, 'Cban wid i ten id izwaren s cwiî kan, jeôôben lwexda igiten nnsen, fellasen aâaqeb aqeôêan.'),
(5142, 59, 16, 'Cban Cciîan, mi s inna i umdan: "ejhel"! Mi ijhel, inna: "nek mgirrde$ k, nek ugade$ Öebbi, Mass imavalen"!'),
(5143, 59, 17, 'D times, ih, ara yilin d taggara nnsen, ad wekkôen dinna. Ayagi d arraz imednas.'),
(5144, 59, 18, 'A wid iumnen! Ëezzbet i Öebbi. Yal yiwen iwata ad iwali acu ihegga i uzekka. Ëezzbet i Öebbi. Ih, Öebbi Ippuxebbeô $ef wayen txeddmem.'),
(5145, 59, 19, 'Ur ppilit am wid ippun Öebbi. Irra ten, ppun iman nnsen. Widak d iballa$en.'),
(5146, 59, 20, 'Ur aâdilen ara at tmes akked at Loennet. At Loennet d imerbaê.'),
(5147, 59, 21, 'Lemmer id Nessader Leqwôan agi af udrar, a t twaliv iunez, ifelleq, si tugdi n Öebbi. D wigi ay d imedyaten id Neppawi i medden, amar ad meyyzen.'),
(5148, 59, 22, 'Neppa d Öebbi, ur illi ôebbi siwa Neppa, Amusnaw n wayen iffren akked wayen ur neffir. Neppa, d Aênin Ipêunun.'),
(5149, 59, 23, 'D Neppa, ur illi ôebbi siwa Neppa, ay d Agellid, d Ssid, d Tifrat, d Bab n liman, d Aâssas, d Uzmir, d Ajebbaô, d Ameqwôaêan. Gedha s Öebbi, mgal wayen pcaraken!'),
(5150, 59, 24, 'Neppa d Öebbi, d Axellaq, d Bab usisi, d Amessal. I Neppa ismawen imxulaf mavi. Sbuccuâen T akw kra illan di tmurt akked igenwan. Neppa, d Uzmir, d Bab n ûûwab.');
INSERT INTO `ber_mensur` (`index`, `sura`, `aya`, `text`) VALUES
(5151, 60, 1, 'A wid iumnen! Ur ddukulet d icenga W akked icenga nnwen. Teram ten d iêbiben, u nitni nekôen ayen id iusan, $uôwen, n tidep. Èèéaân Amazan, ééaân kwen, imi tumnem s Öebbi, Mass nnwen. Ma teff$em a ppenna$em deg ubrid iW, u tepnadim ôôva W, day a ten terrem, s tuffra, d iêbiben? Nek, Ife$ akw akken èôi$, ayen teffrem akked wayen tennam. Win, segwen, ixedmen akka, innetlaf seg ubrid umâin.'),
(5152, 60, 2, 'Ma $elben kwen, ad u$alen d icenga nnwen, a kwen merten s ifassen nnsen akked yilsawen nnsen, ad ssirmen a pjehlem.'),
(5153, 60, 3, 'Ass n tnekra, ur kwen infaâ walag, ne$ tarwa nnwen, d awez$i. Ad Ifrez garawen. Öebbi Ipwali igiten nnwen.'),
(5154, 60, 4, 'Ni$ illa i kunwi umedya ucbiê di Ibôahim akked wid illan yides, mi nnan i ugdud nnsen: "nemgirred ikwen, kunwi akked wayen teppanzem, war Öebbi. Nenkeô ikwen. Taâdawt akked dd$el, ersen d garane$, i lebda, alamma tumnem s Öebbi Yiwen". Kkes ed awalen i inna Ibôahim, i baba s: "ad velbe$ a ppeppusemmêev, xas ur iyi Ikellef Öebbi, fellak, s wacemma". A Mass nne$! Ppkal nne$ fellaK; nutub iK; $uôeK tu$alin.'),
(5155, 60, 5, 'A Mass nne$ ur a$ Ppara d ahewwel i wid ijehlen. A Mass nne$! Semmeê a$. Ih, Keçç d Uzmir, d Bab n ûûwab.'),
(5156, 60, 6, 'Ni$, i kunwi, amedya nnsen ucbiê, i wid iggunin Öebbi akked wass aneggaru. Ma d win iwexxôen, ihi, Öebbi d Asâay, d Amaâzuz!'),
(5157, 60, 7, 'Ahat Öebbi ad Irr tadukli garawen akked wid, segsen, i illan d icenga nnwen. Öebbi d Uzmir, Öebbi Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu.'),
(5158, 60, 8, 'Ur awen Ikkis ara Öebbi, a pmaânem u tweznem, ar wid ur kwen nepna$ di ddin, ur kwen nessuffu$ seg ixxamen nnwen. Öebbi, s tidep, Iêemmel wid iweznen.'),
(5159, 60, 9, 'I awen Ikkes Öebbi, d tadukli akked wid i kwen ipna$en di ddin, i kwen issuff$en seg ixxamen nnwen, ppaken afus mara kwen ssuff$en. Wid iddan yidsen, widak d imednas.'),
(5160, 60, 10, 'A wid iumnen! Ma usant ed $uôwen tid iumnen, iunagen, jeôôbet pent. Öebbi Iéôa sennig akw liman nnsent. Ma tufam tent d tid iumnen, ur tent pparat ara i ijehliyen. Ur asen êellent, ur asent êellen. Efket asen ayen ûûeôfen. Ulac u$ilif ma tu$em tent, ma tefkam asent tuççit nnsent. Ur pnasabet tijehliyin. Ssutret ayen tûeôôfem, ad ssutren ayen ûûeôfen. Akka ay d aêuddu n Öebbi. Ipêuddu garawen. Öebbi d Amusnaw, d Bab n ûûwab.'),
(5161, 60, 11, 'Ma terwel tmeîîut, si tlawin nnwen, ar ijehliyen, sinna, tâaqbem, efket, ayen ûûeôfen, i wid iwumi ôôuêent tlawin nnsen. Ëezzbet i Öebbi, syiS ay tumnem.'),
(5162, 60, 12, 'A Nnbi! Ma usant ed $uôek tid iumnen, ad ak gallent ur pcarakent i Öebbi acemma, ur ppakwrent, ur zennunt, ur neqqent tarwa nnsent, ur teccvent s ifassen ne$ s ivaôen nnsent, ur k ppâuûunt di lewqama, eôêeb yisent, ssuter i Öebbi ad asent Isemmeê. Öebbi, s tidep, Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu.'),
(5163, 60, 13, 'A wid iumnen! Ur ddukulet akked agdud i$ef Izzâaf Öebbi. Ni$ uysen laxeôt, akken uysen ijehliyen wid illan di tneîlin.');
INSERT INTO `ber_mensur` (`index`, `sura`, `aya`, `text`) VALUES
(5164, 61, 1, 'Sbuccuâen Öebbi, kra illan deg igenwan, akked kra illan di tmurt. Neppa d Uzmir, d Bab n ûûwab.'),
(5165, 61, 2, 'A wid iumnen! Acimi id teqqaôem ayen ur txeddmem?'),
(5166, 61, 3, 'D lâaô meqqwôen, ar Öebbi, ma teqqaôem ayen ur txeddmem.'),
(5167, 61, 4, 'Ih, Öebbi Iêemmel wid ipna$en deg ubrid iS, d ûûef, nitni, amzun d lebni, iéevêen.'),
(5168, 61, 5, 'Mi inna Musa i ugdud is: "a yagdud iw! Acimi la yi teîîuôum, u ni$ teéôam nek d amazan n Öebbi $uôwen"? Mi ff$en i ubrid, Öebbi Issuffe$ i ubrid ulawen nnsen. Öebbi ur Inehhu ara agdud iballa$en.'),
(5169, 61, 6, 'Mi inna Âisa, mmi s n Meryem: "A yAt Isôail! Nek d amazan n Öebbi $uôwen, ad tebbte$ ayen iyi d izwaren n Tuôa. U a kwen beccôe$ s Umazan ara d iasen, deffir i, ism is Aêmed". Mi ten id iusa s ubeggen, nnan: "wagi d ssêur n ûûeê".'),
(5170, 61, 7, 'Anwa idensen sennig win id igren tikerkas af Öebbi, u neppa ipwanced ar wannuz? Öebbi ur Inehhu agdud imednas.'),
(5171, 61, 8, 'B$an ad ssexsin tafat n Öebbi, s imawen nnsen. Öebbi ad Itim tafat iS, di nneqwma ijehliyen.'),
(5172, 61, 9, 'D Neppa id Iuznen Amazan iS, s nnhaya, d ddin n tidep, iwakken a t issifrir f ddin meôôa, di nneqwma ijehliyen.'),
(5173, 61, 10, 'A wid iumnen! Ma d awen Mle$ ssuq ara kwen isellken seg uâaqeb aqeôêan?'),
(5174, 61, 11, 'Amnet s Öebbi akked Umazan iS. Nna$et deg ubrid n Öebbi s wayla nnwen, u s yiman nnwen; ppif akka i kunwi, lemmer tessinem.'),
(5175, 61, 12, 'Ad awen Isemmeê ibekkaven nnwen; a kwen Issekcem ar leonanat degsen isaffen ppazzalen, tinezdu$in igerzen, di leonanat n Âaden; d wagi ay d rrbeê ameqwôaêan.'),
(5176, 61, 13, 'Ayen têemmlem nniven: afus s$uô Öebbi akked l$elb aqôib. Ssefôeê lmumnin.'),
(5177, 61, 14, 'A wid iumnen! Illit d iwiziwen n Öebbi, akken inna Âisa, mmi s n Meryem, i inmahalen is: "anwi ay d iwiziwen iw ar Öebbi"? Nnan d inmahalen: "nekwni d iwiziwen n Öebbi". Tumen terbaât, tejhel terbaât, n At Isôail. Nefka afus i wid iumnen, mgal icenga nnsen, d$a rebêen.');
INSERT INTO `ber_mensur` (`index`, `sura`, `aya`, `text`) VALUES
(5178, 62, 1, 'Sbuccuâen Öebbi, kra illan deg igenwan, u kra illan di tmurt. Agellid, Ssid, Uzmir, Bab n ûûwab.'),
(5179, 62, 2, 'D Neppa id Iuznen i wid ur ne$ôi, Amazan segsen, iqqaô asen issekniyen iS. Izizdig iten, isselmad asen Tazmamt akked ûûwab, xas llan, zik, di ttelfan n ûûeê.'),
(5180, 62, 3, 'U i wid nniven, mara awven $uôsen. Neppa, d Uzmir, d Bab n ûûwab.'),
(5181, 62, 4, 'D wagi ay d lfevl n Öebbi. Ippak it i win Ib$a. Öebbi, d bab n lfevl ameqwôahan.'),
(5182, 62, 5, 'Am wid iwumi ippukelfen s Tuôa, ur p ssawven. Cuban a$yul ibubben tizmamin. I icmet umedya n ugdud inekôen issekniyen n Öebbi! Öebbi ur Inehhu ara agdud imednas.'),
(5183, 62, 6, 'Ini: "a yudayen, ma t$ilem d kunwi ay d iêbiben n Öebbi, war imdanen, ssutret tameppant, ma tessawalem tidep"!'),
(5184, 62, 7, 'Ur p ssuturen ara, d awez$i, ilmend igiten nnsen. Öebbi Issen imednas.'),
(5185, 62, 8, 'Ini: "tameppant iwumi tregwlem, a kwen id temmager, war ccekk. Sinna, a kwen awin ar Win Iéôan ayen iffren akked wayen ur neffir. Ad awen Imel ayen txeddmem".'),
(5186, 62, 9, 'A wid iumnen! Ma ssawlen d i téallit, ass unejmuâ, $iwlet ar usmekti n Öebbi, êebset ttjaôa. Ppif akka i kunwi, lemmer tessinem.'),
(5187, 62, 10, 'Mi tfukk téallit, mfaôaqet di tmurt, nadit lfevl n Öebbi, mmektit ed aîas Öebbi, amar a prebêem.'),
(5188, 62, 11, 'Mi walan ssuq, ne$ anecôeê, ad azlen $uôes, a k ooen tbeddev. Ini: "ayen illan ar Öebbi yif anecôeê akked ssuq. Öebbi Yif akw iôeééaqen".');
INSERT INTO `ber_mensur` (`index`, `sura`, `aya`, `text`) VALUES
(5189, 63, 1, 'Ma usan d $uôek ixabiten, ad ak inin: "a ncehhed ar keçç, war ccekk, d Amazan n Öebbi". Öebbi Iéôa ar keçç, war ccekk, d Amazan iS. Öebbi ad Icehhed ar, s tidep, ixabiten d ikeddaben.'),
(5190, 63, 2, 'Ëesben tagallit nnsen d laânaya, d$a ssefôa$en abrid n Öebbi. Ihi, a yicmet wayen xeddmen!'),
(5191, 63, 3, 'Akka, acku llan umnen, sinna, jehlen. Ppusel$en wulawen nnsen, d$a nitni ur mêiûen.'),
(5192, 63, 4, 'Mi ten twalav, a k taâoeb tiddi nnsen. Ma mmeslayen, tessemêasev i wawal nnsen. Amzun nitni d is$aôen i isenden, $ilen yal ti$ôi fellasen. Acengu, d nitni; êader iman ik segsen. A ten Ine$ Öebbi! Acêal wexxôen!'),
(5193, 63, 5, 'Ma nnan asen: "yyaw, ad issuter Umazan n Öebbi a ppeppusemmêem", ad bernen iqweôôa nnsen, a ten twaliv wexxôen s tem$weô.'),
(5194, 63, 6, 'Iâuva fellasen tessutrev, ne$ ur tessutrev ad ppusemmêen. Ur sen Ipsemmiê Öebbi, d awez$i. Öebbi, s tidep, ur Inehhu agdud iballa$en.'),
(5195, 63, 7, 'Nitni i iqqaôen: "ur pseddiqet, i wid iddan akked Umazan n Öebbi, alamma mmebruzzâen". N Öebbi igerrujen igenwan akked tmurt, maca ixabiten ur mêiûen.'),
(5196, 63, 8, 'Qqaôen: "ma nu$al ar Lmadina, war ccekk, uzmir ad issuffe$, segs, uôhif". Tazmert, n Öebbi akked Umazan iS, akked lmumnin, maca, ixabiten ur éôin.'),
(5197, 63, 9, 'A wid iumnen! £uôwat a kwen ssbaâden, af usmekti n Öebbi, wayla nnwen akked tarwa nnwen! Wid igan akka, ihi, widak d imexsuôen.'),
(5198, 63, 10, 'Ssedqet seg wayen i wen Nefka, uqbel a d tas tmeppant ar yiwen degwen, ad yini: "a Mass iw! Lemmer ad iyi Teswexxôev ar lajel aqôib, ad seddqe$, ad ili$ seg wid imaânen".'),
(5199, 63, 11, 'Ur Irennu Öebbi di laâmeô, d awez$i, ma iusa d lajel is. Öebbi Ippuxebbeô $ef wayen txeddmem.');
INSERT INTO `ber_mensur` (`index`, `sura`, `aya`, `text`) VALUES
(5200, 64, 1, 'I illan deg igenwan, i illan di tmurt, sbuccuâen Öebbi. IneS tagelda; ineS wannuz; Neppa Izmer i yal cci.'),
(5201, 64, 2, 'Neppa ikwen Ixelqen; segwen ajehli, segwen lmumen. Öebbi Ipwali ayen txeddmem.'),
(5202, 64, 3, 'Ixleq tamurt akked igenwan, s tidep. Imsel ikwen, Iûeggem amsal nnwen. £uôeS tu$alin.'),
(5203, 64, 4, 'Iéôa i illan di tmurt akked igenwan. Iéôa ayen teffrem akked wayen tennam. Öebbi Iéôa i illan deg idmaren.'),
(5204, 64, 5, 'Ma iusa kwen id usali n wid illan, zik, d ijehliyen? Jeôben lwexda n tikli nnsen. Fellasen, aâaqeb aqeôêan.'),
(5205, 64, 6, 'Ayagi, imi sen ppasen imazanen nnsen s ubeggen. Nnan: "aâni d amdan ara $ inhun"? D$a jehlen, xedâan. Ur Iclaâ Öebbi. Öebbi d Asâay, d Amaâzuz.'),
(5206, 64, 7, 'Pputebten ijehliyen ar, d awez$i, ur d pnekkaren. Ini: "xaîi! S Mass iw, ard a d tekkrem, sinna ard a ppepwaxebbôem $ef wayen txeddmem"! Ayagi, i Öebbi, d ushil.'),
(5207, 64, 8, 'Ihi, amnet s Öebbi akked Umazan iS, akked tafat id Nessers. Öebbi Ippuxebbeô $ef wayen txeddmem.'),
(5208, 64, 9, 'Ass ideg ara kwen Issemlil, i wass ujemmel, ass nni, d ass um$uôôu. Win iumnen s Öebbi, ixeddmen ayen ilhan, ad as Ikkes tucmitin is, a t Issekcem ar leonanat, ddawat sen isaffen ppazzalen, degsen ad iwekkeô i lebda. D wagi ay d rrbeê ameqwôaêan.'),
(5209, 64, 10, 'Wid ijehlen u inekôen issekniyen nne£, widak d at tmes, degs ad wekkôen. A taggara icemten!'),
(5210, 64, 11, 'Ur d teppas twa$it, siwa ma Irad Öebbi. Win iumnen s Öebbi, ad Inhu ul is. Öebbi Iéôa yal cci.'),
(5211, 64, 12, 'A$et awal i Öebbi, a$et awal i Umazan! Ma twexxôem, i iwatan kan, i Umazan nne£, siwa anabi ipbegginen.'),
(5212, 64, 13, 'Öebbi, ur illi ôebbi siwa Neppa. £ef Öebbi ara ppeklen lmumnin.'),
(5213, 64, 14, 'A wid iumnen! S tidep, kra n tlawin nnwen akked tarwa nnwen, d icenga nnwen. Ëadret iman nnwen segsen! Ma tsemmêem, teppum, tsemmêem, Öebbi, s tidep, Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu.'),
(5214, 64, 15, 'Ayla nnwen akked dderya nnwen, d ahewwel kan, wanag, ar Öebbi, illa warraz ameqwôahan.'),
(5215, 64, 16, 'Ëezzbet i Öebbi ayen iwumi tzemrem. Ëesset, ôavit, seddqet! Yif it i iman nnwen. Wid ikksen ccêa i iman nnsen, widak d imerbaê.'),
(5216, 64, 17, 'Ma tôevlem i Öebbi aôeîîal igerzen, ad awen d Irr sin imuren, ad awen Isemmeê. Öebbi Iceffu, Iêellem.'),
(5217, 64, 18, 'Amusnaw n wayen iffren akked wayen ivehôen, Uzmir, Bab n ûûwab.');
INSERT INTO `ber_mensur` (`index`, `sura`, `aya`, `text`) VALUES
(5218, 65, 1, 'A Nnbi! Mara tebrum i tlawin, brut asent mara tâaddi tallit n tarda nnsent. Ëesbet tallit. Ëezzbet i Öebbi, Mass nnwen. Ur tent ssuffu$et si texxamin nnsent, ur d teff$ent, siwa ma, s tidep, ccvent. D tigi ay d tilisa n Öebbi. Win izegren tilisa n Öebbi, ni$ idens imanis. Ur teéôiv ara, ahat Öebbi a d Iazen lameô, ssyen $eô da.'),
(5219, 65, 2, 'Mi ssawvent lajel nnsent, âacôet pent s lewqama, ne$ mfaôaqet yidsent, s lewqama. Awit ed sin inagan iêeqqiyen segwen, a d cehhden zdat Öebbi. Ataya wayen u$uô ppunedôen, wid iumnen s Öebbi akked wass aneggaru. Win ipêezziben i Öebbi, ad as Ildi tibbura,'),
(5220, 65, 3, 'a t I$it s wanda ur iêtim. Win iîîfen di Öebbi, a t Iqennaâ. Ih, Öebbi Issâadday lameô iS. Ni$ Öebbi Iwzen yal cci.'),
(5221, 65, 4, 'I tigad, n tlawin nnwen, i iuysen tarda, ma illa ccekk, tallit ugani nnsent: krav wagguren. Akken i tid ur nebdi tarda. Tid ibbwin tadist, tallit nnsent ar tinnufra nnsent. Win ipêezziben i Öebbi, s lameô iS, ad as Istiser.'),
(5222, 65, 5, 'D wagi ay d lameô n Öebbi i wen d Issers. Win ipêezziben i Öebbi, ad as Ikkes tucmitin is, ad Issali arraz is.'),
(5223, 65, 6, 'Ad asent tefkem tanezdu$t anda tzed$em, akken tewâam. Ur tent îîuôôut s tririt nnsent ar lêeôs. Ma llant s tadist, ûeôôfet fellasent, alamma d tinnufra nnsent. Ma ssuîvent tarwa nnwen, efket asent taqdiât nnsent; mwafaqet s tiéeî. Ma temnamarem, a ppessuîîev tmeîîut nniven.'),
(5224, 65, 7, 'Bu udrim ad iûeôôef segs. Win ixuû ôôeéq ad iûeôôef seg wayen i s Ifka Öebbi. Ur Ipkellif Öebbi taôwiêt, siwa ar ayen i s Ifka. Öebbi ad Issuffe$ laâtab ar tafat.'),
(5225, 65, 8, 'Acêal n temdinin i inuqmen lameô n Mass nnsent akked imazanen iS! Nêuseb itent leêsab uqsiê. Nâaqeb itent s uâaqeb issexven.'),
(5226, 65, 9, 'Jeôôbent lwexda igiten nnsent. D lexsaôa ay d iooa lameô nnsent.'),
(5227, 65, 10, 'Öebbi Ihegga yasen aâaqeb uqsiê. Ëezzbet i Öebbi a yuâqilen iumnen! Ni$ Öebbi Issers awen d asmekti;'),
(5228, 65, 11, 'Amazan i wen immalen issekniyen n Öebbi iberrzen, iwakken ad Issuffe$, si tillas ar tafat, wid iumnen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan. Wid iumnen s Öebbi, ixeddmen ayen ilhan, a ten Issekcem ar leonanat, ddawat sen isaffen ppazzalen, degsen ad wekkôen i lebda. Ni$ Öebbi Igerrez asen ôôeéq.'),
(5229, 65, 12, 'Öebbi i Ixelqen ûa igenwan, akked tmurt am nitni. Lameô iprusu garasen, iwakken a ppeéôem ar Öebbi Izmer i yal cci, u Öebbi Izzi i yal cci s tmusni.');
INSERT INTO `ber_mensur` (`index`, `sura`, `aya`, `text`) VALUES
(5230, 66, 1, 'A Nnbi! Ay$eô tgedlev ayen i k Iêell Öebbi? Tqennâav tilawin ik. Öebbi Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu.'),
(5231, 66, 2, 'Öebbi Iêeppem fellawen a pêentem. Öebbi d Bab nnwen. Neppa d Amusnaw, d Bab n ûûwab.'),
(5232, 66, 3, 'Mi inna Nnbi sser, i yiwet si tlawin is, u temla, Öebbi Issken it i neppa. Ixebbeô s wumur, iffer amur, segs. Mi p iaâlem s waya, tenna: "wi k imlan aya"? Inna: "Imla yi t Win Issnen, Ippuxebbôen".'),
(5233, 66, 4, 'Ma tutubemt Öebbi, ihi knan wulawen n kwent. Ma tedduklemt as, ihi, d Öebbi ay d Bab is, u, deffir waya, ad ilin di talalt is: Jebrayen, ûûam n lmumnin, u lmalayek ad fkent afud.'),
(5234, 66, 5, 'Ma ibra yakwent, Izmer Öebbi ad as d Inûef s tlawin i kwent yifen, timvuâin, tid iumnen, ipéallan, iutuben, iâabden, ippuéumen, tid ijeôben tissulya, ne$ tiâazriyin.'),
(5235, 66, 6, 'A wid iumnen! Ëadret iman nnwen akked twacult nnwen, si tmes, is$aôen is d imdanen akked id$a$en! Fellas lmalayek tuohidin, tuqsiêin, ur nepwexxiô i wayen i sent Iumeô Öebbi, i ixedmen i sent ipwamôen.'),
(5236, 66, 7, 'A wid ijehlen, ulay$eô teste$fôem assa! A ppeppuqeîîim kan $ef wayen txeddmem.'),
(5237, 66, 8, 'A wid iumnen! Utubet Öebbi, ppuba n ûûeê! Ahat Mass nnwen ad awen Ikkes tucmitin nnwen, u a kwen Issekcem ar Loennet, ddaw as isaffen ppazzalen. Assen, Öebbi ur Isdullu Nnbi akked wid iumnen yides. Tafat nnsen teppeddu zdat sen, u yeffus nnsen. Ad qqaôen: "a Mass nne$! Tim ane$ tafat nne$, Semmeê ane$; ih, Keçç, Tzemrev i yal cci".'),
(5238, 66, 9, 'A Nnbi! Nna$ ijehliyen akked ixabiten! Iqsiê $uôsen! Axxam nnsen d Loahennama, d tu$alin tucmip.'),
(5239, 66, 10, 'Ifka d Öebbi amedya i wid ijehlen: tameîîut n Nuê akked tmeîîut n Luî. Llant ger ifassen n sin imdanen, seg wid imaânen n imdanen nne$. £uüôôent pen. Ur zmiren a tent sselken s wacemma, seg ufus n Öebbi. Ancad: "kecmemt ar tmes akked wid ikecmen"!'),
(5240, 66, 11, 'Ifka d Öebbi amedya i wid iumnen, tameîîut n Ferâun, mi tenna: "a Mass iw! Ebnu yi, $uôeK, taxxamt di Loennet, Sellek iyi si Ferâun akked igiten is, Sellek iyi si lqum imednas"!'),
(5241, 66, 12, 'U Meryem ult Âimôan i izazdgen tuzzuft is. Nenfes $uôes si ôôuê nne£, tepputebbet $ef wawalen akked tezmamin n Mass is. Neppat seg wid ipéallan.');
INSERT INTO `ber_mensur` (`index`, `sura`, `aya`, `text`) VALUES
(5242, 67, 1, 'Iôqa Bu tgelda deg ufus iS, u Neppa, Izmer i yal cci;'),
(5243, 67, 2, 'i Ixelqen tameppant, tameddurt, iwakken a kwen Ijeôôeb: anwa degwen ara ixedmen igiten ilhan sennig wiyav. Neppa d Uzmir, Ipsemmiê;'),
(5244, 67, 3, 'i Ixelqen ûa igenwan d idurra. Deg wayen Ixleq Uênin, ur tepwaliv ayen ixuûûen. Ernu sikked ma a pwaliv i$isiyen!'),
(5245, 67, 4, 'Sinna, ger tiî ik berdayen. Iéôi a d iu$al $uôek, iêfa, u inzef.'),
(5246, 67, 5, 'Ni$ Ncebbeê igenni aqôib s teftilin, Nôeooem yisent cwaîen, Nhegga yasen aâaqeb n tmes.'),
(5247, 67, 6, 'I wid inekôen Mass nnsen, aâaqeb n Loahennama. A tu$alin tucmip!'),
(5248, 67, 7, 'Mi pwaveggôen $uôes, ad slen la tesraâriâ, u neppat trekkem.'),
(5249, 67, 8, 'Qôib a ppeftutes seg iûiv. Yal tikelt ara iwaveggeô $uôes urbaâ, a ten steqsin iâssasen is: "aâni ur kwen id iusi ara uneddaô"?'),
(5250, 67, 9, 'Ad inin: "ih, iusa ya$ d uneddaô, nenkeô u nenna: ur illi ay d Issuder Öebbi, aql akwen kan di le$wlav meqqwôen"!'),
(5251, 67, 10, 'U nnan: "lemmer nelli nsell ne$ nfehhem, ur nelli seg wat tmes".'),
(5252, 67, 11, 'Qaôôen s ibekkaven nnsen. Asêaq i at tmes!'),
(5253, 67, 12, 'Wanag, i wid ippagwaden Mass nnsen, di tbavnit, ssmaê akked warraz meqqwôen.'),
(5254, 67, 13, 'Hedôet s sser ne$ âinani, ihi, Neppa Iéôa ayen illan deg idmaren.'),
(5255, 67, 14, 'Day ur Iéôi ara Win Ixelqen, Laîif Ippuxebbôen?'),
(5256, 67, 15, 'Neppa i wen Irran tamurt d tamvuât. Elêut deg ibraêen is, ççet si ôôeéq is. £uôeS tanekra.'),
(5257, 67, 16, 'Ma tepputebtem ar, Win Illan deg igenni, ad Irr tamurt a ppertem yiswen? Appan la teppembwiwil.'),
(5258, 67, 17, 'Ma tepputebtem, ar Win Illan deg igenni, awen d Iazen tabucivant n yid$a$en? D$a, a ppissinem anwa t unabi W.'),
(5259, 67, 18, 'Ni$ nekôen imezwura nnsen. Amek d Zzi$ fellasen!'),
(5260, 67, 19, 'Ahat ur walan ara ifôax, sennig sen, d idurra, afriwen ceôqen, ur côiqen. Siwa Aênin iten Iîfen. Neppa, ih, Issikkid yal cci.'),
(5261, 67, 20, 'Anwa wa ay d aâsekôiw nnwen, ara kwen isellken, war Aênin? Ijehliyen atnan kan di le$ôuô.'),
(5262, 67, 21, 'Anwa wa ara kwen iôeéqen ma Ijmaâ l$it iS? Maca, vellelen deg u$unfu akked leqbaêa.'),
(5263, 67, 22, 'Win iteddun, ibra i uqeôôu, day ipwanha sennig win iteddun, irfed aqeôôu, deg ubrid uwqim?'),
(5264, 67, 23, 'Ini: "d Neppa ikwen id Ixelqen. Irra yawen timejjin, allen, ulawen. Drus ay tesnemmirem"!'),
(5265, 67, 24, 'Ini: "d Neppa ikwen isseftin di tmurt, ar $uôeS ara tepwafesrem".'),
(5266, 67, 25, 'La qqaôen: "melmi lemâahda agi, ma d tidep ay tessawalem"?'),
(5267, 67, 26, 'Ini: "i Iéôan siwa Öebbi. Nek d aneddaô kan ipbegginen.'),
(5268, 67, 27, 'Mara a t walin iqeôb ed, ad ndellen wudmawen n wid ijehlen. A d inin: "atan wayen tessuturem".'),
(5269, 67, 28, 'Ini: "ma twalam ma In$a ya$ Öebbi, nek d imeddukwal iw, ne$ ma Iêun fella$? Ihi, anwa ara isellken ijehliyen seg uâaqeb aqeôêan"?'),
(5270, 67, 29, 'Ini: "Neppa d Aênin, syiS numen, fellaS neppkel. A ppeéôem anwa i illan di ttelfan n ûûeê".'),
(5271, 67, 30, 'Ini: "ma twalam, lemmer ad zzren waman nnwen, w ar awen d iawin aman ippazalen"?');
INSERT INTO `ber_mensur` (`index`, `sura`, `aya`, `text`) VALUES
(5272, 68, 1, 'N. S wamru akked wayen pjerriden!'),
