(5278, 68, 7, 'D Mass ik, ih, i Izôan sennig wiyav, anwa iff$en abrid iS. D Neppa i Izôan, sennig wiyav, anwi ipwanhan.'),
(5279, 68, 8, 'Ihi, ur ppak awal i inekkaôen.'),
