(5299, 68, 28, 'Inna uêdiq mavi nnsen: "day ur awen nni$ ara: a lemmer tesbuccuâem"?'),
(5300, 68, 29, 'Nnan: "nesbuccaâ Mass nne$. Nella, s tidep, d imednas".'),
