(5304, 68, 33, 'Am akka, aqeîîi. Aqeîîi n laxeôt, war ccekk, meqqweô kteô, lemmer éôin!'),
(5305, 68, 34, 'Ih, i wid ipêezziben i Mass nnsen, Loennet n ssuâada.'),
(5306, 68, 35, 'Aâni Nerr imvuâen am ibe$wviyen?'),
(5307, 68, 36, 'Acu ikwen iu$en? Amek tepêuddum?'),
(5308, 68, 37, 'Ne$ tesâam tazmamt ideg tlemdem,'),
