(5320, 68, 49, 'Lemmer ur t id issukkes l$it n Mass is, a d iu$al ar lxali, d amaâfun.'),
(5321, 68, 50, 'Ifren it Mass is, Irra t seg iâaôviyen.'),
(5322, 68, 51, 'Qôib i k smalen ijehliyen, s wallen nnsen, mi slan i usmekti. La qqaôen: "ar neppa d aôehbani".'),
