(5330, 69, 7, 'Iêeppem it, fellasen, ûa wavan, îam wussan, d imezgi. A pwaliv din imdanen seôâan, am ize$wôan n tezdayt iruzen.'),
(5331, 69, 8, 'Twalav ma illa wacu d igwran segsen?'),
(5332, 69, 9, 'Iusa d Ferâun akked wid i t id izwaren, akked tid ippin, s lfalîat.'),
