(5342, 69, 19, 'Wanag win iwumi fkan tazmamt is, yeffus is, a d yini: "atan, e$ôet adlis iw;'),
(5343, 69, 20, 'êsi$, nek, ad afe$ iyi twaêesben".'),
(5344, 69, 21, 'D$a ad yili di tudert igerzen,'),
(5345, 69, 22, 'di leonan aâlayen.'),
