(5348, 69, 25, 'Wanag win iwumi fkan tazmamt is, zelmev is, a d yini: "a ssexv iw, awufan adlis iw ur d iusi!'),
(5349, 69, 26, 'Iqeîîiyen iw, ur éôi$ anwi.'),
(5350, 69, 27, 'Awufan tameppant dayenni.'),
