(5422, 71, 3, 'Âabdet Öebbi, têezzbem aS, tessemêessem iyi.'),
(5423, 71, 4, 'Ad Isemmeê seg ibekkaven nnwen, ad awen Ifk lmudda ar lajel ipwassnen. S tidep, lajel n Öebbi, ma iusa d, ur ipwexxiô, lemmer peéôim"!'),
(5424, 71, 5, 'Inna: "a Mass iw! Nek, ssawale$ i ugdud iw, am yiv am ass.'),
(5425, 71, 6, 'Siwa tugin i sen terna ti$ôi w.'),
(5426, 71, 7, 'Nek, yal tikelt ara ten neccde$ iwakken a sen Tsemmêev, ad rren ivudan nnsen deg imeééu$en nnsen, ad pplen deg iceîîiven nnsen. Ggernennen, zuxxen s tem$weô.'),
(5427, 71, 8, 'Sinna, ssawle$ asen s uâaggev.'),
(5428, 71, 9, 'Sinna, âinani nni$ asen; s tuffra, sser, mli$ assen.'),
(5429, 71, 10, 'Nni$: "ssutret ssmaê i Mass nnwen; Neppa ard Win Ipsemmiêen.'),
(5430, 71, 11, 'Ippazen awen d ageffur, seg igenni, d ihedman.'),
(5431, 71, 12, 'Ayla akked tarwa, Issuget awen; Ifka yawen timizar; Irra yawen isaffen.'),
(5432, 71, 13, 'Acu kwen iu$en, Öebbi, ur aS tgim ccan?'),
(5433, 71, 14, 'Ni$ i waya, Ixelq ikwen.'),
(5434, 71, 15, 'Ur twalam ara amek Ixleq Öebbi ûa igenwan d idurra?'),
(5435, 71, 16, 'Irra degsen, aggur d tafat. Irra iîij d asavef.'),
(5436, 71, 17, 'Öebbi Issem$i kwen seg wakal, am im$an.'),
(5437, 71, 18, 'Sinna, a kwen Irr $uôes; sinna, d tuff$a ara kwen id Issuffe$.'),
(5438, 71, 19, 'Öebbi Irra yawen tamurt d tuwsiât,'),
(5439, 71, 20, 'iwakken, degs, a ppafem iberdan d tiza".'),
(5440, 71, 21, 'Inna Nuê: "a Mass iw! Atnan âuûan iyi. Ddan akked win iwumi, ayla s akked tarwa s, ay s rnan, siwa lexsaôa".'),
(5441, 71, 22, 'Sxedmen tiêila meqqwôen.'),
(5442, 71, 23, 'Nnan: "ur ppaooat iôebbiten nnwen! Ur ppaooat Wadd, Suwaâ, Ya$ut, Yaâuq, akked Naûô"!'),
