(5453, 72, 6, 'Ih, seg imdanen, llan irgazen ijjemen ddkeô n leonun. Snernan lbe$wv nnsen.'),
(5454, 72, 7, 'S tidep, $ilen, akken t$ilem, ar Öebbi ur d Isskar yiwen, d awez$i.'),
(5455, 72, 8, 'Aql a$ nqelleb igenni, nufa t iççuô d iâssasen uqsiêen, akked ijujaê.'),
(5456, 72, 9, 'Nella nep$imi $uôes, seg imukan nessemêas; win issemêessen tura, a t id immager usafu d aâessas.'),
(5457, 72, 10, 'Nekwni, ur neéôi ma iura lhemm, af at ddunit, ne$ ma Ib$a, Mass nnsen, ad pwanhun.'),
(5458, 72, 11, 'Llan garane$ iâaôviyen, llan wid ur nemâin; ur naâdil iberdan.'),
(5459, 72, 12, 'Nmeyyez nufa, war ccekk, ur nesfunnug Öebbi di tmurt, ur T nesfunnug ma nerwel.'),
(5460, 72, 13, 'Nnhaya mi s nesla, yis numen. Win iumnen s Mass is, ur ippagwad ara t ixaûen, ne$ ara t ivuôôen.'),
(5461, 72, 14, 'Ih, garane$ imvuâen, garane$ lâaûûap. Wid iunzen, widak, xtaôen lewqam.'),
(5462, 72, 15, 'Ma d lâaûûap, di Loahennama, d nitni ay d is$aôen".'),
(5463, 72, 16, 'Lemmer deg ubrid ay ddan, yili Nefka yasen aman iqwan.'),
(5464, 72, 17, 'A ten njeôôeb yissen. Win iooan asmekti n Mass is, ad isâaddi aâaqeb aqesêan.'),
(5465, 72, 18, 'Leowamaâ n Öebbi. Ur naâôet yiwen ar tama n Öebbi.'),
(5466, 72, 19, 'Atan, mi ikker umdan n Öebbi ad inuj $ureS, qôib lesqen $uôes.'),
(5467, 72, 20, 'Ini: "pnuju$ kan ar Mass iw, ur aS pcarake$ yiwen".'),
(5468, 72, 21, 'Ini: "nek, ur pwakelfe$ $ef vveôô nnwen ne$ $ef nnhaya nnwen".'),
(5469, 72, 22, 'Ini: "nek, ur iyi ipfukku yiwen seg ufus n Öebbi, d awez$i. War Neppa, ur ppafe$ ssôan,'),
(5470, 72, 23, 'siwa anabi s$uô Öebbi, akked tebrap iS". Ih, i wid iâuûan Öebbi akked Umazan iS, times n Loahennama, ad wekkôen degs, i lebda.'),
(5471, 72, 24, 'Alamma mi walan ayen i sen ippuwaââden, ad éôen anwi ay d uôhifen mavi, i leslak, anwi drus iten mavi.'),
(5472, 72, 25, 'Ini: "ur éôi$ ma iqeôb ed wayen i wen ippuweââden, ne$ ma a t Iweooel Mass iw;'),
