(5489, 73, 14, 'Ass ideg tamurt akked idurar ad rgagin, idurar ad u$alen am ôômel ippazalen.'),
(5490, 73, 15, 'Atan Nuzen awen ed Amazan, d anagi nnwen, akken Nuzen amazan i Ferâun.'),
